context:
{
  "id": "line:03a5e04",
  "node": "Examine_Alley2",
  "text": "Player: Back"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc37e9",
  "node": "Talk_Alley2",
  "text": "Player: What did you see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c751f5",
  "node": "Talk_Alley2",
  "text": "Player: BACK"
}

{
  "id": "line:071f341",
  "node": "Present_Alley2",
  "text": "Player: Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:051f0b1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "We made our way back to the alleyway that Tymora brought us to a month ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b918d4",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "The alley was quiet,[p/] but I wasn't sure if I could trust that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9eda2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "We got looks from people living in the nearby buildings.[p/] They shut their windows the moment they saw us.[p/] I hoped I hadn't raised any alarms."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f5f93",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "It would be too conspicuous to bring the Kingsguard with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab429f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Celeste actually planned the entire operation.[p/] They would walk through the streets and quickly storm the building the moment trouble arose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd1fa8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "They gave Celeste an enchanted Runestone to hold and channel her magic into."
}

{
  "id": "line:0230050",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "If she ever stopped focusing her magic,[p/] that would send a signal to the Kingsguard to storm the building."
}

{
  "id": "line:0482053",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you ready?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec9f7f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes...[p/] Let's do this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0054f41",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "The Eyetaker was our prime suspect.[p/] Everyone else had an alibi and lacked a motive."
}

{
  "id": "line:058af66",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Not to mention,[p/] Eris was with Beatrice when she went missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:060b13e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "I didn't want to suspect her,[p/] but her father [i]was[/i] a criminal,[p/] and she still hadn't turned up since the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:01df852",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright.[p/] On three."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd0eff",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Tyrion: One."
}

{
  "id": "line:0171faa",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Celeste: Two."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a5a5a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Alley2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Three!"
}

{
  "id": "line:039770a",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Debris"
}

{
  "id": "line:03eb4dd",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's some sort of debris on the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:032b699",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "I picked up one of the pieces and rolled it around in my palm.[p/] It appeared to be some kind of gravel."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7d59",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Debris"
}

{
  "id": "line:0501910",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Celeste: There are traces of [b]transmutation[/b] on this debris."
}

{
  "id": "line:04802e9",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That would imply that a spell specifically targeted or created whatever this came from..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cbd79",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I doubt someone intentionally created these bits of gravel."
}

{
  "id": "line:0651b0a",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It must have broken off from something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8dff3",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Balcony"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4484a",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This balcony provides a perfect view of Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:092f0d2",
  "node": "Examine_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: A lot of people probably come here when the Grand Cathedral is open to the public."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7bd02",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We heard that you saw the prosecutor acting strangely here."
}

{
  "id": "line:09586a3",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you tell us more about what you saw?[p/] Did it look like she was afflicted with Mageblight?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8411d",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I wouldn't go [i]that[/i] far.[p/] But she was certainly acting strangely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeedaa",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you come across her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a02ed",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Well, I was on my way to the Prayer Room.[p/] I always recite prayers from the draconic texts around that time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a79897",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "...[i]He[/i] was heading to the Prayer Room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0776f0f",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: When I saw her,[p/] I first thought she was just enjoying the view of the lake."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c1154",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I was about to greet her,[p/] but when I approached her,[p/] I saw that she was [i]pushing[/i] something off the edge of the balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a07933",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You must have seen her dumping Sibyl's body..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af802e",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: You're [i]probably[/i] correct..."
}

{
  "id": "line:041098e",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I came to the same conclusion after they found that poor woman's body below us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f97475",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: But it feels wrong somehow..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebd4df",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0706e14",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...I only saw it for a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:076e23f",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Lady Sibyl was wearing much brighter colors this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0259d5e",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Whatever Lady Steelwind threw into the lake,[p/] it looked much darker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0593048",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What does [i]that[/i] mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:014305d",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I'm sorry.[p/] I can't really explain it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0696e71",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Perhaps I was just seeing things.[p/] My eyes aren't as good as they used to be, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0967bf2",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: It could have just been a trick of the light."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1e1e",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: The Prayer Room"
}

{
  "id": "line:000e6f9",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] If you saw Aria dumping Lady Sibyl's body,[p/] she must have [i]just[/i] murdered her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d830b",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That means you must have been heading to where [i]we[/i] were at that time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0949b5c",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Oh?[p/] Were you praying there with Lord Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07675e7",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Not exactly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8322e",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: What?[p/] That's not what the guards told me."
}

{
  "id": "line:009edc8",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The guards?[p/] Do you mean the ones standing watch outside the Prayer Room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c5b5b",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Yes.[p/] They told me that Pierce was praying with some acquaintances of his."
}

{
  "id": "line:044d298",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: They said the same thing to Lady Steelwind as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0467fa0",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/][s/] [i]Steelwind[/i] was there too?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6fa55",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Yes...[p/] She appeared to be waiting for something."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2ed6",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I didn't want to disturb them,[p/] so I went back to my quarters to pray there."
}

{
  "id": "line:000c82c",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "The High Speaker didn't see her fighting Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6aca4",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "She must have started her attack [i]after[/i] he left,[p/] but why would she bother waiting?"
}

{
  "id": "line:034e27c",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Either way,[p/] we can't exactly question those guards."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fc89d",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] They're still comatose after the attack."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b06e48",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Why didn't you hear anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1c393",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Actually,[p/] the High Speaker's Quarters aren't that far away from the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3f565",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Didn't you hear the fight between Steelwind and my bodyguard?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0157668",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Ah...[p/] It must have been because of the magical wards in my room."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fb09b",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Magical wards?[p/] Are they there for security reasons?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de4906",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Not exactly."
}

{
  "id": "line:098fdd6",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I actually suffer from chronic insomnia.[p/] Even the smallest sound will wake me up at night."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f34ae",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Years ago,[p/] I had some mages enchant the walls so sound couldn't travel through them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1ad0a",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I can't hear anything from outside the room once I shut my door."
}

{
  "id": "line:00208e4",
  "node": "Talk_Balcony1",
  "text": "...That did sound [i]awfully[/i] convenient,[p/] but I doubted that he'd lie about something so easily verified."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d794d4",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Runestone"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5db39",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: A Runestone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f7dab",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's my Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fafaa",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Ah,[p/] I recall the Duke of Commerce telling me about this device."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a017ec",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Artificery is yet another gift granted to us by the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0298260",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But they only draw power from ley lines.[p/] It has nothing to do with Rathallion."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bbc31",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...All arcane magic is derived from the ancient dragons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d35591",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: To say otherwise is sacrilege."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6d608",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f80398",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you [i]have[/i] heard of me, High Speaker."
}

{
  "id": "line:013a5c0",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...I have. [h=\"He's not|what I was expecting...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03877c3",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You shouldn't believe every story you hear from the aristocracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:061d0be",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...I-[p/][s/]I don't know what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:09daace",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Aria|Archeus's Encounter"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b13b3",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I can't believe Lady Steelwind would do something like this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0273ebb",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...But I can't really doubt what I saw with my own eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:059f993",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Why was she acting so strangely?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b885d9",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There's more to this than we're all seeing."
}

{
  "id": "line:006dab8",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I'm going to get to the bottom of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8ac48",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: For her sake,[p/] I hope you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:005283b",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Garrick|Autopsy Report: Garrick Pierce"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b8b97",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you know Lord Pierce?[p/] He was one of the victims."
}

{
  "id": "line:00719a1",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I didn't know him well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0752f15",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Not to insult House Pierce,[p/] but he wasn't a noble of high standing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76cb5",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I never had many opportunities to speak with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0503af8",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Coraline|Autopsy Report: Coraline Sibyl"
}

{
  "id": "line:053f808",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you know Coraline Sibyl?[p/] She was the head of one of the Four Pillar Families."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6cb57",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I did...[p/] It's quite unfortunate what happened to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afd517",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Of the four families,[p/] I felt that House Sibyl was the one most loyal to the Church."
}

{
  "id": "line:067e922",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "...For better or for worse."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e4e5d",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Lloyd|Autopsy Report: Lloyd von Sanctus"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2ee52",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you know Lloyd von Sanctus? He was the head of House von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0746d03",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Yes. I knew him well."
}

{
  "id": "line:093edfe",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: We often worked together in matters of enterprise."
}

{
  "id": "line:03258f3",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why would the [i]Church[/i] need to discuss matters of enterprise?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0968021",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...Perhaps I've already said too much."
}

{
  "id": "line:00554ed",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Marriage Meeting"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6cff5",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I [i]do[/i] hope the allegations against Ms. Steelwind are false."
}

{
  "id": "line:056e268",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: She and His Majesty looked so happy this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:010ac75",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Right.[p/] The King of Wyverngarde can't exactly marry a serial murderer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0750bfb",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "She was the most resilient person I knew,[p/] but the possibility of losing her engagement with Aster probably weighed heavily in her mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0135712",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Debris Near the Balcony"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e0c74",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know where this debris came from?"
}

{
  "id": "line:077c505",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I have no idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cc888",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: The groundskeepers are very diligent in keeping the Grand Cathedral clean. [i]Especially[/i], today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0794bcf",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means this debris must have fallen here recently..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06224a6",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Soundproof Room"
}

{
  "id": "line:077cb99",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You must have been really desperate if you needed to soundproof your room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0949ce7",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: How light of a sleeper are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b70a4b",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: So much so that the sounds of morning cicadas can wake me up at times."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f0443",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Player: Theon"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6aed5",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Forgive me if I'm being rude,[p/] but what [i]is[/i] a High Speaker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead251",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: You seriously don't know?[p/] How ignorant are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0095c9b",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay, [i]that's[/i] a little rude."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1bf5",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: The Church of Bahamut seeks to honor and revere the Scaled Lord Rathallion."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c093d",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: We are all called to spread the word of his greatness throughout Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cec198",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: The High Speaker leads the Church through this mission."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fdcf4",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, High Speaker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d58a58",
  "node": "Present_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: My apologies.[p/] But there's not much to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:094f0da",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "We arrived at the west balcony of the cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:023807a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Supposedly, [i]this[/i] was where the murderer threw Sibyl's body into the lake."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eece5",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Oh...[p/] Hello, there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9b53a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "As I inspected the area,[p/] I caught the attention of an old man nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:070b76e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "From his garb,[p/] he appeared to be someone who worked at the cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c40ac0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: I...[p/] don't believe we've met before.[p/] What are you doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cde2c0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sorry for the intrusion.[p/] I'm Tyrion Cuthbert,[p/] and this is my bodyguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b51da",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...We're investigating the murders on behalf of Prosecutor Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0749391",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Tyrion Cuthbert...[p/] I [i]have[/i] heard of you. [h=\"He doesn't look [i]nearly[/i] as criminal|as I expected him to be...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:021e9ce",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "He probably hadn't heard anything good..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3299d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...But forgive my rudeness,[p/] I am Theon Archeus:[p/] High Speaker of the Church of Bahamut."
}

{
  "id": "line:061a371",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]you're[/i] the one who saw Steelwind here during the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f62e42",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you mind if we ask you some questions?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083a04d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1d128",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "Theon: ...I suppose there would be no harm in that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd7f22",
  "node": "Check_Events_Balcony1",
  "text": "I found everything I could here.[p/] It was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:09441e6",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Window"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c79bf",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a stained glass window.[p/] A small ray of sunlight is shining through it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0200956",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Seats"
}

{
  "id": "line:095207c",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are rows upon rows of seats for worshippers to sit at."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bdaa5",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: At full capacity,[p/] this room could probably host thousands of people at a time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0750b63",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Middle"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4a40f",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's an altar at the end of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:085bc4e",
  "node": "Examine_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: A religious figure would probably give a sermon here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de8a1a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: What did Virgilae see?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f6cfc",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Grace,[p/] where were you when the murders took place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1e808",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Just what are you trying to insinuate?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca2210",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Please, Alaric.[p/] There's no need for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:061c6a3",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: To answer your question,[p/] I was speaking with Lady Frega's familiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f95de9",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Tracker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:032c26b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: No...[p/] It was the demon who calls himself \"Marrunath\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ab5ad",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...[i]What[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0260806",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: He was actually the one who sent for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b215b2",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: According to him,[p/] he had some information that was of great import to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b89b6e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Did you make a contract with him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058fa59",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Of course not.[p/] He gave me the information he had freely..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09910b7",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d50224",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Demons are supposedly always trying to trick humans into making deals with them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acd508",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Looking back,[p/] it must have been a distraction..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6e377",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: What a fool I was...[p/] I knew he was playing with me,[p/] but I knew he was unable to lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0049c9d",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: And the information he had was too important to ignore."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a9dfe",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If you don't mind me asking,[p/] what was the information about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb0c25",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3852c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: I'm sorry,[p/] but I won't reveal what he told me."
}

{
  "id": "line:001fa90",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: ...It would be a danger to everyone here."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e5f93",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: But rest assured,[p/] it had nothing to do with the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:00144d1",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Grace.[p/] We've only [i]just[/i] met."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac5573",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't exactly just take your word for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:078dfd6",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: I suppose that's fair,[p/] but believe me when I say that I plan to take this information to my grave."
}

{
  "id": "line:059d46b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "...That was ominous,[p/] but he was clearly intent on keeping their conversation a secret."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfb2af",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Anyways,[p/] several members of the Kingsguard were watching us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0422519",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: They can verify my alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:063aa4f",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: How long did this conversation last?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d0a39",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: I arrived to speak with him at 1:50 PM,[p/] and I didn't leave until 3:10 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c29424",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "So he was accounted for during the time frame of the murders..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c377f1",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "But why would Marrunath go to the trouble of distracting him in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e55418",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Whoever orchestrated this also used a [b]Force Cage[/b] to trap Aster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7873b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Were they trying to distract the forces in the Cathedral?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7c59c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Or were they trying to keep certain people out of the crossfire?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088518c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Steelwind's spell"
}

{
  "id": "line:0491e4e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Highness.[p/] We heard the prosecutor cast a spell on you when you saw the fire in the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46aef",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell us more about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a53ed0",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I can't believe she [i]attacked[/i] a member of the royal family!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041c434",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: She was completely irresponsible with her magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad58b5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand your feelings about this,[p/] but we can't say for certain that she inflicted Mageblight on herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c520ea",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We don't even know if it was [i]actually[/i] her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0091788",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I [i]saw[/i] her with my own eyes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbfa17",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Plenty of other people did too!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07375ab",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Either way,[p/] where did this happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c46b5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: It was on the path outside the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb312e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I saw smoke coming from the building,[p/] and I saw Steelwind walking away from it."
}

{
  "id": "line:037779a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "So this must have been [i]after[/i] she murdered von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:073344d",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have a feeling I already know the answer...[p/] But was she behaving erratically?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae3d05",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: No![p/][s/] She very [i]deliberately[/i] cast a spell on me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0873e08",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Which once [i]again[/i] implies that Mageblight wasn't behind this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a6d65",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know which spell she cast on you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03997e9",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I'm not sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e23722",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I've never been affected by a spell like that before."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b503c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: From the magical traces on him,[p/] we know that it was a [b]transmutation[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0502a86",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: [b]Transmutation[/b] spells manipulate and change physical matter..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e282a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: It's scary to think about what that might do to a human body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0459294",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you sure he's okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0514239",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Lord Asclepius inspected him,[p/] and he didn't appear to have any lasting injuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f238",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: We're hoping the spell's effects were only temporary."
}

{
  "id": "line:029ab39",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you describe what you felt while you were affected by it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09d51",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That might help us identify which spell it was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c70b5d",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Well...[p/] I was extremely dazed,[p/] and my ears were ringing."
}

{
  "id": "line:088fdcc",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: My vision was also partially blurred.[p/] It was as if my mind was in some sort of fog."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef818e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Whenever I tried to speak,[p/] I couldn't even form words with my mouth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5237d",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I could only make grunting sounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:073a641",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I couldn't walk either.[p/] So I had to crawl on the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1897c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry you had to go through that.[p/] That must have been traumatic."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d3c88",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:024837b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "But what kind of [b]transmutation[/b] spell would do that to him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dc528",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "It had to be something that affected his senses."
}

{
  "id": "line:02031ad",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Steelwind's Demeanor"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b55f2d",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You already told us that she wasn't acting erratically,[p/] but was there anything off about her demeanor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07947f1",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I only saw her for a moment..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f62c76",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: But she was definitely different than usual.[p/] She was completely emotionless."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cd9a5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Y-[p/]Yeah.[p/] That's exactly what she was like when I fought her, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:085480b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: She was like an Arcane Construct.[p/] Her movements were almost robotic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0254aba",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] [i]Are[/i] there any Arcane Constructs on the Cathedral grounds?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038dfc8",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: No,[p/] not for lack of [i]trying[/i] on Lloyd's part."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c9920",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: The High Speaker and I have specifically forbidden the staff here from using them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ea33c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] It would've been [i]really[/i] convenient if all of this was done using a Construct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0983b15",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] was anyone else around when Steelwind cast that [b]transmutation[/b] spell on you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cef0cb",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: No.[p/] She moved away quickly after she incapacitated me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b56d4a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: And even if someone [i]was[/i] around,[p/] I don't think I could've seen them anyways."
}

{
  "id": "line:015cc31",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Commander White also said that he was surprised no one saw the prince until after that spell wore off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a826bf",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral1",
  "text": "What happened to him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c36fe",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: ...Why are you showing this Runestone to me, knave?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0679b15",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's my Attorney's Runestone.[p/] It proves that I'm a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a2962",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Hmph...[p/] Just like a peasant to fawn over such a monday-ed piece of artificery. [h=\"I want one...\" e=\"s\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:09328b6",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Hmph...[p/] Every time I see you,[p/] something horrible ends up happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d4c98",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: It's as if you bring trouble wherever you go."
}

{
  "id": "line:01818fb",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: My occupation just puts me in these positions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcbb63",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: So you go around [i]looking[/i] for trouble then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe158c",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Well,[p/] he's not wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:08019bc",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Aria|Lloyd|Coraline|Garrick|Autopsy Report: Lloyd von Sanctus|Autopsy Report: Coraline Sibyl|Autopsy Report: Garrick Pierce"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec7889",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I can't believe Lady Steelwind would do something like this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e522e",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: After everything my brother has done for her,[p/] [i]this[/i] is how she repays him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a074",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's more to this than we're all seeing.[p/] She can't be responsible for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:029a7b2",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Hmph...[p/] We'll see."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3b12",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Aster"
}

{
  "id": "line:04eb0d1",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Out of everyone,[p/] I think my brother has gotten the worst out of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01077dc",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] He has to choose between protecting his fiancée and maintaining an image of objectivity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0650e37",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I hope he's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c04ff8",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: Remus"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec0aac",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe I've gone this long without knowing who you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e7696",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why haven't I ever heard of you before, Your Grace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cae27b",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: His Grace does not see it fit to mingle with the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:018dd70",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: He only concerns himself with the matters [i]befitting[/i] of his station."
}

{
  "id": "line:034a918",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Player: The Report|Alaric's Testimony|Alaric"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a94efb",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a good thing you came out of this unharmed..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0917024",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: A lot of people lost their lives today."
}

{
  "id": "line:021ac86",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Hmph...[p/] Steelwind knows better than to harm a member of the royal family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0119e13",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Back"
}

{
  "id": "line:0475ace",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Your Highness?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b4376",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Hmph...[p/] Pondering such things is beneath someone of my stature."
}

{
  "id": "line:070894b",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral1",
  "text": "He could have just said he has nothing to say..."
}

{
  "id": "line:075527d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: She attacked a member of the royal family and [i]killed[/i] several nobles!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5a172",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: What [i]else[/i] is there to investigate?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da5a19",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: The laws are clear about what we must do![p/][s/] We should execute her immediately!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a396e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Alaric.[p/] This situation is of far too much import to make such rash decisions."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d08f7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: We need to approach this calmly and carefully."
}

{
  "id": "line:0181294",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "As we returned to the nave,[p/] I spotted the young prince stomping around as he argued with the nobleman I saw earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0612ef5",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Now that I thought about it,[p/] he was the only person here I didn't recognize..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0397112",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: ...Oh, it's [i]you[/i] two."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ec419",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Highness..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0052e4f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And I don't think [i]we've[/i] been introduced."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba8d99",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:033f8ac",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: I see you're still as insolvent as ever..."
}

{
  "id": "line:034fb89",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: You stand before Sir Remus Virgilae:[p/] Archduke and Royal Visor to the Wyverngarde Throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e0002",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I believe he means [i]ad[/i]visor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0803ff9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "\"Archduke\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4f56d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "I didn't even know the Kingdom of Wyverngarde [i]had[/i] a title like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aebfd6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Why hadn't I ever heard of him before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0431887",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: ...Why [i]are[/i] you two still here anyways?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9900e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: I thought the cathedral was closed for the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0171249",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're investigating what happened on behalf of Prosecutor Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc068",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cb89a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Anyways,[p/] I have much to attend to.[p/] I'll be taking my leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0314bf1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Actually,[p/] since we have you here,[p/] we'd like to ask you some questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6d8ed",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...[i]Both[/i] of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7f9d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Alaric: Hmph...[p/] You should know your place, knave."
}

{
  "id": "line:086a8d6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That covers [i]Alaric's[/i] account of what happened,[p/] and we even got the Archduke's statement too."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b0edd",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But there's still one last person we need to speak to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec7779",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Celeste: Aria..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ce820",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She and Beatrice supposedly have no memories of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a51dba",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If it were only Beatrice saying that,[p/] I'd probably doubt it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0130eb8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if [i]Steelwind[/i] also doesn't have any memories,[p/] it becomes a lot more credible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0781728",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She definitely has the missing piece we need to put this together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b45535",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Are you going to the dungeon to speak with her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06499a0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:07456b8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: Wonderful.[p/] I'll be accompanying you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0763e6e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da0363",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: As the royal advisor,[p/] I have a vested interest in the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cfba2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Remus: While I trust Lucio to leave no stone unturned,[p/] I hear you have quite the talent for seeing what the Crown cannot."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2102",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b29999",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Lucio Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5b42c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Why are you looking at me like that, Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e00b40",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "After he attacked me in Frega Manor,[p/] I'd always been a little wary of him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0522532",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "If it weren't for Celeste's reflexes,[p/] he might have very well killed me that day..."
}

{
  "id": "line:000b06c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I'm [i]not[/i] going to attack you again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0137021",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You [i]did[/i] almost kill me the last time we met."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a16c8c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ca8a5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: That's not—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c471c5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0044247",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Something changed in you between Dracogen's trial and Frega's trial.[p/] Your aura became stronger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1b367",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0597702",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion's Aura"
}

{
  "id": "line:0479215",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What does my aura have to do with this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:018e8d7",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...It's difficult to explain to someone like you,[p/] but warriors such as I must hone and develop our senses to survive in battle."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a90e27",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Eventually,[p/] we develop the ability to sense hidden enemies and anticipate danger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a36081",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: I'd heard that such senses are heightened when in the presence of \"extraplanar\" entities."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e895a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Until I met you and Beatrice Frega's familiar,[p/] I thought those stories were complete nonsense."
}

{
  "id": "line:02414f8",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath and me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da861f",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: As a heavensborn,[p/] your blood is said to originate from the heavens."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e6235",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: I wouldn't go so far as to say that I [i]believe[/i] in the existence of other planes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0524c9f",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: But I admit that I [i]still[/i] feel a certain aura from you that doesn't feel quite human."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8462e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Okay,[p/] but you've met me before in Aurinax."
}

{
  "id": "line:093b476",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: And something clearly changed since then.[p/] Even now,[p/] your aura is very noticeable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a77ee1",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "...Wait.[p/] Was this because of that riddle I solved?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbe183",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Did I gain the [b]Divine Edict[/b] because my powers had gotten stronger?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080a654",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Wyverngarde is no friend of the Theocracy.[p/] When I sensed you,[p/] I thought a cleric had somehow made it into the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0196662",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Do you not sense it too, McCoy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00be941",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02eb6ff",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Surely you noticed a change in him during the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4bc73",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is that true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f61ce4",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: I [i]did[/i],[p/] but I didn't think it was a [i]magic[/i] thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a6f0b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did you think it was?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06478af",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Well,[p/] sometimes you have someone in your life,[p/] and well—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e0dea",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: You start looking at them differently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7046e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4b3ba",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: I regret bringing this up."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dcf31",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Aster as a suspect"
}

{
  "id": "line:07faa2a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster.[p/] I'm sure you know why I'm here."
}

{
  "id": "line:07338b5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: It's because I'm one of your suspects, isn't it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9a250",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Your Majesty.[p/] You are the [i]reigning[/i] king of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fced3",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: I expect you to conduct yourself with more dignity..."
}

{
  "id": "line:048765b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: O-[p/][s/]Of course.[p/] My apologies, Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0db73",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] questioning you is honestly a formality at this point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0715b50",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ea025",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: A lot of the evidence works in your favor."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cc320",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "He didn't have a Blood Contract with the Empress of Discord after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bb0c8",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Well, I appreciate your vote of confidence nonetheless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb4890",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: The Force Cage"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2dded",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio,[p/] have you made any headway in figuring out who set that trap for Aster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab7a09",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: No,[p/] I haven't."
}

{
  "id": "line:028e6aa",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...It makes me uneasy that you let someone get [i]that[/i] close to my father's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0849ae3",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...I can't begin to apologize for my men's incompetence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0143764",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: If they were more vigilant,[p/] perhaps we could have avoided this whole tragedy entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d65dd",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So your men [i]were[/i] guarding the late king's coffin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd6dfd",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Yes.[p/] There wasn't a single moment when his body was left unguarded."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c56c9",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: We found traces of [b]illusion[/b] magic at the location of the [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaa651",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Although we're still not sure about [i]who[/i] could have set that trap."
}

{
  "id": "line:044cee8",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...There are also members of the Kingsguard that can cast both [b]Force Cage[/b] and [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ad1d",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Many of them fell comatose during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa09bf",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Do you think my men are [i]that[/i] weak, Your Majesty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095834b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...I think anyone can be made weak when pushed far enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:03df1a6",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] Regardless,[p/] we have no way of telling [i]who[/i] may have been guarding the coffin when the trap was set."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efb552",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: This means that we have no way of telling [i]when[/i] that [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b] was set."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e2562",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was actually meaning to ask about that.[p/] Couldn't we wait for the forty-eight hours to elapse?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037445c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we make note of the exact time the traces of [b]evocation[/b] disappear,[p/] we can work backwards to discern the exact time the trap was set."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4fe53",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Well...[p/] [i]Normally[/i] we could."
}

{
  "id": "line:009842a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: When the spell activated,[p/] I unfortunately panicked and cast a [b]Fire Bolt[/b] to try to destroy it."
}

{
  "id": "line:041e469",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...Of course,[p/] it didn't even put a dent in the [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:057cd76",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Because of that,[p/] he left traces of [b]evocation[/b] at the exact location of the [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0feacc6",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: We can't discern which traces were left by the Patron's [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b] or His Majesty's [b]Fire Bolt[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0ba29",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: I'm terribly sorry about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a46acd",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "I couldn't blame him for reacting like that,[p/] but it was going to make figuring out who did this that much more difficult."
}

{
  "id": "line:0674d69",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Aria Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4bfe4",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I heard you two visited Aria earlier today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d27dcc",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: How is she doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0afcfd3",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have either of you spoken to Aria since the trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2d902",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...We have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0362391",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: I think she's doing the best she can.[p/] She's quite the resilient girl."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d415e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...No thanks to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:013e334",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdb599",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: She's only [i]in[/i] this situation because of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:040a0b0",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio...[p/] That's not—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bd911",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...Me?[p/][s/] You're the one who's heartlessly prosecuting her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0294269",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...She's far too weak for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd363a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: If [i]that's[/i] what you truly think of her,[p/] you're grossly misunderstanding the kind of person that she is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d427",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: She defied the role you tried to [i]force[/i] onto her,[p/] and she instead dedicated herself to fixing our broken kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:050414a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ever since this started,[p/] all you've done is insult her.[p/] You know [i]nothing[/i] about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0a80c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's always carved her own path and pursued her own justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0099670",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Her \"[i]own[/i] path\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:004e9e7",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...She only [i]became[/i] a prosecutor because of His Majesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa0d69",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0190048",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: She became a prosecutor to fix our corrupt justice system from the inside."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bfd0c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: And who do you think put those ideas into her mind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0792ef5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: If she wanted to \"fix\" our justice system,[p/] she could easily have done so by slowly weakening House Sibyl's influence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0641f05",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: But she [i]knew[/i] about your strange idolization of Ruby Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:041dd2c",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: And she [i]knew[/i] how closely you followed [i]each[/i] and every one of her cases."
}

{
  "id": "line:058c108",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: She thought that if she became like your idol and defeated her,[p/] you might finally notice her."
}

{
  "id": "line:092b610",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: That's ridiculous.[p/] Why would she ever care if I noticed her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a16f4",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Even [i]now[/i], you're blind to it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:029a1d2",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: When you were engaged to Lady Frega,[p/] you flaunted your relationship in front of her with no regard for her feelings!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0633ef5",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Every time you two visited her,[p/] she spent the entire night silently crying to herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:009cc5e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "...This was the first time I'd ever seen him that angry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0737b1a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...I had no idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d43126",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: My daughter is far stronger than any of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dabfe0",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...But she's weak when it comes to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d4d79",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio...[p/] Let's focus on getting through this trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cae811",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion Cuthbert"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d9e2a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...I must ask you, Cuthbert.[p/] Why are [i]you[/i] going to such lengths for my daughter?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0597dc6",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07482c0",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Surely you understand the gravity of the situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a78d8a",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: By taking part in this trial,[p/] you risk drawing the ire of [i]both[/i] the nobility and whoever this \"Empress of Discord\" is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfc9e9",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...What are you planning?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c5425",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio...[p/] I'm not an agent of the Theocracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:054e29b",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Please.[p/] Do you honestly expect me to believe that you're doing this out of the goodness of your heart?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e21895",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:040ef28",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Scaled Lord...[p/] You actually [p/][i]are[/i] doing it for that reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0517034",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: I'd read the Theocracy's texts,[p/] but is this really what [i]all[/i] heavensborn are like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4bd09",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't like thinking about it that way."
}

{
  "id": "line:068dc1e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not doing this because of my divine blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0384df9",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I admire Prosecutor Steelwind a lot,[p/] and I know what it's like to feel hopeless."
}

{
  "id": "line:052e38e",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I won't let her story end like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7b9e0",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] I wouldn't throw around such promises so loosely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0186dc0",
  "node": "Talk_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not.[p/] I [i]will[/i] save her, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:0570eca",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Ah,[p/] your Attorney's Runestone.[p/] I was wondering when I'd be able to see it again."
}

{
  "id": "line:06022f1",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Wouldn't someone like you have one too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc0c9c",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Oh,[p/] I have a Runestone,[p/] but it's not an [i]Attorney's[/i] Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0739f8c",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm glad someone finally understands the difference."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3e93b",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: ...I don't understand [i]either[/i] of your fixations on that thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd2596",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's an Attorney's Runestone, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:087a7eb",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: It proves that he's a certified attorney!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e8289",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c886ae",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: I'm really quite glad we have you working on this case, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0c9c9",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...I feel a lot more at ease knowing that you're looking into this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5bffb",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Don't thank me yet.[p/] We still need to find out what really happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebf846",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: If it weren't for you,[p/] we would have never even [i]known[/i] about Lady Steelwind's Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab6c20",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Don't thank me yet.[p/] We still need to find out who the Patron is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0858aa9",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Nevertheless,[p/] you have my gratitude."
}

{
  "id": "line:07172be",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac3323",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: So Lady Steelwind truly fought Ms. McCoy that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cdad0",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: If it were anyone else,[p/] I'm sure they would've never stood a chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f3c6a",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] it looks like even House Steelwind isn't strong enough to take down the Crimson Demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0924e20",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...S-[p/][s/]Sorry,[p/] did I go too far?"
}

{
  "id": "line:051c6e8",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was just trying to lighten the mood..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a6c0",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh no![p/] I'm just a little distracted."
}

{
  "id": "line:084e4c9",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa62d6",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: D-[p/][s/]Don't apologize.[p/] It's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d17e65",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Aria|Steelwind's Testimony|Aria's Blood Contract"
}

{
  "id": "line:020978b",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: It pains my heart to see Lady Steelwind like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf91c9",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: I wish there was something I could do."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c0e1c",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Please, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Do everything you can to save her."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f2f05",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That was my goal from the very beginning."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ed6a2",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: The Trapped King|The Trapped King 2|Contingent Spell"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a4771",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b] common for mages to know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c68f5f",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: No.[p/] It's extremely useful,[p/] but it's also very advanced."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f95ad4",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: It essentially involves casting two spells at the same time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0787623",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: So whoever set that trap was a powerful mage..."
}

{
  "id": "line:033edfe",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Celeste: But considering the people who were here,[p/] [i]that[/i] hardly narrows it down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0686ae9",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Lloyd von Sanctus is actually dead..."
}

{
  "id": "line:087bd04",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] Despite my feelings about him,[p/] no one deserves to be killed in cold blood like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a70aa",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: If there's [i]some[/i] silver lining to this,[p/] it's that his greed will no longer put people in harm's way."
}

{
  "id": "line:077f05e",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Autopsy Report: Coraline Sibyl|Coraline Sibyl"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f834cb",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: I can't believe someone killed Lady Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:088e985",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you know her well?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3f33f",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Quite well.[p/] We had many debates about how her family ran the judicial system."
}

{
  "id": "line:0931c23",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: I found them quite...[p/] frustrating."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c55b2",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...After speaking to her,[p/] I can kind of understand what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7776d",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: Alaric|Alaric's Testimony"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f14b4",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry about what happened to your brother."
}

{
  "id": "line:0464721",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure that experience must have been traumatic for him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c3a9d",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Luckily,[p/] it seems that the spell was only temporary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a143a3",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: There's no lasting damage to his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0316474",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Player: No Blood Contract"
}

{
  "id": "line:030dc08",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the way,[p/] I attempted to issue a Divine Edict against you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4c0aa",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] Why?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e5c09",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: My original plan was to issue an edict to every person I could think of."
}

{
  "id": "line:01365dc",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But apparently,[p/] issuing them recklessly can have dire consequences."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eebac2",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: At the very least,[p/] we know [i]you[/i] aren't the Patron."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b64168",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You would've had a Blood Contract with the Empress of Discord otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26ad6",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Well,[p/] I suppose I'm happy I'm not a suspect anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b7c8a",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Aster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcac40",
  "node": "Present_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: My apologies, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I don't have much to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:09957a8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Knight: Sir,[p/] I've spoken with the groundskeeper."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1f327",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Knight: His Majesty and the Grand General are currently visiting Lady Steelwind,[p/] but they'll be here later today to talk to the High Speaker."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b7889",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll just have to come back later."
}

{
  "id": "line:02568e6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Oh, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2114c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "As we entered the Nave,[p/] we spotted Aster,[p/] Alaric,[p/] and Lucio gathered near the altar."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d1485",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio was standing still,[p/] staring blankly at the empty benches which would've normally hosted hundreds of attendants."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d84c0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Prince Alaric was sitting on a bench,[p/] swaying his legs back and forth while he stared at the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d0d79",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster seemed to be putting on a brave face.[p/] His face lit up as he saw us enter the Nave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46fe6",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "He waved us over,[p/] but his eyes widened when he saw me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0877f65",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00553ec",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Aster: Your face looks pale."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a5dc2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "I scratched the back of my neck and avoided meeting his eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:059921d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There was a bit of an accident earlier..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fbd3a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: Well...[p/] Try to exude more caution next time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0f189",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Lucio: It'd be dishonorable if you didn't fall by my hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:06746b3",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why is [i]everything[/i] you say so damned aggressive?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08528b2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Now for the next suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:079201d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Although judging from what happened at the Study,[p/] it was unlikely that [i]Aster[/i] was the Patron."
}

{
  "id": "line:0507d15",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Nevertheless,[p/] the [b]Force Cage[/b] that trapped him was an instrumental part of the Patron's plot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcbedd",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Maybe he saw something that might point to who set that [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffd37f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "Damn it all...[p/] Judging from the [b]Spell Compendiums[/b] I had,[p/] neither Aria nor Beatrice could have set that trap."
}

{
  "id": "line:08deb61",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "If the Patron was a mage,[p/] it was very likely that [i]they[/i] were the one who cast [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd722d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Cathedral2",
  "text": "But I was out of options.[p/] There was only one more person I could talk to."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ceb5",
  "node": "Examine_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "It's a stained glass window.[p/] A small ray of sunlight is shining through it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c73d4",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Player: Aster de Wyverngarde"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b888a",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: I think I saw Aria over there.[p/] We should go say hi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef91dd",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Are you sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0120017",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "As we approached the group,[p/] both the Grand General and the unnamed noble didn't break their gaze with Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:026eccb",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um...[p/] Hello."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f56621",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "The nobleman's eyes went to me and then to Celeste.[p/] He scanned the both of us,[p/] saying nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:072002e",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "He then walked away without a word."
}

{
  "id": "line:008c261",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Rude."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef2d23",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: Mr. Cuthbert and Ms. McCoy.[p/] I'm surprised to see you here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcd3bd",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: What?[p/] I thought [i]you[/i] were the one who invited them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9e50e",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sad to say that I didn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b881b",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: Although,[p/] I [i]am[/i] happy to see you two nonetheless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa62e7",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: What brings you to the Grand Cathedral today?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4c9eb",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: We were actually invited by [i]another[/i] noble.[p/] We have a meeting with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3a8a1",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: What...?[p/] None of the people here are allowed to invite [i]guests[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc938",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: Why didn't the guards stop you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04efab5",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh...[p/] They said they were expecting us."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d4223",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0336ded",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aria: It was Lord Pierce who invited them."
}

{
  "id": "line:067990c",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: Pierce?![p/][s/] That little—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ebdac",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: And to [i]think[/i] I granted his request for temporary release!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcd8c1",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sure he meant no disrespect by it.[p/] He probably had his reasons."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b6c47",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: How can you say that?![p/][s/] This is the day of your—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b480f9",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "He stopped himself and cleared his throat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0920d21",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] He thinks because he's a dead man that he has nothing to lose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0239a31",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: I'll be sure to correct that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c71280",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Player: A Gathering of Nobles"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8043e",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have to ask...[p/] Why are all of these nobles gathered here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f85185",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've taken over the entire Cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:0042938",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Everyone seemed to tense up at that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e6fd2",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sorry,[p/] but I'm not at liberty to tell you that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac506a",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: ...It's a matter of public safety."
}

{
  "id": "line:062f964",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cde9ed",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "That was a little strange,[p/] but I could read the room.[p/] I said nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e0993",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Player: Tyrion and Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0702b5d",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: You said that Lord Pierce invited you here?[p/] For what reason?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aef171",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I can't really tell you that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fa319",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: You [i]will[/i] tell us if it poses a threat to the nobles in attendance."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e3be6",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: P-[p/][s/]Please, Grand General.[p/] There's no need for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:083b9fb",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: Mr. Cuthbert would never do anything to put [i]anyone's[/i] life in danger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3fc7c",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: As you wish, Your H-[p/]... Majesty. [h=\"Is [i]this[/i] the reason why|Pierce asked for temporary release?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:010a65c",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "So Pierce was temporarily released to attend whatever...[p/] [i]this[/i] was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d117a3",
  "node": "Talk_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "I could have met with him in his cell.[p/] Why would he pick such a strange location?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0576bcd",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: Ah,[p/] PRESENTING your Runestone as always, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03634e0",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's a bit of a habit,[p/] but maybe I should stop."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b167a5",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't.[p/] You always look so excited when you show it to people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0176a02",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't even know what this thing means to me anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:029e98c",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: I mean, it's still useful.[p/] You can take pictures and write notes about things [i]other[/i] than crime scenes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7c10d",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: It's always a pleasant surprise to see you, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ac17b",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: R-[p/][s/]Really...?[p/] I honestly thought that you'd be angry at us..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdb628",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: I don't blame you for what happened with Beatrice,[p/] and I'm ultimately glad you caught her in the end."
}

{
  "id": "line:03eafc9",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: After what she said during the trial,[p/] it frightens me to think about what she might have done with House Frega's resources."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e42596",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0659678",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: Ah, Ms. McCoy.[p/] It's nice to see you again."
}

{
  "id": "line:003529a",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: You look as radiant as ever."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9fbef",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] Uh—[p/][s/] Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb03eb",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aria: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd94a3",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: ...Why are you all looking at me like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c88eb7",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Player: Aria"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc78f9",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: So, Aster.[p/] Have you made any progress with Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076c058",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: ...\"Progress\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0437d44",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aria: C-[p/][s/]Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ed7c7",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Leave the poor girl alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ac12f",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sorry, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I don't have much to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc3264",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about [i]this[/i] Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a54a3",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Sorry, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:060f3da",
  "node": "Present_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't think I can help you with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b429d4",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Nobleman: Lady Steelwind.[p/] Your Majesty.[p/] The High Speaker is ready to speak with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc2e63",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aria: O-[p/][s/]Oh,[p/] um—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:090dda0",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Steelwind's face ran red as it usually did around the Crown Prince.[p/] Her eyes darted around the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f69c99",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: Wonderful.[p/] I've been looking forward to this all day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0e782",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: Shall we go together, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:065b1e2",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Yes, Your Majesty.[p/] She [i]would[/i] like to accompany you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0048f5d",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aster: We shouldn't keep him waiting."
}

{
  "id": "line:02837e8",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Aria: O-[p/][s/]Okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d033c5",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: Scaled Lord...[p/] How does she plan to marry him if she can't even get a word out in his presence?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff59c9",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Seriously."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c05c6",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Alaric: I-[p/][s/]I [i]also[/i] have something important to do!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0517253",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Alaric: Good day to you all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0ca1",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "The little prince trotted out of the room,[p/] his head held high."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ae94b",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Isn't that the washroom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:055665a",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: I will be taking my leave as well,[p/] but make no mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:01480f7",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Lucio: My men [i]will[/i] be keeping an eye on you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c38b9f",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah, yeah."
}

{
  "id": "line:025a270",
  "node": "Check_Events_CathedralIntro",
  "text": "The room was empty now.[p/] It was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:055f87b",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even now,[p/] the sunlight is shining through the stained glass windows."
}

{
  "id": "line:0155494",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It looks like the fire reached them before it was put out."
}

{
  "id": "line:07af2d3",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Altar"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf7487",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Scorch"
}

{
  "id": "line:06dea60",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are scorch marks all over the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:098923b",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The fire must have spread pretty far."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a91f1",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] It was probably going for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9b7b2",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: No one even noticed it until Prince Alaric told the Kingsguard that he saw smoke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f80d1c",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Interesting...[p/] We should speak with him and see if he saw anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1a556",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Body"
}

{
  "id": "line:082f4f8",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a chalk outline in the center of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727d64",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This must be where they found von Sanctus's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9d0f3",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's even bits of ash there...[p/] It must be the burnt remnants of his body..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc8b43",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Center"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b16ca3",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: There's a trace of [b]abjuration[/b] magic in the center of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0372436",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] Do the traces overlap with the body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d7601",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Kind of...[p/] It's sort of...[p/] square-shaped?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d35f56",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Square-shaped...?[p/] I can't see the traces,[p/] but there also seems to be a square-shaped outline around the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f8959",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: You're right![p/] They overlap perfectly!"
}

{
  "id": "line:010c43f",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The area inside the square is a lot less burnt now that I look at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8b208",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure what this means yet.[p/] But it's definitely worth taking note of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f90546",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Body"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a056ce",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: There's a trace of [b]evocation[/b] magic near the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c4534",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That matches his autopsy report."
}

{
  "id": "line:077668e",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The murderer must have hit him with an [b]evocation[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7777d",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] I wonder if the murderer hit him with an [b]evocation[/b] spell..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d6573",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Water"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d54af9",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: There are traces of [b]evocation[/b] in a bunch of different spots around the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b41cf1",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: We think some oil from the lanterns got knocked over during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a4d97",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: The perp must've lit it on fire with some [b]evocation[/b] spells,[p/] but we don't know if they did it on purpose or accidentally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0749b2e",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: And the Kingsguard used a bunch of [i]water-based[/i] [b]evocation[/b] spells to put it out before the fire spread."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7358f",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] That makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a68ff4",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: With that knowledge in mind,[p/] there's nothing out of the ordinary here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00afb5f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: The Murders"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ed540",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Ugh...[p/] This whole situation's a damned mess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0513b8f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Has the Inquisition found any clues to explain what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d16918",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: We haven't exactly had a lot of time.[p/] We've only [i]just[/i] received the autopsy reports."
}

{
  "id": "line:088b238",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's still pretty useful.[p/] Do you have copies of them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0485547",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Sure.[p/] Knock yourselves out."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fadba",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Pierce was killed with a frozen blade?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06bfa2f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Isn't that similar to how [i]he[/i] killed Flinhart McCoy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0769292",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...S-[p/][s/]Sorry![p/][s/] I didn't mean to—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d3ecd",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] It's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cdc64",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "I could imagine a scenario where a struggle happened and the killer used whatever was nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e234d3",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "However,[p/] it still felt like a convoluted series of events."
}

{
  "id": "line:054e70f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways...[p/] The [i]times[/i] of death also tell a story."
}

{
  "id": "line:0589ffe",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Purely based on the times of death,[p/] the murderer must have killed von Sanctus,[p/] then Sibyl,[p/] then Pierce,[p/] in that order."
}

{
  "id": "line:023c515",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] That's [i]our[/i] working theory too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7f058",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: How were the bodies discovered?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04121a1",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: When did they discover the bodies?[p/] Who came across them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0940246",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: It all started when Prince Alaric ran up to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:014de30",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: He told us that he saw a fire breaking out in the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a01af",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: ...He also saw Steelwind there,[p/] but when he tried to talk to her,[p/] she hit him with some kind of spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cf335",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...She attacked one of the [i]princes[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:074fdc5",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] but it didn't sound like she hurt him."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ead9f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Lord Asclepius inspected him,[p/] and he told us he wasn't injured."
}

{
  "id": "line:0480df8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm glad that he's okay,[p/] but wouldn't Aria have used a more violent spell if she was afflicted with Mageblight?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b672e2",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: It's possible she was throwing spells randomly,[p/] and he just happened to get [i]really[/i] lucky."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2cc8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose that's [i]possible[/i],[p/] but was there anyone else nearby when this happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07546f8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I would've expected a prince of Wyverngarde to be under constant guard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0459ac1",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] That was kind of my mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dbf84",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: I ordered the knights to give him some space,[p/] considering what just happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d0a28",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] His father just died recently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbbf68",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And that would be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbed70",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Sorry, kid.[p/] If you don't know,[p/] it's not my place to tell you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f23008",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: I have orders from the top to stay quiet about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f18fe4",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Then I would need to ask someone higher up.[p/] It was still strange, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0129763",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Why were all these nobles gathered here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5e8a7",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Anyways,[p/] whatever the perp hit him with,[p/] it only put him in a daze."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc0ce8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: He could barely walk or talk.[p/] He couldn't even approach us until the spell had worn off."
}

{
  "id": "line:04aad1d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: The weirdest thing about it was that he should've been pretty close to where we were."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73412",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: But for some reason,[p/] we didn't find him until [i]after[/i] the spell wore off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0811685",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That must have been traumatic...[p/] I hope he's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cb7d9",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "But why didn't anyone see him during this time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec8304",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: After he told us about what was happening,[p/] we went to put out the fires."
}

{
  "id": "line:029c43c",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: [i]That's[/i] when we saw a bunch of guards knocked out outside the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf0667",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Did you see [i]me[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea8a2a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: No.[p/] This all happened around 3:10 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d542aa",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] That was probably well after Steelwind moved into the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d87e63",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste must've already followed her into it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07caafa",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: The Comatose Guards"
}

{
  "id": "line:09057dc",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: When you arrested Steelwind,[p/] I recall you mentioning that a bunch of guards were comatose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a25d3e",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did the murderer use some kind of spell to knock them out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033798d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: They didn't.[p/] I'm just as lost as you are about that.[p/] Some of the victims didn't have [i]any[/i] magical traces on them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0233349",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: We [i]know[/i] that they're not under the effects of a spell,[p/] but they still haven't woken up."
}

{
  "id": "line:091b1c3",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's odd, to say the least..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d9f3a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is there any common thread between the knights who fell comatose?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae0829",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That might help us deduce what happened to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:029d77a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Well...[p/] We found all of them near the Common Room and the Prayer Room:[p/] all the locations where Steelwind was spotted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e28df0",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: That [i]can't[/i] be a coincidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0895b1f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "So it wasn't random,[p/] yet it wasn't the effect of an arcane spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd287f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander White...[p/] You keep saying \"the perp\" instead of \"Steelwind\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a66c2",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even though everyone [i]else[/i] seems to think she was responsible for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0265f6e",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you also suspect that she's being framed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ec2bc",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: It just doesn't add up."
}

{
  "id": "line:039886a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: If she [i]did[/i] give herself Mageblight,[p/] her actions wouldn't have been so deliberate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0817f64",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And she's definitely not the type of person to just go around murdering people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0eef4",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Even if she was,[p/] she's led a lot of the Inquisition's investigations recently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f004cb",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: She's investigated plenty of homicides with us,[p/] and she knows [i]exactly[/i] how we do things."
}

{
  "id": "line:063572a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Whoever did this got the job done,[p/] but they were sloppy about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:046089b",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: A bunch of witnesses saw her.[p/] She didn't even [i]try[/i] to hide herself using her magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ddc6d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: So either she [i]had[/i] Mageblight,[p/] which doesn't match with her behavior."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebe36f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Or she did this [i]intentionally[/i] and [i]wanted[/i] to get caught."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f67483",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Neither scenario makes any damned sense..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acce33",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Someone [i]has[/i] to be framing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:093c7aa",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's the only reasonable explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d49d6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: ...Honestly,[p/] I'm not so sure about [i]that[/i] either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0707030",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b3989",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: You saw her when we arrested her, didn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0afa738",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: She [i]wanted[/i] us to lock her up."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d83ce",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: It's like she thought she was a danger to herself and others."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e13038",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] That's the same impression I got as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:092ae64",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: If it weren't for the witness's statements,[p/] I'd be [i]sure[/i] she gave herself Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f89bfd",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: The strangest thing is that I've never seen her that scared before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b542e5",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Something really rattled her about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb6246",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:009909b",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you follow up on what I said about Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a88c1f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]know[/i] she was in the room when Pierce and I fell unconscious."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a3bac",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She has to be involved in this somehow..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d490cd",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Well,[p/] she's already in prison.[p/] So we're already ahead on that account."
}

{
  "id": "line:04387ba",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: But when we asked her what happened,[p/] she said that she couldn't remember anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8bfe9",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's such an obvious lie.[p/] She has to be hiding something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0035ab7",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Normally,[p/] I'd agree with you,[p/] but she's not the only one with missing memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:042b1c9",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Steelwind also can't remember anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0b93",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "I'd just have to speak with her about that later."
}

{
  "id": "line:066afc3",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] what about Eris and that knight who was guarding her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056586a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did [i]they[/i] see anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f03bd2",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Sorry, kid,[p/] but Eris Illmater has been missing since everything went down."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d8702",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0299b35",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: I wouldn't be [i]too[/i] worried."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e53dde",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: A witness to the crime is [i]missing[/i] and possibly hurt!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0752738",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Look, kid.[p/] You may be a hotshot attorney,[p/] but [i]I've[/i] been in this business a lot longer than you have."
}

{
  "id": "line:036a25f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Sometimes when these things happen to civilians,[p/] they get spooked and run away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0527b6e",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: I've seen it a million times."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b679ce",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "...Eris [i]was[/i] the daughter of a crime lord.[p/] I doubt she was in any rush to speak with law enforcement."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d0509",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: We don't have the resources to look for her,[p/] but I'm sure she'll turn up eventually."
}

{
  "id": "line:0766516",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well...[p/] I suppose we can't do anything about that now..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdea18",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] what about the knight guarding Beatrice?[p/] Surely [i]he[/i] didn't go missing as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0005564",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: That's the thing...[p/] The knight who was supposed to be watching her was one of the guards who went comatose."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d97f9",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: We found him in front of the Prayer Room, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de9df0",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] Did he follow Beatrice to the Prayer Room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:032e6b7",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: To make matters worse,[p/] that Frega chick knows how to cast [b]Invisibility[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd751",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: So even [i]if[/i] she was telling the truth,[p/] very few people would've actually [i]seen[/i] her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10f1d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Would you happen to have a recent version of her [b]Spell Compendium[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a7a1a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Sure.[p/] We already have it on record."
}

{
  "id": "line:021cac4",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] I forgot how many spells she used during Lord Frega's murder..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0711c89",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: The First Victim: Lloyd von Sanctus"
}

{
  "id": "line:0736076",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's all a little difficult to take in.[p/] I still can't believe it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ff7cf",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: After everything he did,[p/] von Sanctus was just murdered..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8f345",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: I'm surprised to hear that from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:086b347",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Didn't he basically get away with almost blowing up your hometown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b73fd",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: The way I see it,[p/] he got what he deserved."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fcf6f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That still doesn't sit right with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d48b2",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: No matter [i]who[/i] the victims might've been,[p/] [i]no one[/i] deserves to die like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a81b6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Hmph...[p/] You're definitely a bigger man than I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a931a6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] von Sanctus's autopsy report says that he died of suffocation."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e06bc",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: We think the murderer overpowered him and choked him with a rope or something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2c2a0",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That [i]hardly[/i] sounds like something someone would do during a psychotic episode."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d17e7",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] The more info I collect,[p/] the more I think you might be onto something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6f16b",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: But either way,[p/] the fire that the perp started in this room burnt his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2afe8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: It didn't [i]completely[/i] turn it to ash,[p/] but there's not a lot left."
}

{
  "id": "line:05afdb6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] So that fire would've burnt away any evidence of the minor wounds he had."
}

{
  "id": "line:0722035",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] We're lucky we even discerned he was hit with an [b]evocation[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:033e899",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] The autopsy report mentioned that too..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbf259",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if a fire was started,[p/] is it possible that he died from smoke inhalation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d872b",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: No.[p/] The [b]divination[/b] spell we use always identifies smoke inhalation as \"death by poisoning\",[p/] not \"death by suffocation\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1f99d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose that [i]kind of[/i] makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:062c776",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Spell Compendiums"
}

{
  "id": "line:044e878",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: While we're at it,[p/] do you have records of each of the victims' [b]Spell Compendiums[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc8b91",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They might help us understand what each of the victims was doing during the attack."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c5194",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay, wow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d43b69",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That's[/i] a lot to work through."
}

{
  "id": "line:005efc1",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yep...[p/] [i]This[/i] is what happens when a bunch of mages are caught in the middle of a murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a21f8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Honestly,[p/] you've been lucky until now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d073ff",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Nevertheless,[p/] I'll need to look over each of these spells when they become relevant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf9178",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: ...Kid, why?"
}

{
  "id": "line:044e4fe",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's my—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e53be1",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: I know![p/][s/] It's your Attorney's Runestone,[p/] and it proves you're a certified attorney!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a5fd1",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: I caught the last hundred times you waved this thing in my face."
}

{
  "id": "line:06493bd",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Hmph...[p/] Trouble seems to follow you wherever you go, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2e7ed",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't help it...[p/] Sometimes I feel like [i]I'm[/i] the one who goes looking for it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9c9e0",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Well...[p/] You've certainly [i]found[/i] it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05557c8",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: It's a real mess this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:017f9b7",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Huh...[p/] I see you're still working with the mage girl."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d4827",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I have a name, you know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0befe4c",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Save it, sweetheart.[p/] You may have everyone else fooled,[p/] but we've seen today what mages like you are capable of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3a275",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] lucky for [i]you[/i],[p/] Celeste and I are here to help you in sorting this mess out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0d231",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah, yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03963f8",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Just tell her to keep her magic under control.[p/] We need answers,[p/] not [i]more[/i] fireworks."
}

{
  "id": "line:083a03a",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Man...[p/] Steelwind has gotten herself in the middle of a real mess this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0c681",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know...[p/] This whole situation is unbelievable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7eeb8",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] None of it makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f51cc4",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Orym"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cf2ee",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So...[p/] How have you been, Commander White?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fd127",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Well...[p/] A bunch of nobles got offed during,[p/] what was apparently,[p/] some kind of big aristocratic event."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e5512",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: The Crown is breathing down my neck to figure out what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e77fe",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: How do [i]you[/i] think my day is going?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0636c3d",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6cc3b",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Coraline"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a61b3",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Hmph...[p/] I can't believe someone just offed the Minister of Justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0473894",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Her family is responsible for the justice system.[p/] Have you met her before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:019dfae",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Only in passing."
}

{
  "id": "line:05326ba",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: And whenever I [i]did[/i] talk to her,[p/] she'd always say kooky things about the \"universal balance\".[p/] Or some kind of hooey like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a0db7",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Frankly,[p/] I could never understand a word she says."
}

{
  "id": "line:092572f",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Lloyd"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6a812",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: So, von Sanctus is actually dead..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e33128",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Honestly,[p/] I'm not going to lose any sleep over him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e832e8",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Serves him right after what he and Frega tried to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b589",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even so...[p/] A dangerous murderer is on the loose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e85016",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Neither of us can relax until we catch them and put them away."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ab9b3",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Hmph...[p/] You're always working, huh?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d8c77",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Garrick"
}

{
  "id": "line:09100ab",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: So,[p/] Pierce got offed too..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0322878",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Not that it changes much...[p/] His execution was scheduled for next month anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e89ff0",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "It was clear she had many conflicting emotions about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:04acdbf",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "When this was all over,[p/] I wanted to give her a break from guarding me."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e8493",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about [i]this[/i], Commander White?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b7f62",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Sorry, kid.[p/] I don't got much to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ad771",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "We retraced our footsteps and found the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb07b0",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "This was the last place I'd seen von Sanctus and Sibyl before everything happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:08681bd",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "I looked around.[p/] The once pure white room was completely scorched."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fad7d",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "I could still smell the scent of burnt cloth and flesh in the air."
}

{
  "id": "line:01eebbf",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What happened here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09241e5",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Was there some kind of fire?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0929e89",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] We think the perp lit a fire using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e513d7",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "As we entered the room,[p/] Commander White waved us over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6e6cf",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "He was accompanied by his usual legion of knights."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbe7d3",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander White."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cd7c6",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Hey, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdc781",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: You investigating what happened, too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0588639",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We just want to figure out what really happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:082914c",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: Hmph...[p/] You and me both."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b781a",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: [i]Nothing[/i] about this makes any damned sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:08632f3",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "Orym: ...I could honestly really use your help in trying to figure this out."
}

{
  "id": "line:07af0f8",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "I wasn't sure [i]who[/i] I could trust at this point,[p/] but like always,[p/] the commander [i]was[/i] leading the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c85639",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "I'd found everything I could relating to von Sanctus's murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0714d",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoom1",
  "text": "It was time to MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e89f48",
  "node": "OrymDeduce1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we look at this map,[p/] we can see where the Prayer Room and the Common Room are."
}

{
  "id": "line:057ae6e",
  "node": "OrymDeduce1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lady Sibyl's body was found in the lake west of here."
}

{
  "id": "line:06297fa",
  "node": "OrymDeduce1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Grand Cathedral was built on a cliff."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8e687",
  "node": "OrymDeduce1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There would only be one way for her to reach the lake in such a short amount of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b33a0a",
  "node": "OrymDeduce2",
  "text": "0000"
}

{
  "id": "line:066ee0c",
  "node": "OrymDeduce2",
  "text": "Player: Fail"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2f44b",
  "node": "OrymDeduce2",
  "text": "No...[p/] I was concerned with how Lady Sibyl's body ended up in the lake west of the cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:064c38b",
  "node": "OrymDeduce2",
  "text": "The murderer couldn't have dragged her body there in such a short amount of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0773137",
  "node": "OrymDeduce2",
  "text": "There was a far simpler explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c38752",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Grand Cathedral was built on a cliff over the lake,[p/] and the westward balcony just happens to be right over it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6d7ad",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] I guess that makes sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:055def8",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Orym: We even have a witness who saw Steelwind there."
}

{
  "id": "line:04847a8",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/] Who was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dee250",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Orym: It was High Speaker Theon Archeus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac6123",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"High Speaker\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ed7fd",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Orym: He's the shot-caller of the Church of Bahamut,[p/] and he stands at the top of the religious hierarchy from what I hear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cca4fc",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Orym: He spotted Steelwind near the west balcony and noticed that she was acting suspiciously."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a6039",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Orym: He called out to her,[p/] but she ignored him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0736b6f",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: So she [i]knew[/i] that he saw her,[p/] but she didn't attack him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:064662d",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] this whole \"Mageblight\" story doesn't really add up."
}

{
  "id": "line:050929e",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Either way,[p/] we'll just have to talk to him directly to find out more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0031f11",
  "node": "OrymDeduce3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Putting that aside,[p/] there's something else that's strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aceba",
  "node": "OrymDeduce5a",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What's that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c6843",
  "node": "OrymDeduce5a",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's about the [i]order[/i] that the murders occurred in."
}

{
  "id": "line:03de1ec",
  "node": "OrymDeduce5a",
  "text": "Tyrion: From the times of death,[p/] the murderer must have killed von Sanctus,[p/] Sibyl,[p/] and Pierce—[p/]in that order."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fc4f5",
  "node": "OrymDeduce5a",
  "text": "Tyrion: This means that the murderer went to the Common Room,[p/] then the West Balcony,[p/] and then finally the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0387a71",
  "node": "OrymDeduce5a",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if we look at the map,[p/] the murderer's route seems a bit strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:0626cfc",
  "node": "OrymDeduce6",
  "text": "No...[p/] There was a clear route between each of the rooms."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ce1bf",
  "node": "OrymDeduce6",
  "text": "The murderer would have traveled to the Common Room,[p/] then the Balcony,[p/] then the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcaf58",
  "node": "OrymDeduce6",
  "text": "But there's clearly a more direct path they could have taken if they wanted to murder the three victims quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:045370b",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The murderer must have passed right by the Prayer Room before they dumped Sibyl's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e1346",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why wouldn't they just murder Pierce on the way there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:082e019",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Orym: Maybe they wanted to dump Sibyl's body first."
}

{
  "id": "line:0432902",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Or they were afraid of fighting me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0586fb6",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Orym: ...Aren't you giving yourself a little too much credit?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d9b36",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/] She has a point."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c7373",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Out of everyone who fought the murderer,[p/] Celeste was the only one who didn't die or fall comatose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7fdb3",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] there [i]has[/i] to be a reason why the murderer deliberately chose that route."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf4d99",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "I'd created a rough outline of the murderer's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ddafd",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "But the real clues would lie in how each of the individual murders occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:06de29f",
  "node": "OrymDeduce7",
  "text": "...First,[p/] I'd need to figure out how von Sanctus was murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e51025",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "The sunlight was shining through this glass window."
}

{
  "id": "line:0757fd9",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "A ceramic altar was at the end of this room."
}

{
  "id": "line:079a3e9",
  "node": "Examine_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "There were candles on top of it made out of pure gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fdeae",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: Coraline Sibyl"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e58037",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What did you mean when you said that you owed us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cdfb4",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You played your role well.[p/] Your actions have brought to light the crimes of William and Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:0562fb6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: N-[p/][s/]Nothing has been proven legally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab049a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ...Yet it was evident in every other aspect. [h=\"You disgusting cur...\" e=\"as\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0637514",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "...Her thoughts were livid,[p/] but her demeanor remained blank."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e739b",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You and William paid off the representatives within [i]my[/i] House of Lords."
}

{
  "id": "line:0135d1e",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You two made a complete mockery of everything that my noble house has stood for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d80c42",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: And for what?[p/] So you could temporarily snatch power away from the Steelwinds?"
}

{
  "id": "line:014c43a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I was merely thinking about the future of my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:026a593",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: You [i]know[/i] Lucio can't be trusted."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2855",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: He [i]executed[/i] Lady Ophelia—[p/]his [i]own[/i] wife!"
}

{
  "id": "line:010a7ed",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The Grand General executed his wife?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da3462",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is [i]that[/i] what really happened to her mom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c0237",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: He was carrying out his duty.[p/] Ophelia committed a crime that demanded absolution."
}

{
  "id": "line:0693820",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I understand that you...[p/] [i]cared[/i] for her,[p/] but you're spitting on her memory by using her to justify your actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0066846",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f09c5",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Enough.[p/] I've had enough to mourn for today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdecc6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb6dbc",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: Wyverngarde's Justice System"
}

{
  "id": "line:0951893",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Your Grace,[p/] this [i]has[/i] to have opened your eyes to the corruption in the justice system."
}

{
  "id": "line:022b7a1",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have the power to change it![p/][s/] You have to do [i]something[/i] to fix it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0953c71",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76f3d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: How [i]dare[/i] you take advantage of her poor mood to plant your [i]insidious[/i] ideas?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:027581d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ...Why the outrage, Lloyd?[p/][s/] Should he have given you and William credit for the idea?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bed688",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] have you ever heard of the saying that \"justice is blind\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d96703",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Yes,[p/] I guess so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0172c",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: That saying is incorrect.[p/] Justice isn't blind.[p/] It must be [i]kept[/i] blind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8df05",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I'm sure I must look like a naive and blind fool to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04955f8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: The truth is that I've had my own suspicions of William and Lloyd for years."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b529ce",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Every instinct in my body has been screaming that they were plotting behind our backs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e146fe",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce3497",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ...However,[p/] I could never definitively prove it—[p/]not even to myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d5fe2",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Humans are inherently flawed.[p/] It is our very nature."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6494e",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: What many refer to as \"instinct\" is simply the drive for an individual's own survival."
}

{
  "id": "line:0024000",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I would not be arrogant in saying that House Sibyl holds the most power among the four pillars."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2969c",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: We oversee the exchange of resources between noble houses.[p/] We authorize the movement of our forces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8fe5f",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: The other Pillars are the arms and legs of Wyverngarde,[p/] but House Sibyl is its beating heart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0898a17",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: To put my finger on the scales of justice would be to disrupt the harmony of our system.[p/] It would disrupt the Cosmic Balance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbf07a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: The Cosmic Balance"
}

{
  "id": "line:055ceba",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you [i]talking[/i] about?![p/] What even [i]is[/i] the \"Cosmic Balance\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0591e65",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: It's the natural order of the world.[p/] It is the guiding philosophy of House Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecb9e8",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: It is the belief that everything naturally progresses towards something better."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aae7d0",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you just [i]expect[/i] things to get better without having to do anything?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f650e0",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: The people of the kingdom are [i]suffering[/i] because of your inaction."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b4b77",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: [i]My[/i] inaction?[p/] You place the blame on me,[p/] but what about [i]you[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01da1b1",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You were once a champion of your so-called \"justice\",[p/] but you've stopped your work as a defense attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cf808",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: How many lives could you have saved in the month that you spent on vacation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d637d5",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a8431",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not [s/][i]his[/i] responsibility to clean up [i]your[/i] mess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0559eff",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: You have no idea how much he's suffered doing this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c17cc",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You're right.[p/] He shouldn't bear that kind of responsibility alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ced778",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Every commoner has the ability to learn and practice law as you do, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d270d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: So why are [i]you[/i] one of the few commoners that do so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05043c6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: From what I've heard,[p/] you're one of the few people who defend mages of the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0557076",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Every other attorney wouldn't even consider taking them as clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:0741b7b",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Perhaps the problem lies in the commonfolk, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0892ff7",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: They are fully capable of rising to defend the innocent,[p/] yet they do nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f9d12",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: Final Plea"
}

{
  "id": "line:039f61b",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Your Grace,[p/] you [i]have[/i] to do something."
}

{
  "id": "line:027f516",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: You have more power than possibly anyone else in the kingdom.[p/] You have a voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:06be534",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: That's [i]precisely[/i] why I can't act so recklessly.[p/] A power like mine can't be invoked so clumsily."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd4f9a",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I must trust that the system my family has built will allow the Cosmic Balance to guide us to a better tomorrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:084fe86",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: The rules must be followed.[p/] Otherwise,[p/] there would be nothing separating us from the animals."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f60ee",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I choose to have no voice,[p/] because it is my responsibility to make sure that everyone else has one."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bffca",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: And what about the late Duke of Finance?[p/] Look how easily he bent your system to his own ends."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bea255",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: People like you are a part of the system as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:072eed2",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Akin to white blood cells in an organism,[p/] you sought out the infection and corrected it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0042846",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was only out of sheer luck![p/][s/] Do you have any idea how badly William's plot could have ended if it had gone any other way?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c7329",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ...I'll admit that the House of Lords was far more fallible than I expected,[p/] and I'm sincerely thankful that you brought it to light."
}

{
  "id": "line:004ee67",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: The system isn't perfect,[p/] but incidents like this allow us to prevent such abuse from happening in the future."
}

{
  "id": "line:031e3a4",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Like a species evolving over history[p/]—like a stream smoothing out the edges of a stone—[p/]the Cosmic Balance will bring us to a better future."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cce8e6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: That said,[p/] while [i]I[/i] choose not to have a voice,[p/] I think yours could be of great help to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c1e0c",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Shortly after her indictment,[p/] Lady Beatrice made a plea deal with Prosecutor Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ab554",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Her evidence and testimony have allowed us to arrest several seat members within the House of Lords."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c704d",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: There are many vacant seats now.[p/] Would you be interested in having one, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ef9a5",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Coraline,[p/] you can't be serious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a134d6",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I've realized that the House of Lords could use a lot more oversight—[p/]something I think you can provide."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c6efb",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Of course,[p/] I'd need to consult the other representatives,[p/] but I think they'll agree."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e5ad4",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I'll give you some time to think about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3b6f9",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Wait![p/][s/] Coraline.[p/][s/] Coraline!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0691201",
  "node": "Talk_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "The Minister of Justice ignored him and left the room.[p/] The Duke of Commerce chased after her frantically."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d1c1b",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: It's your Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0d8d7",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I'm glad you've been keeping it in good shape."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d36866",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Be grateful.[p/] You only have access to such sophisticated artificery because of [i]my[/i] house's ingenuity."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e7b20",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ...I've been to Arcarus, Lloyd.[p/] I'm aware that you stole your designs from them."
}

{
  "id": "line:081fa5f",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Tyrion Cuthbert...[p/] It appears we were fated to meet."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dd9a3",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I mean...[p/] It was [i]bound[/i] to happen eventually."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed3930",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: My business tends to step on the toes of the Four Pillars."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f6a4d",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I concur.[p/] Our souls were drawn together by the Cosmic Balance."
}

{
  "id": "line:025e949",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Is she hitting on you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6eff1",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I have no idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa0935",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d20f8e",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Hm...[p/] It is not my role to speak of such things."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e1107",
  "node": "Present_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "In other words,[p/] she had nothing to say about it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:050b098",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Oh, what are [i]you[/i] doing here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3428",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Did you follow us?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5af5f",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Not [i]intentionally[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b03e27",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Trust me...[p/] You're the [i]last[/i] person we wanted to see today."
}

{
  "id": "line:01425b9",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04abb22",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: If they are here by chance,[p/] it is because the Cosmic Balance wills it so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2674b",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ...Anyways,[p/] I owe a lot to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a3652",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "...What did she mean by that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce683c",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Wow...[p/] I wasn't expecting that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd871f",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: The idea's ridiculous..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d8a5f",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: I kind of understand her worldview in a way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e998a1",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?[p/] She's just using that \"Cosmic Balance\" nonsense as an excuse to do nothing..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bec84",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: But think about what it'd be like to have that much power."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cf168",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Everything you do could potentially affect the entire kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baf241",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Imagine being responsible for the lives of [i]millions[/i] of people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0718639",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Now imagine nobles like William, Lucio, and von Sanctus all trying to manipulate you to get what they want."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d215fa",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't blame her for not trusting herself to use that power."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdf808",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't agree with her,[p/] but I'm just saying that I understand where she's coming from."
}

{
  "id": "line:0952000",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: You probably know it better than anyone else.[p/] The right thing to do isn't always so plain and simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:017f69f",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'll admit that she [i]does[/i] seem sincere in trying to do right by the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0572db9",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I suppose auditing the House of Lords would be a simple thing with the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f0f42",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you going to take her offer?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ee4dc",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "I just sighed and scratched my head.[p/] My problems were always with Wyverngarde's justice system."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb4b06",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "There was a lot of good I could do if I had a seat at the table,[p/] but at the same time,[p/] was I really going to jump headfirst into this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0568703",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a [i]lot[/i]...[p/] I'll have to sit on it for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:079a84c",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Coraline![p/][s/] Wait!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0423579",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: Are you seriously going to put [i]that[/i] boy in the House of Lords?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07265c5",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: He [i]admitted[/i] that he's a cleric of the Theocracy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:007cfc7",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: He can't be trusted!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a30661",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: ...Shut up, Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eddd9",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: ...W-[p/][s/]What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cc026",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: C-[p/][s/]Coraline,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0cf62",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You and William orchestrated the death of hundreds of innocent people behind my back,[p/] and yet you feel nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:038f661",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: What is [i]wrong[/i] with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0561db5",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: W-[p/][s/]Well,[p/] it was really [i]William's[/i] idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:021011b",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: Don't give that trite."
}

{
  "id": "line:04af7e4",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You've been like this since we were children."
}

{
  "id": "line:0259814",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You always lick the boot of whoever you think is strongest and hide behind them like a snivelling child."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b84c8",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I may not use my voice,[p/] but you just parrot whoever is willing to put up with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4733f",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Lloyd: I-[p/][s/]I don't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfc3e3",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I can see the truth, even if [i]you[/i] can't."
}

{
  "id": "line:09faed0",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You aligned yourself with William because you were too much of a coward to go against him."
}

{
  "id": "line:025d1ac",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You justified it,[p/] using your little vendetta against Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:009fcc4",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: All because the Grand General executed Ophelia:[p/] the woman you never had the balls to even [i]try[/i] to win the heart of."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9fe89",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: You are pathetic,[p/] and I [i]personally[/i] hope the House of Lords votes to dismantle House von Sanctus piece by piece."
}

{
  "id": "line:027f33a",
  "node": "Check_Events_CommonRoomIntro",
  "text": "Coraline: I will [i]not[/i] make the mistake of trusting you again, Lloyd..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09018fe",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb9098",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: We're definitely lost."
}

{
  "id": "line:0023d88",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "We followed the Grand General's directions to the letter."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e81a6",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "We were expecting to arrive at some sort of noble estate or convention hall."
}

{
  "id": "line:0112ee4",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Instead,[p/] we found ourselves in the ruins of a long-forgotten city."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c540dd",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "The grass was overgrown.[p/] Moss was growing around the ruins."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f701b",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "It looked like no one had lived here for centuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:05be047",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I double-checked everything.[p/] The map even has that giant tree north of here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9daef",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: This [i]can't[/i] be the city of Ladon that Virgilae mentioned."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a885a",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: It doesn't look like [i]anyone's[/i] lived here in centuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c32c2",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait a minute..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b2159",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Did he give us the wrong location on [i]purpose[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d4092",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:0469240",
  "node": "Courtroom1",
  "text": "Lucio: Enough gawking.[p/] The trial will commence shortly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd0eab",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "He wasn't alone either.[p/] A division of the Kingsguard was marching behind him,[p/] forming a perimeter around Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0003141",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "It was difficult to tell if she was their liege or their prisoner."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a22de",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "A grey luminous sphere was centered on the prosecutor,[p/] following her as they made their way to one of the ruins."
}

{
  "id": "line:0388fd7",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "It had the same colour as most [b]abjuration[/b] spells.[p/] It must have been an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bf845",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]this[/i] is where we'll be hosting the trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fbec5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Lucio: Yes.[p/] The \"Archduke\" could never bring himself to stray far from this place for too long."
}

{
  "id": "line:0730024",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Lucio: I doubt a normal courtroom would be large enough anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2ba79",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Lucio: Kingsguard,[p/] bring the prisoner to the temple.[p/] I will have words with Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af360b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Lucio: That includes you, McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5795a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1",
  "text": "Celeste: I am [i]not[/i] leaving you alone with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c8a3f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste, it's fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfa9c3",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Celeste: But—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db548d",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can handle him.[p/] Just stay close by."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a728b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Her jaw tightened as she shifted around uneasily.[p/] Nevertheless,[p/] she stepped aside without any objections."
}

{
  "id": "line:0668018",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Lucio: No wonder she's so insubordinate.[p/] You keep such a loose leash around her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04030cf",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you want, Lucio?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e775c8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Lucio: The Archduke allowed you to serve as Prosecutor Steelwind's attorney.[p/] Why?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ca050",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I guess I earned his trust somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fa07d",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Lucio: Cuthbert,[p/] do you remember what I told you after Dracogen's trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:073b583",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Lucio: You are now going to be [i]my[/i] agent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c520d3",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Lucio: There will come a day when I will require your skills and abilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0911cf5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1b",
  "text": "Lucio: The Eye of Radiance is too powerful a weapon for me to squander.[p/] I imagine it will be of great use to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b0fba",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Lucio: You will now be acting on my orders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf5205",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you think I'd even consider throwing the trial for—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05951e6",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Lucio: I will come at you with everything I have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0997de9",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Lucio: Use your Eye of Radiance.[p/] Use every trick Tymora taught you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0226e3d",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Lucio: No matter who lies before you,[p/] cut them down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3f6b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Lucio: I will not accept victory without a proper fight from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cee18",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...So what is this to you—[p/]some kind of duel?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9cd48",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your [i]daughter's[/i] life hangs in the balance, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba368c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "Lucio: ...Follow my orders,[p/] or I'll have you executed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4e94c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_1c",
  "text": "I just glared at him as he made his way towards the temple."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abfaf5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "The ruins were filled with the nobles who were at the Grand Cathedral that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:09190e9",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "This temple was ancient.[p/] It was basically falling apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d18d9",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Moss had grown into every crevice.[p/] Insects were crawling everywhere.[p/] I even spotted a few rats at some point."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c08ac",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "The nobles present looked like they wanted to flee as far from this place as possible,[p/] but the Kingsguard blocked anyone trying to leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:035cbb1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "The Grand General's expression was blank but focused.[p/] He was acting like nothing was out of the ordinary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbc72d",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "He'd taken his position at the opposite end of the room.[p/] It seemed that he truly planned on prosecuting his daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:051e385",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Remus: Thank you all for coming here today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0160ad2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Remus: I appreciate your cooperation with our investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:079f6c0",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Gallery: Why have you brought us here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f5608",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Gallery: This place is [i]disgusting[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea312c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Remus: What happens here today must be kept away from prying eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf33cc",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Remus: I hope I don't need to remind you that whatever happens here today must never be discussed."
}

{
  "id": "line:037766c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Remus: But nevertheless...[p/] I welcome you all to my home."
}

{
  "id": "line:010aece",
  "node": "Courtroom1_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/][s/] You [i]live[/i] here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfc5e0",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: I do..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d0fc3",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Your Grace.[p/] Is this truly what you wish to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1c77",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "LucioC: There will be no going back after this."
}

{
  "id": "line:081f2c1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: I've made many mistakes in my lifetime..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a8261",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: I gave Wyverngarde the means to protect themselves,[p/] but grew bitter when seeing what I created."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4da53",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: I thought my best course of action was to stay in isolation and leave Wyverngarde to fend for itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0754aaa",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: ...I see now what a fool I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a9df1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: I abandoned my kin to survive in an unjust world,[p/] and now foreign powers have ingrained themselves in [i]my[/i] kingdom—[p/]all because of my negligence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1e32f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "\"Foreign powers\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e47830",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Did he [i]still[/i] suspect me of being an agent of the Theocracy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d1fd1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: Well, no more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0496892",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Remus: It's time that the people of Wyverngarde [i]and[/i] their enemies remember [i]who[/i] watches over them."
}

{
  "id": "line:025cd75",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "He raised his hand,[p/] magical light gathering in his palm."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cc7cd",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "The room began to shake more violently with every moment.[p/] It was as if he were commanding an earthquake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f639ee",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "I normally couldn't sense aether like Celeste and Aster,[p/] but even [i]I[/i] could feel the mass of energy in the room coalescing around him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f9c26",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/]What's going on?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:025dc7b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Several nobles in the gallery screamed out in terror.[p/] Some fell to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0211e00",
  "node": "Courtroom1_3",
  "text": "Whatever spell he was casting,[p/] it was unlike anything I'd ever seen before."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fd309",
  "node": "Courtroom1_4",
  "text": "A blinding light flooded into the room.[p/] I had to shield my eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e7795",
  "node": "Courtroom1_4",
  "text": "But as the light faded,[p/] I finally saw it.[p/] I finally saw him in his true form."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4ef2e",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02317f5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]It's a dragon!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b6d1c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "The gallery broke out into hysteria."
}

{
  "id": "line:016d49e",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Some of them kneeled in reverence to the ancient dragon.[p/] Some simply fell to the ground and cowered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0827751",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "I even saw some of them attempt to flee before they were shoved back by the knights guarding the exits."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dbcf8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Rath: This may not be a court,[p/] [i]but[/i] I will have order!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05daab1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...An ancient dragon."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cb6d9",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] You're the [i]last[/i] ancient dragon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5caca",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Rath: ...That is correct, heavensborn.[p/] I am the first Lord of Wyverngarde and descendant of the God of War."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6ebc8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Rath: I am Rathallion:[p/] the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbdbed",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Rath: \"Remus Virgilae\" is an alias I assume when I walk amongst your kind."
}

{
  "id": "line:048a317",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Rath: Until now,[p/] only the Lords of House Steelwind and the Kings of Wyverngarde have known my true identity,[p/] but I will hide no longer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9b808",
  "node": "Courtroom1_5",
  "text": "Rath: My will alone will determine how this trial ends."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e55e7a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to these legends,[p/] dragons can't die of old age.[p/] Presumably,[p/] he'd still be alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:08022f4",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "ERIS: I wouldn’t be surprised."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc7fbd",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "Eris: Despite everything,[p/] the kingdom includes him in our constitution."
}

{
  "id": "line:027da86",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "TYRION: Wait...[p/] Really?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fb42b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "ERIS: As the savior of our kingdom,[p/] he and his kin were given an honorary position in our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f00ef8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "ERIS: The Scaled Lord made Wyverngarde what it is today.[p/] He was given authority that befits such a legacy."
}

{
  "id": "line:036b04b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You're the only individual with the authority to convict [i]any[/i] and all of the nobles here."
}

{
  "id": "line:046f2f7",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "Rath: ...Make no mistake, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b35aa",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6",
  "text": "Rath: I will remain impartial regardless of what transpires here."
}

{
  "id": "line:067907b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Rath: I will not interfere in this trial,[p/] nor will I try to manipulate its outcome."
}

{
  "id": "line:028abe0",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Rath: I will only mediate its proceedings."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b25e9a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Rath: ...And pass judgment when necessary."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c160f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Rath: Even in my human form,[p/] I have [i]always[/i] had the strength of an ancient dragon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0894304",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Well, [i]that's[/i] certainly terrifying..."
}

{
  "id": "line:083bcd2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Rath: Now, then.[p/] With introductions out of the way,[p/] shall we proceed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffb9e1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "LucioC: Of course, Your Grace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c454b1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "LucioC: The prosecution is ready."
}

{
  "id": "line:097a362",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Dragons aside,[p/] this was like any other trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0723739",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Tyrion: The defense is also ready."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ad6b2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Rath: I'm sure we're all [i]thoroughly[/i] aware of why we've gathered here,[p/] but for the sake of doing this properly,[p/] could you please list the charges, Lucio?"
}

{
  "id": "line:019f7cd",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "LucioC: The defendant:[p/] Aria Steelwind,[p/] is charged with several counts of manslaughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3af5b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "LucioC: Her victims include many knights from the Kingsguard who remain unresponsive."
}

{
  "id": "line:06999bc",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "LucioC: And of course,[p/] there's Lloyd von Sanctus and Coraline Sibyl:[p/] the Duke of Commerce and the Minister of Justice, respectively."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff7b70",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Gallery: ...What is this farce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cc569",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Gallery: This trial has been over before it began."
}

{
  "id": "line:0672fa2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Gallery: Lady Steelwind clearly overestimated herself.[p/] Even a [i]child[/i] knows to be wary of Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e893d1",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Gallery: ...No![p/][s/] Don't you see?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:094d327",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Gallery: [i]This[/i] is Bahamut's judgment!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03af766",
  "node": "Courtroom1_6a",
  "text": "Gallery: The divine powers that be [i]clearly[/i] think she is unfit to rule at the king's side!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0189c43",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Might I remind the court of my [i]own[/i] testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0854438",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]witnessed[/i] Beatrice Frega enter the Prayer Room before I lost consciousness."
}

{
  "id": "line:000c57b",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Isn't it suspicious that this occurred around fifteen minutes [i]before[/i] Pierce's death?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c156c",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "LucioC: You only caught a glimpse of her.[p/] You don't know if it was someone [i]else[/i] disguised in an illusion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76952",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "LucioC: You didn't even speak to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07616fa",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's all the more reason to call her to the stand to explain herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0531c68",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "LucioC: She has already testified that she has no memories of what transpired during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe01f4",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "LucioC:  ...There is no need to drag this out any longer than necessary, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f169d5",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: My client [i]has[/i] a right to a fair trial,[p/] and Beatrice's involvement clearly implies [i]some[/i] greater plot!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0afc411",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Rath: Enough.[p/] I find Mr. Cuthbert's request to be reasonable."
}

{
  "id": "line:067c749",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Rath: I agree that Lady Frega's actions are quite suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:08dfc36",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "LucioC: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7e24a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "LucioC: Very well.[p/] Let the defense have its battle."
}

{
  "id": "line:033dca0",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "LucioC: I only hope for his sake that his blade strikes true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee28be",
  "node": "Courtroom1_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why is everything a combat metaphor with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d018b6",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice..."
}

{
  "id": "line:011a6e8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I'm glad you're safe, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d467ad",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not for lack of trying on your part..."
}

{
  "id": "line:008fa07",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: I have no memories of what I did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b610e9",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e29717",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: If I hurt you,[p/] I [i]am[/i] truly sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc622",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "She actually looked pretty sincere,[p/] but it wasn't as if this were the first time she's lied to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f03836",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: To be honest,[p/] I'm still a little doubtful about your \"memory loss\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d66bdd",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm not the only one who experienced it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aee156",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: Aria [i]also[/i] lost her memories of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb66ac",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "LucioC: ...And how would you know that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0285f16",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless.[p/] If you truly have no memories of what happened,[p/] could you testify about what you [i]do[/i] remember?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2eec2",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:088df56",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: I was with my sisters and my...[p/] guide,[p/] Eris Illmater."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e1c7a",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: I was speaking with them in the garden,[p/] when I suddenly felt ill and lost consciousness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b21fd0",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: When I woke up,[p/] my sisters found me.[p/] They said that I had gone missing for over an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0003e43",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: I was confused,[p/] but when I later heard what happened,[p/] I realized that someone must have taken control of my body."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ef438",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: I have no memories of what happened,[p/] and from what I understand,[p/] the same thing happened to Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a367a8",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "Beatrice: And to make matters worse,[p/] there's [i]nothing[/i] that indicates who may have controlled our actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1991f",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "...There was something [i]off[/i] about the way she was testifying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c000a3",
  "node": "Courtroom1_8",
  "text": "She was actually being a lot less vague than I was expecting.[p/] What was she doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00da5d8",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She's been missing since the massacre happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac9d78",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: I really hope she's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c652bc",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh, make no mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acabf6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: She's [i]definitely[/i] okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7df51",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What makes you so sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a6fef",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember [i]anything[/i] about what happened to her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07cda7b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...No,[p/] but it's just a feeling."
}

{
  "id": "line:0321583",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "LucioC: Enough about that peasant."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fd2ba",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "LucioC: Tell us what happened next, Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f62b9",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: If they were with you,[p/] shouldn't your sisters have noticed this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b1e81",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "LucioC: According to Laefe and Miriam,[p/] their pet dog was running amok in the hallways."
}

{
  "id": "line:092c7f5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "LucioC: They left the witness with Illmater to chase him down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df99ca",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "LucioC: And when the sisters returned to the garden,[p/] both Beatrice and Illmater were gone."
}

{
  "id": "line:058604f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember [i]anything[/i] after that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead620",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: I"
}

{
  "id": "line:0950c02",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: No...[p/] I really [i]want[/i] to remember,[p/] but I can't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd3415",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And you have [i]no[/i] memories of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc02a6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: No...[p/] None at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9a360",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: I can only imagine what I was forced to do while I was unconscious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0003667",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Forced\"...?[p/] What do you mean by that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5a2de",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: I was confused.[p/] But when I later heard what happened,[p/] I realized that someone must have taken control of my body."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e7b13",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you're [i]also[/i] saying that someone else controlled your body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:026e4ba",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Yes.[p/] It's the only explanation for why you saw me in the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:019aacf",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "LucioC: Absolutely ridiculous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbdc65",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "LucioC: You're clearly spinning a fairy tale to absolve yourself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4e867",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "I had no reason to trust her,[p/] so why did I feel like something was wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ac115",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Think what you will,[p/] but please believe me when I say—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e7f97",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: I have no memories of what happened.[p/] And from what I understand,[p/] the same thing happened to Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:051a644",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your statement [i]does[/i] match up with what happened to my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f28dfb",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But you clearly already [i]knew[/i] what happened to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb542e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: You could just be using that knowledge to fabricate an alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0097370",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I know it doesn't mean much coming from me,[p/] but I [i]am[/i] telling the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c445b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: That remains to be seen."
}

{
  "id": "line:00858e4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why would you even bring that up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbfbed",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Well,[p/] if you had evidence that someone [i]else[/i] was controlling us,[p/] it would exonerate both me [i]and[/i] Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:03206db",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: That would be the best-case scenario, wouldn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0995129",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d77503",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Beatrice: It's nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8fc5d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Her brow furrowed and creased in frustration."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7d041",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Player: Overflow"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f61761",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "The way she was testifying was a little bit strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e82b0",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "She immediately concluded that someone had taken control of her,[p/] and why was she bringing up what happened to Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d35d93",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Player: Objection"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7ddf4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Honor![p/][s/] It's clear that the witness's testimony is contradictory!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0641e17",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: And this piece of evidence proves it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00e5ba6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Rath: I fail to see how that proves anything, Mr. Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0873f82",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Beat",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] I guess you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:002cc8d",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "...Why would she say something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:005d70b",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "I found the contradiction,[p/] but she might as well have dropped it into my hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0540277",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Beatrice,[p/] you said there's no indication of who orchestrated this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac6711",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But there is [i]one[/i] piece of evidence that does just that,[p/] albeit loosely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0afdd",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...And what would that be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e30e2",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]This[/i] symbol..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0fa96",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "I pulled out the parchment that Aria gave me.[p/] It had the Purple Mark on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0fe15",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Beatrice: Marrunath...[p/] What are you doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a717c",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Marrunath: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aaea52",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:030afe8",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Beatrice: He's suppressing our connection."
}

{
  "id": "line:010e321",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "LucioC: ...\"Connection\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9783c",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Beatrice: I can't [i]actually[/i] see what you're trying to show me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a039f9",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Marrunath.[p/] Can you stop being petty and just let her see it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4459b",
  "node": "BeatObj",
  "text": "Marrunath: ...I don't take orders from you, heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c1bf3",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I wonder, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] What is on that parchment?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069bbf4",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You see, Beatrice,[p/] Aria has been investigating a string of murders throughout Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cb31d",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: These murders [i]appear[/i] to be unrelated,[p/] despite how gruesome they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e5daf",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But they all share one thing in common."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b2d3a",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]This[/i] symbol was found at each and every crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:042b17c",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: Don't tell me my daughter has roped you into her little conspiracy theory..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d0282",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: Your \"mind control\" defense would be laughable if it weren't downright insulting."
}

{
  "id": "line:028c164",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Grand General,[p/][s/] during the gap in Aria's memory,[p/] someone [i]placed[/i] this mark in her pocket!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dca681",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was clearly some sort of taunt from whoever orchestrated this."
}

{
  "id": "line:066aad2",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: Nonsense![p/] She clearly drew that symbol [i]herself[/i] during her psychotic episode!"
}

{
  "id": "line:030cd59",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: I've had to listen to her go on and on about her insane theory!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab281f",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: She was obsessed with it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0087ed2",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Aren't you curious about what just happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fc611",
  "node": "BeatObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080ca50",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Think about it.[p/] Why did"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c656f",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Beatrice: My apologies.[p/] I don't know why I said that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0974014",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...[p/][s/]Ugh."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ed9b6",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Her frustration was rising with each word she said."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecb6ef",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is everything okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a751b7",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Yes...[p/] I'm [i]perfectly[/i] fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d0c5f",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Anyways,[p/] it looks like you'll have to figure the rest out on your own."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b947d",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Figure out the rest on my own\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2e949",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: Your Grace![p/][s/] These two are making a mockery of us by spouting these [i]insane[/i] theories!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0475e4d",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: The defense clearly has no case![p/][s/] End this at once!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db36cd",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Rath: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09108c5",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Rath: ...Considering what I know,[p/] I'd like to indulge this theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:081b68b",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "The judge was finally giving me a chance for once.[p/] [i]That[/i] was a first."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6c51a",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Beatrice had been acting strangely since the trial began..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8193b",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "It was suspicious,[p/] but not in the way that seems to implicate her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be5804",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "It's almost like...[p/] She was [i]intentionally[/i] trying to bring something to my attention."
}

{
  "id": "line:055dd67",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3d14",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "...I decided to pull on this thread a little."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe0ec5",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "She just asked me if I was \"curious about what just happened\",[p/] but every time I asked her to elaborate,[p/] she said nothing..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc201",
  "node": "BeatObj3",
  "text": "Whatever she was trying to draw my attention to,[p/] it had to be significant in some way."
}

{
  "id": "line:028e1d3",
  "node": "BeatObj4",
  "text": "No...[p/] Beatrice was trying to draw your attention to something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0779f53",
  "node": "BeatObj4",
  "text": "What just happened that was worth thinking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3258f",
  "node": "BeatObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath...[p/] He didn't allow Beatrice to see the Purple Mark."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6fff4",
  "node": "BeatObj5",
  "text": "He'd only do that if Beatrice [i]would[/i] recognize it normally."
}

{
  "id": "line:083a5ac",
  "node": "BeatObj5",
  "text": "Marrunath is her familiar and he [i]used[/i] to follow her orders,[p/] but things have clearly changed now that she belongs to the \"Empress of Discord\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:014095b",
  "node": "BeatObj5",
  "text": "So why would a demon like Marrunath interfere like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0459d00",
  "node": "BeatObj6",
  "text": "No...[p/] There was a common thread here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0987f42",
  "node": "BeatObj6",
  "text": "First,[p/] Beatrice seemed to know about the Purple Mark that Aria had been investigating."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aab6a",
  "node": "BeatObj6",
  "text": "Second,[p/] Marrunath is [i]preventing[/i] Beatrice from seeing it,[p/] and he's a demon who [i]wouldn't[/i] personally care about the politics of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a2002",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "The Purple Mark must be related to a demon somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f44a78",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "That's the only explanation as to why he would prevent her from seeing the Mark..."
}

{
  "id": "line:079a30d",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "But Aria had been investigating murders [i]throughout[/i] Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a9e85",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "Did that mean that her investigation [i]also[/i] had something to do with a demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b38309",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "...Aria suspected that each of the murderers in those cases was acting against their will."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cf3e4",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "And in this case,[p/] both Aria and Beatrice were [i]also[/i] claiming they were controlled."
}

{
  "id": "line:078426d",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "I couldn't explain what happened to Aria and these other individuals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0108776",
  "node": "BeatObj7",
  "text": "But I did know why [i]Beatrice[/i] might not have full control of her actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:08326e1",
  "node": "BeatObj8",
  "text": "No...[p/] The ability to control people's minds is nothing I've ever encountered before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa2474",
  "node": "BeatObj8",
  "text": "However,[p/] I didn't know much about demons outside of the Empress of Discord's Contract with Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3d1cf",
  "node": "BeatObj8",
  "text": "Was there something a demon could do to compel another person to act a certain way?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b4bf6",
  "node": "BeatObj9",
  "text": "I recalled what was written on Beatrice's contract during her trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:081fc49",
  "node": "BeatObj9",
  "text": "It said what would happen if she failed to claim House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f48d46",
  "node": "BeatObj9",
  "text": "Her soul,[p/] her [i]mind[/i],[p/] and her life would all be claimed by the Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a852cd",
  "node": "BeatObj9",
  "text": "If this \"Empress of Discord\" owned Beatrice's \"mind\",[p/] would that mean they could also control Beatrice against her will?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0daeff1",
  "node": "BeatObj9",
  "text": "But if that were true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d40410",
  "node": "BeatObj10",
  "text": "No...[p/] I potentially had an explanation for how Beatrice may have been controlled against her will."
}

{
  "id": "line:086682d",
  "node": "BeatObj10",
  "text": "But if I followed that logic,[p/] it revealed a grim conclusion for Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0babce7",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "No...[p/] That couldn't be right,[p/] could it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e5e41",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "Why would Aria do that...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d73a63",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "...But it was the conclusion that made the most sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0299160",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "I couldn't think of any [i]other[/i] way someone could control her against her will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e051c2",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "...And there [i]was[/i] one way to find out for certain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d966b2",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "The Divine Edict.[p/] That same ability I used against Beatrice during [i]her[/i] trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0178b22",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "I didn't fully comprehend it at the time,[p/] but I now had some understanding of how it worked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab6339",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "It created a copy of a Blood Contract between a contract holder and the demon who created it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7310f",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "But for it to work,[p/] I needed to know the name of the contract holder and the name of the demon who drafted it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09599cc",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "Right now,[p/] I was relying on speculation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f88983",
  "node": "BeatObj11",
  "text": "But going off of what I knew,[p/] the demon who made the contract must be..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0443442",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "0"
}

{
  "id": "line:0579689",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "1"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b27aa2",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "No...[p/] Marrunath was constantly around Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e762d",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "Whoever made this contract with Aria probably made contracts with each of the murderers in this conspiracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:023b97f",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "The Purple Mark must be some sort of symbol of that demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a25a5e",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "...And going off of what I'd deduced so far,[p/] Beatrice would recognize that mark."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d4930",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "2"
}

{
  "id": "line:085cc58",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "What...?[p/] Why would I even—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b3a8a",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "As far as I knew,[p/] Eugene the monkey was [i]not[/i] a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0738f77",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "There was a far more reasonable guess."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c53b7",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "3"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5baf1",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "There was apparently an entire hellish plane [i]filled[/i] with demons."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d7ade",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "So it's possible that the demon involved is one I'd never heard of before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf53bf",
  "node": "BeatObj12",
  "text": "But even so,[p/] there'd be no harm in taking a guess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbb3fd",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "The so-called \"Empress of Discord\"..."
}

{
  "id": "line:001a963",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "She was mentioned in Beatrice's Blood Contract,[p/] but I still had no idea who or [i]what[/i] she was."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f7c14",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "However,[p/] she was mentioned in a Blood Contract created by Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f3342",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Was Marrunath her subordinate in some way?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b53d4c",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "That [i]might[/i] explain why Marrunath didn't want Beatrice to identify the Purple Mark."
}

{
  "id": "line:024b1f6",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "I wasn't sure if a pseudonym was enough,[p/] but it was the closest I could get with what I knew so far."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e0f35",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Rath: ...You've been awfully quiet for a while, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:036a759",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: He's probably imagining [i]new[/i] ways to futilely stall for time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3b7d5",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think...[p/] I've finally figured out [i]why[/i] the witness and the defendant can't remember anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0398d90",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: And it would also explain why they didn't have control of their actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b44cc",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: Hmph...[p/] Again with this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c36421",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: If you're so convinced of my daughter's conspiracy,[p/] why don't you prove it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:089f1a8",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ca221",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: Hmph...[p/][s/] I knew it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09edbba",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: Even [i]you[/i] don't believe in the nonsense you're spouting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8fc53",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lord Steelwind...[p/] I want to be wrong about this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db6f72",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If I'm right,[p/] the implications don't bode well for [i]anyone[/i] involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e23c1",
  "node": "BeatObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: So instead of [i]telling[/i] you,[p/] I think it would be better to show you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed8d15",
  "node": "BeatObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Empress of Discord![p/][s/] Wherever you may hide!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0019af1",
  "node": "BeatObj14",
  "text": "Marrunath: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af9d8c",
  "node": "BeatObj14",
  "text": "Beatrice: It's about time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3b56d",
  "node": "BeatObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the Eye of Horus,[p/][s/] I issue upon you a divine edict!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf81a7",
  "node": "BeatObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Release thy guards and manifest your Blood Contract with Aria Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0861718",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Rath: No...[p/] This [i]can't[/i] be true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:084994e",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "LucioC: This is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0389593",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Rath: Enough![p/][s/] Stop prattling amongst yourself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:084a3b4",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "LucioC: No![p/][s/] This is a sham!"
}

{
  "id": "line:078c985",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "LucioC: This [i]wretch[/i] has used magic to create a convincing fabrication!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012d8b6",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Rath: ...It's genuine, Lucio.[p/] I can sense it."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e6930",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Rath: It's impossible to falsify something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8a34f",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't deny the truth anymore, Grand General."
}

{
  "id": "line:059bf85",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: There [i]is[/i] a way to control someone else's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a3da0",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria Steelwind wasn't affected by Mageblight!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0249dc4",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: She was controlled against her will,[p/][s/] and her memories were overwritten!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f80f0d",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Rath: ...With this evidence,[p/] there's no doubt that Aria [i]did[/i] sign a Blood Contract,[p/] but it still doesn't make sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c2ff6",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: I agree..."
}

{
  "id": "line:001f3c3",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even [i]if[/i] Aria was the type of person to make a deal with a demon..."
}

{
  "id": "line:070e7d6",
  "node": "BeatObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: There isn't a single part of this contract that benefits her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3deb4",
  "node": "BeatObj16",
  "text": "No...[p/] Aria would never make a contract with a demon willingly."
}

{
  "id": "line:078ed11",
  "node": "BeatObj16",
  "text": "Even if she did,[p/] [i]no one[/i] would ever agree to terms like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0633161",
  "node": "BeatObj16",
  "text": "There was only one explanation for why she would sign this."
}

{
  "id": "line:060555d",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a large empty space above the terms of your daughter's contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:01868b5",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: When I issue a Divine Edict,[p/] it creates a copy of the Blood Contract that I call for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0a70e",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think when she was given this contract,[p/] it probably looked like something entirely different."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6f09d",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Something [i]else[/i] was written in this empty space to make it look like a normal legal document."
}

{
  "id": "line:0623e37",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means that my client was [i]not[/i] in control of her actions that day!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0982004",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: Enough of this![p/][s/] [i]All[/i] of you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae2ff6",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you see now, Grand General?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b82ddc",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your daughter was not responsible for what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fb633",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: [i]That[/i] remains to be proven."
}

{
  "id": "line:007fe90",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you [i]talking[/i] about?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03227bc",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: She has a Blood Contract that relinquishes control of her free will!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09964fc",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: Not having control and not being responsible are two [i]very[/i] different things, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a99f4",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ca7b9",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: I'll admit...[p/] The defendant may not have had control of her actions when she murdered the victims."
}

{
  "id": "line:051101b",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: ...[i]However[/i], she [i]did[/i] have full control of herself when she [i]signed[/i] this Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0096b80",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you serious?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdddd3",
  "node": "BeatObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: No one in their right mind would [i]willingly[/i] sign a Contract like this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:090df1e",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: ...And what of Beatrice Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb2460",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: Was [i]she[/i] in her right mind when she made a Contract with the demon Marrunath?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042a17c",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:069a49c",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: If we can't hold the defendant responsible,[p/] [i]surely[/i] we should also acquit Lady Frega for the murder of her father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fb407",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "Tyrion: T-[p/][s/]That's [i]hardly[/i] the same thing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:038045d",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: [i]I[/i], for one, fail to see the difference."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c71e6c",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: A fool made a deal with a demon,[p/] and as a result several esteemed members of the nobility were killed."
}

{
  "id": "line:000ed46",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's your [i]daughter[/i], Lucio!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf3f7c",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: And how does [i]that[/i] change anything?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c2ffd",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "...He seriously doesn't care if he convicts Aria.[p/] What kind of father is he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ca53e",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: Honestly...[p/] This only places [i]more[/i] responsibility on her for what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:09720a3",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: I could have [i]accepted[/i] if she had been reckless and [i]accidentally[/i] induced Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a210a3",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: But to sign a Contract with a [i]demon[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffd6b9",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: That only further espouses the need to [i]put her down[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0569495",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "Tyrion: She was clearly [i]tricked[/i], Lucio!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022e5b7",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: Is that so?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02443f1",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: She's an attorney just like you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0202cdd",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: Would you really sign a Contract without [i]carefully[/i] inspecting it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2facb",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09db317",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: Whether it was through foolishness,[p/] negligence,[p/] or both."
}

{
  "id": "line:0168b4e",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: The defendant willingly signed a Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ab8b1",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: She compromised herself,[p/] and as a result,[p/] three people died,[p/] and many more were incapacitated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d03939",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "LucioC: The responsibility falls [i]squarely[/i] on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0107572",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dddf97",
  "node": "BeatObj17a",
  "text": "Even if she willingly signed that Contract,[p/] that wasn't entirely true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a59592",
  "node": "BeatObj17b",
  "text": "No...[p/] I couldn't really disprove what he was saying,[p/] even if it was completely outrageous."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eaa11",
  "node": "BeatObj17b",
  "text": "Objectively,[p/] I couldn't prove that Aria didn't willingly sign that Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0119602",
  "node": "BeatObj17b",
  "text": "But even if I admitted that,[p/] there was [i]someone[/i] else involved that was clearly acting with malice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0854c0a",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio![p/][s/] There's clearly someone else to blame for Aria's actions that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fd7ba",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "LucioC: Oh?[p/] And who would that be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0610ecc",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd like to reread my client's Blood Contract to the court."
}

{
  "id": "line:04faf15",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"By signing this contract,[p/] Aria Steelwind surrenders her mind,[p/] body,[p/] and soul to the Patron.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:022ff95",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That[/i] can only mean one thing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdc8b0",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever this Patron is,[p/][s/] [i]they[/i] took control of my client and [i]used[/i] her to murder the victims!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0208fe5",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Gallery: T-[p/][s/]That's right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6b0c0",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Gallery: They could still be out there!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8b4ad",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Gallery: None of us is safe until this \"Patron\" is apprehended!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8a2b1",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Surely[/i] we can't end this trial while every member of the Wyverngarde nobility is in danger."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fd231",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "LucioC: Hmph..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06150f0",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Rath: I'm compelled to agree with Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8e088",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Rath: Trickery or not,[p/] it's clear [i]someone[/i] wished ill intent."
}

{
  "id": "line:021fff8",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And until we know [i]who[/i] this Patron is,[p/] you can't pass judgment on my client."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b889e",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not until we know the circumstances under which she signed that Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4bf4a",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "LucioC: ...And what would [i]you[/i] have us do, Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07da590",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "LucioC: The Contract has no stipulations about proximity or [i]how[/i] this mind control works."
}

{
  "id": "line:00827d6",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "LucioC: For all we know,[p/] this \"Patron\" could have murdered the victims all while sitting in their very home."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db9327",
  "node": "BeatObj17c",
  "text": "Tyrion: There was a clear intent behind this attack."
}

{
  "id": "line:0767f44",
  "node": "BeatObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even [i]if[/i] the Patron didn't directly participate in the murders,[p/] they definitely had a motive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e65603",
  "node": "BeatObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Aria was being controlled,[p/] then we can analyze her behavior to determine [i]who[/i] was controlling her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c7adb",
  "node": "BeatObj18",
  "text": "Rath: I see..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bb869",
  "node": "BeatObj18",
  "text": "Rath: Despite the questions raised,[p/] we've clearly made some headway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a75285",
  "node": "BeatObj18",
  "text": "Rath: I believe we should take a brief \"recess\" to process these revelations."
}

{
  "id": "line:016266d",
  "node": "BeatObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaeb26",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "We stepped outside the Scaled Lord's lair to get some fresh air."
}

{
  "id": "line:0322c09",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "I did a few stretches and some breathing exercises—[p/]anything to take my mind off of what had been revealed."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bc504",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "Celeste silently sat on a rock near the ruins,[p/] her eyes looking down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f52c9a",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "Aria had become a close friend of hers over the last few months.[p/] She was probably taking this harder than anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:02188d9",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "Celeste: Aria...[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a24335",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm so sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ada979",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "Aria: ...Don't be.[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:006e3f3",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "She couldn't find the words.[p/] She just sighed and sat down next to Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ccd83",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "She'd always been stoic,[p/] but it was clear even [i]she[/i] has her breaking point."
}

{
  "id": "line:03611d6",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't imagine what you're feeling right now,[p/] but it's not as hopeless as it looks."
}

{
  "id": "line:052618d",
  "node": "Interm1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we can find out who did this to you,[p/] we can still save you."
}

{
  "id": "line:098cbe4",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember if you've signed [i]anything[/i] recently?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00255d2",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Aria: N-[p/][s/]No,[p/] I don't..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d9330",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Damn it all...[p/] For all we knew,[p/] it could have been [i]any[/i] of the documents she signed while she was doing her job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0377830",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Aria: I still don't understand.[p/] I would never be that careless."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a5819",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] As much as I hate to admit it,[p/] Lucio was right."
}

{
  "id": "line:07de0e5",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're an attorney like me.[p/] We always carefully look over contracts before we sign them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b53a5d",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Aria: I just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae3941",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron can control your memories, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4ecd4",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Tyrion: For all we know,[p/] they could have used any number of tactics to coerce you into signing that Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9204d",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Aria: I suppose that's possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bce1dc",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:014775d",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "As we were deliberating amongst ourselves,[p/] the Grand General approached us alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca026b",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What are [i]you[/i] doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e82acc",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Aria: ...Father."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b3ffe",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "Lucio: ... [h=\"\" e=\"asf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:028d12e",
  "node": "Interm2",
  "text": "He only glared at Aria silently before walking away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1c26a",
  "node": "Interm3",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't believe him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a85c90",
  "node": "Interm3",
  "text": "His actions said otherwise,[p/] but I could've sworn I saw something through the Eye."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2dd89",
  "node": "Interm3",
  "text": "...Well,[p/] no matter what he felt internally,[p/] he made it clear that he wouldn't relent.[p/] He was my enemy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee63db",
  "node": "Interm3",
  "text": "[i]Whatever[/i] his motivations are,[p/] I'd overcome him—[p/]just like everyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:06aebbc",
  "node": "Interm3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should also head back, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f38812",
  "node": "Interm3",
  "text": "Celeste: Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d3d88",
  "node": "Courtroom1B",
  "text": "Rath: Court is now resumed.[p/] Shall we pick up where we carried off?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe4957",
  "node": "Courtroom1B",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Grace,[p/] I think we should review what we [i]do[/i] know about the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf0dbb",
  "node": "Courtroom1B",
  "text": "LucioC: ...We [i]do[/i] have a plethora of witnesses to work with."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b370e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's start from the beginning."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b1c04",
  "node": "Courtroom1B",
  "text": "Tyrion: It all began at noon yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0debb1a",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was at my house in Ratholme with Aria and my bodyguard:[p/] Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aead73",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was speaking with them when a courier suddenly delivered a letter to my home."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b4402",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was from Garrick Pierce.[p/] He wanted to meet with me and Celeste at the Grand Cathedral of the Scaled Lord at 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b50b2",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: To make sure we were on time,[p/] we arrived at the Grand Cathedral at 1:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:042c742",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: At the time,[p/] we didn't know that the cathedral was closed to the public."
}

{
  "id": "line:0742972",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the knights guarding the cathedral allowed us through anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8c2d3",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Apparently,[p/] they were expecting us."
}

{
  "id": "line:02502ab",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Which should [i]not[/i] have happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:043bd36",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "LucioC: Due to the solemnity of the situation,[p/] we were very particular about who was permitted to enter the cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edd784",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's possible someone pulled some strings to let us through."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f21827",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "LucioC: ...[i]Or[/i] you two entered the Cathedral illegally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0744e44",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "LucioC: I know about [i]every[/i] order given to the Kingsguard,[p/] and [i]none[/i] of them were told to let you two through."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cb1e5",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Tell me, Lucio,[p/] were the knights stationed at the entrance among the knights who fell comatose?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092a4b6",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Rath: Perhaps we should continue..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0384abd",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We arrived at the church and spent the next hour sightseeing before we went to meet with Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:006edcb",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: In that time,[p/] we met with the Archduke,[p/] Grand General,[p/] my client,[p/] His Majesty,[p/] and Prince Alaric."
}

{
  "id": "line:057866e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And around that time,[p/] Aria and Aster left together to meet with the High Speaker in his quarters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba1868",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: While exploring the cathedral,[p/] we spoke with the Duke of Commerce and Minister of Justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:082697b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then we spoke with the three Frega sisters and Eris Illmater."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de12c4",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "LucioC: Eris Illmater?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab0b18",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's a friend of Beatrice Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:040bb73",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Kingsguard wouldn't let her bring Marrunath into the cathedral,[p/] so she brought Eris to guide her instead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa04fd",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_3",
  "text": "LucioC: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cffdfc",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] we left the garden at around 1:45 PM to meet with Pierce in the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5ee5a",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And at around the same time,[p/] Aria left her meeting with the High Speaker and felt nauseous."
}

{
  "id": "line:013f1f6",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The last thing she remembers is looking at Lake Galakrond over the west balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2a773",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "LucioC: A [i]likely[/i] story."
}

{
  "id": "line:043f01d",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Regardless[/i],[p/] at 2:00 PM,[p/] Aster went to pay respects to his father's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d1a90",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Unbeknownst to him,[p/] a mage had placed a [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b] in front of his father's coffin."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f978d",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was set to trap him within a [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f62ca2",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Rath: What a despicable act..."
}

{
  "id": "line:076a11a",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "LucioC: Considering what followed,[p/] the attack on His Majesty must have been a diversion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0931d3c",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was also at this time that both Beatrice and Eris went missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f631b9",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering the timing of it all,[p/] someone must have taken control of Beatrice's body [i]after[/i] the trap on Aster was sprung."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a72da",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_4",
  "text": "LucioC: ...And are you saying this \"Patron\" controlled [i]her[/i] as well?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0919dda",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/] I don't think so..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e926aa",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to her Contract,[p/] her mind belongs to the Empress of Discord,[p/] not the Patron."
}

{
  "id": "line:0873b29",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Furthermore,[p/] Aria's Blood Contract was [i]created[/i] by the Empress."
}

{
  "id": "line:074015a",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I believe the Patron and the Empress [i]were[/i] in league with each other,[p/] but they were two distinct individuals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0727d2b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Wonderful.[p/] [i]Another[/i] demon we have to worry about."
}

{
  "id": "line:003ce83",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: At that moment,[p/] the Patron and the Empress had all of the pieces they needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e0534",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's when they began the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0077ede",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron took control of Aria's body,[p/] and von Sanctus was murdered at 2:05 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b64469",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whether it was intentional or an accident,[p/] oil was spilt from the lanterns in the Common Room and a fire started."
}

{
  "id": "line:0988ae3",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Since von Sanctus's body was found there,[p/] this must have happened after he was murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0962ba4",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Shortly after,[p/] Prince Alaric spotted smoke from the fire and asked Aria what was going on."
}

{
  "id": "line:09124a6",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria responded by using an unknown [b]transmutation[/b] spell to incapacitate him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d84705",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "LucioC: To think they would use her to attack the prince as well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb3d55",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Luckily,[p/] the effects of that spell were only temporary,[p/] and Alaric came out unharmed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0964fbc",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: After this,[p/] the Patron used Aria to murder Sibyl at 2:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6c2e9",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: She brought Sibyl's body to the westward balcony,[p/] where she dumped it into Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:004f553",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: High Speaker Archeus witnessed this,[p/] but he wasn't aware of what she'd thrown off the balcony until much later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8cd93",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The High Speaker thought this encounter was strange,[p/] but he continued with his business."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d093f",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: He headed to the Prayer Room,[p/] but was turned away by the knights standing guard there."
}

{
  "id": "line:033b002",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Meanwhile,[p/] Celeste and I were speaking with Lord Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:06df200",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: When we showed up for the meeting earlier,[p/] he was clearly expecting someone else to show up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0813f04",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: We tried to get to the bottom of what was happening,[p/] but he refused to answer our questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b52b6",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: And at about 2:20 PM we heard a commotion outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cd8e7",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste went to investigate."
}

{
  "id": "line:060377b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And that's when Celeste fought Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f61b5f",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron's target was Garrick Pierce,[p/] but Celeste was too powerful to neutralize."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1128e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: They fought each other for about fifteen minutes before Aria was finally able to push past her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e3ff6",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: During their fight,[p/] the Empress sent Beatrice into the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbeb85",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: She probably had Beatrice cast [b]Invisibility[/b] to move undetected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdad2a",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: She then used her to cast a [b]Sleep[/b] spell on Pierce and me to knock us out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a994a9",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I remember checking the time close to when this happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0670d7b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: This must have happened at 2:30 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:04831dc",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "LucioC: ...If your testimony is correct,[p/] Beatrice Frega was actively used in this plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6ace3",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes,[p/] and considering how quickly the massacre unfolded,[p/] the Empress must have been coordinating with the Patron."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dc721",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering how oddly some of the knights were acting,[p/] it's possible they had other accomplices too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d04b45",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: They probably planned how they would use Beatrice and Aria to carry out the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:046170e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] after Beatrice knocked us out,[p/] Aria finally pushed past Celeste and entered the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fec4f",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: And before Celeste could catch up to her,[p/] she had already murdered Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da4441",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria and I were already unconscious by the time Celeste entered the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d05e4",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron had already achieved their goal of murdering the three nobles."
}

{
  "id": "line:0393c94",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: So she probably fell unconscious when they released their control over her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c094",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria and I regained consciousness shortly after."
}

{
  "id": "line:0377319",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's when the Inquisition arrested her for the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fc2b6",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "LucioC: Hm...[p/] Lord Pierce was one of the victims."
}

{
  "id": "line:082cd50",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "LucioC: Your meeting clearly had more significance than I'd realized."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea606e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "LucioC: So tell us, Cuthbert.[p/][s/] What was your discussion about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6cad3",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...It's fine.[p/] You can tell them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d4a4",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Alright..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1374e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...For the past few months,[p/] Celeste and I have been investigating who her birth parents are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdd386",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "LucioC: Hmph...[p/] I recall receiving many complaints about her during the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:05613fc",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Supposedly,[p/] Garrick Pierce had the information we were looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c281b7",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: That letter he sent us said that he wanted to \"trade this information for his freedom\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc80da",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]assumed[/i] this meant that he wanted me to be his attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0105ed5",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "LucioC: Do you honestly expect us to believe that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08dd3f3",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "LucioC: Why would he ask for help from the attorney who indicted him in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a6241",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]We[/i] thought the same thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:013c9de",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: And when we arrived for the meeting,[p/] it was clear [i]I[/i] wasn't the intended recipient."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c61cc",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: This means that Pierce sent that letter to someone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7628e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "LucioC: ...You better not be lying to us, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0993ee8",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Frankly,[p/] I don't much care if you believe me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba58e3",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless,[p/] if we examine every action Aria took,[p/] we can build a psychological profile of the Patron."
}

{
  "id": "line:09addb8",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "LucioC: Hm...[p/] One [i]can[/i] often learn a lot about a person by how they approach combat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec96fb",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: To begin,[p/] the defense would like to call the Commander White to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a172b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: His testimony might shed some light on how von Sanctus and Sibyl died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0901528",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Despite all these witness accounts,[p/] we still only know how [i]Pierce[/i] was murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0149071",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "LucioC: Yes...[p/] He was impaled using a blade magically frozen from his own blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:078889b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "In a grim sort of way,[p/] it was almost poetic that he died the same way Flinhart did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d677a4",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "...But I doubted that gave Celeste any kind of closure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bede44",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] we need to find out [i]exactly[/i] how Aria murdered von Sanctus and Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:098e144",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Tyrion: The massacre was swift and efficient.[p/] It must've required a lot of forethought and coordination."
}

{
  "id": "line:062c4fe",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we figure out who might've had this knowledge,[p/] we might be able to find out who did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:034b56b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "LucioC: Kingsguard![p/][s/] Escort Commander Orym White to the witness stand!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d7e70",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "LucioC: Witness.[p/] Please state your name and occupation."
}

{
  "id": "line:023df9d",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Orym: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/][s/] I—[p/][s/] Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d1630",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Orym: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd6a2b",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bbaf0",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Orym: I'm sorry![p/][s/] I just can't do this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0585fc6",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Orym: How am I supposed to act like this is normal?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfd7d1",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Orym: A giant lizard is standing [i]right[/i] behind me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0956b52",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_10",
  "text": "Rath: ...Calling me a lizard is [i]highly[/i] offensive, Commander."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ab436",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Orym: S-[p/][s/]Sorry, your scaled lordship...[p/] sir..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fd9a4",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander...[p/] Just try your best to testify about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:05380ac",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Orym: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a48bc3",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Orym: It all started when we received a report from the Kingsguard.[p/] The prosecutor attacked Prince Alaric and a fire had broken out in the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bb102",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Orym: We weren't sure what the deal with Steelwind was.[p/] So we went to the Common Room to put out the fire."
}

{
  "id": "line:0964e0e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Orym: But when we got there,[p/] we noticed a bunch of unconscious knights in front of the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff32e",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Orym: We went to the Prayer Room.[p/] That's when we found Steelwind and Cuthbert unconscious next to Pierce's dead body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5e903",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_11",
  "text": "Orym: We later found the bodies of von Sanctus and Sibyl, too.[p/] That's when we realized that she offed all three of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0324d30",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_12",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you still have no idea how Steelwind was used to murder von Sanctus or Sibyl?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0938a82",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_12",
  "text": "Orym: Not a clue."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7884c",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_12",
  "text": "Orym: It's especially worse for von Sanctus.[p/] That fire burned a lot of the physical evidence off of his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:085a355",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_12",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about Sibyl?[p/] Was there any physical evidence on her body?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ffdac",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_12",
  "text": "Orym: No idea about that either.[p/] She didn't have any wounds either."
}

{
  "id": "line:03967b0",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_12",
  "text": "Orym: All we know is that she died of suffocation."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c9560",
  "node": "Courtroom1B_12",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] There was definitely more information I could glean from their investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0432bbb",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: It all started when we received a report from the Kingsguard.[p/] The prosecutor attacked Prince Alaric,[p/] and a fire had broken out in the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:058b625",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: And this is mainly based on Prince Alaric's testimony.[p/] Am I correct?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a4b45",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] We still have no idea which [b]transmutation[/b] spell she hit him with."
}

{
  "id": "line:0742256",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Judging from the time of the report,[p/] this must have been well after all three of the murders occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e4238",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] It was unfortunate how that played out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0025cff",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: If Steelwind really [i]was[/i] controlled,[p/] whoever controlled her knew how to get the job done quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:032590a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "That left the question of [i]how[/i] they did this so efficiently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f34efd",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was that wise?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbd79a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless of who it was,[p/] someone assaulted a Prince of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7cb6e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: We were already dealing with the King who was trapped in that [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:082e065",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Honestly,[p/] a [i]lot[/i] happened in that hour,[p/] and most of our attention was focused on keeping the royal family safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:069f456",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: We can already conclude that the attack on the King was a distraction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd4c10",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: Whoever orchestrated this must have known we'd focus our attention on keeping him safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0365fb2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "The casualties included many knights from the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:070a6db",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "They probably had to spread their forces thin to protect everyone else [i]and[/i] handle the fire in the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca5c2e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: What did you do when you arrived at the Common Room, Commander?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f78abc",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: When we got there,[p/] we noticed a bunch of unconscious knights in front of the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:003d395",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see Aria or Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0afa4ad",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: No...[p/] We only saw the aftermath of their fight."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b0414",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: There were marks and craters everywhere in that hallway."
}

{
  "id": "line:099164e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: Pierce's time of death was 2:45 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0858b67",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: And the knights didn't arrive at the Common Room until 3:10 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0246426",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: They didn't arrive at the Prayer Room until well after the battle had taken place."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e4263",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Wouldn't that mean you were in that room with Pierce's body for twenty-five minutes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8956d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why didn't you look for help?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0108ea1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]You weren't waking up for some reason,[p/] so I kept channeling my healing magic into you."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c9114",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: Looking back,[p/] I probably should have just looked for help."
}

{
  "id": "line:00556c1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: But even if Aria was unconscious,[p/] I didn't want to leave you alone in that room with her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab3cb2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:094b7be",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Judging from the timing,[p/] this would have been several minutes after he'd already died."
}

{
  "id": "line:05416bf",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah,[p/] And we had no idea what was going on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0874a3c",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Pierce was already dead,[p/] and you and Steelwind were unresponsive."
}

{
  "id": "line:009ea75",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can see why [i]I'd[/i] be unresponsive.[p/] I was hit with a spell specifically designed to make people sleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:084b405",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: But why was Aria unconscious too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b16fab",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: We have no idea.[p/] We've never even [i]heard[/i] of demonic possession until today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e43d70",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: For all we know,[p/] it could've all been a side effect of being controlled for over an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0930e52",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] That last statement was a little vague."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d85b2b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Steelwind must have attacked von Sanctus in the Common Room and suffocated him somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fae762",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: And due to the lack of physical evidence,[p/] you're not sure what she used."
}

{
  "id": "line:06031af",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: Von Sanctus and Sibyl both died via suffocation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8b429",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: We can probably assume that the Patron used the same method to murder both of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3e593",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Well, you know what they say about assuming."
}

{
  "id": "line:0136da9",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Don't be cute, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:025fed7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not like he can help it."
}

{
  "id": "line:022e3a7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "...[i]Anyways[/i],[p/] Lucio's assumption [i]did[/i] make sense,[p/] but I didn't want to jump to conclusions yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed2c1d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] was [i]von Sanctus[/i] the victim I wanted to focus on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1899",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: From the burns on his body,[p/] she must have hit him with a [b]Fire Bolt[/b] to keep him from getting away.[p/] He didn't have anything to defend himself with."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c2a16",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] [b]Fire Bolt[/b] [i]is[/i] in her [b]Spell Compendium[/b],[p/] and I doubt von Sanctus was much of a fighter."
}

{
  "id": "line:089c302",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] The poor sap didn't have a chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:031914c",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: He must have been in immense pain from that attack."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d32abd",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Steelwind must have attacked Sibyl somewhere close to that balcony.[p/] And going by the autopsy report,[p/] she must have suffocated her somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:035e71f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: And since someone cast [b]Mend Wounds[/b] on the body,[p/] we still don't know how."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5dff2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] It's going to be a real headache figuring that out."
}

{
  "id": "line:095accb",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "No one saw the murder.[p/] The High Speaker only witnessed the moment Aria dumped the body,[p/] and even [i]he[/i] didn't see that much."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1ce5e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] was Sibyl the victim I wanted to focus on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5c7f5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: We later discovered her body in Lake Galakrond.[p/] From the High Speaker's testimony,[p/] Steelwind must have dumped her body from the balcony above."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f9b80",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did you know her body was there anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048124b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: When bodies started dropping,[p/] we noticed that she was nowhere to be found."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ad0d2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: One of the Kingsguard cast [b]Locate Creature[/b], and realized she was somewhere in the lake."
}

{
  "id": "line:01313b0",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: It took us an hour before we finally fished her out."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ec9a5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: Based on the High Speaker's testimony,[p/] she was dead long before that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2aa19",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: From McCoy's testimony,[p/] we know that Steelwind killed Pierce in the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3619b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Out of all the murders,[p/] Pierce's is the one we have the most information about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1abad",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] From what it sounds like,[p/] this Patron wasn't planning to let McCoy live."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf3730",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: That drawn-out fight must have really thrown a wrench into their plans."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e61ebe",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: I find [i]that[/i] a little strange though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5f523",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070c543",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: My daughter is a worthless soldier.[p/] She has no talent for combat,[p/] and [i]I've[/i] witnessed McCoy's battle prowess firsthand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d74981",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: As much as I hate to admit it,[p/] McCoy should have easily overcome her in an even fight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701cb2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/]It was her magic that was the problem."
}

{
  "id": "line:038e49f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: I had no idea what kind of spells she could throw at me.[p/] So I had to be careful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acd73e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Celeste: ...And despite everything,[p/] I [i]really[/i] didn't want to hurt her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0607e92",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: Hm...[p/] That kindness could be the death of you, McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c29695",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] was Pierce the victim I wanted to focus on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:007f1ae",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: She probably didn't have time to suffocate him like the other two.[p/] So she must have improvised a weapon using [b]Shape Liquid[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:090a397",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which is strangely similar to how he murdered Flinhart McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2731a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: Lord Pierce [i]was[/i] one of the targets of the Patron."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be1094",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: It's likely they knew about what happened during McCoy's trials and drew inspiration from that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f88da7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Still, though...[p/] It seems awfully creative for something that they came up with at the moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca53bc",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "LucioC: Well...[p/] Don't the legends say that [i]demons[/i] engage in contrapasso?"
}

{
  "id": "line:055b8f0",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Orym: ...Say what now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fd508",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: Some people believe that when souls are sent to hell,[p/] they're punished in a way that relates to their sins."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b18948",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: In Pierce's case,[p/] he committed murder with a frozen blade."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b888b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's possible this Empress wanted the Patron to murder him in the same way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee5d7d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "...Although,[p/] I still couldn't say for sure..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a13ff3",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "Despite how much I knew,[p/] there were a lot of details missing about how von Sanctus and Sibyl died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0329336",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "But the Inquisition might have found some clues that I missed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb4be1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Orym",
  "text": "I needed to ask the commander to elaborate on what they knew about each of the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0553b57",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Whose murder should he elaborate on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a41d0",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Lloyd von Sanctus"
}

{
  "id": "line:063ac76",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you elaborate more on von Sanctus's murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0070d5e",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was there any evidence that implied how he died?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d82375",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Like I said,[p/] it's trickier with von Sanctus because the fire partially burned his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b64d3",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Our [b]divination[/b] magic could only tell that he died of suffocation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b27981",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see.[p/] So there's no other physical evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1749a",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Well, there [i]is[/i] one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:07130cd",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: From his burn marks,[p/] we [i]do[/i] know that he was hit with some kind of mundane projectile before he died."
}

{
  "id": "line:026537f",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you mean like an arrow or something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5688d",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria's a mage, though.[p/] Why would she use a mundane weapon to attack?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b0b37",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "LucioC: Talentless mages will often use mundane weapons to make up for their weakness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d31635",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Either way,[p/] she probably wanted to weaken him before she dealt the final blow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9dcb0",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: So he took a direct attack from her before he died."
}

{
  "id": "line:015245e",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Coraline Sibyl"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d2865",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you elaborate more on Sibyl's murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a01b7",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was there any evidence that implied how she died?"
}

{
  "id": "line:077e2a3",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Using our [b]divination[/b] magic,[p/] we know she died of suffocation."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a8608",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: But we're not exactly sure how."
}

{
  "id": "line:06475e8",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: But unlike von Sanctus,[p/] Sibyl's body wasn't burned."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cf129",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Shouldn't there have been wounds around her neck if she was suffocated?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0538c92",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Well, we found traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0002264",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: We think Steelwind cast [b]Mend Wounds[/b] on her body after she offed her."
}

{
  "id": "line:043aea4",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Someone must've learned that trick from Nightgrave's case.[p/] It removed any wounds on the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7c141",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's exactly like what happened with Catherine Bellwether."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a0c55",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] The only wounds she has are from the impact of falling into Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf854f",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Garrick Pierce"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4b64b",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you elaborate more on Pierce's murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020c53c",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Well, [i]that[/i] one is simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ef3e7",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: McCoy chased Steelwind into the Prayer Room but didn't arrive fast enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afacae",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: When she got there,[p/] Pierce was already dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:08630b7",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: He was killed using a blade magically formed from his own blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f41d7",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But why would she do something like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2b657",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: When he murdered Flinhart McCoy,[p/] he only used [b]Shape Liquid[/b] to avoid leaving behind any evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:04661c6",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: I doubt the Patron would make Steelwind do that for the same reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ec6a3",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Their intent was to pin the crime on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b70335",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: We think she knew McCoy was on her tail."
}

{
  "id": "line:00acab8",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: She didn't have enough time to suffocate him as she did with von Sanctus and Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd28d4",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: And she didn't have any weapons on her.[p/] She must have had to improvise."
}

{
  "id": "line:017da3b",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: But she [i]has[/i] other spells that could've done the job."
}

{
  "id": "line:0944455",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: She could have hit him with a [b]Steelwind Strike[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eea43a",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "LucioC: Hmph...[p/] I know from experience that she is [i]terrible[/i] at controlling that spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b35c8",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "LucioC: It's possible she didn't want to unleash such a powerful spell in a closed room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a61ffe",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "That [i]sort[/i] of tracked,[p/] but it still didn't feel right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0635245",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] the other two murders were really well planned."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d298",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Pierce's murder was the only one that required improvisation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b76343",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "LucioC: It's possible the Patron severely underestimated McCoy's combat capabilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d6ed7",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "LucioC: She fought my daughter for almost half an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e237b",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "LucioC: Meanwhile,[p/] the other two murders occurred within quick succession of one another."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1dab",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah.[p/] I see what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:00600b3",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "No One's"
}

{
  "id": "line:0964bda",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "I decided to keep the testimony as is for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0802e1a",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Perhaps there was something there I could still use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b66394",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] please add this to your testimony, Commander White."
}

{
  "id": "line:001aec4",
  "node": "OrymPress",
  "text": "Orym: Sure.[p/] Whatever you say, kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a1f6b",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] That's strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ffdd1",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "LucioC: ...What is it now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4c1d",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Commander White.[p/] You said that Steelwind attacked von Sanctus with a projectile [i]before[/i] she suffocated him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce1720",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah.[p/] She probably wanted to injure him so he'd be easier to subdue."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bdf83",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But [i]that's[/i] what I find strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dc335",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus knew he was under attack."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca3c9",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: So wouldn't he cast [b]Force Cage[/b] to repel her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0506b91",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Orym: ...Hm.[p/] I guess that's true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f75f98",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "LucioC: Von Sanctus was hardly a warrior, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:025bbde",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "LucioC: [b]Force Cage[/b] is an extremely useful spell,[p/] but it [i]has[/i] to be aimed."
}

{
  "id": "line:004da80",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "LucioC: He was shot with a projectile.[p/] He must have been in immense pain."
}

{
  "id": "line:053d45e",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "LucioC: I doubt he'd be able to think clearly under those circumstances."
}

{
  "id": "line:0372659",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'd normally agree with you,[p/] but the crime scene tells another story."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cec297",
  "node": "OrymObj",
  "text": "Rath: What do you mean, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce61c2",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": ":Von Sanctus: Traces of Abjuration"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2fe81",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "Default"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d17eb",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "No...[p/] The general's theory was somewhat believable."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d5d34",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "But I remembered something that I'd found at the crime scene."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c9bad",
  "node": "OrymObj2",
  "text": "And it told me whether von Sanctus cast [b]Force Cage[/b] or not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8acd3",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: When we investigated the crime scene,[p/] we found traces of [b]abjuration[/b] magic that formed a perfect square around the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:074ec9b",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sure if we measured the dimensions of that square,[p/] it would be 10ft by 10ft."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d8ea6",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Which is the same length and width as the cube created by [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0946efb",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Like you said,[p/] he was in no shape to aim it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03139bc",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: So he cast [b]Force Cage[/b] on [i]himself[/i] to create a makeshift barrier."
}

{
  "id": "line:018220c",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: Nonsense![p/][s/] If von Sanctus [i]had[/i] cast [b]Force Cage[/b] on himself,[p/] he should have been protected from further harm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0874774",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: The defendant wouldn't have been able to suffocate him after that."
}

{
  "id": "line:026ad54",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Perhaps there's some way to [i]bypass[/i] [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:092a790",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: Your ignorance of the Arcane Arts is apparent."
}

{
  "id": "line:028f333",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: [b]Force Cage[/b] is one of the most powerful [b]abjuration[b/] spells in existence."
}

{
  "id": "line:01960d4",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: It can't be dispelled,[p/] and [i]no one[/i] could teleport into or out of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:006029c",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] Aster was also trapped in a [b]Force Cage[/b],[p/] and [i]he[/i] had to wait for the hour duration to elapse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8de42",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Wait."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b10792",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: If [b]Force Cage[/b] is a perfectly closed space,[p/] is it possible that he ran out of air?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc425b",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: That would be a [i]glaring[/i] weakness."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ec8d1",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: House von Sanctus obviously designed that spell to only allow oxygen through the barrier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7b717",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "LucioC: ...And before you ask,[p/] poisonous gases can't be pushed through the barrier either."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cb397",
  "node": "OrymObj3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] And even if they [i]had[/i] used poisonous gas,[p/] the autopsy report wouldn't have said he was suffocated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0714950",
  "node": "OrymObj4",
  "text": "Only oxygen can travel through the bounds of a [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a1705",
  "node": "OrymObj4",
  "text": "So how did Aria suffocate von Sanctus despite that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093d630",
  "node": "OrymObj5",
  "text": "No...[p/] Aria had no way to physically harm von Sanctus [i]or[/i] prevent him from breathing."
}

{
  "id": "line:080641f",
  "node": "OrymObj5",
  "text": "If she were outside the [b]Force Cage[/b],[p/] how could she have suffocated him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e77c5",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: [b]Force Cage[/b] is specifically designed to allow oxygen through its barrier."
}

{
  "id": "line:084fe39",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: But what if there was no oxygen [i]left[/i] in the room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0803cea",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: No oxygen...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04eac3f",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Ah."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afc1b9",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Rath: It was the fire in the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb1f29",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Rath: Von Sanctus couldn't be harmed once he was in that [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:098e8c8",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Rath: So she started a fire to eat all of the oxygen within the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:048eea6",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: What [i]should[/i] have protected him ended up trapping him."
}

{
  "id": "line:033926d",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: And the inability to dispel it ended up sealing his fate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdb6c1",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Rath: Well, I suppose that explains how the defendant murdered von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cc66d",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Rath: But with that in mind...[p/] a [i]lot[/i] of this plan sounds like it was improvised at the moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d532cf",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Just like the murder of Pierce..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0826f2b",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: And not only that.[p/] We assumed that the Patron used the same method to kill both Lord von Sanctus and Lady Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:07add22",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I doubt Lady Sibyl died under the same circumstances."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cdd64",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: Correct...[p/] There was only [i]one[/i] fire."
}

{
  "id": "line:043bd77",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: And if Sibyl was in that [b]Force Cage[/b],[p/] the defendant wouldn't have been able to throw her body into Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0867bc1",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: Which means Sibyl must have died by asphyxiation elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5f675",
  "node": "OrymObj6",
  "text": "Rath: Then it's clear our next course of action is to determine how [i]Lady Sibyl[/i] was murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdc401",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] We still don't know [i]where[/i] she was murdered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce6c64",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: The only witness who saw her around this time was the High Speaker."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c5b0a",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Which was [i]after[/i] the defendant disposed of Sibyl's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fed7e4",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] the High Speaker's testimony is as good a start as any."
}

{
  "id": "line:08af61c",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: For our next witness,[p/] the defence would like to call High Speaker Theon Archeus to the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2803c",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f98f0",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: ...It's nothing.[p/] Carry on."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b4769",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "LucioC: Kingsguard![p/][s/] Escort High Speaker Archeus to the witness stand!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0306453",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "LucioC: Witness.[p/] You will testify about—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc13e3",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: Oh, great and [i]blessed[/i] Scaled Lord!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04284a7",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: To think you would grace us with your presence!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0810c47",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: ...Oh my god."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6afae",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: A-[p/][s/]Ah...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1166b",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: Forgive me, Lord Rathallion![p/][s/] I spoke out of turn! [h=\"He must think|I'm an arrogant fool!\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d2a86",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: How many times do I have to tell you people that I'm [i]not[/i] a god?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:035f736",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: [i]Yes[/i]...[p/] I revere and serve the God of Dragons,[p/] but I'm [i]not[/i] an avatar of Bahamut!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac3b82",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: B-[p/][s/]But...[p/][s/] You're the [i]Scaled Lord[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:097e522",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: I'm just a [i]dragon[/i].[p/][s/] I'm not even a [i]powerful[/i] one!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0389b34",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: I'm [i]not[/i] a deity!"
}

{
  "id": "line:076eb9a",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: ...This humility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d78866",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: That's [i]exactly[/i] what Bahamut's avatar would say."
}

{
  "id": "line:0900a6a",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: I swear to god..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0722d",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Theon: He even swears by the god's name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2702e",
  "node": "OrymObj7",
  "text": "Rath: ...Lucio,[p/] please handle this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b2780",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: Perhaps [i]another[/i] approach is warranted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0144125",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: High Speaker Archeus![p/][s/] The Great and [i]Powerful[/i] Rathallion calls upon you today!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0270f8b",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: We require your—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc59a6",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: You require my life?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cd9f5",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: Of course![p/][s/] I will gladly give my [i]life[/i] for the Scaled Lord!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09fd633",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: ...What?![p/][s/] No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d8bd9",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: Of course![p/][s/] My blood could [i]never[/i] be enough!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0839b44",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: Would you just let me—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:081aa17",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: I will do as you wish, my Lord!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e074a7",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: It might take some time, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c569cb",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: I'll need some time to gather some devout followers of the faith and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0740915",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Rath: Oh my god![p/][s/] We [i]just[/i] want your testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f9fe0",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Rath: ...Just tell us what you saw when Ms. Steelwind was at the westward balcony yesterday."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa081d",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: ...O-[p/][s/]Oh, I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa1e23",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Theon: If [i]that's[/i] what you truly wish, my Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2c03",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are we just going to [i]ignore[/i] how willing he was to commit mass murder?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04028c9",
  "node": "OrymObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: Be quiet![p/][s/] We [i]just[/i] got him to calm down!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08fd7bf",
  "node": "OrymObj9",
  "text": "Theon: I was doing some paperwork in my quarters,[p/] and I suppose I lost track of the time.[p/] My alarm went off and I realized that it was time for my afternoon prayers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0688475",
  "node": "OrymObj9",
  "text": "Theon: I began heading to the Prayer Room when I spotted Lady Steelwind looking over the westward balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cdac2",
  "node": "OrymObj9",
  "text": "Theon: I tried to greet her,[p/] but she didn't respond to me.[p/] That's when I noticed she was pushing something large over the balcony and into Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10dc6",
  "node": "OrymObj9",
  "text": "Theon: I asked her what she was doing,[p/] but again,[p/] she ignored me and went towards the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:03caa7a",
  "node": "OrymObj9",
  "text": "Theon: I thought nothing of it and made my way there as well.[p/] That's when the guards there turned me away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d616be",
  "node": "OrymObj9",
  "text": "Theon: I went back to my quarters to do my Prayers there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f41c64",
  "node": "OrymObj10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering the timing of it all,[p/] this must have all happened minutes before she began attacking the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:06544a4",
  "node": "OrymObj10",
  "text": "Theon: Yes...[p/] I consider myself lucky.[p/] The Scaled Lord must have graced me with divine luck."
}

{
  "id": "line:044e5ec",
  "node": "OrymObj10",
  "text": "Rath: Please.[p/] Just...[p/] stop."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0a1e1",
  "node": "OrymObj10",
  "text": "Considering how quickly she was moving,[p/] there [i]has[/i] to be a reason why she waited there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abd854",
  "node": "OrymObj10",
  "text": "Was she waiting for the High Speaker to leave?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04de08c",
  "node": "OrymObj10",
  "text": "Perhaps I needed to closely examine the timing of these events."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e63b9a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: An alarm?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e61fa",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: It's a rudimentary artificery device.[p/] I use it to remind me to conduct daily prayers."
}

{
  "id": "line:03be8dc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I see.[p/] And do you have it set to go off at a specific time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c67b5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Yes.[p/] It's set to go off at 2:10 PM: five minutes before my afternoon prayers."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fce9b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I was in my quarters when my alarm went off at 2:10 PM.[p/] I realized that it was time for my afternoon prayers."
}

{
  "id": "line:071dda1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you usually say your afternoon prayers at 2:15 PM?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab70b1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Yes.[p/] It is said that time is the holiest hour of the God of Dragons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0933f49",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Rath: ...This is the first [i]I've[/i] heard of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe6d74",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Was I mistaken?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0908e1f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Forgive me, my lord![p/] I can't believe I've dishonored your deity!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae880a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Rath: Ugh...[p/] You know what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bee962",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Rath: Just forget I said anything..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e63b07",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: What was her expression like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01bac9f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: It was very cold and emotionless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a92171",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: ...The Patron must have had control of her when this happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d65755",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Yes.[p/] That certainly makes the most sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b23365",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: What time did this happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dc6fe",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: It was shortly after my alarm went off.[p/] It would definitely be before 2:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc6f31",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I began heading to the Prayer Room when I spotted Lady Steelwind looking over the westward balcony.[p/] This happened before 2:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:036c2d1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: So she was looking over Lake Galakrond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:047b0a6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Knowing what I know now,[p/] it's possible that she was making sure she could throw Lady Sibyl's body [i]into[/i] the lake from there."
}

{
  "id": "line:02785f5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: But she was clearly fine with [i]you[/i] witnessing her act suspiciously."
}

{
  "id": "line:063976a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would she even go to the trouble of hiding Sibyl's body in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16268",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: The Patron clearly needed to delay when the murders were discovered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce7d06",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: The defendant wasn't able to murder Pierce until much later, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e2a67",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "I suppose they didn't [i]plan[/i] for her to fight Celeste for that long."
}

{
  "id": "line:032f326",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "But there [i]had[/i] to be a reason why she threw Sibyl's body into the lake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0771502",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I tried to greet her, but she didn't respond to me.[p/] That's when I noticed she was pushing something large over the balcony and into Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7f409",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: So she ignored you?[p/] What was her expression like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0029f3c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: What time did this encounter happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa390c",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: It was shortly after my alarm went off.[p/] It was definitely before 2:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:08707d1",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: It was still before 2:15 PM.[p/] Our encounter was short.[p/] That's when I noticed she was pushing something large over the balcony and into Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0382039",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And that must have been Sibyl's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:033382a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: ...I suppose so."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a3981",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You don't sound so sure of it yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0884081",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: It's just that I recall Lady Sibyl's garb to be much brighter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0bb52",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Meanwhile,[p/] the thing I saw Lady Steelwind throw over the balcony was much darker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ace97f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] You mentioned that before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0916a4b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: It's clear it was just the lighting of that space."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7f655",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: That balcony is directly above where we found Lady Sibyl's body in Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be52b8",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: You [i]obviously[/i] saw the defendant dumping the body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0322463",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: What [i]else[/i] could it have been?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d484a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Yes...[p/] I suppose you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d86fc5",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron was probably trying to keep her on track,[p/] but I'm surprised she didn't attack you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc2332",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if the Patron was trying to frame her,[p/] she hadn't killed Pierce yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e8e96",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Yes.[p/] I'm a little confused about that myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6e7b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Perhaps I should just be happy I came out of that encounter unharmed."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e1155",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] how long did you talk to her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091715a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Our encounter was very brief since she was ignoring me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0484809",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: It couldn't have lasted for more than two minutes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8af3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I only spent about two minutes trying to speak with her,[p/] but she ignored me and went towards the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:016dc04",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: It must have been a short exchange then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d85171",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: The Patron was controlling her at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b054d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: They must have been hoping that he would leave if she ignored him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15195",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "But wouldn't it have been easier to just murder him then and there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033b33a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "She could have easily done it quickly and thrown his body into the lake.[p/] Just like she did with Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c2a47",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right,[p/] and those guards are still comatose."
}

{
  "id": "line:016796a",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: We [i]still[/i] don't have an explanation for that either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e159cd",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Did the Empress of Discord use some kind of demonic magic to do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02cd485",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus doesn't leave magical traces.[p/] So it's possible that demonic magic is the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:0892ea9",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] it was awfully convenient he left right [i]before[/i] the attack on the Prayer Room happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcc2f3",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] what time did this happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec01fa",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I believe it was 2:15 PM.[p/] That's when I usually arrive at the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:094a4ce",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I thought nothing of it and made my way there as well.[p/] That's when the guards there turned me away at 2:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6465b",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were in your quarters during the massacre?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f8f9f",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: Yes.[p/] As I've mentioned before,[p/] my room is magically soundproof."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a544b2",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: My guards and I were woefully unaware of what was happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af3e04",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: We didn't know what was happening until some members of the Kingsguard came to inform me of what had happened to the King."
}

{
  "id": "line:09134bb",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: How long were you in your quarters for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e4eb0",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I waited there until the Kingsguard notified me that it was safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a8361",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I think I waited there until 3:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baf1cf",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Which was around the time that Aria was arrested."
}

{
  "id": "line:0796573",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: I went back to my quarters to do my Prayers there.[p/] I was there until 3:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:070c5d6",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means you were in your quarters until the massacre ended."
}

{
  "id": "line:073a22e",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did your guards see Steelwind during that time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4495d",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: No.[p/] They didn't.[p/] All we knew was that His Majesty had been trapped."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba5733",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "Theon: We had no idea Lady Steelwind had been attacking people."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bae19",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: It's clear that the High Speaker wasn't one of the Patron's targets."
}

{
  "id": "line:0702bcc",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "LucioC: They made no attempt to direct my daughter there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e832dd",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "There was a very small time frame between Sibyl's death and Aria's attack on the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8e7ec",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "The details of his testimony could make a huge difference depending on when each event happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0548d47",
  "node": "Cross_Examination_Theon",
  "text": "I needed to see if he remembered the exact time each part of his testimony occurred."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8f5b9",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/][s/] What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0408557",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Theon: ...Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:003d9bc",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: There [i]is[/i],[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:043caf7",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not really sure what it means."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b21fa",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "LucioC: Stop stammering and [i]say what you want to say[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb6f6b",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: High Speaker.[p/] You said that you saw Aria dumping [i]something[/i] over the ledge of the balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0067498",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "LucioC: There's no need to be vague, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f88ad8",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "LucioC: It's clear from the evidence that he saw my daughter dumping Lady Sibyl's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5bd7b",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's the thing, Lord Steelwind.[p/] It [i]couldn't[/i] have been Sibyl's [i]body[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be6eb8",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "LucioC: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e84498",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "LucioC: The location from that balcony to where we found Lady Sibyl's body lines up perfectly!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74c64",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That may be,[p/] but the witness just said he saw Aria dumping the body [i]before[/i] 2:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc748",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Wait."
}

{
  "id": "line:0201cd9",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You see it too, don't you, Lucio?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5648a",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did Aria dump Coraline Sibyl's body into Lake Galakrond [i]before[/i] 2:15 PM..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dfa28",
  "node": "TheonObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...if her time of death was 2:[i]18[/i] PM?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0613877",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "Rath: I see...[p/] That [i]does[/i] seem peculiar."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d13f7",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: But we [i]know[/i] the defendant threw Sibyl's body from that balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:07093f6",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: There would be no other explanation for how it ended up there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b93257",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes...[p/] That's also true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4e54c",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "Rath: Perhaps she was still alive when Aria threw her off of that balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0426bc0",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "Rath: She could have been knocked unconscious with a [b]Sleep[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:09053e1",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: Your Grace.[p/] There were no traces of [b]conjuration[/b] magic on her body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0247901",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: And even if she [i]was[/i] asleep,[p/] she wouldn't have survived a fall from that height."
}

{
  "id": "line:0113271",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: The distance from that balcony to the lake is more than thirty stories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baec4d",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "LucioC: And the autopsy report says that the cause of death was suffocation,[p/] not blunt force."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f11f7",
  "node": "TheonObj2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0f936",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "So when [i]did[/i] she die?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0937617",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "Player: She died before she was thrown"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f91a18",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": ":The High Speaker testified that he saw Aria dumping the body before 2:15 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b557a",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "Was he mistaken?[p/] Perhaps the time was later than he'd thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:058f317",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": ":No...[p/] Celeste began fighting Aria at 2:20 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:013c67f",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": ":If the High Speaker saw her dumping Sibyl at 2:18 PM,[p/] he would have been close enough to hear the fight break out."
}

{
  "id": "line:006484a",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "She could have only died after Aria dumped her off the ledge."
}

{
  "id": "line:050af64",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "Player: She died while she was falling"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a74f3",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "Did she die [i]while[/i] she was falling?"
}

{
  "id": "line:016b86a",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "No...[p/] The cause of death was suffocation."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fcfd5",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "Aria couldn't have possibly suffocated her while she was falling toward Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adf607",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "There were no wounds on the body.[p/] This means Aria couldn't have obstructed her airway [i]after[/i] she was thrown off of the balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a513e",
  "node": "TheonObj3",
  "text": "Player: She died after she hit the water"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b1755",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She must have died [i]after[/i] she hit the water."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe8be2",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "Rath: But Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] Lucio just said that she would have died upon impact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe87b",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that's [i]assuming[/i] she didn't do anything to lessen the blow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0736980",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She might have had the opportunity to cast a spell to protect herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8df68",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That [i]might[/i] explain why her body wasn't as damaged despite falling from such a great height."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cc207",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: Again.[p/] [i]That[/i] doesn't match with the evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c6b95",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: Lady Sibyl's [b]Spell Compendium[/b] contains the spell: [b]Slow Fall[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8cb12",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: If she had the opportunity to cast a spell,[p/] she would have used [i]that[/i] spell to slow her descent."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f28bc",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: And she wouldn't have taken [i]any[/i] damage from hitting the lake if she'd done that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a439e",
  "node": "TheonObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's...[p/] a really good point,[p/] but just indulge me for a second."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f86c1",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "Stone Skin"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dddce8",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "Slow Fall"
}

{
  "id": "line:0860891",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "No...[p/] Sibyl [i]could[/i] have used [b]Slow Fall[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d84bdb",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "But if she did,[p/] she wouldn't have taken [i]any[/i] injuries from hitting Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4106d",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "For whatever reason,[p/] she must have been protected by another spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe1996",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "One that lessened the impact,[p/] but didn't completely negate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f51f6",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "No...[p/] Sibyl must have been affected by a spell that would've lessened the impact of hitting Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:039ef89",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "Which spell [b]Compendium[/b] would do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:010831e",
  "node": "TheonObj5",
  "text": "She was probably also together with Lloyd before the massacre broke out,[p/] but they clearly got separated at some point."
}

{
  "id": "line:09762a0",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I think Lloyd must have cast [b]Stone Skin[/b] on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03791a2",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: [b]Stone Skin[/b]...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0124763",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you recall,[p/] the High Speaker mentioned that something was strange about the object Aria threw over the balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5549f",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was much darker,[p/] and didn't match with Sibyl's usual garb."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acef1e",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Almost as if there was something else Sibyl was \"wearing\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e594d",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Rath: That \"object\" was actually Lady Sibyl,[p/] protected by a layer of stone."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f463f",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lloyd cast [b]Stone Skin[/b] on her [i]before[/i] she was thrown into the lake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0957efd",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria must have attacked them,[p/] and Lloyd must have cast that spell to protect her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf6d74",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: That coward?[p/] I'd have imagined he'd simply worry about protecting himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:09aef96",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: But I'll admit that spell [i]would've[/i] protected her from the [b]Steelwind Strike[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:00741be",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Theon: But that doesn't seem quite right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef1df0",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Theon: I may not have seen much,[p/] but I saw that the object Aria dumped was stiff and motionless."
}

{
  "id": "line:00642b8",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Theon: If it [i]had[/i] been Lady Sibyl,[p/] she would have been struggling against her,[p/] wouldn't she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e1b01",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That's[/i] a good point too..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e65969",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The High Speaker saw Aria dumping a motionless Sibyl,[p/] but if we assume my logic is correct,[p/] she would've [i]also[/i] still been alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0468344",
  "node": "TheonObj6",
  "text": "So why wasn't she struggling against Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cea60",
  "node": "TheonObj9",
  "text": "000"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e47069",
  "node": "TheonObj9",
  "text": "No...[p/] Following your logic thus far,[p/] Sibyl was affected by [b]Stone Skin[/b] [i]and[/i] she was still conscious."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e80b8",
  "node": "TheonObj9",
  "text": "She would be immune to most blunt force impacts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c646e4",
  "node": "TheonObj10",
  "text": "She must have been affected by a spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:051d079",
  "node": "TheonObj10",
  "text": "And considering it kept her from resisting Aria,[p/] the Patron must have made [i]Aria[/i] cast that spell on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0593279",
  "node": "TheonObj11",
  "text": "Hold Creature"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d7892",
  "node": "TheonObj11",
  "text": "No...[p/] Aria must've cast a spell on Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2ea85",
  "node": "TheonObj11",
  "text": "And that spell would have prevented her from resisting Aria while she threw her from the balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b7aa4",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was [b]Hold Creature[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04237dd",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lloyd must have cast [b]Stone Skin[/b] on Sibyl when Aria attacked them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05295cd",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron must have known that Aria couldn't physically damage her like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6ef18",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: So they ordered her to restrain Sibyl with that spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76674",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "LucioC: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:035e04b",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "LucioC: And Sibyl died by suffocation..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d72e9",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's right, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2ee9d",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if she was restrained,[p/] Sibyl was still protected by [b]Stone Skin[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:04385b3",
  "node": "TheonObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: That would've left only [i]one[/i] option for the Patron."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c67a62",
  "node": "TheonObj13",
  "text": "No...[p/] The Patron must have known that they couldn't physically harm Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a861a",
  "node": "TheonObj13",
  "text": "But they needed to murder her quickly before anyone realized what was going on."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d7bc8",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sibyl suffocated when Aria threw her into Lake Galakrond."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6ec97",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Her [b]Stone Skin[/b] lessened the impact of the fall,[p/] but it also made her drop like a literal rock."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d95d9e",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria's [b]Hold Creature[/b] spell prevented her from moving,[p/] and since Lloyd stayed in the Common Room,[p/] he didn't know his spell was signing her death warrant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d43926",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: She was helpless as she sank to the bottom of the lake!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03301e0",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Rath: I believe that covers all three of the murders, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e1e1f",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "LucioC: Yes..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eebef8",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "LucioC: Lord von Sanctus suffocated to death in his own [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fc5d9",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "LucioC: Lady Sibyl drowned after Aria cast [b]Hold Creature[/b] on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a30d9",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "LucioC: And Lord Pierce died after being wounded by a blade created with [b]Shape Liquid[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddb704",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Rath: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b79651",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Rath: The only common thread I see is that the Patron knew how to use his victims' spells against them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0569b7a",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "...But how did that connect to Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3b85d",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Did he cast [b]Shape Liquid[/b] to make a blade to defend himself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0557f20",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Maybe the murderer took it from him and used it to deal the final blow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a20266",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "...No,[p/] but he was knocked unconscious alongside me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d11bbb",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "He [i]couldn't[/i] have been the one to create that blade."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5c129",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Anyways,[p/] whoever did this had an in-depth knowledge of each of the spells they used to defend themselves."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b914ea",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: They knew that Von Sanctus couldn't dispel his own [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbc148",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: They also knew that he still needed oxygen from within it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f768c",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: And in Sibyl's case,[p/] they knew Aria couldn't physically harm her once she had [b]Stone Skin[/b] active."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b6ec7",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "LucioC: They also knew that [b]Hold Creature[/b] would prevent Sibyl from moving while she sank to the bottom of the lake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3cb9b",
  "node": "TheonObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not only that.[p/] They did all of this in a quick time frame."
}

{
  "id": "line:0534720",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus and Sibyl died within thirteen minutes of each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cd7a6",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Tyrion: And if Aria hadn't encountered Celeste,[p/] Pierce might've died [i]just[/i] as quickly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4007e",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Rath: So whoever did this had an in-depth knowledge of high-level magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fdb4a",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "LucioC: Not only that...[p/] They came up with creative ways to bypass the defenses put up by von Sanctus and Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb8856",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Rath: Yes...[p/] They had the ability to react quickly and decisively."
}

{
  "id": "line:051ab07",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "LucioC: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] But considering the circumstances...[p/] that [i]hardly[/i] narrows it down."
}

{
  "id": "line:033541a",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "LucioC: Several members of the Four Pillar Families were present that day.[p/] Each and every one of them studied at the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa954e",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "LucioC: They would all be knowledgeable in magic and its applications."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa14ea",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "What they were saying wasn't sitting right with me for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fef69",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "There was [i]something[/i] there.[p/] So why couldn't I see it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041137d",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But there's another angle to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6f4a0",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Consider [i]who[/i] the Patron did and [i]didn't[/i] target."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b79420",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Tyrion: The victims were Lloyd von Sanctus,[p/] Coraline Sibyl,[p/] and Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ece946",
  "node": "TheonObj14a",
  "text": "Tyrion: What's a similarity that we can draw between at least two of them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b7538",
  "node": "TheonObj15",
  "text": "No...[p/] The victims were von Sanctus,[p/] Sibyl,[p/] and Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:06eb999",
  "node": "TheonObj15",
  "text": "It doesn't quite work for all three of them,[p/] but there was a common thread between at least two of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05324ab",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Von Sanctus and Sibyl were the heads of their respective noble houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a149ca",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Rath: Are you saying the Patron's goal was to assassinate leaders of the Four Pillars?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06480d9",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's the motive that makes the most sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:09aff7b",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But that [i]does[/i] leave one question."
}

{
  "id": "line:053ae16",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "LucioC: Don't be coy.[p/] I'm not [i]daft[/i], Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0612b",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Actually,[p/] I [i]highly[/i] doubt it was you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7083",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Really, now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001d2e2",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Out of most of the people there,[p/] you could have easily tricked your daughter into signing a Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dc48a",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: But [i]why[/i] would you need to do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0332f95",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're the Grand General of Wyverngarde's military,[p/] and the Cathedral was [i]filled[/i] with your men."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ad292",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: You could have easily equipped one of your best mages to carry out this massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:07703d6",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: And you wouldn't even [i]need[/i] to make a deal with a demon to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f1752",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Rath: So why [i]wasn't[/i] Lucio targeted then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:029b02c",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: From her encounter with Celeste,[p/] it's clear there's a limit to Aria's combat capabilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:063a577",
  "node": "TheonObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron might've simply doubted Aria's ability to defeat the Grand General,[p/] but there's also another explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0232695",
  "node": "TheonObj17",
  "text": "No...[p/] The Patron made no attempt to kill Lucio Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:08295c8",
  "node": "TheonObj17",
  "text": "And when they were controlling Aria,[p/] they didn't make any attempt to hide her actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d13f0",
  "node": "TheonObj17",
  "text": "They [i]wanted[/i] people to see her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c71bf",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron [i]wanted[/i] people to suspect House Steelwind for the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f9b8b",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: They used Lucio Steelwind's daughter to commit the crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3a21a",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then they intentionally left him alive to cast suspicion on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7a6e8",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: ...[i]That's[/i] why they used my daughter?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0002b7b",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "...What was that tinge of anger just now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:062a4df",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Anyways,[p/] [i]that[/i] leads me to my next point."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8a7f",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Imagine if we never discovered Aria's Blood Contract with the Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea6e45",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: What would have happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e43275",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Rath: ...We'd still think that Ms. Steelwind succumbed to Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:06829d6",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Rath: She would have been convicted for the murders,[p/] and trust in House Steelwind would be forever diminished."
}

{
  "id": "line:092e451",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: About a month ago,[p/] House Frega lost the Duke of Finance,[p/] and his successor:[p/] Laefe Frega,[p/] was woefully unprepared to take his place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0704c10",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Now[/i],[p/] the heads of House von Sanctus and House Sibyl are dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0bcf2",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...With House Steelwind being held responsible for it all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0484a1c",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Rath: All four of the Pillar families would have been weakened as a result of the massacre..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04281d0",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I think there's another layer to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eec647",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Everything fits together if we assume that the Patron's goal was to weaken the Pillar Families."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1d82a",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...[i]Except[/i] for the murder of Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:043ace0",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: Yes...[p/] In contrast to Sibyl and von Sanctus,[p/] Pierce's political power pales in comparison."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc2d33",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Furthermore,[p/] Pierce was already scheduled to be executed next month for the murder of Flinhart McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db272a",
  "node": "TheonObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would the Patron go to the trouble of murdering a condemned man?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cd0c3",
  "node": "TheonObj19a",
  "text": "No...[p/] Pierce was [i]going[/i] to die regardless of what the Patron did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6e554",
  "node": "TheonObj19a",
  "text": "But there [i]has[/i] to be something Pierce did recently."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d51cd7",
  "node": "TheonObj19a",
  "text": "Something that made the Patron decide to murder him as soon as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df6c28",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron murdered Pierce because they [i]needed[/i] him to die as quickly as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1fc2b",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Pierce [i]knew[/i] the identity of Celeste's biological parents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad4473",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Celeste: ...My parents?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053eea9",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember what Pierce said when we showed up for the meeting?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090634f",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Garrick: Ah...[p/] You've finally arrived..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d5eaa",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Garrick: I suppose this means you've finally decided—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0030a02",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Garrick: What...?[p/][s/] [i]You[/i] two?"
}

{
  "id": "line:008df6f",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Celeste: We got your letter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1a5a9",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Garrick: Letter?[p/][s/] [i]What[/i] letter?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:006b2eb",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: You sent us a letter, Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ae3e",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: It said that you knew who Celeste's parents were."
}

{
  "id": "line:080debf",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Garrick: I [i]did[/i] send that letter,[p/] but not to [i]you[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f35893",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: We weren't the intended recipients of that letter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0802822",
  "node": "TheonObj19",
  "text": "Celeste: ...That's right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10937",
  "node": "TheonObj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]that[/i] leaves one last question."
}

{
  "id": "line:01da06c",
  "node": "TheonObj21",
  "text": "No...[p/] I had a feeling that Pierce sent that letter to someone closely tied to this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f59ab4",
  "node": "TheonObj21",
  "text": "There was only one person he could have sent it to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a04b44",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one person Pierce could have sent that letter to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca8682",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: The person who orchestrated the massacre in the first place![p/][s/] The Patron!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09646e4",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "LucioC: But that means—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056cd36",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron is someone who would be threatened by Celeste's parentage!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72e5c",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Rath: Order![p/][s/] Order in the court!"
}

{
  "id": "line:074df30",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Celeste: But...[p/] I don't understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:07aadcc",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry.[p/] I know this is a lot to take in,[p/] but I think they were targeting you for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc8bc7",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: Pierce knew the identity of Celeste's parents and attempted to blackmail the Patron with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:066f962",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "Tyrion: Instead of complying with Pierce's demands,[p/] the Patron sent the letter to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a76e9e",
  "node": "TheonObj22",
  "text": "LucioC: But why go to the trouble of luring [i]you[/i] there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:046d96c",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "LucioC: They could have just allowed Pierce to wait in the Prayer room while the defendant made her way to murder him."
}

{
  "id": "line:01af087",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: Looking back on it,[p/] it's possible they wanted to kill Celeste too."
}

{
  "id": "line:002cac7",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cbcc5",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: They knew I would never meet with Pierce alone,[p/] and the information was about [i]her[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d28a11",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Patron correctly guessed that I'd bring her with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:020bf52",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: By killing both Pierce and Celeste,[p/] they'd eliminate any threat Celeste would pose to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1460b",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "Rath: ...But who would be threatened by such information?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0967f9c",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "LucioC: The mere [i]existence[/i] of McCoy posed a threat to them..."
}

{
  "id": "line:053cf25",
  "node": "TheonObj23",
  "text": "LucioC: It must have [i]something[/i] to do with her birthright."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fda4e",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: So who would that leave?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0676ca1",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "The Royal Family"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f1748",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...King de Wyverngarde just recently died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0419730",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: What if Celeste were a member of the royal family?"
}

{
  "id": "line:040d391",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You think I'm a princess?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06de787",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't want to suspect Aster,[p/] but we [i]need[/i] to consider every possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee7f97",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: And when it comes to conflicts of inheritance,[p/] a royal line of succession is the first thing that comes to mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c384bd",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not only that,[p/] the King would have the authority to pardon Pierce for his crimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb23fb",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: But that wouldn't entirely make sense."
}

{
  "id": "line:0453846",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: If McCoy was abandoned at a tavern in Kornhaven,[p/] we must assume she's a bastard child."
}

{
  "id": "line:013e0cb",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Celeste: Okay...[p/] I don't know why you have to bring [i]that[/i] up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7360f",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: ...My [i]point[/i] is that King Olivier wouldn't abandon a child of pure royal blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0269a10",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: The kingdom requires heirs to continue the royal bloodline."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a9654",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: He would've leveraged her in a diplomatic marriage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0492544",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's disgusting."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b2ef4",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: That's diplomacy, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c61617",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: Anyways,[p/] even if McCoy was of royal blood,[p/] Aster is the King's eldest child,[p/] and he's of [i]pure[/i] royal blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df0f78",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: McCoy would have no claim to the throne under these circumstances."
}

{
  "id": "line:015b582",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] I see what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0d2e2",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose that eliminates Aster for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c10a0",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "House Frega"
}

{
  "id": "line:06170d1",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: I recall during Beatrice Frega's trial,[p/] we heard William Frega's last will and testament."
}

{
  "id": "line:08acc3c",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: It mentioned that House Frega's assets would be divided evenly between [i]all[/i] of his children."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebc264",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: Ah...[p/] If McCoy were to be revealed as a Frega,[p/] his daughters would be legally obligated to share the estate with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fee377",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Could I seriously be a Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06421f9",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't want to suspect Laefe or Miriam,[p/] but we [i]need[/i] to consider every possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:020ce82",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: And as we've seen,[p/] the Fregas are no strangers to making deals with demons."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f68cf",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: However,[p/] it still doesn't quite fit.[p/] I doubt Laefe or Miriam would do something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0306083",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Rath: ...What are you basing that on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09090a0",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: I tend to be a good judge of character,[p/] and they just don't seem like the type to do something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a82a1",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: Bah,[p/] you're far too trusting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9d146",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: I hold no doubt that [i]any[/i] of William's children would be capable of something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0facf89",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose we'll have to see."
}

{
  "id": "line:01070f6",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "House Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:06319e1",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...As much as I have my doubts,[p/] House Steelwind [i]is[/i] the only Pillar Family whose House leader survived the past month."
}

{
  "id": "line:0872f9b",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: ...You think [i]I'm[/i] McCoy's biological father?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0153606",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] You're barely a father to your [i]actual[/i] daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a65aca",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm only stating that possibility for the sake of argument."
}

{
  "id": "line:006f7a8",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: As I've said,[p/] it wouldn't make sense for you to frame your own daughter when [i]House Steelwind[/i] would be blamed,[p/] but we need to consider every possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c2e35",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "The Eyetaker"
}

{
  "id": "line:009070a",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What if the Eyetaker orchestrated this whole thing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bd566",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: The Eyetaker?[p/] That common criminal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e1e1f",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: What reason would [i]he[/i] have to do this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001a126",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've heard firsthand that he was planning to expand his influence throughout Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0070fbc",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was actually plotting with Beatrice to use House Frega to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b94b8",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: Since I ruined his original plans,[p/] setting up this massacre might've been his backup plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f622b5",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: Perhaps we're looking at this all wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7f3bc",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: What if Celeste [i]was[/i] a part of the royal family and they were planning to use her to take the throne?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d79a0e",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: But if he wanted to do so,[p/] why would he put McCoy in danger by having my daughter attack her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07579bf",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: Not only that.[p/] He also had the perfect opportunity to murder His Majesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b2ff3",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: Imagine if he had placed a more lethal contingent spell in that [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b77023",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "LucioC: His Majesty might have very well died alongside von Sanctus, Sibyl, and Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e19a3",
  "node": "TheonObj24",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose you're right,[p/] but we need to consider every possibility."
}

{
  "id": "line:059f848",
  "node": "TheonObj24a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] we should consider the other suspects first."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c9ad",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's honestly all I can think of."
}

{
  "id": "line:005fbcf",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "LucioC: Yes.[p/] There's a flaw with each suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0844b0c",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "LucioC: Your logic is clearly flawed."
}

{
  "id": "line:041f01a",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There's [i]something[/i] here I'm not seeing."
}

{
  "id": "line:009c58e",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I [i]know[/i] I'm close."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdb115",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a missing piece that ties this all together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0641bee",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Regardless,[p/] we still have no idea who or what this \"Empress of Discord\" is."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ac378",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "LucioC: I am loath to allow such an individual to walk freely through Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8bfdd",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Grace.[p/] You've been alive since the creation of Wyverngarde and magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab5a5",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you know who this demon is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a0f84",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Rath: I can't say I do..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac6686",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Rath: Demons tend to take on many titles over their lifetimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:016291a",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Rath: ...But whoever this Empress is,[p/] they are brave to so blatantly encroach on my domain like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a77c73",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Well,[p/] I suppose we'll just have to cross that bridge when we get there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1f5a9",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Rath: We've obtained a lot of information today.[p/] But we clearly have many questions that need to be answered."
}

{
  "id": "line:035f8ee",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Rath: How should we proceed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d817d0",
  "node": "TheonObj25",
  "text": "Rath: ...We [i]have[/i] been working at this for quite a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:089874d",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "Rath: Perhaps we should suspend proceedings so that we can look into these new leads."
}

{
  "id": "line:097cbd8",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "LucioC: Hmph...[p/] I have no objections."
}

{
  "id": "line:0003b39",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "LucioC: It would give [i]my[/i] men some time to look into what we've discovered today."
}

{
  "id": "line:03352b1",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "Rath: Then it's settled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0892b15",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "Rath: We'll be postponing proceedings for now,[p/] but you'll all be expected to return here by tomorrow morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4b2a7",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "LucioC: You are all free to return to your homes for the time being."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a34ebe",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "LucioC: But make no mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dff44",
  "node": "TheonObj26",
  "text": "LucioC: The Kingsguard [i]will[/i] be keeping careful watch over [i]all[/i] of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:058dac5",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "There was still this constant nagging sensation in the back of my mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:087cec0",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey...[p/] Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bae6c3",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "It's as if I were overlooking something extremely important."
}

{
  "id": "line:08560ac",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3127d",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "What [i]was[/i] it?![p/][s/] What could be so important yet [i]so[/i] difficult to remember?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bb7a3",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0d741",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Ah![p/][s/] S-[p/][s/]Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ca748",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was thinking about everything."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d1e11",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: You're looking really stressed out.[p/] Do you want to head back to your house to rest?"
}

{
  "id": "line:002e48e",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] We only have a day until the trial resumes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf6139",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we can't figure out what happened after tomorrow,[p/] the magical traces will disappear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0646aaf",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: But you already [i]know[/i] what happened,[p/] you just don't know who did it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd321a",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...We should speak with the suspects again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be7d20",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe if I get lucky,[p/] I'll see something through the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4eb1b",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: But one of the suspects is the Eyetaker..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00111ee",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: What are you going to do about him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0455e41",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose I'll have to speak with him too."
}

{
  "id": "line:036eb80",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd0038",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: What if he tries to kill you again?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af2e32",
  "node": "TheonObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's just a risk I'll have to take.[p/] Aria's life is on the line."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dff99b",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion...[p/] Do you even understand what you've been pulled into?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015a465",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: Someone just murdered a bunch of nobles,[p/] and they even attacked members of the royal family."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f80d1",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: Now there are Ancient Dragons and Demon Lords involved too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb74a5",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: Isn't this above your pay grade?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df5853",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Ouch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b49255",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: You [i]know[/i] that's not what I meant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c22c6f",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: It's just this whole situation is [i]crazy[/i], isn't it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f38e74",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's fine.[p/] It's just like any other of our investigations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2a91e",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not, though!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb1ff6",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: What if the Empress of Discord attacks you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0712224",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: What if the Patron decides that you're getting too close to the truth?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ea15c",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]What if I can't...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc649",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Her voice broke,[p/] and her hands began to tremble."
}

{
  "id": "line:074d64f",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfdcb4",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you [i]still[/i] worried about what happened during the massacre?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0635f31",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm fine.[p/] I already told you that you didn't do anything wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be57e0",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: You almost died, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b8f45",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f981d1",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: You.[p/][s/] Almost.[p/][s/] [i]Died[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a5e62",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]know[/i], Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf111a",
  "node": "TheonObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: No, Tyrion![p/][s/] I don't think you do!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07697b4",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Celeste: When I saw you all lying on the floor...[p/] I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb509e",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm always so cocky about how I've never lost a fight,[p/] and because of that you—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dae5b5",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "She can't even complete that sentence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb0a2d",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2e0bc",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "How could I be so thoughtless?[p/] She was attacked by Aria and almost died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edf46f",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry.[p/] I didn't think—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0523f94",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't apologize.[p/] Just [i]please[/i]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027b26f",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Celeste: Please just leave this to Lucio and the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4208c",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Celeste: You've done enough already.[p/] They can figure the rest of it out."
}

{
  "id": "line:038637c",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And what if it's not enough?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0722a5b",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Celeste: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b65f2",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not so arrogant that I think they can't do it without me."
}

{
  "id": "line:099ec07",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: But what if they [i]can't[/i] figure out who the Patron is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3ba29",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria will spend the rest of her life in prison."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7254e",
  "node": "TheonObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: What if I could have done something to prevent that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0deaad1",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02918d4",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't care if that happens..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a74f2",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste!"
}

{
  "id": "line:007c497",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't care, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3f15",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll apologize to her all you want after this,[p/] but all I want is to keep you safe!!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5c953",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: ...And I don't know if I'm able to do that anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:0616bd0",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Even [i]she[/i] seems surprised by what she said..."
}

{
  "id": "line:049a6d0",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I-[p/][s/]I'm sorry.[p/] I didn't mean to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0213539",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm really happy you're a part of my life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1ff10",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f4858",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know what you're saying is coming from a place of care."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fea858",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I'm really sorry about how much I've been worrying you lately,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a39eed",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You're not going to stop, are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d618e6",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm going to talk to Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8e91d",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: If we're going to meet the Eyetaker again,[p/] we're bringing some knights with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0302407",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] That's hardly—"
}

{
  "id": "line:004729d",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: Nope![p/][s/] You don't get a say in this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e98827",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Celeste: And if you're not here when I get back,[p/] I [i]will[/i] find you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf4bb2",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Judging from her expression,[p/] that wasn't an empty threat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f46528",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Tyrion: F-[p/][s/]Fine.[p/] Just go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4b4af",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "She might have a point though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8e061",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Before everything happened,[p/] I wasn't even sure if I [i]wanted[/i] to continue practicing law."
}

{
  "id": "line:0496fb5",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "Maybe I needed to consider a safer, quieter life after this is all done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa80cf",
  "node": "TheonObj30",
  "text": "...I hoped she would still be a part of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c72d2",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "Ugh...[p/] What was I thinking about now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a22d1",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "I couldn't stop thinking about her lips on my cheek,[p/] however brief that was."
}

{
  "id": "line:06476c2",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright.[p/] Lucio's cleared it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9732a",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: It was surprisingly easy to convince him."
}

{
  "id": "line:023e8fe",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] U-[p/][s/]Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73291",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce473",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I'm fine...[p/] Let's not waste any more time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d068fd",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "I had to get my face out of her eyeline.[p/] I just quickly walked past her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfe96f",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey![p/][s/] Don't walk so far ahead!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b74c83",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "I needed to stay focused on the trial for Aria's sake."
}

{
  "id": "line:028589e",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "But when this was all over,[p/] I'd have to say those words to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07979e4",
  "node": "TheonObj32",
  "text": "W-[p/][s/]Well...[p/] I suppose I didn't have to think about that until then."
}

{
  "id": "line:081635c",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "I'd finally brought the Empress of Discord onto the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a42ce",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Even with an ancient dragon looming behind her,[p/] she wore the same slightly amused expression she always had."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddf411",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Now that I thought about it,[p/] I could never really glean that much emotion from her."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bf55e",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "What really lay behind those vacant eyes of hers?[p/] Now that I knew the truth,[p/] it felt as if I were looking at a doll being puppeted around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0290a17",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Eris: Hello, your lordship.[p/] I think this is the first time we've met like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:050819f",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Eris: ...You're a lot smaller than I expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0624a96",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Gallery: Who is this woman?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b9711",
  "node": "Courtroom2",
  "text": "Gallery: Why have they brought a [i]civilian[/i] before the Scaled Lord?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b27cd5",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: People of the court.[p/] Until now,[p/] we've known this woman as Eris Illmater."
}

{
  "id": "line:069c7ff",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And ever since the massacre,[p/] we've been trying to determine [i]who[/i] orchestrated this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df478b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We only knew that Aria Steelwind signed a Blood Contract with the Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed9d27",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We still knew very little about this demon.[p/] We didn't even fully understand who they were."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f5f1e",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But we know the truth now."
}

{
  "id": "line:034b3ab",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: People of the Wyverngarde nobility.[p/] The woman on the witness stand [i]isn't[/i] a civilian."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5c043",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She is the demon known as the Empress of Discord!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ee435",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Her form is that of a human.[p/] Using this disguise,[p/] she entered the Grand Cathedral posing as Beatrice Frega's guide."
}

{
  "id": "line:004cf60",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She then aided the Patron by using Beatrice Frega to help Aria Steelwind massacre members of the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b4883",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "LucioC: Why are we continuing with this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:053ab30",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "LucioC: She's already admitted to taking part in the massacre!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d33fe",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "LucioC: Let's force her to tell us who the Patron is and be done with this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e7b1c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Eris: Ah,[p/] how typical."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcbe76",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Eris: The Grand General thinks he can solve [i]all[/i] of his problems with violence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0188be6",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Eris: But let me ask you this.[p/] Why are you assuming that the Patron is a human?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01775c6",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Eris: In Aria's Contract,[p/] it says that \"the Patron\" is the individual who [i]gives[/i] the Contract to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:076ba79",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Eris: How do you know that [i]I'm[/i] not that individual?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0160ecb",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Eris: I go by many names.[p/] The \"Empress of Discord\" is only one of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0162f76",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "LucioC: Hmph...[p/] If what you're saying is true,[p/] that makes this a simpler matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f46c6",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "LucioC: We simply need to execute [i]you[/i] for your crimes against the kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0907e",
  "node": "Courtroom2_1",
  "text": "Eris: If you destroy my body,[p/] I'll simply reform in the Abyssal Hells."
}

{
  "id": "line:08af8b9",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: You're always trying to protect her, Lucio,[p/] but all you ever do is hurt her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06824ca",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: [i]Everything[/i] is about duty with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a508e4",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: You expected your duty to save Aria at the cost of your wife.[p/] How did that work out for you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0167117",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "LucioC: ...How dare—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8bf50",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: You couldn't bear the way she looked at you after that, could you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085e925",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: That terrified look in her eyes must have felt like a knife to the heart each day."
}

{
  "id": "line:020659e",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "LucioC: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:059ff30",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: She had no one.[p/] She was alone,[p/] save for her unrequited affections for a man who would never look her way."
}

{
  "id": "line:06632bf",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: Did you think arranging that marriage for them would [i]ever[/i] atone for beheading her mother?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da283b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Eris,[p/] stop this."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e8bc0",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: All you did was find a [i]new[/i] way to make her suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1f9ed",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: I must commend you.[p/] You'd make a great demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:044a172",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: Since I pity you so much,[p/] I'll let you in on a little secret."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9956a",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: Killing me won't save your daughter,[p/] and you [i]don't[/i] have the means to confine me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d8554",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "LucioC: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09bb552",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: But I suppose there's [i]one[/i] possible way to end my Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a292c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "LucioC: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] What is it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:058684d",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: My Contract \"will bind Aria Steelwind to the Patron so long as they [i]both[/i] live.”"
}

{
  "id": "line:023893e",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: If you truly want to free your daughter from my control,[p/] all you have to do is [i]kill[/i] her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da3ec8",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Eris: Do the poor thing a favor and put her out of her misery."
}

{
  "id": "line:025ceb3",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "LucioC: You [i]little[/i] wretch![p/][s/] I will hunt you until the end of—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0742f5e",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Rath: Enough of this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbc7b1",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Rath: Lucio...[p/] Don't indulge her.[p/] We brought her here for a reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f36978",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I just don't understand, Eris.[p/] Why are you doing this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01797e1",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're not a noble...[p/] You're not even a citizen of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0119450",
  "node": "Courtroom2_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would you go through the trouble of doing [i]any[/i] of this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9c725",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: ...Tyrion.[p/] Why are [i]you[/i] here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c1b20",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: Why do you constantly risk your life for the sake of others?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c504a",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: Why do you try to seek justice in a [i]clearly[/i] unjust world?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0544ed2",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't know.[p/] It's just what I've always done."
}

{
  "id": "line:085785c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: The answer is simple.[p/] You do it because it satisfies you."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a563a",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: You save people.[p/] You \"fight\" the system."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e4293",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: You just love indulging in your own heroics, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd00f3",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Celeste: That's not—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8fb0f",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: Does it feel good, Tyrion—[p/]to know that you're the only righteous person in an unjust society?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e469c2",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: When you succeed,[p/] you're hailed as a hero."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c14952",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: And if you fail,[p/] it's [i]society's[/i] fault,[p/] not yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed7871",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: No matter what happens,[p/] you can take solace in the knowledge that you're so much [i]better[/i] than everyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0330bc2",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: That superiority you feel over them must be intoxicating."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fef5c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Eris: Your divine blood makes it so.[p/] You just can't resist giving in to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ac489",
  "node": "Courtroom2_3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's not—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8e0bc",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: Just as your divine blood compels you to do good,[p/] [i]my[/i] hellish blood compels me to do the opposite."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6bde7",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: I just can't [i]help[/i] but take every opportunity to make each and every one of your faces contort in agony and despair."
}

{
  "id": "line:01de05c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you're just a monster—[p/]through and through."
}

{
  "id": "line:0593524",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: ...Humanity is a stain in the universe, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a5978",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: They're worthless parasites who steal,[p/] maim,[p/] and kill to get what they want."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc0649",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: That's all they are,[p/] and I [i]despise[/i] those who try to pretend that they're [i]anything[/i] different."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d073f",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I truly pity you if that's all you see in us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0605df3",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: Oh,[p/] so now it's \"us\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0652a05",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: Heaven has always condemned beings like me,[p/] all while watching humanity suffer from their secluded little heaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3f56c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: They realized that humanity would never [i]willingly[/i] choose good over evil,[p/] so they created the heavensborn to tip the balance in their favor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d94132",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: It's so self-gratifying that it makes me want to puke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f53b7c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...[i]That's[/i] what the heavensborn are?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e555d8",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: It is,[p/] and I've made it my eternal mission to break them and send them back to their creators in pieces."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e5144",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: I throw them into the deepest pit of despair before extinguishing their lives."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ed14d",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: There's been no greater joy in my eternal life."
}

{
  "id": "line:080380b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: ...And it took a lot of work to get [i]you[/i] right where I need you, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4b3aa",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Are you saying—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e0d1b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_4",
  "text": "Eris: You asked me why I did this, didn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d23b75",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "Eris: My actions that day were for you, my dearest Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a00d96",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "Eris: All so I could see the despair on your face when you realized the [i]truth[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0529f",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0741d0d",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "LucioC: That's enough out of you, you witch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b32f19",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d2839",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "LucioC: Cuthbert![p/][s/] I gave you an order under threat of execution,[p/] yet you still falter?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f6d3e",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f1f7c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "LucioC: No matter who lies before you,[p/] cut them down."
}

{
  "id": "line:018f575",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "LucioC: I will not accept defeat without a proper fight from you."
}

{
  "id": "line:041239b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "LucioC: Are a few empty words enough to force a retreat from you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbd855",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "LucioC: Is [i]that[/i] all it takes to defeat the infamous Tyrion Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a88bb",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "...If Eris was the Patron,[p/] there was very little hope for Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:050d9f9",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "Unlike Beatrice's,[p/] her Blood Contract was short and concise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3b3f3",
  "node": "Courtroom2_5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But what kind of attorney would I be—[p/] No...[p/][s/] What kind of [i]friend[/i] would I be if I didn't see this through?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0809200",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Eris.[p/] We didn't call you here today to talk about philosophy."
}

{
  "id": "line:017259c",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The people you've harmed have a right to know what you did that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:05014d6",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Tyrion: So either give us your testimony or [i]get out[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:03571d1",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: Even now,[p/] you're still undeterred.[p/] I really [i]do[/i] love that about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:094e517",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: ...But I do wonder how long that will last."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cecd4f",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: It's true.[p/] I was the one who masterminded this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef24cd",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: I knew about the King's funeral at the Grand Cathedral.[p/] So I forced Beatrice Frega to allow me to accompany her."
}

{
  "id": "line:09182f0",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: When I was there,[p/] I used my Contracts with Beatrice Frega and Aria Steelwind to compel them to act against their will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0911508",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: And through the actions of Beatrice Frega and Aria Steelwind,[p/] I facilitated the deaths of Lloyd von Sanctus,[p/] Coraline Sibyl,[p/] and Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0290717",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: The only motivation for my actions that day was to harm Tyrion Cuthbert's friends and make him suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7ab1b",
  "node": "Courtroom2_6",
  "text": "Eris: And before you ask...[p/] Aside from my thralls,[p/] I was acting alone that day.[p/] I didn't follow direct [i]or[/i] indirect orders from anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:06aa9cb",
  "node": "Courtroom2_7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your testimony is pretty...[p/] thorough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d59874",
  "node": "Courtroom2_7",
  "text": "Eris: Of course.[p/] I [i]am[/i] a demon after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0411147",
  "node": "Courtroom2_7",
  "text": "Eris: Since I'm unable to lie,[p/] I thought it would be best to be as detailed as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:018c4c6",
  "node": "Courtroom2_7",
  "text": "Eris: That way,[p/] there's no room for doubt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4fea7",
  "node": "Courtroom2_7",
  "text": "Eris: Isn't that wonderful, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ab6f2",
  "node": "Courtroom2_7",
  "text": "She may not have [i]technically[/i] lied,[p/] but she wasn't here to act in good faith."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d66b48",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: So you completely carried out this plan yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9c34f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Well,[p/] I clearly had the help of Beatrice Frega and Aria Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6060b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: So I wasn't [i]truly[/i] acting alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fce6ba",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know what I meant."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aede10",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Yes, yes.[p/] I just can't help myself sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7713a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: To state things plainly,[p/] no human [i]willingly[/i] helped me with my plan that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:047687e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How [i]did[/i] you find out about it?[p/] It was supposed to be a closely guarded secret."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cd3c2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, Tyrion.[p/] I can't tell you [i]all[/i] of my secrets.[p/] Now can I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d68dc",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "It wasn't as if I could charge her with perjury..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0deca6b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "I would just have to play along with her games."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d774a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That[/i] ability of yours is dreadful..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b1d5a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Thank you for noticing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffa60a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: That wasn't a compliment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd8e0e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I find it all quite sickening how you demons prey on people."
}

{
  "id": "line:03df845",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: \"Prey\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cc9a4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: People know what they're signing up for when they sign a Contract with a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b287f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: You can hardly blame [i]me[/i] for collecting what was freely offered."
}

{
  "id": "line:061b296",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please.[p/] We [i]both[/i] know that Aria didn't knowingly or willingly sign that Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0012dd1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: ...Aren't you just assuming that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0221a10",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: How do you know that she [i]didn't[/i] knowingly sign a Contract with me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0546ba7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: My client would never [i]willingly[/i] sign a Contract with you, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0657d1d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Really?[p/] What if I were to threaten her dearest fiancé?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0698708",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: You may see Aria as a paragon of justice,[p/] but everyone has their breaking point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e42e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: If that's true,[p/] tell us under what circumstances Aria signed the Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f917b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c24f4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Through the actions of Beatrice Frega and Aria Steelwind,[p/] I facilitated the deaths of Lloyd von Sanctus,[p/] Coraline Sibyl,[p/] and Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e246f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why are you using their full names?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0abba1e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: You know I can't lie.[p/] So I thought I'd give you [i]something[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b227e6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: For example,[p/] I could have easily referred to [i]another[/i] Steelwind or another Frega that I've enthralled."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a6eb1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: That list is [i]very[/i] long, you know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da8bf5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways...[p/] Aside from Pierce,[p/] von Sanctus and Sibyl were key members of the Wyverngarde nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3ee2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: What reason could you possibly have to kill the three of them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a136c5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Hm...[p/] I didn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:056fd54",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: I didn't have a reason to kill them.[p/] I just [i]happened[/i] to facilitate their deaths."
}

{
  "id": "line:08764d1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] But..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2510b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]specifically[/i] went after them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0deb11f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: I [i]did[/i],[p/] but I didn't have any particular reason to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:073ac2c",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that doesn't make any sense!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a3cab",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: I suppose it doesn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:03cddfe",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Anyways,[p/] would you like me to add that to my testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba7b19",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: It would help you, wouldn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0416b3c",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: I—[p/] Yes...[p/] I suppose so."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b36b8",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: I didn't really have a reason to kill [i]them[/i] specifically.[p/] I just needed Aria to kill my victims as quickly and efficiently as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0670662",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: We already established that Pierce was killed due to his knowledge of Celeste's parentage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0ea41",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could you possibly have no motivation to see them dead?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:026ae3e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm [i]not[/i]![p/][s/] That's the only logical conclusion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d53d76",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: And that's where you made your mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c72933",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: You're assuming that I act logically."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a87b12",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Every murder I'd investigated had followed [i]some[/i] kind of logic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04960f2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "But Eris was a different beast, entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2adc8",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "For all I knew,[p/] she could have done this all for the fun of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d460ba",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: My only motivation for my actions that day was to harm Tyrion Cuthbert's friends and make him suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d4246",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Is something wrong, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:016acdc",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: I went to all this trouble to get your attention.[p/] The least you could do is appreciate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f446d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "LucioC: Enough![p/] Stay on subject, witness."
}

{
  "id": "line:033104d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm not complaining about this,[p/] but if you really wanted to make me suffer,[p/] why wouldn't you just go after the people close to me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8a536",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Oh,[p/] but what would be the fun in that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a30899",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Killing people is such an [i]easy[/i] task to accomplish—[p/]even a [i]child[/i] can do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d12cb6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: It's like cooking a meal.[p/] You need to let all the ingredients marinate to get something truly delectable."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cc180",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why do you find the need to specify that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ec90e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: To leave less room for doubt."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b42b2b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Beatrice used an indirect order to feign innocence in your previous trial, didn't she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0da4dc5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: But [i]did[/i] you work together with anyone to facilitate the massacre?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03edcc6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Of course, I did."
}

{
  "id": "line:003e8fc",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: I worked together with Beatrice Frega and Aria Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae6de4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] You [i]know[/i] what I meant, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a2efb",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: My apologies.[p/] I just can't help myself sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0289f1f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: I was acting of my own free will.[p/] I didn't have a Contract with anyone to facilitate any of those murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:09678f1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "She technically couldn't lie,[p/] but she was clearly hiding something in her words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c45ac3",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Instead of examining the wording of her statements,[p/] I needed to focus on what she was clearly trying to imply with each statement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd3a2d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Sorry,[p/] but that wasn't the correct answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c2baa",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Eris: Did you notice how the music didn't stop?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b79a7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "Tyrion: I—[p/] What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5313a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "I was a little confused about what she was saying,[p/] but she [i]was[/i] right."
}

{
  "id": "line:082c770",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Eris",
  "text": "That wasn't the contradiction I was looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0569ffa",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris...[p/] You said that you needed Aria to kill them as quickly and efficiently as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:071c3cf",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that's not exactly what happened, did it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:057d5d2",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Eris: Yes...[p/] It appears I underestimated your little bodyguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb52ce",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Eris: Things lasted a [i]lot[/i] longer than I anticipated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0829c99",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's [i]not[/i] what I was referring to."
}

{
  "id": "line:017e082",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Eris: Oh?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b50ec4",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said that you needed Aria to kill \"them\" as efficiently as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c80443",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that doesn't really match with what happened to Garrick Pierce, does it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d467be",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Eris: ...Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0172c5e",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "...Why did she look so pleased with herself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04438c8",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Eris,[p/] unlike the murders of von Sanctus and Sibyl,[p/] Pierce was murdered with a blade frozen with magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa29e7",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's such an extremely convoluted way to kill someone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e94e63",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: It would only make sense if you were [i]trying[/i] to hide the evidence,[p/] but that clearly wasn't your intent."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c5127",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Eris: I agree.[p/] So why would I do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7e78c",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "LucioC: For the love of god,[p/][s/] can you [i]stop[/i] speaking in riddles?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca44e1",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "Eris: I have no love for [i]any[/i] god aside from myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0722133",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "She was behaving differently from the way she did during her testimony.[p/] She finally started being vague."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c6079",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": "I needed to stick to the facts that I knew for certain."
}

{
  "id": "line:09660af",
  "node": "ErisObj",
  "text": ":In her testimony,[p/] she said the following:"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d57e15",
  "node": "ErisObj2",
  "text": "She could have been trying to mislead me."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e4c17",
  "node": "ErisObj2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Considering who she was,[p/] she was [i]definitely[/i] trying to mislead me."
}

{
  "id": "line:020c1d3",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Player: \"I didn't really have a reason...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb1cd6",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] For all I knew,[p/] she could have had a [i]very[/i] specific reason to kill them."
}

{
  "id": "line:02554cc",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "...But she'd said multiple times that she [i]didn't[/i] have a reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d90b5d",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Out of all the parts of that statement,[p/] [i]that[/i] seems the most direct."
}

{
  "id": "line:048e783",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Perhaps one of her other phrases had something I could use."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e18e4a",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Player: \"...to kill [i]them[/i] specifically.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0c20a40",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "She used the word \"specifically\".[p/] Would that have changed the meaning of the entire phrase?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6e4a2",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "She didn't have a reason to kill the three specific victims,[p/] but she might have had a reason to kill in general..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d2b8f",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] That seemed like a stretch, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdd75e",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "She [i]did[/i] say that she did all of this for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e6545",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Did she set all of this up so I would have a mystery to solve...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0318b5c",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Perhaps one of her other phrases has something you can use."
}

{
  "id": "line:044ebad",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Player: \"I just needed Aria...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0737640",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "She said that she \"needed Aria to kill the victims\",[p/] but that phrasing didn't necessarily mean that she required Aria to do this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0318e91",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Although,[p/] I still didn't know the circumstances under which she signed that Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26d42",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Perhaps Aria was the only powerful mage she could trick or coerce into giving up control of herself,[p/] but either way,[p/] that didn't really mislead you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03be4b9",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Player: \"...to kill my victims...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0da0625",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Player: \"...as quickly and efficiently...\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3029d",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "She needed Aria to commit murders quickly and efficiently,[p/] but because of Celeste's combat prowess,[p/] that didn't end up happening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e46657",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "But that hardly seems like something intentional on her end."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d6709",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "She admitted multiple times that she \"underestimated\" Celeste.[p/] This means that she was truly caught off guard by her."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a27ca",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Player: \"...as possible.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:00c7337",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "The phrase \"as possible\" changed how that sentence read."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ad9b0",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "It's possible Aria couldn't kill Pierce quickly because of Celeste's interference."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b18f9",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Her testimony actually implied that Aria [i]didn't[/i] kill Pierce quickly and efficiently at all..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0c862",
  "node": "ErisObj3",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] Maybe one of the other phrases elaborates on this."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f192d",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "She said \"[i]my[/i] victims\" instead of \"[i]the[/i] victims\"..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ed08a",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "It was a small distinction,[p/] but a distinction nonetheless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf873a",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "I even recalled Marrunath using a similar trick during Beatrice's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:08121e4",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "Which could only mean that the victims of this case aren't the same as [i]her[/i] victims."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d377b8",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris...[p/] Which of the people in this case were [i]your[/i] victims?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03713fe",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "Eris: Considering what happened,[p/] you could say that [i]everyone[/i] at the Cathedral that day was my victim."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d035f7",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yes,[p/] but who was killed directly by Beatrice Frega or Aria Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed524",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're hiding something, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c2740",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "Eris: If that's what you think,[p/] it's definitely possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e675f8",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "[i]Again[/i] with the vague answers.[p/] Why did she even agree to testify in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0125d7e",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "There was nothing any of us could threaten her with."
}

{
  "id": "line:03047bc",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "She could have easily disappeared.[p/] She never [i]had[/i] to come here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d70d39",
  "node": "ErisObj4",
  "text": "Which means that she [i]wanted[/i] to come here,[p/][s/] but why?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac5289",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Just tell me, Eris.[p/] Who killed Lloyd von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ae91d",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Eris: Aria Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:04dd70d",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And who killed Coraline Sibyl?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0855934",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And who killed Garrick Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:079d4b6",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why are you staying silent?"
}

{
  "id": "line:089f336",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Demon,[p/] who killed Garrick Pierce?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c92ad",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Eris: I refuse to answer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb77f0",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "She was doing this on purpose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab497a",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "In her own obnoxious way,[p/] she was trying to guide me to the truth,[p/] but for what purpose?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdb5cc",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Was Aria not the one who killed Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f9741",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris.[p/] You're [i]not[/i] \"the Patron\" described in Aria's Contract, are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ee393",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Eris: Who knows?[p/] I never confirmed [i]or[/i] denied that."
}

{
  "id": "line:076b49a",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Rath: What kind of game are you playing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056f146",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "I knew it...[p/] The murders were too politically motivated to have been completely random."
}

{
  "id": "line:0461c3f",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who is the Patron, Eris?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e1261",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who is responsible for all of this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ede0b",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]want[/i] me to find out the truth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d5835",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: So why are you staying silent?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e13a4",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Eris: And what would be the fun in that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a34048",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "She wanted me to find out the truth.[p/] That meant I [i]already[/i] had the evidence I needed to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d446c4",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Eris: You've felt it, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:083981e",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Eris: Ever since the investigation started,[p/] you've felt a nagging feeling in the back of your mind, haven't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01da6c1",
  "node": "ErisObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What?[p/][s/] How did you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0556ec0",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "Eris: Even [i]with[/i] the Eye of a god,[p/] you're still blinded by your human sentimentality."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7a8a7",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "Eris: So think through it carefully."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2bae0",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "Eris: Who killed Garrick Pierce that day?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0711480",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "Okay...[p/] I needed to think through this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ad46d",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "I let everything else disappear from the world.[p/] I needed to look at each of the pieces and where they lay on the board."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c50bc",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "Eris wasn't the Patron.[p/] That meant that someone else was controlling Aria's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0861707",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "But they still coordinated with Eris,[p/] who had control of Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5807b",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "In an extremely roundabout way,[p/] Eris admitted that Aria was used to kill von Sanctus and Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c6e05",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "When the Patron killed those two,[p/] they were able to effectively counter every magical defense they brought up."
}

{
  "id": "line:026f3ac",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "They knew von Sanctus still needed oxygen in his [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b525f6",
  "node": "ErisObj8",
  "text": "And they knew Sibyl could still drown if she was frozen by [b]Hold Creature[/b] and affected by [b]Stone Skin[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0023ddd",
  "node": "ErisObj8a",
  "text": "0000|0200"
}

{
  "id": "line:085a9f4",
  "node": "ErisObj8a",
  "text": "No...[p/] The Patron came up with creative ways to bypass the defenses of both of those spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:0282e3e",
  "node": "ErisObj8a",
  "text": "This wasn't their first time doing something like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fab882",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "They were well-versed in using magic lethally."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fb2f4",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "But something was different about Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fc15e",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "Eris implied that neither Aria nor Beatrice killed Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb6c38",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "So did the Patron kill him personally?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea2b7c",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "But why?[p/] They already [i]had[/i] control of Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8fad7",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "I would imagine the entire [i]point[/i] of enthralling her would be to hide their own involvement."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd4bb5",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "Did they become impatient because Celeste was holding her ground against Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c0b12",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "No...[p/] Beatrice was already able to slip past them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0007ed7",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": ":That was how she knocked me and Pierce out with a [b]Sleep[/b] spell at 2:30 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:028488b",
  "node": "ErisObj9",
  "text": "If the Patron was coordinating with Eris,[p/] she could have easily had Beatrice kill Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a58df1",
  "node": "ErisObj10",
  "text": "No...[p/] Eris had the means to murder Pierce while he was knocked out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0065b18",
  "node": "ErisObj10",
  "text": "It was strange,[p/] but there was one possible explanation for why they killed Pierce personally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeebec",
  "node": "ErisObj11",
  "text": "They [i]wanted[/i] to kill Pierce personally."
}

{
  "id": "line:031ecbd",
  "node": "ErisObj11",
  "text": "Did that mean Pierce's murder was more emotionally driven than the other two?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033cf49",
  "node": "ErisObj11",
  "text": "That might explain why the method used to murder him was so contrived."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c2d4",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "The \"truth\"...[p/] She [i]wanted[/i] me to piece it together."
}

{
  "id": "line:03292d6",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "At first,[p/] I thought she was trying to blame me for what happened,[p/] but if that were true,[p/] she wouldn't still be here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b65d44",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "There's something else that she wanted me to realize—[p/]all to throw me into despair somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea8340",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "Through the way the Patron controlled Aria,[p/] they were creative and skilled at using magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f2893",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "They must've been constantly exposed to situations where they encountered spells and all of their restrictions."
}

{
  "id": "line:078ec6a",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "They also personally handed a Blood Contract to Aria and had her sign it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecc8f6",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "Going by what I knew,[p/] Aria was either threatened or tricked into signing that Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:056b24f",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "So whoever did this must've had the strength to threaten her,[p/] or they were deeply trusted by her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7ae40",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "In addition to that,[p/] they must've been close to the Prayer Room before the attack happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:035e566",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "And lastly—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0131f2c",
  "node": "ErisObj12",
  "text": "—They must've had a personal grudge against Garrick Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0c01d",
  "node": "ErisObj13",
  "text": "Celeste"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3a68d",
  "node": "ErisObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/][s/] That's not—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edf3cc",
  "node": "ErisObj13",
  "text": "But it was where all of the clues led me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0645e46",
  "node": "ErisObj13a",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3c8ca",
  "node": "ErisObj13a",
  "text": "Tyrion: It can't be—![p/][s/] That's not—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01ec95a",
  "node": "ErisObj13a",
  "text": "Eris wanted me to suffer,[p/] but I owed it to Aria not to run away from this."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd1e5",
  "node": "ErisObj13a",
  "text": "No...[p/] I owed it to [i]everyone[/i] within Wyverngarde to see this through."
}

{
  "id": "line:08165ba",
  "node": "ErisObj13b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Stop it![p/][s/] It [i]has[/i] to be someone else!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aecade",
  "node": "ErisObj13b",
  "text": "Tyrion: She would never—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01351f0",
  "node": "ErisObj13b",
  "text": "No matter how much I wanted to,[p/] I couldn't think of anyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0063efe",
  "node": "ErisObj13b",
  "text": "Who else would Eris have chosen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07955af",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Damn it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de8d3f",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Damn it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0e8f7",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: [j]AGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGH![/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb02e8",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "My scream of pure rage echoed through the temple."
}

{
  "id": "line:0300e6d",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "I was giving Eris exactly what she wanted,[p/] but I didn't know what else to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d082bf",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "LucioC: ...What is this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b558c3",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Rath: ...Is everything okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038d097",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] Are you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26324",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "I looked at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0646258",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "We both remained silent,[p/] a shared understanding of the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baaa8d",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Eris: [i]There[/i] it is![p/][s/] You've realized it, haven't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cef7b8",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Eris: I've been waiting for this moment for [i]so[/i] long!"
}

{
  "id": "line:062b48a",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "LucioC: What are you talking about?![p/][s/] I demand an explanation!"
}

{
  "id": "line:000f81f",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Rath: ...Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] What have you discovered?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c3f5b",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Eris: Tell them, Tyrion![p/][s/] Tell them who did this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02792da",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Eris: Issue your Divine Edict, right now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0caa418",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "I [i]wanted[/i] to be wrong.[p/] I'd never wanted anything more in my entire life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8d881",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "Nothing would make me happier than having this Edict fail,[p/] even if it cost me my life..."
}

{
  "id": "line:015f979",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "...But I knew.[p/] I finally realized what had happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:006c0f1",
  "node": "ErisObj14",
  "text": "I barely muttered my next words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0588ec8",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris Illmater...[p/] Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0233528",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Eris: Tyrion Cuthbert...[p/] Attorney of the Arcane."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d97fe6",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the Eye of Horus,[p/][s/] I issue upon you a Divine Edict."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dc2d9",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: Release thy guards and manifest your Blood Contract with..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d97705",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Eris: Say it![p/][s/] Say her name so that [i]everyone[/i] can hear it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0507350",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Release thy guards and manifest your Blood Contract with..."
}

{
  "id": "line:075d394",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f645c0",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] [i]died[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0476908",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/][s/] I'm sorry I—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fae13f",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Rath: ...What the [i]hell[/i] is going on?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00da881",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "LucioC: Demon![p/][s/] What is the meaning of this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f647d3",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Eris: It's exactly what it looks like."
}

{
  "id": "line:0749e1c",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Eris: The Patron you've been looking for has been right in front of you the entire time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0072022",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Rath: ...Ms. McCoy."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b5377",
  "node": "ErisObj15",
  "text": "Rath: Did you sign a Blood Contract with the Empress of Discord?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d8c7c",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0344fd9",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: It was the only thing that would save Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0697097",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: I never fought Aria.[p/] I fought Beatrice and Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3014d",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: Beatrice's illusions were too much for me.[p/] They broke past me and ran into the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b6b57",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: But the person they killed wasn't Pierce...[p/] It was you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0099c9d",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] You..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05658cd",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "She couldn't even bring herself to say it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b26e01",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Eris: Do you realize now, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c1653",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Stop it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01259d1",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Eris: Celeste McCoy was the last person you had that hadn't betrayed you,[p/] and she signed away [i]her[/i] soul to [i]me[/i]...[p/] All so that she could save [i]you[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a47d1",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Eris: Why the somber look, Lucio?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fa070",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Eris: Weren't you going to \"execute\" the Patron the [i]moment[/i] you knew who they were?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001120b",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "LucioC: ...McCoy.[p/] Does this mean what I think it means?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd065c",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Yes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2f43e",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]I'm[/i] the one who tricked Aria into signing that Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a69dc8",
  "node": "ErisObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?![p/][s/] How [i]could[/i] you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:020c6e7",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: I was so stupid...[p/] When I made that deal with her,[p/] I didn't expect her to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb5817",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76910",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She used that Contract to make you act against your will."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d400e",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Rath: So it wasn't just Ms. Steelwind and Ms. Frega who were controlled that day..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f70bba",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Eris: You realize it.[p/] Don't you, Lucio?"
}

{
  "id": "line:064e573",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Eris: As long as the Contract with the Patron exists,[p/] your daughter will always be vulnerable to my influence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2fd02",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Eris: You can't [i]kill[/i] me,[p/] so there's only one solution to free your daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cf94f",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: Indeed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c14f37",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: Understand one thing, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c6cb6",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: After the lengths you've gone to for my daughter,[p/] I have nothing but the utmost respect for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5a02",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: ...But I [i]will[/i] do whatever is necessary to protect her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0451f39",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Rath: L-[p/][s/]Lucio![p/][s/] We can't act rashly!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec3f62",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Eris: I'll let you all in on a little demonic secret."
}

{
  "id": "line:00272b8",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Eris: It doesn't matter if you confine her within a prison."
}

{
  "id": "line:096543e",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Eris: The Patron will be able to take control of Aria,[p/] no matter where she is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c59277",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Eris: But if you kill her,[p/] Aria will finally be free from my control."
}

{
  "id": "line:013bfa3",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:019988a",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you saying?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0832718",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: I should have done this from the beginning..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb54d8",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: When I realized what happened,[p/] I should have just come forward and admitted to what I did,[p/] but I kept holding onto the hope that it was all some kind of trick."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e0b38",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: I prayed and prayed for the Patron to be someone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c71d34",
  "node": "ErisObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion.[p/] I was hoping [i]you'd[/i] find something that would prove that somehow all of this [i]wasn't[/i] my fault."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b8bc3",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "...I'd finally found the culprit I'd been looking for,[p/] and it was absolutely breaking me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6a550",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "That nagging feeling I'd been experiencing—[p/]it was my absolute trust in Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fddae3",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Actually,[p/] it still hadn't gone away.[p/] That uneasiness is still there."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ab442",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: ...I suppose there's no reason to continue with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:04faa0b",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...W-[p/][s/]Wait—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:053d735",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: I sympathize with your position, Cuthbert,[p/] but even McCoy recognizes what must be done."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bc80a",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: ...It's over,[p/] and I will not allow this [i]demon[/i] to control my daughter any longer."
}

{
  "id": "line:043ea67",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]You can't just—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04c6d",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: Kingsguard...[p/] Restrain him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce62f8",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec3a50",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Rath: Lucio!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0048b23",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Aria: That's enough!"
}

{
  "id": "line:030044b",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Aria: ...What kind of \"court\" is this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f4df3",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Aria leapt from the platforms above and landed right onto the witness stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eca34e",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "She kicked Eris out of the way.[p/] Something that even caught [i]her[/i] off guard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0968f7f",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Celeste: Aria...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f11ec9",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I'm so sorry,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfa99d",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Aria: Celeste McCoy is [i]innocent[/i] until proven guilty!"
}

{
  "id": "line:085ffce",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "Aria: I won't let anyone pass judgment on her until [i]that[/i] is unequivocally proven!"
}

{
  "id": "line:074e06a",
  "node": "ErisObj18",
  "text": "LucioC: You fool![p/][s/] What are you doing?![p/][s/] It's your—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e086f",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: ...How [i]dare[/i] you, Grand General?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d2db8",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "LucioC: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06abdcc",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: How could you possibly think that [i]you[/i] have the right to decide who lives and who dies?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03773e5",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: You aren't even a real prosecutor![p/][s/] You're just a child playing at the law!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0066b5c",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Lucio just stood there,[p/] eyes wide and bewildered.[p/] He stammered for a bit but said nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:092de24",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: And [i]you[/i], Tyrion![p/] How can you just stand there?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:033a376",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...M-[p/][s/]Me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1bf8d",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: You're Celeste's attorney![p/][s/] Isn't it [i]your[/i] job to defend her until her last breath?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:041eb36",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't see the truth because I didn't want to believe it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7e1a8",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: I almost let it slip away because of my own personal feelings.[p/] I almost put you at risk."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fee85",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I need to approach this objectively."
}

{
  "id": "line:077713e",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: To [i]hell[/i] with that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0357813",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Huh?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a252",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: Justice may be blind,[p/] but I will [i]not[/i] allow it to be rendered heartless![p/] Not as long as I'm here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1ee69",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: You mean the world to her![p/][s/] She consigned her very [i]soul[/i] to hell to protect you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0669af4",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Aria: If you abandon her when she needs you most,[p/][s/] then you don't [i]deserve[/i] her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03882cd",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a854fa",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "The prosecutor was right.[p/] We were all being cowards."
}

{
  "id": "line:022264a",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Me,[p/] Lucio,[p/] even Celeste—[p/]we all just wanted to run into the inevitable to save us the pain."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7f146",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] Can you testify about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d95826",
  "node": "ErisObj19",
  "text": "Celeste: What...?[p/] But—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7fdbe",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Aria is right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3bb58",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: We need to do this properly."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dd57d",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Rath: ...I agree,[p/] and I will [i]not[/i] pass judgment until we have determined exactly what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec9798",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Fine.[p/] Do as you wish."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa360e",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "LucioC: But the moment we're certain of the truth,[p/] I [i]will[/i] do what is necessary."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e619a",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Rath: ...Very well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0411d65",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Rath: Ms. McCoy.[p/] Please take the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d8354",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion, I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0997798",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Witness,[p/] please testify about what you did that day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db9930",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: ...O-[p/][s/]Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c666fe",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: The truth is that Eris rewrote your memories, Tyrion.[p/] You were actually knocked out at 1:45 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:05448e6",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: We went to the Prayer Room a lot earlier for our meeting,[p/] and that commotion we heard was actually Beatrice and Eris attacking the guards at 1:40 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bccbe7",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: They tricked me and slipped into the Prayer Room...[p/] After that,[p/] Beatrice killed you."
}

{
  "id": "line:02033be",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: I didn't know what to do.[p/] That's when Eris told me she would resurrect you in exchange for killing Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa087d",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: I know I shouldn't have done it,[p/] but I just wanted you back...[p/] I didn't care about what happened to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfa86f",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: I didn't realize that she'd use \"my eternal servitude\" to take control of my body.[p/] She used me to trick Aria into signing [i]another[/i] Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e6137",
  "node": "ErisObj20",
  "text": "Celeste: After that...[p/] I followed through with [i]my[/i] end of the deal.[p/] I killed Pierce so that she would bring Tyrion back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6814f",
  "node": "ErisObj21",
  "text": "That nagging feeling was still there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc4bca",
  "node": "ErisObj21",
  "text": "LucioC: Well?[p/] On with it, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:036195d",
  "node": "ErisObj21",
  "text": "LucioC: Begin your cross-examination, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:01600fb",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She [i]rewrote[/i] my memories?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4a116",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: I didn't realize it until [i]after[/i] you woke up and gave your statement to the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a83d4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: She must've changed your memories when she resurrected you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2e6f2",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Eris had the power to take control of people against their will."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d7d01",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "And she clearly had the power to bring people back from the dead..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b893c",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "But if that were true,[p/] could I even trust my [i]own[/i] memories?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b076d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] I suppose you didn't have control of Aria until then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2cc86",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Does that mean you never even fought her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e1bbe",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: I had to create an alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6d9d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste![p/][s/] The Inquisition arrested her because of [i]your[/i] testimony!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af22cb",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Rath: ...The testimonies of Prince Alaric and the High Speaker also implicated her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5cdf9",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Rath: Ms. Steelwind also knew she was compromised due to finding the Purple Mark in her pocket."
}

{
  "id": "line:074ca51",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Rath: I'm sure things would have ended the same,[p/] regardless of her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:047b527",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "LucioC: What did Frega and that demon do when you found them, McCoy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049800d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: They tricked me and slipped into the Prayer Room...[p/] After that,[p/] Beatrice...[p/] killed you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eed120",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did they trick you so easily?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0acde84",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: When I went to see what was going on,[p/] I only saw Eris and Beatrice standing over the guards' bodies."
}

{
  "id": "line:069edea",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: They acted like someone [i]else[/i] had killed them."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c007b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: Then they lied to me and said that they wanted to go into the Prayer Room for protection."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb0922",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: Beatrice used an illusion to distract me.[p/] That's when she—"
}

{
  "id": "line:012520e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How did Beatrice kill me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ff6c3",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: She hit you with some kind of [b]necromancy[/b] spell,[p/] but it didn't visibly wound you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0184f0e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: When I checked your body,[p/] it was already cold...[p/] Your heart was stopped."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4eb0",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: I think she used [b]Necrotic Blight[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8ac8b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]that's[/i] why Lord Asclepius said that I had traces of [b]necromancy[/b] on me."
}

{
  "id": "line:083c513",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "She must have lied about trying to heal me as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e16ff7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What did you do after I died?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b284b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sure that was her goal from the very beginning."
}

{
  "id": "line:043ff9d",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: She wanted you to make a deal with her.[p/] It was all so she could make [i]me[/i] suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:016f43f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] I'm so—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:017f682",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Stop."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fb239",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Just...[p/] Don't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a60a06",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could you [i]possibly[/i] think that was okay?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:077cfdf",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: I knew it was wrong[p/] but I just couldn't..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e702b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry.[p/] I didn't know what to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0684b3f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Rath: ...There will be plenty of time to discuss this privately, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a65c4",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] That part [i]was[/i] written in a slightly misleading way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0353e2c",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "LucioC: She must've thought that the Empress would whisk her away to serve her in hell,[p/] but instead she took control of her immediately after."
}

{
  "id": "line:047fe10",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "LucioC: ...You should have known better than to trust a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d0141",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How did Eris make you trick Aria into signing that Blood Contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd7aaa",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: She made me tell Aria that Pierce was demanding a plea deal in exchange for telling me who my parents were."
}

{
  "id": "line:0893ad8",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: Eris made Beatrice put an [b]illusion[/b] over the Contract to make it look like a request for an appeal."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ea521",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...And since Pierce was originally convicted for killing my father,[p/] she respected my wishes."
}

{
  "id": "line:01af7d9",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could you think I'd [i]ever[/i] want that, Celeste?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d919aa",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: I knew you wouldn't want this,[p/][s/] but it just wasn't fair!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07831c6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: Why should a person like [i]him[/i] get to live instead of you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:062f02f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...It was an easy choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c3a8b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't care if you hate me after this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd06e9",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: But even now,[p/][p/][s/] I would [i]still[/i] make that same choice!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0874259",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I don't hate—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c15c8f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "I couldn't let my emotions get out of hand.[p/] I needed to focus on the case for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0410f63",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Rath: ...Perhaps we should stay focused on what happened for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:083fa7f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "She wouldn't intentionally lie about something like this,[p/] but why did I feel like something she said didn't match up with the evidence I had?"
}

{
  "id": "line:071ce5c",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Was there really something for me to PRESENT?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06fb3db",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste![p/][s/] Your testimony contradicts the evidence and [i]this[/i] proves it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d802ee",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'm sorry,[p/] but I don't really see how that proves anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e0565",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_Cel",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh...[p/] I suppose you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb30bb",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] According to you,[p/] we heard a commotion at 1:40PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:006d47e",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: You went out to investigate,[p/] and [i]that's[/i] when you saw Eris and Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f21e0b",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I lied all about my fight against Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d9050",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Celeste: I never even fought her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0933c2b",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "If that were true,[p/] how could I explain this discrepancy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c76c5",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "I couldn't trust my own memories,[p/] but Laefe, Miriam, and Lazarick shouldn't have been affected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0524da7",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: The thing is, Celeste,[p/] something about your timeline doesn't match the evidence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ade949",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Celeste: Really?[p/] But I was pretty sure of the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a1084",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Celeste: We were supposed to be at the meeting at 1:45 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:090ae7a",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/][s/] What did you just say?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d1904",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Celeste: Our meeting with Pierce—[p/]it was scheduled for 1:45 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0446eb5",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Rath: ...What's wrong, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f91b0",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] your timeline of what happened is completely off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8a988",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: A lot of your testimony doesn't match what we've learned thus far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc832a",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] But I swear I'm not lying!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a62a38",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Firstly,[p/] it's about the exact time you saw Eris and Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbfc66",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: According to you,[p/] you saw them at 1:40 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:03edcd8",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But Laefe,[p/] Miriam,[p/] and Lazarick didn't lose track of them until 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f78073",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Celeste: What...?[p/] When did they say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0788a79",
  "node": "CelObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You were [i]there[/i] with me when we spoke to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be7272",
  "node": "CelObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: I know![p/] I was paying really close attention!"
}

{
  "id": "line:079cf7a",
  "node": "CelObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: I needed to see how close you were to finding out the truth..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bac8f6",
  "node": "CelObj2",
  "text": "Celeste: So, why can't I remember...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0072dd1",
  "node": "CelObj2",
  "text": "She [i]couldn't[/i] remember?"
}

{
  "id": "line:077701a",
  "node": "CelObj3",
  "text": "Letter from Garrick Pierce"
}

{
  "id": "line:009520c",
  "node": "CelObj3",
  "text": "No...[p/] Celeste said something earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:089ae9b",
  "node": "CelObj3",
  "text": "She said that we arrived at the meeting much earlier than I remembered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f89768",
  "node": "CelObj3",
  "text": "And that contradicted a [i]physical[/i] piece of evidence that I."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7681a",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste![p/][s/] This letter from Garrick Pierce told us to meet him in the Prayer Room at [i]2:00[/i]PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ea920",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris may have changed [i]my[/i] memories,[p/][s/] but changing a physical piece of evidence is a different thing entirely!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02efbdc",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: But we don't know the full extent of her capabilities.[p/] Can we really rule that out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d249ef",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: You were unconscious.[p/] Illmater had plenty of time to access your body [i]and[/i] your belongings."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c8716",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "At that point,[p/] [i]anything[/i] was possible,[p/] and we knew too little about Eris's abilities to say for sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0904514",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "But if Lucio was right,[p/] Eris could have gone around doing whatever she wanted."
}

{
  "id": "line:058bb61",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "She could've wiped the memories of every witness who saw the crimes.[p/] She could've manipulated the crime scenes however she wished."
}

{
  "id": "line:045dd7e",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "But if she had done so,[p/] there would've been logical inconsistencies."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bbb01",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "Until Celeste was revealed as the Patron,[p/] every piece of evidence I'd found or deduced had been logically consistent."
}

{
  "id": "line:010a287",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "The contradictions in what Celeste is saying could be explained by Eris changing several elements of the crime."
}

{
  "id": "line:08744a8",
  "node": "CelObj4",
  "text": "...But there was a far simpler explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a2955",
  "node": "CelObj5",
  "text": "No...[p/] It was possible that Eris really was some kind of omnipotent being.[p/] Maybe she really could change details like that on a whim."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f17db2",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] Eris currently has your \"eternal servitude\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:003dfb4",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: If she could manipulate my memories,[p/] what's to say that she's not manipulating [i]your[/i] memories right now?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a77755",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Celeste: I...[p/] [i]guess[/i] that's possible,[p/] but why would she even bother doing that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:061d9ab",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She wouldn't [i]need[/i] to do that unless she still had something to hide."
}

{
  "id": "line:030d703",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "LucioC: Are you serious?![p/][s/] What more is there left for her [i]to[/i] hide?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0827b",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Whatever it is,[p/] it was important enough to make drastic changes to Celeste's memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f57aeb",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03cbe49",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: If [i]that's[/i] true,[p/] that means Celeste's [i]true[/i] memories will tell us exactly what we need to know."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d0503",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Celeste: B-[p/][s/]But,[p/] even if you're right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0375515",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't remember what really happened.[p/] She has full control of my mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:006627e",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That doesn't matter.[p/] It's just like [i]every[/i] cross-examination we've ever done."
}

{
  "id": "line:04acc5d",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you keep testifying,[p/] she'll keep changing your memories to tell more lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:01324b8",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c89f0b",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] It's really obnoxious how persistent you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:042a869",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Celeste: Why can't you all just give up already?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b86445",
  "node": "CelObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's you![p/][s/] Isn't it, Eris?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae6fe3",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Celeste: Unfortunately,[p/] your little interrogation ends here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01572d8",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "LucioC: Kingsguard![p/][s/] What are you doing?![p/][s/] Destroy Illmater's body!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d47c0",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Celeste: Too late, Lucio.[p/] I win."
}

{
  "id": "line:066432d",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: C-[p/][s/]Celeste?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ffc14",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Damn it all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:015e523",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris![p/][s/] What did you do to her?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a34104",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Eris: I put her to sleep.[p/] Just as I did with Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8ff59",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:067e7f1",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Why would you do such a thing, demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0372dca",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Eris: What do you mean?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:067a573",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Eris: I did it for the same reason I do anything!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e7087",
  "node": "CelObj7",
  "text": "Eris: What would make Tyrion suffer more than putting his love in an eternal sleep?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad047c",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: You could have just done that from the beginning, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:035be29",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: We can't extract any information from her like this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0057257",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: The only person who can tell us what we need to know—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e23746",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: —is Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0758e6f",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Ever since I discovered the truth about what she did,[p/] one possibility had been floating around in my mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a77331",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "But was it even possible?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e26a5",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "No...[p/] That didn't even matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:03980f0",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Eris Illmater."
}

{
  "id": "line:0958ba6",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Eris: What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f56156",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: What would happen if I nullified Celeste's Blood Contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0253200",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Eris: ...Assuming there's [i]anything[/i] to even dispute,[p/] [i]everything[/i] granted by the Contract would be reversed."
}

{
  "id": "line:089e295",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Eris: And I don't think you fully [i]understand[/i] what that means."
}

{
  "id": "line:00def03",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9dd2f",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: ...What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0489648",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your men should know where Ruby Tymora's law office is."
}

{
  "id": "line:048037c",
  "node": "CelObj8",
  "text": "LucioC: They [i]do[/i]..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1f2c6",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: You'll need an attorney to cross-examine Celeste's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf819d",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: She owes me,[p/] and she'll be able to finish this on my behalf."
}

{
  "id": "line:073f428",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Eris: Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abb971",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Tell her I'm sorry I couldn't say goodbye to her in person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0677b00",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Eris: ...You're not [i]serious[/i], are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07435f2",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Eris: I am among the eldest evils who have ever lived.[p/] I-[p/][s/]I would [i]never[/i] create a faulty contract!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d9c86",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris Illmater![p/][s/] Empress of Discord!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0277b41",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Eris: W-[p/][s/]Wait...[p/] You know I can't speak lies, correct?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5beff",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the Eye of Horus,[p/][s/] I demand the opportunity to dispute your Blood Contract with Celeste McCoy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0be98a6",
  "node": "CelObj11",
  "text": "Eris: I-[p/][s/]I'll state it plainly, then![p/][s/] There will be no room for doubt!"
}

{
  "id": "line:037d7a9",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't care."
}

{
  "id": "line:044bd09",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Eris: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d92f9",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste sacrificed her life to save mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:005907f",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could I ever face her again if I didn't do the same for her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0255f8f",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Eris: You're insane!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8e48d",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Eris: You're just risking [i]death[/i] for nothing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0595e02",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Rath: ...Why are you so nervous?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0504a1d",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe this [i]is[/i] pointless,[p/] but I will [i]never[/i] stop fighting for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0364226",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Eris: ...S-[p/][s/]Stop this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00db260",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "Once you pass this point,[p/] you will not be able to SAVE your game for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e667c5",
  "node": "CelObj13",
  "text": "It is recommended that you make a SAVE FILE now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0885e9c",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Tyrion: Just try to tell us what you remember, Celeste.[p/] Any detail might help,[p/] whether it's true or false."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd19f9",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:010f114",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Celeste: I think I remember now.[p/] We went to meet with Pierce at 1:50 PM.[p/] And we heard that commotion outside at 2:20 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:010493d",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Celeste: I saw Aria attacking the guards there.[p/] And I fought her for about fifteen minutes before she broke past me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbf1e8",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Celeste: When I followed her into the Prayer Room,[p/] I found her there with Beatrice and Eris.[p/] They knocked Aria,[p/] Tyrion,[p/] and Pierce unconscious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7bc1a",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I checked Tyrion's body and thought he was dead,[p/] but Beatrice just cast [b]Feign Death[/b] on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:070e1d6",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Celeste: Anyways,[p/] Eris offered her deal to me,[p/] but I couldn't go through with killing Pierce...[p/] I think you know the rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:05aca13",
  "node": "Courtroom2B",
  "text": "Celeste: A few minutes after Pierce died,[p/] Aster,[p/] the Inquisition,[p/] and the Kingsguard showed up to arrest Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c028e",
  "node": "Courtroom2B_2",
  "text": "LucioC: Only the times of each event had changed.[p/] Her testimony remains the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:0955201",
  "node": "Courtroom2B_2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if there's nothing [i]apparently[/i] significant,[p/] I'd still like to cross-examine her."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f222a",
  "node": "Courtroom2B_2",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Go ahead, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fe475",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] We now know for certain that the meeting [i]was[/i] at 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0653b03",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] She only changed my memories so she could trick all of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:09823d5",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Considering that [i]my[/i] memories were intact,[p/] she must have not had the power to change them."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a7c5e",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: Yes...[p/] She never actually used her demonic powers to revive you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0014b0a",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: She merely had Beatrice release the [b]Feign Death[/b] spell that [i]she[/i] originally cast."
}

{
  "id": "line:093073f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways...[p/] Who did you see attacking the guards?[p/] Was it Aria or Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:067d5d1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Originally,[p/] you said that you fought her for a [i]lot[/i] longer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0babc05",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: I had to account for the time I spent speaking to Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0773444",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: I had a [i]feeling[/i] something was off about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6f5c9",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: I knew Tyrion would be really meticulous about the timeline of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f9b87",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: So I had to make my testimony match up with the time of Pierce's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abedf7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'm [i]really[/i] sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ffb27",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Let's just focus on the matter at hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c4d73",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: So we [i]weren't[/i] wrong about Beatrice sneaking past you during your fight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0308492",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] Now that I look back on it,[p/] it was probably a distraction so Beatrice could sneak past me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bda4e6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a39b08",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: What is it, Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ae3e8",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: If the Patron was working [i]together[/i] with Eris,[p/] why would Eris use Beatrice to knock out Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0619bb6",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: I never thought of that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0499429",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Frankly,[p/] I find it hard to believe that the Patron willingly went along with the Empress's convoluted plan."
}

{
  "id": "line:00267a3",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: They clearly [i]needed[/i] Pierce to die,[p/] and relying on McCoy to do it seems foolhardy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0630313",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Right...[p/] Was it possible that Eris went off-script then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09b7033",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "She definitely didn't seem like the type of demon to take orders from a human."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c79d7",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: ...I can't believe you fell for such an obvious deception."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cbab0",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: I thought Tyrion was dead.[p/] I wasn't thinking clearly."
}

{
  "id": "line:029bc71",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Rath: ...Perhaps it's best to stick to the facts for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:018b57f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: ...To think one Blood Contract could have such an effect on the investigation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f18de1",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Celeste: I should have known she was up to something,[p/] but I just wasn't thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:06dae83",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Rath: ...You were put in a difficult situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0557b",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Rath: Take solace in the fact that you stuck to your ideals despite that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05812f8",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: This must have been after they went to investigate the fire in the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd42dd",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm surprised Aster went to the Prayer Room as well.[p/] I'd have thought the Kingsguard would have kept him in a secure location."
}

{
  "id": "line:074b9ef",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Those [i]were[/i] my orders,[p/] but His Majesty demanded that they secure the Cathedral for the safety of everyone there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5dc8f",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Rath: Hm...[p/] Ever the altruist, that one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0112a58",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "Her testimony didn't appear to add any new information."
}

{
  "id": "line:0162430",
  "node": "Cross-Examination_CelFinal",
  "text": "But between the multiple murders and Eris changing people's memories,[p/] there might've been something I'd missed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de7ca0",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/][s/] What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7ad1b",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste.[p/] Are you [i]sure[/i] Aster showed up only a [i]few[/i] minutes after Pierce died?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b8721",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah...[p/] I remember [i]that[/i] part pretty well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0184b40",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Celeste: Eris seemed really worried about being seen by them."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ba6d9",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Rath: Have you figured something out, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095bc32",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's just that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:065dad6",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "LucioC: May I remind you that we are [i]extremely[/i] pressed for time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0077e26",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "LucioC: Out with it![p/][s/] Stop wasting our time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0350e5f",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste.[p/] Garrick Pierce died at 2:45 PM and [i]Aster[/i] showed up in the Prayer Room only a few minutes afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b1b20",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah?[p/] Where are you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee0ad8",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d77d3",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: That raises a big question."
}

{
  "id": "line:08daf24",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: How did Aster enter the Prayer Room around 2:45 PM?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056e607",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...When he [i]should[/i] have been trapped in a [b]Force Cage[/b] until [i]3:00 PM[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e3f73",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]Wait...[p/][s/] You're not serious, are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0efa5ab",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "LucioC: M-[p/][s/]McCoy's memories are clearly unreliable!"
}

{
  "id": "line:042c60d",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "LucioC: My men [i]all[/i] reported that His Majesty led them to the Prayer Room [i]after[/i] he exited the [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ede544",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: Normally...[p/] That [i]would[/i] be more concrete when compared to Celeste's testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8719a",
  "node": "CelFinObj",
  "text": "Tyrion: But we can't trust their testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0006208",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ee119",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: While I was disputing Celeste's Contract,[p/] Eris declared that she made Contracts with multiple members of the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0950758",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:035eff7",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: They were working together with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03869d1",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And if these Contracts were structured similarly to Celeste's,[p/] she must have had the ability to manipulate their memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec4373",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: This means they could've intentionally [i]or[/i] unintentionally lied during questioning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1ad86",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Rath: How could I have let this happen...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e49091",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: That's still ridiculous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b8528",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: Are you saying that [i]everyone[/i] who remembered seeing His Majesty in that [b]Force Cage[/b] had their memories manipulated?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:034b8e4",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: No,[p/] I think there's a simpler explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bdaa0",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: ...And what would [i]that[/i] be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee348c",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: His Majesty must be a powerful mage.[p/] Wouldn't he know how to cast [b]Major Illusion[/b]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0519989",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: If he'd placed an illusion inside the [b]Force Cage[/b],[p/] he could take advantage of the chaos and the contracted Kingsguard to slip away."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d2e5d",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if we assume that he somehow escaped an [i]inescapable[/i] [b]Force Cage[/b],[p/] how did Aster [i]know[/i] to head to the Prayer Room?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d942a0",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: I-[p/][s/]I understand your point..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af65c4",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "LucioC: But do you [i]understand[/i] what you're implying?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:084aea2",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not trying to imply anything.[p/] I'm just stating the facts that we know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f77f87",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: We know that a human,[p/] whether willingly or otherwise,[p/] worked with the Empress of Discord to orchestrate this massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6eee3",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was deeply trusted by Aria Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f23822",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So much so that she didn't even think [i]twice[/i] about signing a Contract that he gave her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5c4b6",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one person who meets those criteria..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03fab8f",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Aster de Wyverngarde:[p/][s/] the reigning king of our kingdom!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ac16e",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Rath: Quiet![p/][s/] All of you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3b285",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Rath: Mr. Cuthbert...[p/] Do you understand the weight of this accusation?"
}

{
  "id": "line:088750b",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Rath: You're claiming that the [i]king[/i] collaborated with a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a6f85",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I do,[p/] but I'm [i]hoping[/i] this is all a misunderstanding."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f03e7",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: After all,[p/] Eris’s goal seemed to be nothing beyond sowing as much discord as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1c47d",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: She made us believe that Celeste and Aria were [i]both[/i] murderers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0681b47",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Aster has information that can save Aria,[p/] we have to find it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e1a02",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Rath: ...Very well, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0975c",
  "node": "CelFinObj4",
  "text": "Rath: I suppose it's only right then,[p/] with everything that has transpired,[p/] that the king should be allowed to explain himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d74b12",
  "node": "CelFinObj5",
  "text": "LucioC: Kingsguard![p/][s/] Please escort His Majesty to the stand!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ca608",
  "node": "CelFinObj5",
  "text": "Aster: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08343e7",
  "node": "CelFinObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Thank you for cooperating, Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:08858c7",
  "node": "CelFinObj5",
  "text": "Aster: Of course.[p/] I understand your position, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e33d07",
  "node": "CelFinObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am hoping you can shed some light on how Aria came to be under the Blood Contract in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a978be",
  "node": "CelFinObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's possible Eris tricked you somehow and made [i]you[/i] carry out the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5cbc4",
  "node": "CelFinObj5",
  "text": "Tyrion: There has to be something we're not seeing,[p/] despite what the evidence points to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0814a44",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: Evidence?[p/] Are you referring to Celeste's testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0abf8fe",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sorry to say this,[p/] but can we even trust her testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000557a",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's no longer under the effects of a Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af4080",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: Which [i]you[/i] claim no longer exists."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffd64b",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: ...But only [i]you[/i] have the power to manifest them in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f395d",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What are you getting at?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c159a",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sorry, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but I suppose what I mean is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9b7aa",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: After everything that just happened,[p/] how can we trust [i]you[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ed9ae",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: You disappeared for quite some time,[p/] to [i]who knows[/i] where."
}

{
  "id": "line:06af708",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: And the only person who was there with you was Celeste and a [i]demon[/i] who can clearly alter people's memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b4685",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: And wasn’t it a [i]little[/i] convenient she was burnt to cinders almost [i]immediately[/i] after your return?"
}

{
  "id": "line:016f660",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: She said it multiple times.[p/] That didn't [i]actually[/i] kill her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a9d52",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: And [i]now[/i]...[p/] You're singling me out as The Patron,[p/] the one ultimately responsible for the murders of von Sanctus and Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef3589",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Aster: If that demon made you into her puppet,[p/] wouldn't this be [i]exactly[/i] what she wanted?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f84f0f",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Gallery: ...That's right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:074b74c",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Gallery: How do we know this \"heavensborn\" can be trusted?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:063ce67",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Gallery: We've all heard the stories![p/][s/] He's practically a dissident!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0773e00",
  "node": "CelFinObj6",
  "text": "Gallery: He's an agent of the Theocracy![p/][s/] It's plain as day!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0958caa",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "I could feel the room turning against us..."
}

{
  "id": "line:069c0aa",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: S-[p/][s/]Sorry![p/][s/] I didn't mean to insult you after everything you've done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc9d9c",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: But I suppose there's [i]one[/i] way to confirm your theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dc09d",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And what's that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd9d30",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: Use your Divine Edict on me.[p/] Just like you've done several times before."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b3214",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: If I truly [i]was[/i] in league with that demon,[p/] shouldn't I have a Contract with her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a4e77",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: It will appear.[p/] Even if I was made to forget about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0508855",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:055feb9",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] That's right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0270cfd",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Celeste: We already tried that before and it didn't work!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1719a",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which means that he definitely [i]doesn't[/i] have a Contract with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e06c9",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: ...Why aren't you doing it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1231f",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] can't.[p/] I already tried and nothing appeared."
}

{
  "id": "line:070eddd",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: I see..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f5614",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sorry, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] I know you care deeply for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb80ee",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: But we all saw Celeste's Blood Contract [i]and[/i] we heard her earlier confession."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dca9c",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: Not to mention,[p/] we have no way of knowing whether Celeste is [i]truly[/i] free from Eris's influence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0447928",
  "node": "CelFinObj7",
  "text": "Aster: If Lady Steelwind is to be saved,[p/] we all must accept what needs to be done."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c5f70",
  "node": "CelFinObj8",
  "text": "Aster: I don't like saying this,[p/] but I think it's time this trial came to its conclusion.[p/] Don't you, Your Grace?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c06acd",
  "node": "CelFinObj8",
  "text": "Was he really just defending himself,[p/] or was this something else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:062eace",
  "node": "CelFinObj8",
  "text": "Either way,[p/] there was clearly a reason why he hadn't been in that [b]Force Cage[/b] for as long as he claimed to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd243e",
  "node": "CelFinObj8",
  "text": "Eris went to so much trouble to hide that fact in Celeste's memories.[p/] Aster [i]had[/i] to have been part of the plan,[p/] intentionally or unintentionally."
}

{
  "id": "line:012d37d",
  "node": "CelFinObj8",
  "text": "There had to have been [i]some[/i] sort of physical involvement on his part."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9a0fb",
  "node": "CelFinObj8",
  "text": "And [i]that[/i] might've left behind evidence that could prove what he did."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cd2e9",
  "node": "CelFinObj9",
  "text": "1000"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d707e",
  "node": "CelFinObj9",
  "text": "No...[p/] If Aster really [i]was[/i] the Patron,[p/] he could've committed the murders through Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:058fdfe",
  "node": "CelFinObj9",
  "text": "He wouldn't have needed to be involved in any of that personally,[p/] but there [i]was[/i] one task that he definitely needed to complete himself."
}

{
  "id": "line:09009b7",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Tyrion: He needed to trick Aria into signing the Contract somehow..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e85bb",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Celeste: ...But you've seen how she is around him."
}

{
  "id": "line:045aa56",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Celeste: That wouldn't have been very hard to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8dc4",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] Aria may be extremely lovesick around him,[p/] but she's still an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebbd99",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Tyrion: She would be careful to read [i]any[/i] contract she signed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0423854",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Tyrion: We deduced earlier that her Blood Contract was disguised as a normal legal document."
}

{
  "id": "line:033b7de",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I remember something.[p/] When you caught a glimpse of it,[p/] you immediately started teasing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0817fe2",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm really trying to,[p/] but I just can't remember what I saw..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0340748",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Celeste: If I was [i]teasing[/i] her about it,[p/] it might have been related to her relationship with Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0692f54",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry...[p/] I know that doesn't really narrow it down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0389a60",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] That's [i]exactly[/i] the clue that I needed."
}

{
  "id": "line:067ccb1",
  "node": "CelFinObj10",
  "text": "Celeste: Really...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:035d341",
  "node": "CelFinObj11",
  "text": "No...[p/] When Celeste caught a glimpse of the Contract,[p/] she immediately started teasing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0754b9a",
  "node": "CelFinObj11",
  "text": "She always had a habit of poking fun at her crush on Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:040d19a",
  "node": "CelFinObj11",
  "text": "King Olivier had just died,[p/] and they were attending his funeral."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afdf75",
  "node": "CelFinObj11",
  "text": "What kind of unique opportunity would that present?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ec4fb",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster![p/][s/] There is [i]one[/i] piece of physical evidence that proves you were involved in this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0303e24",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The Patron controlled Aria and committed each of the murders without having to do [i]anything[/i] personally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0176ef7",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: But this was all contingent on tricking her into [i]signing[/i] that Contract in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e68624",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: I recall that you went to a meeting with the High Speaker right [i]before[/i] the massacre started."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d521dc",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was to discuss your marriage to Aria, wasn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:006d5db",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Aster: ...Yes.[p/] That's correct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf795d",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster,[p/] the Blood Contract that Aria signed needed to [i]look[/i] like a normal legal document,[p/] but I just realized something while reading it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01aed20",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: The language used would've made sense under a [i]different[/i] context."
}

{
  "id": "line:023fc35",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: In that Contract,[p/] Aria gave you her \"mind,[p/] body,[p/] and soul\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae5f2a",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: It would bind her to you so long as you [i]both[/i] live."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eda0b7",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "LucioC: Wait...[p/][s/] Are you saying—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f317d7",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Rath: No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd00ba",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Tyrion: In other words,[p/] \"Till death do you part\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0970345",
  "node": "CelFinObj12",
  "text": "Aster: I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:032ebdf",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: [i]Whoever[/i] tricked my daughter would've surely destroyed the evidence by now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0085c72",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: That demon went out of her way to destroy her memories of signing it."
}

{
  "id": "line:062955a",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "LucioC: I doubt they would've left any copies of the marriage license to be found."
}

{
  "id": "line:0853043",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Rath: Indeed.[p/] Bringing such heavy accusations against the High Speaker [i]or[/i] the King will require more than just speculation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c79363",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Gallery: First he [i]dares[/i] call the King to testify...[p/][s/] And [i]now[/i] he's trying to indict the High Speaker?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b9e36",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Gallery: When will this madness end?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a010b",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: I have more than just speculation, Your Grace."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b9182",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I have a copy of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01071df",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Aster: B-[p/]But your Divine Edict only recreates the terms of the Blood Contract,[p/] not the material that it was written on."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a984d",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Aster: The original document wouldn't be visible on your copy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0278887",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That wasn't the [s/]\"copy\" I was talking about, Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:087d06d",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Aster: ...W-[p/][s/]What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb1e1d",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't you wonder [s/][i]how[/i] I knew about that Blood Contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0339ed0",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Every attorney has a magical runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:01593c1",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: It’s fitted with artificery.[p/][s/] We can use them to take pictures of evidence and crime scenes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3cdb9",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Aster: Y-[p/]Yes...[p/] I'm well aware of that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:027874f",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And did you know Aria took a picture of the marriage license she signed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad9108",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: She was so happy to finally have your union codified,[p/] that she took a picture of your \"marriage license\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea3902",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Even though it was [i]technically[/i] illegal to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d58544",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Aster: ...S-[p/][s/]She—![p/][s/] Why would she—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e4796",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: The moment she regained consciousness,[p/] she thought she was a danger to others."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e3b5f",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: She had [i]no[/i] memories of what she did that day,[p/] but she knew something was wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:098079f",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's why she locked herself in a cell with an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0169bbd",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: She was being [i]rightfully[/i] cautious."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b6278",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: But had she simply left any of those [b]Anti-Magic Fields[/b] and checked her runestone..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0643e80",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She would have found a picture of a marriage license with the exact same words as her Blood Contract!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06692c2",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I'll ask you this, Aster.[p/] Who gave that marriage license to her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de3ce4",
  "node": "CelFinObj13",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was it you or the High Speaker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4266b",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: I was never one for stories.[p/] I found them to be overly tempting distractions from the cruel reality of the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:076177d",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: But when I was a child,[p/] I loved fairy tales and children's stories."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b99a5",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: Back then,[p/] I was once naive enough to believe that the King was the most powerful person in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0c96b",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: I saw the suffering of the people.[p/] I saw the commoners who suffered under the nobility day after day."
}

{
  "id": "line:096998e",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: ...And I saw my father,[p/] sitting on the throne,[p/] watching it all happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4e349",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: I hated him.[p/] I hated his apathy.[p/] I hated his indifference to the people's suffering."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d33de6",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: He did nothing as the Four Pillars bled this country dry to feed their own vices."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f01b56",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: Nevertheless,[p/] I was his firstborn son,[p/] and [i]I[/i] was next in line to the throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:0793e36",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: One day,[p/] I would be able to do what he could not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4413e",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: So I prepared.[p/] I studied the Arcane Arts,[p/] which had become the cornerstone of our culture."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c3f0",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: I mastered the pastimes of the aristocrats,[p/] all so I could earn their admiration and respect."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ef2f0",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: However,[p/] there was a demon inside my head.[p/] She whispered unnerving temptations."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fcc44",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: She told me that villains must fall for the innocent to thrive,[p/] but I would not hear it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cd6a9",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: As young as I was,[p/] I was still a member of the royal family,[p/] and soon,[p/] I would be the most powerful person in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0befd9d",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: I used my position to connect with the commoners who were suffering."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d516f",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: I promised them I would save them from the tyranny of the nobles who would one day answer to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bb7be",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: ...But it was all a lie.[p/] I simply didn't realize it at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bda8d",
  "node": "AsterMonologue",
  "text": "Aster: The more I challenged the Four Pillars,[p/] the more the people suffered."
}

{
  "id": "line:005595f",
  "node": "AsterMonologue2",
  "text": "Aster: My efforts were met with retaliation.[p/] The aristocrats thought I was spoiled,[p/] and they took the rod to the people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0802e7b",
  "node": "AsterMonologue2",
  "text": "Aster: House Frega and House von Sanctus were drunk on their power.[p/] They would slaughter as many people as it took to persuade me to fall in line."
}

{
  "id": "line:086d7db",
  "node": "AsterMonologue2",
  "text": "Aster: House Steelwind,[p/] House Sibyl,[p/] even the Scaled Lord himself—[p/]they all cowered in fear of change and anarchy.[p/] They did nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1c491",
  "node": "AsterMonologue2",
  "text": "Aster: ...My only ally—[p/]who I thought unbreakable—[p/]had been crippled and driven away by this kingdom's cruelty."
}

{
  "id": "line:04586ce",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: I realized why my father sat on the throne with such numbness in his eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:012c7b8",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: It's not that he wouldn't do anything.[p/] He [i]couldn[/i]'t do anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c17e01",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: He was forced to watch in horror as the aristocracy held his people ransom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4a448",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: He carried that despair inside him like it was poison,[p/] and it ate away at him worse than any disease."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da2112",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: Heavy was the crown,[p/] and hell was brought on whoever sat upon the throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca8dbb",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: I'd fallen into despair,[p/] and I had no one to give me hope."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e9486",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: That's when that demon's voice returned."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c30eb",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "FEris: You tried mercy.[p/] You tried diplomacy.[p/] Where has that brought you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d36e48",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "FEris: They prey on the innocent because they thought you wouldn't strike back."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d549d",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "FEris: They butcher them every day,[p/] hoping that you'd become numb to it like your father."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ac9c1",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "FEris: Tell me, young prince,[p/] how many corpses must be stacked before you accept what needs to be done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b671e1",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: ...Eris, how could I make such a choice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b17109",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "FEris: You wouldn't be choosing violence.[p/] You'd simply be choosing who that violence would be directed at.[p/] It's not as if they don't deserve it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c36c7",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "FEris: You could continue to watch the people you love suffer.[p/] You could pat yourself on the back for being more virtuous than your enemies while the innocent burn."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a54b1",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "FEris: What will you do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020b077",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: What I must."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d08fd2",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: In truth,[p/] it was quite easy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0692aaa",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: I always hated how little everyone thought of me,[p/] but it turned out to be quite the blessing."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e4f4b",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: I was worried that Lucio would see through that illusion trapped within the [b]Force Cage[/b],[p/] but he never even gave it a passing thought."
}

{
  "id": "line:0376bf9",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: Hunting von Sanctus and Sibyl was no different than shooting wild boars in the forest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d29def",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: Lady Steelwind moved exactly as I needed her to.[p/] It was as if I were moving and flexing my own arm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0094fca",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: I doubt anyone genuinely missed those two."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b57512",
  "node": "AsterMonologue3",
  "text": "Aster: Even if they did,[p/] they were outnumbered by the lives I had saved with their deaths."
}

{
  "id": "line:0569253",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: So why raise such outrage over that filth?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e7b52",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: ...Why, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a164b6",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you don't want to answer,[p/] we can drag the truth out of both of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d90a01",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Don't bother."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94a4d",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster, no..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02faaba",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: Tell me, Mr. Cuthbert.[p/] Do you know what the best kind of lie is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c863f3",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The kind that's hardest to disprove."
}

{
  "id": "line:0613963",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: No...[p/] Not quite."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e0e68",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: It's the kind where you won’t even try."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fed042",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: The best kind of lie is the one you [i]want[/i] to believe in."
}

{
  "id": "line:03261da",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: The truth can be right in front of you,[p/] but it will make you look away."
}

{
  "id": "line:03090ae",
  "node": "CelFinObj14",
  "text": "Aster: I imagine you're very familiar with that feeling."
}

{
  "id": "line:028d1ed",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Rath: Your Majesty.[p/] What are you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4b6a",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: I'm done with this farce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1f546",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sure if we brought the High Speaker to the stand,[p/] Mr. Cuthbert would just DEDUCE what happened anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ac237",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: It was always going to end this way, I suppose."
}

{
  "id": "line:008b02b",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "LucioC: Y-[p/][s/]You—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08186cf",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Aster, you wretch!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed0d4b",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "LucioC: Are you saying that it [i]was[/i] you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fce187",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: It was, Lucio.[p/] What of it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06155a7",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: I was simply cleaning up all of your messes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0219e52",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: ...If it weren't for Eris's little games,[p/] I would have done it much more cleanly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0950283",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: She promised me that she'd have a leash on McCoy by the end of this.[p/] What a mess she's made..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d664c8",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Rath: ...How [i]could[/i] you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d8c93",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: And what right do [i]you[/i] have to judge my actions,[p/] oh [i]Great[/i] Scaled Lord?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0011aa8",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Rath: Pardon me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1630c",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: No...[p/] I think I'll be pardoning myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4a8e7",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: I [i]am[/i] the King of Wyverngarde, am I not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af9ea8",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Aster: Is that not my right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f6be2",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You're insane."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf26a2",
  "node": "CelFinObj15",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you seriously think everyone in this room will let you get away with this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03c3703",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: I do.[p/] Who is going to stop me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d52a6",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Scaled Lord!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06aebad",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's why he hosted this trial in the first place.[p/] His authority [i]is[/i] above yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d628f6",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: I didn’t ask who could stop me, Tyrion.[p/] I asked who was [i]going[/i] to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a54a39",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Tyrion: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c8631",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why aren't either of you saying anything?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0defbc3",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: Yes.[p/] Rathallion.[p/] Have me arrested."
}

{
  "id": "line:07234e5",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: Put my [i] seven-year-old [/i] brother on the throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff4635",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sure history will tell you [i]exactly[/i] how a kingdom fares when a child wears the Crown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0841007",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: Or would you take the throne for yourself?"
}

{
  "id": "line:080e05b",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: I've read the uncensored records of what happened the last time."
}

{
  "id": "line:02364d9",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: But I'm sure centuries of isolation have done wonders for your ability to lead."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b0947",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Tyrion: Rathallion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb0ffc",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Rath: ...Aster will not kill indiscriminately, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:005ee3f",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Tyrion: He just admitted to murdering two people!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7dfa7",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Rath: He's been prepared to lead from his birth...[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5e529",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Rath: [i]I[/i] willingly turned my head away from this kingdom.[p/] I know nothing of what Wyverngarde needs."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e590a4",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Rath: I may not know the best course before me,[p/] but I know with painful certainty that it is [i]not[/i] to seize control of this nation."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c6e42",
  "node": "CelFinObj15a",
  "text": "Aster: Not really surprising..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0541f6a",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: From everything I’ve seen,[p/] negligence has been your [i]one[/i] consistent trait."
}

{
  "id": "line:08978cf",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: And what about you, Lucio?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0caffed",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: Are you going to try to depose me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb7d6d",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: The beloved prince,[p/] now King of Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c82fa4",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: I have nothing but contempt for William Frega,[p/] but I suppose I must be thankful."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e47ad",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: He did a wonderful job of tearing you down.[p/] The people would never accept you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c98ea8",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: You're a man with the blood of thousands on your hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c907b",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: Imagine if [i]you[/i] deposed the new King of Wyverngarde before the previous king’s body was even interred."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae6fbf",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: I wonder just how [i]bloody[/i] of a civil war that could plunge this nation into."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af645f",
  "node": "CelFinObj15b",
  "text": "Aster: I am sure you can imagine just how tempting a weakened Wyverngarde would look to the other nations."
}

{
  "id": "line:0633b37",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster![p/][s/] You're holding everyone hostage!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f459aa",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Aster: Tell me.[p/] Does this terrify you all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb7f47",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Aster: To know that I can do whatever I please,[p/] with no one who can stop me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a45fbc",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Aster: Is this not what [i]you’ve[/i] all been doing to the rest of this country?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbcc4f",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Aster: And I think [i]that[/i] makes Checkmate, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0172c71",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Aster: It [i]is[/i] quite exhilarating to say.[p/] I can see why you're so fond of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc3c96",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: What are you all doing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef20c2",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: Lucio![p/][s/] She's your [i]daughter[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022581d",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "Celeste: You have to do something!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0090903",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "LucioC: ...My daughter would not sacrifice the stability of Wyverngarde for her freedom."
}

{
  "id": "line:05254c0",
  "node": "CelFinObj16",
  "text": "LucioC: You know that to be true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cac38",
  "node": "CelFinObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddb5ce",
  "node": "CelFinObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: He killed so many people.[p/] He enslaved Aria...[p/][s/] He almost did the same to [i]me[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:003c54e",
  "node": "CelFinObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why [i]did[/i] he need you to sign away your soul?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0debaa7",
  "node": "CelFinObj17",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What do you mean?[p/][s/] [i]Eris[/i] was the one who wanted it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7bf01",
  "node": "CelFinObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: But this was [i]his[/i] plan.[p/] That outcome had to have benefited them both."
}

{
  "id": "line:09986b8",
  "node": "CelFinObj17",
  "text": "Tyrion: If Aster is the Patron,[p/] that also means that Pierce [i]originally[/i] sent that letter to [i]him[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e995fe",
  "node": "CelFinObj17",
  "text": "LucioC: Even if McCoy was of royal blood,[p/] Aster is the King's eldest child,[p/] and he's of [i]pure[/i] royal blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:009333b",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you [i]were[/i] his half-sister,[p/] you wouldn't have a claim to the throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:035f7ad",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: So why would he go to so much trouble to murder Pierce and gain control of you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cb027",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Maybe he just wanted to be sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06dbc6e",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: But he wouldn't have had Eris head to the prayer room personally if it wasn't important..."
}

{
  "id": "line:026064b",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: She can't lie.[p/] If she promised to do a job,[p/] that job would've been done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd1a94",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: He needed to silence both you [i]and[/i] Pierce during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e3e83",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which means you two were even more important targets than von Sanctus and Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:0156d1b",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Celeste: Okay...?[p/] But my potential claim to the throne would be the only reason why he'd be scared of me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5a469",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Celeste: If [i]that[/i] wasn't a problem,[p/] why would he be so scared of Pierce's blackmail?"
}

{
  "id": "line:050d675",
  "node": "CelFinObj18",
  "text": "Would the line of succession be the [i]only[/i] reason why he'd be scared of Celeste's parentage?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc951f",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "I recalled what I knew about Wyverngarde's laws regarding the royal throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:020d4cf",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Wasn't there something someone mentioned about that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c86b0",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "The Church of Bahamut"
}

{
  "id": "line:057e592",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "I recalled a conversation I had with Theon Archeus."
}

{
  "id": "line:076a98a",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Theon: The Church of Bahamut is important not only to Wyverngarde's culture but to its civil stability."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f43ac",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Theon: Faith is a powerful and unifying force."
}

{
  "id": "line:023e864",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is that why you revise Wyverngarde's history and keep heavensborn outside the country?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0b335",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Theon: I don't know [i]what[/i] you're trying to insinuate. [h=\"Dissidents like him|will be the end of our culture.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9a893",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Aster didn't murder the High Speaker when he had the chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0550989",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "So it's possible that the Church of Bahamut played a role in his future plans."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee887e",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "But that wouldn't explain why he needed Pierce to die."
}

{
  "id": "line:064fea7",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "The Theocracy of Lumina"
}

{
  "id": "line:0129be2",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "I recalled a conversation I had with Harold Haroldson."
}

{
  "id": "line:0806fcb",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Harold,[p/] what do you know about the celestial gods?"
}

{
  "id": "line:078ab2d",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: I haven't been able to find anything about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed135",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Harold: That makes sense.[p/] They're primarily worshipped by the people of the Theocracy of Lumina."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea79d6",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "That might explain why worship of them was outlawed."
}

{
  "id": "line:087ede8",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Lumina was the kingdom west of us,[p/] but I knew very little about them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5c959",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "All I knew is that we fought them during the first war of Wyverngarde,[p/] and then later during the Great Luminite War."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dd5d3",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "They'd been Wyverngarde's longstanding enemy for a while.[p/] Simply asking about them could raise accusations of treason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6b0be",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Harold: There are nine celestial gods,[p/] each representing a divine domain in heaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:015dda7",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Harold: Deus,[p/] Odin,[p/] Machina,[p/] Horus—"
}

{
  "id": "line:079a539",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry...[p/][s/] One of them is named \"[i]Horus[/i]\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c490e9",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "If Aster's actions had anything to do with the Theocracy,[p/] he would've targeted me,[p/] not Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c24c0b",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "And that also wouldn't explain why he needed Pierce to die."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e680f",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "The Scaled Lord"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f1c28",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "...I recalled a conversation I had with Eris Illmater."
}

{
  "id": "line:00878a9",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "TYRION: How have I never heard of this before?[p/] I've memorized all of Wyverngarde's laws."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f97c59",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Eris: Practically speaking,[p/] it's never been invoked.[p/] It's merely a law spun of reverent words to praise the Scaled Lord and appease the Church."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d181a8",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Wait...[p/] The Scaled Lord [i]and[/i] his kin could override the King's rule...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0317ff1",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0002588",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Pacts with Demons"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb03a",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Celeste: Isn't making a deal with a demon just [i]asking[/i] for trouble?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d481a2",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Celeste: They'd definitely betray you the first chance they got."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bad243",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Harold: Legends say that demons often drafted Blood Contracts for this reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0370bcb",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: Would that be similar to a [i]legally binding[/i] contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfde25",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Harold: The concept is similar,[p/] but once you sign a Blood Contract,[p/] both you and the demon are magically compelled to fulfill its terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0948c74",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Harold: It's said that violating its terms will result in instant death for the offender...[p/] No matter who they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0414042",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I guess there's [i]some[/i] protection..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a43493",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Harold: Well...[p/] As an attorney,[p/] I'm sure you understand that it's possible to exploit and use loopholes in [i]any[/i] contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0235bca",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "Hm...[p/] Aster [i]did[/i] make a deal with the Empress of Discord,[p/] but they never actually made it official with a Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc405b",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "They were probably using each other to accomplish their goals."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f51141",
  "node": "CelFinObj19",
  "text": "...But that still didn't explain why he needed to kill Pierce or bind Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73516",
  "node": "CelFinObj20",
  "text": "Rath|Remus"
}

{
  "id": "line:086509b",
  "node": "CelFinObj20",
  "text": "No...[p/] The Scaled Lord and his [i]kin[/i] had the authority to override the will of Wyverngarde's King."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fa3c1",
  "node": "CelFinObj20",
  "text": "And if Aster was worried about Celeste's parentage,[p/][s/] that could only mean—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:057ce95",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "A flood of memories came back to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a25b6",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "Orym: Celeste McCoy![p/][s/] By the authority of the Wyverngarde crown,[p/][s/] I'm placing you under arrest!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6b778",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "The knight tried to grab her arm,[p/] and it was like something flipped inside of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a72f96",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "She slammed her palm into the knight's chest,[p/] his plate armour reverberating as he fell to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7f5c6",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "Three other knights rushed forward.[p/] They tried to grab her and pin her to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0959987",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "She let out a guttural scream against them,[p/] almost sounding like a feral animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:008417a",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "It looked like it was taking all of their strength to keep her pinned down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b02784",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "Aria: ...You can't teach yourself magic, Ms. McCoy.[p/] That's not possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af9ef7",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "CELESTE: Hey![p/] I've got a system, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf8d0f",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "Celeste: I even learned a few new spells today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da8692",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "Aria: ...How long did it take you to learn these spells?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2c0f3",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "CELESTE: A few hours, I think."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e60fd5",
  "node": "CelFinObj21",
  "text": "ARIA: ... [h=\"She taught herself multiple spell formulas|within a few hours?!\" /]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06b824e",
  "node": "CelFinObj22",
  "text": "Aster: When a mage casts a spell,[p/] they draw and harness the aether from within their own body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0411a3a",
  "node": "CelFinObj22",
  "text": "Aster: Artificery, on the other hand,[p/] draws aether from the natural ley lines that run through the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:053fbe8",
  "node": "CelFinObj22",
  "text": "Aster: I am someone who has practiced arcane magic for my entire life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0472b3b",
  "node": "CelFinObj22",
  "text": "Aster: I've slowly learned how to sense how aether moves around me."
}

{
  "id": "line:03eabad",
  "node": "CelFinObj22",
  "text": "Celeste: You can do that, too?[p/] I thought I was the only one."
}

{
  "id": "line:064a99a",
  "node": "CelFinObj22",
  "text": "Aster: Oh,[p/] that talent is quite a rarity—[p/]even among the royal family."
}

{
  "id": "line:0383dad",
  "node": "CelFinObj22",
  "text": "Aster: I suppose I shouldn't expect anything less from the Crimson Demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fa4f3",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] What is it, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:055ff82",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Her ridiculous strength,[p/] her natural talent for learning magic—[p/]she inherited [i]all[/i] of it from [i]him[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08350a7",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you okay?[p/] You got really pale all of a sudden."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b0c45",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Once I revealed this,[p/] there was no going back for her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2dbcc",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Did I really have any right to do this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009f110",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "No...[p/] Aria's freedom rode on this."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c8143",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbf7fb",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: This could ruin your life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8d4e7",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1adc3",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "...How could I even begin to explain this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:065bc6a",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: Do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a505a",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't understand—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0382fc1",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: I owe you [i]and[/i] Aria for what I did..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f036b4",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: Whatever we need to do,[p/] it's to save Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0476ec0",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: Just keep your promise...[p/] Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b334c",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: Like I said,[p/] we're in this together,[p/] and I'll always be there when you need me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0777ebc",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: No matter where you go,[p/] we're going there together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e55793",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1cb81",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Aster: Hmph...[p/] Are you two done [i]flirting[/i] with each other?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b306c",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:038b245",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]know[/i] the identity of Celeste's father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e24190",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Celeste: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0784473",
  "node": "CelFinObj23",
  "text": "Aster: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] You're bluffing...[p/] You [i]have[/i] to be. [h=\"\" e=\"fa\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ade605",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said that no one could contest your rule of Wyverngarde aside from the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a88968",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But there's [i]one[/i] more person.[p/] Isn't there, Aster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e12ed",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "LucioC: What are you talking about...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e5c0a",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "LucioC: Only [i]the Scaled Lord[/i] can override the will of the king."
}

{
  "id": "line:074cb05",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And his kin, Lucio."
}

{
  "id": "line:070b7f6",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "LucioC: I suppose that's—"
}

{
  "id": "line:044a51f",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster de Wyverngarde,[p/] you [i]needed[/i] Eris to capture Celeste during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0778210",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's because her existence would [i]always[/i] pose a threat to your rule."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd3535",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Celeste: ...This can't be real."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd4bb7",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: People of the Wyverngarde nobility!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03066ca",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your current king was fearful of my bodyguard's parentage,[p/][s/] and [i]now[/i] we know why!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b59bff",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste McCoy is the daughter of the Scaled Lord Rathallion:[p/][s/] Ancient Dragon and creator of all Arcane Magic!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce054e",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Judging from your reaction,[p/] I'm right, aren't I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6c8f7",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm...[p/][s/] half-dragon?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d3aed",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well, [i]I'm[/i] apparently part-angel,[p/] so you're in good company."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9d48b",
  "node": "CelFinObj25",
  "text": "Rath: So that demon [i]was[/i] speaking the truth..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9be48",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aster de Wyverngarde!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee3f7d",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Tyrion: As the Scaled Lord's kin,[p/] Celeste has the authority to pass judgment on you [i]and[/i] override your rule!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcdae1",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Tyrion: And when you're gone,[p/] [i]she[/i] will take your place as the ruler of Wyverngarde!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0067beb",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: Celeste...![p/] Think about this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07472e5",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: Can you even begin to [i]grasp[/i] what it takes to lead a nation,[p/] much less one so broken?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0ceed",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: You'd just be trading one hell for another..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d043",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Celeste: Just tell me one thing, Aster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0182636",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Celeste: ...How could you do this to Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070a7ef",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Celeste: She trusted you...[p/][s/] She [i]loved[/i] you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0234d43",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: \"[i]Loved[/i]\" me?![p/][s/] She hated me,[p/][s/] and why wouldn't she?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:028203a",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: I was weak back then![p/][s/] I was pathetic!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e56532",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Celeste: You idiot![p/][s/] She wanted to change Wyverngarde [i]together[/i] with you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068cab4",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Celeste: You didn't need to do any of this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a9758",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: Is [i]that[/i] what you really think?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d15226",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: ...I suppose you would."
}

{
  "id": "line:06167a7",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: You probably also think you two are the first people to try to change this nation,[p/] while still working within its laws."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8a1f",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Celeste: There’s nothing wrong with having ideals and working within the law!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ade50d",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: My father was like that, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a78dd",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: He was a man of ideals...[p/] [i]once[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ce2be",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: I watched for my whole life as he compromised on [i]everything[/i] he believed in,[p/] one ideal after another."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cdb2e",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: \"It was to keep the peace.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0f50474",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: \"We [i]must[/i] maintain the stability between the noble houses to uphold law and order.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0c83989",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: And do you know [i]who[/i] paid the price every time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f38aa2",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: Not him,[p/] not me,[p/] not [s/][i]any[/i] of the nobles gathered here."
}

{
  "id": "line:078b4a4",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: No...[p/] The people who paid the price were the commoners."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a398a",
  "node": "CelFinObj26",
  "text": "Aster: The kind of people [i]you[/i] two are always trying to save."
}

{
  "id": "line:0270e66",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: I would have honestly thought you'd understand by now..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dacc81",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: A gulf exists between what is just and what is lawful in this kingdom..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1e2bc",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: We [i]know[/i] it's not fair!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0175244",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: But we're capable of [i]changing[/i] it![p/][s/] You [i]had[/i] the power to do just that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb0289",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: I [i]AM[/i] changing it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02df57f",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: You worked [i]so[/i] hard to find the truth behind those murders!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06eddb9",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: But here’s a little bit of \"truth\" that's evident to [i]everyone[/i] in this room [s/][i]except[/i] you two!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e88347",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: Half of the people present here today are [i]glad[/i] that they’re gone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a04f6",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: And the [i]other[/i] half wants to be the ones to replace them!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f10b24",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: The blood I shed in a single hour did more good for this kingdom than you two would have done in years!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a20d7c",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]that’s[/i] how you plan on fixing this country’s problems?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019843e",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: By working with demons and [i]killing[/i] your way to a \"brighter\" future?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d4400",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: If I [i]have[/i] to,[p/] why not?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0916e71",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: Every day,[p/][s/] [i]across[/i] this nation,[p/][s/] commoners are killed and oppressed at the hands of the very nobles gathered here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09cfac1",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: They [i]bleed[/i] this country dry,[p/] and feed on its people like carrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e25a8c",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: ...I am merely returning a much-needed sense of equality."
}

{
  "id": "line:0001007",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: Do you really think [i]any[/i] of you are in a position to judge me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ec98e",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: All of you,[p/] who came running at the news of my father’s death?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c84e4",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: All so you could be the [i]first[/i] to fill my ears with your sycophantic praises!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0921cdd",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: Do you know what the difference between the Empress of Discord and all of [i]you[/i] is?![p/][s/] That demon was just a [i]bit[/i] more honest!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0546a81",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria [i]wanted[/i] to stand with you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2b45e",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: Aria is too [i]stupid[/i] and too [i]naive[/i] to do [i]anything[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f14a4",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: She loved you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0543457",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: How could you—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f7b2f",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: She loved her [i]idea[/i] of me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:028e3e9",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: She loved a [i]weak[/i] and [i]ineffectual[/i] prince,[p/] who would have borne watching his kingdom rot,[p/] with a damned [i]smile[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2c210",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Celeste: S-[p/][s/]She loved your kindness."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cf1cc",
  "node": "CelFinObj27",
  "text": "Aster: [i]THIS[/i] is kindness!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ace31a",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: The blood I will spill will be the greatest [i]kindness[/i] this kingdom has ever known!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f93b09",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: And once I am done,[p/] Wyverngarde will be better and stronger for it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4a157",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Celeste: Aster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:012f149",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: McCoy![p/][s/] I don’t care [i]what[/i] you are!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbbe41",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: The Scaled Lord’s daughter?![p/][s/] The rightful heir?![p/][s/] [i]None[/i] of that matters to me!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0669562",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: I will [i]save[/i] my kingdom and its people![p/][s/] And I will carve the rot out of its heart, piece by bloody piece!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5df32",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: Nothing will stand in my way!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd03c2",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: I am Aster de Wyverngarde![p/][s/] King of Wyverngarde,[p/][s/] and consort to the Lord of the Sixth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:056437a",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "Aster: I am—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05955aa",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "LucioC: —nothing but a dead man."
}

{
  "id": "line:0384aba",
  "node": "CelFinObj27a",
  "text": "LucioC: [b]Vulnus[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa2abb",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "Aster: [j]Lu...[p/]cio...[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:080476c",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b09262",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "Rath: ...Lucio.[p/] What have you done?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04702",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "LucioC: The Blood Contract, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:06505e1",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "LucioC: My daughter's Blood Contract![p/][s/] Does it still exist?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:050a10d",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "I checked my satchel...[p/] Sure enough,[p/] Aria's Blood Contract had completely disintegrated into ash."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c90a6c",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "...Its conditions had been fulfilled, hadn't they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08fe7fd",
  "node": "CelFinObj28",
  "text": "One of them no longer lived."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a80a1",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "LucioC: Excellent..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4f46c",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "Rath: Lucio...[p/] This is—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0296ffb",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "Rath: This is [i]not[/i] what we discussed!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d705bd",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "LucioC: My daughter would never be free as long as that wretch lived."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e697c6",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "LucioC: McCoy agreed to take his place.[p/] This was [i]always[/i] how it was going to end."
}

{
  "id": "line:035cf09",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "Tyrion: Lucio...[p/] I understand,[p/] but how could we possibly—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0645a07",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "LucioC: Save your breath, Cuthbert.[p/] I already know."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bb7dd",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "LucioC: Kingsguard![p/][s/] What are you standing around for?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06dae65",
  "node": "CelFinObj29",
  "text": "LucioC: The Grand General has just committed regicide![p/][s/] Arrest him at once!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b336f",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "We sat at the nearby ruins.[p/] It looked like several of the nobles here were doing the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1ebed",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "We didn't know what to say to each other.[p/] I could feel my stomach churning."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ba02d",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Celeste: He was a terrible person.[p/] He [i]killed[/i] people."
}

{
  "id": "line:090c9ec",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Celeste: He tried to kill us.[p/] He took control of Aria like it was nothing to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc69cc",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Celeste: But I really wish we could have—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f1c33",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Changed his mind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6ae9d",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Sometimes people are beyond salvation.[p/] He made his choice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb8f3e",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Celeste: But Aria,[p/] how is she—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ff6ff",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Aria: Hello.[p/] I'm glad I found you before you left. [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c1712",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "The Eye of Horus could only see an abyss where her heart was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6ba5c",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Aria!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0667ed3",
  "node": "CelFinObj29a",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm so—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0225a29",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: McCoy,[p/] I've come to inform you that I'll be charging you with perjury. [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b9565",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Okay,[p/] whatever you—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01221fb",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: No one is above the law. Not even the Queen.[p/] That was made apparent when—  [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ecda1",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "She didn't trail off.[p/] Her voice didn't break."
}

{
  "id": "line:094da2d",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Her voice simply stopped like a machine that had ceased function."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea754e",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Celeste: Um...[p/] Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d842db",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: ...Anyways,[p/] I'm sure it's nothing to worry about.  [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:009b7a3",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: You [i]do[/i] have a talented defense counsel after all.  [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:004469d",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "...What do I say to her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb315c",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: Anyways,[p/] I wanted to thank you for the work you've done, Mr. Cuthbert.  [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:03beb8b",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: I truly mean it when I say you have my gratitude.  [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:015267b",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Tyrion: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] Y-[p/][s/]Yeah...[p/] Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:030c659",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: Anyways,[p/] I have much work to get done now that my—  [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0814be4",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Aria: —Now that the Grand General is in custody.  [h=\"\" e=\"\" color=\"#110623\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e89514",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0917e96",
  "node": "CelFinObj31",
  "text": "Celeste: What was [i]that[/i] all about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0762c1a",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: Why didn't you say anything to her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ef74b",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/] I didn't see [i]anything[/i] through the Eye..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a49b8b",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: I guess I don't really blame her for guarding her emotions."
}

{
  "id": "line:044a73f",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: No, Celeste...[p/] I didn't see [i]anything[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3dd36",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: I looked at her with the Eye.[p/] She wasn't holding anything back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0303df6",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: There was no anger,[p/] no sadness,[p/] no fear,[p/] no joy..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0473fe4",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've never seen that before..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd7b2e",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But you're right...[p/] I should have said something..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eff0fe",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm going to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de698e",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste grabbed my hand before I could leave."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e3a0f",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'll talk to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2f127",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4ab94",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: She's my friend,[p/] and I owe her."
}

{
  "id": "line:061abf5",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "It looked like I'd gotten the acquittal of yet another client,[p/] but it didn't tie up [i]quite[/i] so neatly as I'd hoped."
}

{
  "id": "line:052380c",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: What do you mean, she's gone?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcea3c",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: She was [i]just[/i] here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d437",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Knight: I-[p/][s/]I'm sorry, Your...[p/] Majesty?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd61c6",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "I didn't know what the future had in store for all of us,[p/] but it's not as if that were different than usual."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9dbc3",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": ":We had the power now:[p/] the power to give hope to every commoner in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0517bcb",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Together,[p/] we would give them the kingdom they deserved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4e21d",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn it, Aria...[p/] Where are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f93db4",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Remus: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c834f",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh...![p/] H-[p/][s/]Hello."
}

{
  "id": "line:031386f",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "Celeste froze.[p/] This man was the person she'd been looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:05330a8",
  "node": "CelFinObj32",
  "text": "What was she supposed to say to him?[p/] She never thought she'd get this far."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa0a13",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Remus: ...You're looking for Ms. Steelwind, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01eab1a",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah![p/][s/] How'd you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a381fd",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Remus: ...She's been sitting outside my lair for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:0153bc6",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Remus: I tried speaking to her,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f052b9",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I get it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08362dd",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm going to try anyway."
}

{
  "id": "line:076f9d9",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Remus: O-[p/][s/]Of course..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f25985",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: Rathallion."
}

{
  "id": "line:09af06a",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Remus: Yes...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0649c36",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm not mad about it, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a33569",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: Jolene and Flinhart are a part of my life because of what you did."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e506b",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: Plus![p/][s/] Now I know that I'm half-[i]dragon[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c3c75",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: That's pretty cool, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d18d1",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Remus: Ms. McCoy..."
}

{
  "id": "line:063f8ea",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on![p/] Don't call me that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0084035",
  "node": "CelFinObj34",
  "text": "Remus: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] Of course, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a2419",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Remus: So...[p/] I've been meaning to ask..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1a64",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Remus: About you and Mr. Cuthbert...[p/] Are you two—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef4d1e",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, wow![p/] [i]Look[/i] at how late it is!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08461a8",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: I'd better go talk to Aria, [i]right now[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00fc0dd",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll see you later, Scaled Dad![p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]I mean,[p/][s/] Scaled—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b41cd0",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: Agh![p/][s/] Just—![p/][s/] Bye!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d7b80",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Remus: Hmph...[p/] No wonder Lucio went so far..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfb96d",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Hey, Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b698b",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Aria: Oh, Celeste.[p/] What are you doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0934526",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: Just making sure you're doing okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2a4c7",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: You [i]are[/i] doing okay, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd0d4e",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Aria: I am.[p/] There's no need to worry about me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0940a2c",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you looking at the stars?"
}

{
  "id": "line:033711a",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Aria: I was looking at the moon.[p/] It's full tonight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d145e3",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Do you mind if I watch it with you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:038fe48",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Aria: Do as you wish.[p/] You're my superior."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d29e6d",
  "node": "CelFinObj35",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You know.[p/] It was also a full moon outside the night my parents found me in their inn."
}

{
  "id": "line:03148b6",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: That's why they named me \"Celeste\".[p/] It's an ancient word for the \"moon\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0540887",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Aria: ...Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d23020",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] They thought I was a gift from the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fde86",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: It's a little funny when you think about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:061f9d1",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: ...By the way,[p/] I never got to thank you for sticking up for me before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0743801",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Aria: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2c5c",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: Remember?[p/] You [i]jumped[/i] down onto the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b8b58",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't think even [i]Tyrion[/i] believed in me at that point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0253f56",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: If you'd never done that,[p/] who [i]knows[/i] how this could have ended up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7c94c",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: Thank you for that, Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:09544c9",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Aria: I was merely taking the most obvious course of action..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d676c1",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I guess I don't know why I expected anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:028f839",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: You're...[p/] not [i]really[/i] going to charge me with perjury, are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbf0b0",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Aria: Of course I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be7b67",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6cdde",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Aria: But we [i]do[/i] require your help to hold the structure of our kingdom together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0babcf5",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Aria: We won't sentence you to the dungeons,[p/] but we'll have to consider some community service."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a4971",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] Fine..."
}

{
  "id": "line:093c120",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Aria: My father told me I was being too lenient."
}

{
  "id": "line:0611ef6",
  "node": "CelFinObj36",
  "text": "Celeste: Lucio needs to keep his mouth shut."
}

{
  "id": "line:0640262",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: I understood in some way.[p/] We all do stupid things for the people we love, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:035e75d",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: [j]...........stupid.[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0441249",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: [j]H-[p/][s/]How...[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f145e",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: ...How could I be so [i]stupid[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e84ba3",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Celeste: H-[p/][s/]Hey...[p/][s/] You're not—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0878ee7",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: I am![p/][s/] I'm a complete and utter fool!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0649506",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: I'm an [i]attorney[/i], for Lord's sake!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea463e",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria:  I've read [i]countless[/i] legal documents!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8cb5b",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: And when I signed that Contract,[p/] I [i]felt[/i] something was wrong!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bd2ed",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: But I was just so [i]stupidly[/i] happy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0291159",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Celeste: That's not fair."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d0e44",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Celeste: No [i]one[/i] expected him to do something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:035a1c8",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: Now my father,[p/][s/] h-[p/][s/]he's going to pay for [i]my[/i] mistakes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:055f740",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'm sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f61b92",
  "node": "CelFinObj37",
  "text": "Aria: [j]Celeste.[p/] He used me like a puppet...[p/] With [i]my[/i] hands and [i]my[/i] magic,[p/] he made me—[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f6e97",
  "node": "CelFinObj38",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry, Aria.[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02267d7",
  "node": "CelFinObj38",
  "text": "Celeste: What he did to you was horrible."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b88dc",
  "node": "CelFinObj38",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't know how to make it better,[p/] but you're not alone, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:079f074",
  "node": "CelFinObj38",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll be here as long as you need me to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0283c29",
  "node": "CelFinObj38",
  "text": "Aria: ...Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:037f020",
  "node": "CelFinObj38",
  "text": "Aria: ...I think I'll drop the charges of perjury against you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b624c1",
  "node": "CelFinObj38",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] Are we still on that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcce65",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Remus: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] we've received word from House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:089ac8e",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Remus: The story we created should be printed in the papers as we speak."
}

{
  "id": "line:0111c9d",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I don't like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:08024fb",
  "node": "FinalScene",
  "text": "Celeste: We're lying to the people of Wyverngarde about what [i]really[/i] happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d3c4e",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Celeste: Not to mention,[p/] this story paints me like I'm some kind of god."
}

{
  "id": "line:078b425",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand your reservations,[p/] but Aster [i]was[/i] right about how the commonfolk felt about him."
}

{
  "id": "line:036fc72",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we told the people what [i]actually[/i] happened—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a72670",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: They would never believe it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7df52",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: They'd think that his death was a part of some sort of political conspiracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e9c0a",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: Even [i]with[/i] this cover story,[p/] we can't be certain that they [i]still[/i] won't suspect that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb6159",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Aria?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcc81a",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Celeste: Shouldn't you be resting?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08e1dd7",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: Nonsense,[p/] I'm not going to sit around feeling sorry for myself while everyone else fixes my mistakes. [h=\"I will move forward.\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:079ae2e",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "She may have been hiding her pain behind a smile,[p/] but she wasn't shutting down her emotions like before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eca919",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: As much as it pains me,[p/] we should strive to carry forth the virtues that His—[p/] that [i]Aster[/i] represented to the commonfolk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d59755",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: Wyverngarde will gain more from those false virtues than from the person that he truly was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0814519",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: The stability of our nation must be maintained if we're to move forward,[p/] and if we must use the people's piety to do that,[p/] then so be it."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bf65f",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Aria: And as the Grand General of Wyverngarde,[p/] I will also do my part to support your rule."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c3370",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Remus: As will the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:059687d",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Celeste smiled in gratitude to their words,[p/] but she meekly glanced at me expectantly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f35670",
  "node": "EndA",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you even have to ask?"
}

{
  "id": "line:075f970",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Celeste: Hehe..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c85fd5",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Tyrion: And it's not just us.[p/] I'll do my best to make sure that the rest of Wyverngarde supports you, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9e39b",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, yeah.[p/] Since you two patched things up,[p/] we could also ask for Ruby's help."
}

{
  "id": "line:077e19a",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ah, right![p/] I forgot that I was supposed to meet with her this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f83844",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'll need to apologize to her about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e72e82",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/][s/] Have you [i]still[/i] not told her about what happened yet?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0433d64",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Tyrion: We had more important things to worry about.[p/] I'm sure that she'll understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dab33",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion,[p/] the last time you saw her,[p/] you manifested a Blood Contract without explaining anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f504c",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Then[/i] you vaguely said something about helping Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ded87",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry.[p/] I'll explain everything to her once things quiet down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a245f9",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion![p/][s/] That story we fabricated is being printed right [i]now[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e9f15",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Everyone[/i] in Wyverngarde is going to read about it in the paper,[p/] [i]including[/i] her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4700a",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d09f0",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Ruby: ...What's all of this noise about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0801735",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Peasant: What?![p/][s/] Have you been living under a rock, lady?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:014d67a",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Peasant: Read the morning paper![p/][s/] The Scaled Lord has returned!"
}

{
  "id": "line:081eae9",
  "node": "EndB",
  "text": "Ruby: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a52ef2",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Ruby: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c705bd",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Ruby: ...\"Demonic Attack Claims Lives of Prominent Figures\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a95e6",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Ruby: \"Chaos broke out yesterday during the private wedding between Aria Steelwind and Crown Prince Aster de Wyverngarde.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0395377",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Jolene: \"In a surprise attack orchestrated by a malevolent demon,[p/] a devastating loss was inflicted upon our kingdom,[p/] shattering the very foundations of our power and stability.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:06ecc6c",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Wallace: \"The carnage left in the wake of this abyssal assault was nothing short of catastrophic.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:08ea46f",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Valentina: \"Among the fallen were Lady Coraline Sibyl,[p/] Lord Lloyd von Sanctus,[p/] and Lord Lucio Steelwind.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8b9a9",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Jan: \"Both King Olivier and Crown Prince Aster made a heroic attempt to repel the foul monster.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0aedfc3",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Stefanic: \"And while the profane demon was felled and defeated,[p/] the King and the Crown Prince tragically lost their lives in the ensuing battle.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4591e",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Mosourika: \"However,[p/] amidst the chaos and despair,[p/] a glimmer of hope emerged to prevent the kingdom from descending into further disarray.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:09f7fe4",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Laefe: \"The Scaled Lord himself descended from the heavens,[p/] restoring order,[p/] and making a profound proclamation.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbc82e",
  "node": "End",
  "text": "Gavin: \"In a [i]selfless[/i] act to maintain the integrity and unity of Wyverngarde,[p/] the Scaled Lord anointed his holy daughter as the new Queen of Wyverngarde.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbf9c0",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: Ugh...[p/] [i]Again[/i] with this Scaled Lord nonsense..."
}

{
  "id": "line:049f151",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: This [i]reeks[/i] of a violent political coup by this \"holy daughter\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:06365e7",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: Hmph...[p/] It says there's a picture of her on the next page."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b232d",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7c526",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Wallace: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a358b2",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Valentina: Is that—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d65c7",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Stefanic: ...How interesting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1ad7",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...Celeste?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aeee2c",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Gavin: I'm tellin' you![p/][s/] I don't know how she did it, but she took over the entire kingdom!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0b0d0",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Wyatt: She's not gonna [i]come[/i] for us, is she?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b5ea6",
  "node": "End2",
  "text": "Ruby: ALRIGHT![p/][s/] WHAT THE [i]FU[/i][p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0edb626",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Rhys: After hearing about what happened to my former Lord,[p/] I've thought a lot about my actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0003050",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Rhys: I won't ask you to forgive me, Your Majesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e842f",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Rhys: But I want to continue to atone for all the harm I've caused."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b0f18",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Miriam: I will continue my studies in the field of [b]conjuration[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:07636cf",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Miriam: With the kingdom in such disarray,[p/] it falls onto people like [i]me[/i] to maintain order."
}

{
  "id": "line:0343b29",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Miriam: Why are you looking at me like that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac5cc5",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Valerie: We'd never be able to do this if it weren't for the Dracogen Trading Company."
}

{
  "id": "line:0471fe4",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Aria: I feel partially responsible for what happened at the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea4886",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Aria: I'd like to make amends however I can."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4398b",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Valentina: Don't worry about [i]that[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c50b3",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Valentina: Business has been [i]booming[/i] ever since we set up shop in Ratholme!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b6389",
  "node": "Credits",
  "text": "Jan: Ugh...[p/] More customers just means more work for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f0c5d",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Wallace: I've been developing my necromancy ever since I began working under Lord Asclepius."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b172e",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Wallace: I think I've grown quite good at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ca9ee",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Lazarick: Don't get ahead of yourself.[p/] You've grown [i]competent[/i] at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf27f1",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Wallace: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0495881",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Lazarick: T-[p/][s/]That was a joke."
}

{
  "id": "line:042d563",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Lazarick: [i]You're[/i] probably the best necromancer I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3bd7f",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Lazarick: ...Aside from [i]me[/i],[p/] of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:011e304",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Theodore: ...I'm sorry,[p/] but I still can't remember anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:083568b",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Theodore: ...But from what I've read in my record,[p/] perhaps that's for the best."
}

{
  "id": "line:043fc35",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Aria: Even if your memories are gone,[p/] your crimes can't be changed."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ee011",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Aria: You still have to serve your sentence,[p/] but I [i]do[/i] hope you can live out the rest of your life in peace."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c848f8",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Gavin: ...What [i]you[/i] lookin' at?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0db4f1c",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Gavin: Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02caae3",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Wyatt: Oh no...[p/] It's [i]you[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9b13d",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Gavin: That crazy chick isn't with you,[p/][s/] is she?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032b16e",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Um..."
}

{
  "id": "line:055bba2",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Wyatt: ...Why you lookin' behind me, man?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2fcbc",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What did you just call me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b47e21",
  "node": "Credits2",
  "text": "Wyatt: Oh, Lord![p/][s/] Run for it, Gavin!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ba716",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Stefanic: Good to see you, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cdfc0",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Stefanic: From what I hear,[p/] you've certainly moved up in the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbdba9",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] A [i]lot[/i] has happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e9c1b",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't even know where to begin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0302040",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm glad to see the Refinery is doing well."
}

{
  "id": "line:08daa90",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Stefanic: Well, I suppose I have [i]you[/i] to thank for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:038a8f3",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Stefanic: You're quite the—[p/] What did Her Majesty call you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b331d3",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] An angel investor..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b44bb",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Stefanic: Yes![p/][s/] That's it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f6b69",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Actually,[p/] I'm here on behalf of Her Majesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:094d9db",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We both had an idea for a business venture."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fa8ca",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And we think it would set a good precedent if we employed a company with your business practices."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af2c5c",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Stefanic: Oh...[p/] I think I [i]like[/i] the sound of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a0569",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Laefe: I still have much to learn about leading a noble house."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fbfa3",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Laefe: But I hope I can bring House Frega and Wyverngarde to a brighter future."
}

{
  "id": "line:028b8c9",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Aria: I think it's about time we ended the constant feuding between the Steelwinds and the Fregas."
}

{
  "id": "line:0184184",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Aria: And I'd like for us to work together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0bbd9",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Laefe: I may not know much,[p/] but that certainly sounds like a step in the right direction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eff2e6",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker will do best to help Queen."
}

{
  "id": "line:06595ab",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Laefe: I appreciate the gesture, Tracker,[p/] but I don't think—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0addb6c",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tracker: Banks need gold, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:087a127",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker can dig for gold."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dbd321",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Eugene: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da2142",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Eugene: And that makes Checkmate, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:052c620",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Celeste: Did you just [i]lose[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ae7b3",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Tyrion: No![p/][s/] I [i]demand[/i] a rematch!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c47c66",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Eugene: ...Learn to lose with dignity, for Lord's sake."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a89eb",
  "node": "Credits3",
  "text": "Harold: ...I'm glad I let him keep those Armbands."
}

{
  "id": "line:079ab56",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Theon: To think the Scaled Lord's daughter would descend to lead our kingdom to prosperity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f16441",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: Theon...[p/] You were [i]there[/i] for most of that trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0174bca",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: You [i]know[/i] what actually happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffbb69",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Theon: The Scaled Lord works in mysterious ways.[p/] Fate has brought you to where you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:090a99c",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: Ugh...[p/] I guess you're kind of right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae83c9",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Orym: You may have everyone [i]else[/i] fooled,[p/] but I know how this story goes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b330b3",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Orym: A mage is still a mage,[p/] and a noble is still a noble."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c7b12",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on.[p/] Don't be like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c89ad",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Orym: Hey...[p/] If you want to prove me wrong,[p/] by all means..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0417d60",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Orym: ...I ain't holding my breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:010af8d",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose you have every reason not to trust anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fa390",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Tyrion: But we [i]are[/i] going to fix this kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2779a",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: I really wish he would talk to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee7caf",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: He needs time to process everything that happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4536a",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: And I don't think he'll be very receptive to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fb3b5",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: At least,[p/] not right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e438e",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...We should [i]probably[/i] hire a professional he can talk to."
}

{
  "id": "line:003f21a",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: Yes...[p/] I really appreciate you coming here with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0916fb9",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: His actions were absolutely deplorable..."
}

{
  "id": "line:081f594",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: I was hoping coming here would give me closure...[p/] But..."
}

{
  "id": "line:065c8bc",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: With von Sanctus and Sibyl gone,[p/] we [i]have[/i] had a much easier time repairing our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d6711",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: I feel uneasy about all this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:006a2b5",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...No.[p/] I also see what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:01405ef",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: He may have had good intentions,[p/] but he refused to let anyone work with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0910c9f",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: Even with Eris,[p/] they were just using each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ba66",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: I do think he really wanted to change Wyverngarde.[p/] But he would [i]only[/i] do it on his own terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b26801",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: Even if he [i]did[/i] end up achieving his goals,[p/] the legacy he'd leave behind would be one of blood."
}

{
  "id": "line:0107c22",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: No lasting peace or justice could have that at its foundation."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ae470",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: That's...[p/] [i]surprisingly[/i] mature for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dc140",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Celeste: Hey![p/][s/] I'm [i]always[/i] mature."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5c012",
  "node": "Credits4",
  "text": "Aria: Goodbye, Aster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a37599",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you kidding me, Ruby?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0485d00",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Tyrion: What kind of ridiculous case [i]was[/i] that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af70f3",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Ruby: Weren't [i]you[/i] the one who called a monkey to the stand during Beatrice's trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d95bcc",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I suppose you have a point."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d13bda",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Ruby: Truth is often stranger than fiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:0758815",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Ruby: [i]You[/i] should know that better than anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbc671",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh my god...[p/] I just realized..."
}

{
  "id": "line:044322b",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is [i]this[/i] what I've been doing to Aria?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae7586",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Ruby: Hey.[p/] [i]You're[/i] the one that wanted to be lead prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:054e61d",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm only filling in for her until we can find a qualified replacement..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e37db",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Ruby: Well,[p/] if you ever get bored of life as a royal,[p/] there's always a spot open at my office."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f2863",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Aria: ...I see they allowed you to keep your axe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eba492",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Lucio: I thought I ordered you to stop visiting me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7e0af",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Aria: I outrank you now, Father."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff068",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Lucio: Hmph...[p/] McCoy's impertinence is rubbing off on you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f48291",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Aria: I'll take that as a compliment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c08a4c",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Lucio: I [i]am[/i] glad to see you in such good spirits."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f91a32",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Lucio: I suppose I underestimated you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7b5c2",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm surprised you're not sentencing me to death."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b9b85",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Beatrice: I [i]suppose[/i] I should be grateful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9e4b8",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] We kind of need you alive so we know when Eris is back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f918b3",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Beatrice: You're...[p/] [i]using[/i] me like a canary in a coal mine?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d7729",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm almost [i]proud[/i] of you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1764c",
  "node": "Credits5",
  "text": "Beatrice: Although...[p/] I [i]am[/i] curious as to why she hasn't returned yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a1311",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Eris: What the [i]hell[/i] is this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c0d8b",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Eris: Why are you preventing me from leaving?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00698f0",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Asmodeus: ...Well, I can't very well let you make a fool of yourself a [i]second[/i] time."
}

{
  "id": "line:072ee4d",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Asmodeus: You are not to leave the Sixth Circle until I tell you otherwise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0ee23",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Asmodeus: So says the Word of Asmodeus."
}

{
  "id": "line:057bdf3",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Eris: Are you...[p/] [i]grounding[/i] me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecb788",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Asmodeus: If you want to behave like a petulant child,[p/] I'll treat you like one."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b0716",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Eris: I swear...[p/] When I get out of here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bf66a",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Asmodeus: ...What have I told you about speaking in [i]future[/i] tense?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e042c1",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you sure you don't want to move into the castle with us, Mom?"
}

{
  "id": "line:084e7c1",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Jolene: No...[p/] I've grown attached to this place."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a539d",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Jolene: It was your father's,[p/] and it doesn't seem right to abandon it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e6a04",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I get what you mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:095a948",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Jolene: Anyways,[p/] I want to give [i]you[/i] two some privacy."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dc368",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: Mom..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b75335",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Jolene: So stop dragging your feet, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:01880f3",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Jolene: I want to live to see my grandkids."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e86ad9",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Mom!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4dd8b",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Noah: Oh![p/] Ahoy, Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:077b118",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Noah: I have everything ready for tonight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da8751",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I-[p/][s/]It's nothing!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0808bba",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]*whisper*[/i] Pretend like you don't know anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:04661de",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Noah: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6905",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Noah: Oh...[p/] I see.[p/] So it's for [i]her[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e2b20",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What are you doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7a09d",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's...[p/] a surprise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de0a50",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Alright, whatever you say."
}

{
  "id": "line:017da14",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] I was wondering."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e7847",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: You've lived for a [i]really[/i] long time, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6583f",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Remus: ...I have."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cb81f",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: Do I have any siblings?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3c4b0",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Remus: No...[p/] I’m sorry.[p/] There was... [i]one[/i] many centuries ago,[p/] but I lost her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c411c8",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Remus: It was rare,[p/] even across the centuries,[p/] when I’ve sought...[p/] companionship."
}

{
  "id": "line:091b35f",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Remus: Dragons are magical beings and the creation of offspring is rare."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e824a0",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Remus: So much so,[p/] that it's a miracle that [i]you[/i] were born."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7dc95",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Remus: I'm sorry,[p/] but you are alone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1f7d0",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: Hm...[p/] I don't really feel that way."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d49b7",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: I think I spend so much time with Aria,[p/] that she's basically my sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f76a70",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: A-[p/][s/]And Tyrion...[p/] Well..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a09d7c",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Remus: ...Perhaps I should have some words with Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bea45",
  "node": "Credits6",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't you [i]dare[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afada6",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Mosourika: So we meet again, Crimson Demon!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f9acf",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Celeste: Who keeps [i]telling[/i] people about that nickname?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5049c",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Who knows?[p/] It could have been anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:06370e9",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Mosourika: ...You don't like it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9f259",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Mosourika: I could help you come up with a new one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4484f",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm good.[p/] Thanks."
}

{
  "id": "line:09163c5",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Mosourika: How about...[p/] \"Scaled Empress\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7c621",
  "node": "Credits7",
  "text": "Celeste: Okay...[p/] I actually [i]really[/i] like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5c611",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] Yeah."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b6078",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Celeste: That's how it all happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f8bc0",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Beatrice: He really did it...[p/] He voided a Blood Contract drafted by the Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db81d1",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Celeste: I thought you'd be more happy after what Eris did to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c03711",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Beatrice: He has no idea what he's done."
}

{
  "id": "line:0148547",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Come on,[p/] it can't be [i]that[/i] bad."
}

{
  "id": "line:072c303",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Demons naturally despise the celestials and their magic,[p/] and they pride themselves on their ability to deceive others."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701d56",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Beatrice: A voided Blood Contract—[p/]especially by a heavensborn—[p/]is the highest disgrace for a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ead38",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Beatrice: It rarely happens.[p/] Even the weakest demons know not to leave any openings like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0332d01",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Beatrice: It honestly irritates me how much less meticulous she was when she made your contract.[p/] What was she thinking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd7e22",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Is she really that big of a deal?"
}

{
  "id": "line:029ea81",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Beatrice: Asmodeus is the King of Demons—[p/]a god among gods.[p/] Eris is his [i]daughter[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0282fa2",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice",
  "text": "Celeste: So what?[p/] Is she going to tell on us to him?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d68eed",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: This is serious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca583c",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: No one has ever voided a Contract drafted by a Lord of Hell.[p/] It's unheard of."
}

{
  "id": "line:003f5e9",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Your sweetheart is going to attract a lot of unwanted attention from hell [i]and[/i] heaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:0559ec8",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Then I need you to tell me everything you can.[p/] I need to know what's coming."
}

{
  "id": "line:0368922",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I want concessions."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b2122",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I don't plan on spending the rest of my life in this cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd731b",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Beatrice,[p/] you committed first-degree murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b0d1a",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: He was a terrible person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0757857",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Celeste: He was your [i]dad[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e9d0c",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: He would've been executed for his crimes anyway,[p/] assuming he didn't just run."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0de13",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Can you imagine how difficult it would be to track down someone with that much gold?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6c70e",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: The way I see it,[p/] I saved you people a lot of trouble."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a96469",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm not going to pardon you, Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc0ad8",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I don't want to be pardoned.[p/] I just don't want to listen to Lucio working out in his cell all day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0842fb3",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: Honestly,[p/] get that man a book or something.[p/] He needs a hobby."
}

{
  "id": "line:02417f6",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Celeste: Fine,[p/] I'll see what I can do about getting you some [i]heavily supervised[/i] outings."
}

{
  "id": "line:04391c4",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm blind.[p/] What am I going to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d1482",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Turn yourself invisible and run away?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5aa66",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I am [i]insulted[/i] that you think I'm that uncreative."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dfe9f",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Are you all really going to be okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:028b14f",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Celeste: What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:002279e",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: You are now the ruling Queen of Wyverngarde:[p/] the most powerful kingdom in the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ca2ce",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Every order you make—[p/]every word you say—[p/]could have unimaginable worldwide consequences."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7a584",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Celeste: Can you please not remind me of that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd7289",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: So you [i]do[/i] recognize that, then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a86b4",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Celeste: Why are you telling me this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0874d1a",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Because you're going to live the rest of your life in a world of glass."
}

{
  "id": "line:01df6c6",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Anything and everything you do could shatter the lives of millions."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d707a",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm rooting for you all.[p/] I really am,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e6c22",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: The weight of that responsibility is what drove Aster insane."
}

{
  "id": "line:085c324",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice3",
  "text": "Beatrice: Even Rathallion couldn't handle it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0476b2d",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Wait, [i]he[/i] took the crown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de75af",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Many centuries ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:067c80b",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: All it took was one lapse in judgment for him to cause one of the largest famines in Wyverngarde's history.[p/] Millions died."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f7b00",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh my god..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0645391",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Just something to think about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4d1b0",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: Thanks, Beatrice..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05adaa2",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Anyways,[p/] if you want to know more about Hells' hierarchy,[p/] we'll need to start with the Lords of Hell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a58cb7",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: You're actually familiar with one of them—the Lord of the First: Bahamut."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea5306",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: The Scaled Lord's a demon?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05ab8f6",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Did the horns,[p/] scales,[p/] and fiery breath not imply that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:025e820",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i] I guess that makes me demon-adjacent then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0eeb4",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: Is that making you rethink your feelings for the heavensborn?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00aa3be",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Honestly,[p/] I think that makes me like him more."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e97002",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I think I might actually hate you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b20dd",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah,[p/] well,[p/] you're stuck with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:076b82b",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...For now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebeda2",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "Celeste: Whatever,[p/] tell me more about Lords two through nine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef9b3d",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "The eldest Frega had some idea of what was coming,[p/] but perhaps it would be best to hold onto it for now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f069a0",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "It wasn't as if she fully understood the politics of the gods either."
}

{
  "id": "line:084401b",
  "node": "CelAndBeatrice4",
  "text": "But from what little she knew,[p/] demons wouldn't be the only ones coming after them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0833da4",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Orym: Hey, I'm clocking out for today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8904d",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Aria: Thank you for your work, Orym.[p/] I'll see you tomorrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ce4a",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Orym: Uh...[p/] So—"
}

{
  "id": "line:048fbf9",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Orym: Are you getting back into the swing of things?"
}

{
  "id": "line:027d11b",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Aria: I'd like to think so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0691699",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Aria: I need to make sure everything is in order for when Tyrion takes over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0609a6d",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Aria: He's capable,[p/] but he's never managed an organization of this size."
}

{
  "id": "line:0462601",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym",
  "text": "Orym: I can't believe I'm going to have to take orders from that kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:00807dc",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Aria: ...Was there something else, Orym?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06030e9",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: Uh...[p/] Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b1aee",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f5be1",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Aria: Spit it out.[p/] I'm very busy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caeeb9",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: ...Men are idiots, Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:024b4b3",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: Yeah...[p/] We're all just dumb idiots."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfc465",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: We just bumble around,[p/] bumping into shit,[p/] without a care in the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ec014",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: Sometimes we're just blind to what's right in front of us, you know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b239e0",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: So...[p/] Don't let one idiot get you down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0001dae",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: You're—[p/] You're a good kid, Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba9ef7",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: You deserve the best."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b345a9",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Aria: ...I don't think you should be calling your superior a \"kid\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:002c92f",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: I—[p/][s/] Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01138ea",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "The commander stammered for a while before his face just squeezed into a scowl."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ff10",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: ...Then write me up!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe3581",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Orym: I don't care anymore!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06251ab",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "He slammed the door before stomping his way into the city streets.[p/] He grumbled under his breath the entire time."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b5f77",
  "node": "AriaAndOrym2",
  "text": "Aria let out a chuckle.[p/] A part of her was really going to miss working with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0336184",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Celeste: Okay,[p/] so they're just going to turn the lights on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07dd53d",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Tyrion: During certain times of the year,[p/] the leylines around Aurinax become extremely potent."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e0282",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Tyrion: A lot of the businesses here take advantage of that to charge the Arcane Power Cells within their homes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0018309",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Tyrion: Those effects are amplified when they do it simultaneously."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c42d88",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Celeste: You're such a nerd..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6211e",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait...[p/] If this is all happening in the city,[p/] why are we out on the ocean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05dacb6",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Come on.[p/] You'll love this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b5797",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "The ocean was quiet—[p/]save for the humming of the small boat's engine against the water."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d0094",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] It's really dark...[p/] Are you sure it's safe to sail a boat out here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1c408",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't worry...[p/] There will be plenty of light soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:044f249",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Celeste: \"Soon\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a42d05",
  "node": "Confess",
  "text": "Tyrion: In about..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01de043",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "One by one,[p/] each of the buildings in Aurinax lit up like a flame spreading across the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:090bdca",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Every light in every house lit up,[p/] their collective warm glow washing over the city and shimmering off the ocean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf88cf",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Celeste just stared at the sight wide-eyed.[p/] Her eyes were gleaming.[p/] Their topaz colors reflected the warm glow of the city."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a1420",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Okay,[p/] I take it all back.[p/][s/] I love this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a03224",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Noah used to bring my mother and me out here every year for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2755d",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's actually a lot brighter than it ever was back then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c738ef",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm glad I got the chance to show it to you, Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ad0dc",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Celeste: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/] Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:070db29",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "She began fidgeting with her fingers,[p/] looking away from me."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e2fbf",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "We just sailed in silence again,[p/] drinking in the sight of the lit city."
}

{
  "id": "line:084226d",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "The wind shifted.[p/] It carried the scent of salt and seaweed with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0154aa4",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I've really missed being able to spend time with you like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:09eddbd",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] Me too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09560",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Celeste: It was so much simpler when you were just an attorney,[p/] and I was your bodyguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:046fce8",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Celeste: But now I'm the Scaled Lord's daughter and [i]you're[/i] the lead prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0299b9a",
  "node": "Confess2",
  "text": "Celeste: We barely get to see each other..."
}

{
  "id": "line:006c4ed",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But at least we're together now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cccbe5",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And you have something to remember whenever we're apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aac689",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Yeah. [h=\"This is so sweet...|I love you...\" e=\"hf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0122e67",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Y-[p/][s/]Your thoughts are leaking, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:04997e5",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Celeste: What do you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb2e59",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Her eyes widened,[p/] realizing what I just saw."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b50957",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Celeste: Agh![p/][s/] It's been so long, I forgot to—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce21ae",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]It's not fair![p/][s/] [i]You[/i] were supposed to say it first!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c707fc",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a46ccd",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Celeste: U-[p/][s/]Um...[p/][s/] I didn't really mean—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1bf7f",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] I-[p/][s/]I [i]did[/i] mean it, but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb2b64",
  "node": "Confess3",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I kind of [i]hate[/i] the Eye of Horus sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:01671f1",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "I just silently moved to sit next to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:085a307",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "She didn't seem to object,[p/] but she couldn't meet my eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4e8eb",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "She glanced at me for a moment.[p/] Her eyes widened,[p/] and she quickly turned away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0807b1f",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "But she slowly slid closer to me.[p/] My shoulder pressed against hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0427640",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Her hand slid into mine.[p/] I squeezed as if it were the most precious thing in the world to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a42160",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "She slowly turned to me,[p/] then I turned to face her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c21f87",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "We just stared at each other.[p/] Sharing a thousand confessions in one look."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1592a",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "We were both going to see a lot of changes in our lives."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d42688",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "But this moment was one of them.[p/] And I wouldn't take any other path that didn't lead here."
}

{
  "id": "line:00890a7",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You'll always keep your promise, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00cfa13",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Tyrion: No matter where each of us goes,[p/] we'll always be together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb8eda",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I love you, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0009abe",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Celeste: I love you, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:0274361",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Celeste: S-[p/][s/]Sorry...[p/] This is all a little much."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d1756",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d45aaf",
  "node": "Confess4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right now,[p/] we have all the time in the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:07364f9",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: ...Have you heard about what happened in Wyverngarde?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaff1b",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: Is [i]that[/i] why you've called me here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0782664",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: This could've been in an email, High Inquisitor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9667b",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: This is serious!"
}

{
  "id": "line:033edd1",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: I must accept responsibility.[p/] Keeping records of the heavensborn was my duty."
}

{
  "id": "line:093ada4",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: I have no idea how this \"Tyrion Cuthbert\" slipped past me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e8f63",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: Frey was always a slippery one.[p/] Even [i]I[/i] lost track of her."
}

{
  "id": "line:075f0ea",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: And I'm happy she got the chance to settle down after everything that happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ee5c7",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: Miles!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb28cd",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: Illia,[p/] he's just [i]one[/i] heavensborn.[p/] He's harmless."
}

{
  "id": "line:01453af",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: He brought the Lord of the Sixth to the Court of [i]bloody[/i] Azathoth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00030f2",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: Do you have [i]any[/i] idea the amount of damage they could have done to all of creation from there?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:086640f",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: You're worrying too much.[p/] We're still here, aren't we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f1ba9",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: The multiverse is intact and [i]everything[/i] is fine..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07db9e7",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8f708",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Illia: Miles...[p/] He has the Eye of Odin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b22cbc",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia",
  "text": "Miles: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fa79c",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: ...That's impossible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9f4d2",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: I borrowed some of your drones from the armory.[p/] I sent them into the Court of Azathoth myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0701a40",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: Illia—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00486a7",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: These readings...[p/] They are [i]exactly[/i] the same as the ones we gathered during our experiment with Frey."
}

{
  "id": "line:0857a39",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: He awakened its power,[p/] albeit briefly."
}

{
  "id": "line:044a566",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: ...And he did it [i]in front[/i] of the Lord of the Sixth."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b72ba",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: We must assume that the Lord of the [i]Ninth[/i] knows about it as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12428",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: Does His Majesty know?[p/] Did he approve of your little reconnaissance mission?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d388b",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: Of course not,[p/] but I believe the path forward is clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0025ba4",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: We must inform heaven.[p/] They'll want to know about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf9f7f",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: I've been hearing some rumors through the grapevine lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b46e98",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: ...The Lord of the Ninth has begun moving his forces."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6de4c",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: He must [i]know[/i], Archsentinel."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0121e",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: You know better than anyone else."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e5a86",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: [i]Nothing[/i] is impossible when the House of Horus is involved."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d576bc",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: ...Alright, alright.[p/] You win."
}

{
  "id": "line:0430500",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: Look into this.[p/] Try to sell it to Wyverngarde as a \"diplomatic mission\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d0b76",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: But exercise discretion...[p/] If they [i]ever[/i] find out about what we did with Frey—"
}

{
  "id": "line:051b535",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: I understand.[p/] It would mean war with Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0513b46",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: Thank you, Archsentinel.[p/] I'll speak to His Majesty about this at once."
}

{
  "id": "line:001ebbc",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Illia: ...I'm sorry for disturbing your evening."
}

{
  "id": "line:0153b99",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: You don't understand, Illia..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6f6b9",
  "node": "MilesAndIllia2",
  "text": "Miles: If what you're saying is true,[p/] it could spell war with the Outer Planes."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d057b",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Door"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3f596",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "There was a steel door that led into the cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0822c98",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "A magical mechanism covered by a steel box was placed over the lock."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dde6a",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Torch"
}

{
  "id": "line:09218da",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Lit torches were hanging on the cell walls.[p/] It seemed a bit irresponsible to light a fire in here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b46993",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "But prisoner safety was probably the last thing on the Inquisition’s mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:070f321",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "The cell had a barred window.[p/] The bars were rusted."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d4e8f",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "If a prisoner tried to escape,[p/] there would be a three-story drop to freedom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcfd15",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Room"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfd407",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Celeste: There are traces of [b]abjuration[/b] all over the cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edeabf",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...This cell is specifically designed to suppress the magic of mages within it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a659b4",
  "node": "Examine_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: It's covered in an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:022c67b",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042c9a9",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We heard that you don't have any memories of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0167518",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is that true?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c33be",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: It is..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9b9a1",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: No matter how much I try,[p/] I can't recall anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf4647",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is the last thing you remember?"
}

{
  "id": "line:036ba34",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I believe I was leaving my meeting with the High Speaker and His Majesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d7562",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: After the meeting,[p/] I was planning to return to the Nave to speak with my father,[p/] but I suddenly felt something churning inside my stomach."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6404b",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I thought some fresh air might help stave off the nausea,[p/] so I went to the balcony."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b651f0",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Remus: The one over Lake Galakrond?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020c123",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Yes.[p/] That one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a8432b",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: The last thing I remember was losing consciousness as I looked at the lake."
}

{
  "id": "line:085f208",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And did you cast any magic before this happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0952145",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: No...[p/] I didn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:03df267",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hm...[p/] Are you sure you don't remember anything after that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:068b98b",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I don't...[p/] All I remember is waking up to the sound of someone sobbing."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e2e84",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...It was Celeste.[p/] It seemed that you'd just regained consciousness, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0703ea0",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Magic that can affect the mind"
}

{
  "id": "line:06daeac",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I feel like we've completely ruled out Mageblight..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e6d3e",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I doubt [i]that's[/i] why you can't remember anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:002aa69",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are there any spells that can specifically modify or destroy people's memories?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ef78f",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It would certainly explain a lot of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff5a21",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: No...[p/] Arcane spells can only affect the physical world."
}

{
  "id": "line:07042ca",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: But throughout history,[p/] mages have [i]attempted[/i] to develop spells that can affect the mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:017cdb5",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: There's no recorded history of any of them succeeding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0863d61",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Remus: ...You can't assume that arcane spells are the only type of magic that exists."
}

{
  "id": "line:0398fbd",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Remus: I think you've observed it already.[p/] There are magical creatures in this world that don't use [i]arcane[/i] magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:05cf391",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Remus: ...Isn't that right, Mr. Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0806fc6",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure what you're trying to imply."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f1d07",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Remus: If I learn that Lumina had [i]any[/i] hand in this—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e65156",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Grace.[p/] I'm [i]not[/i] an agent of the Theocracy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa44fb",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And even if what you're saying is true,[p/] [i]I[/i] wasn't the one who manipulated Steelwind's memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ac62e",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But I suppose you raise a good point."
}

{
  "id": "line:085b7fd",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If something affected Steelwind's memories,[p/] it wasn't necessarily an arcane spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:022cbb4",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: In fact,[p/] it [i]couldn't[/i] have been an arcane spell.[p/] It was definitely something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:055f551",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...You're probably right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a03c84",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Which proves that I'm responsible for the murders..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02db54b",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Aria did this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbdaa7",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You just said that you don't have any memories of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d1d47",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why are you so convinced that you're responsible for this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9d5af",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I told the Inquisition already.[p/] I [i]saw[/i] Beatrice before I passed out."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e778b",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]She's[/i] clearly involved in this somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b440d8",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: There's more to this than you realize, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:03300b9",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...For the past few months,[p/] the Inquisition and I have been investigating a string of seemingly unrelated murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0049503",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: During each of those cases,[p/] we were able to apprehend the perpetrator without issue."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ece90",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: But there was always something...[p/] off about them during questioning."
}

{
  "id": "line:097d2b6",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: The murders were always abnormally gruesome and passionate.[p/] And each of the perpetrators said the same thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dac1f",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: They all said that they \"had no choice\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:038ab07",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...\"No choice\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de466b",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Cases like this have been occurring throughout Wyverngarde.[p/] And very little connects the perpetrators to each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:0201c11",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: All except one thing.[p/] Each of them acted as if someone had controlled them against their will."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3d21a",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They were probably just desperate..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0171af6",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Most murderers try to make excuses after they're caught."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bf0f4",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They could even just be in complete denial."
}

{
  "id": "line:091ebeb",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Orym said the same thing,[p/] but these cases were far too similar for me to ignore."
}

{
  "id": "line:03908e5",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I wondered if they were telling the truth.[p/] Perhaps each of these murders [i]was[/i] committed by an unknown party."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f33ebd",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I didn't have any concrete evidence,[p/] but I knew I was getting closer to...[p/] something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0494cba",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: The Purple Conspiracy"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b613da",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind...[p/] I don't mean to be rude,[p/] but this sounds—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0515d",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Completely insane?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0792623",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't even have any physical evidence to prove these murders are connected."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fa0b2",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...There's [i]one[/i] piece of evidence,[p/] but it's hardly concrete."
}

{
  "id": "line:09adc4a",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: But it does tie each of these cases together."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f06dc",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "She took out a small parchment from her pocket and showed it to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e87686",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's...[p/] a purple symbol."
}

{
  "id": "line:015359c",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Several of the people we arrested had an item with this symbol on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a494e",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: None of them could remember where it came from,[p/] or even what it was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd7227",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: But they all somehow knew that it was called the \"Purple Mark\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:04edd25",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But there [i]has[/i] to be an explanation for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4f51e",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It could just be some esoteric superstition that we don't know about..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a31ce7",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: If that's true,[p/] then ask yourself one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a23cda",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Where did [i]I[/i] get this parchment from?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0866d1a",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't mean-...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9562a",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I found it in my pocket after I was properly confined."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1fc89",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: This symbol must be a calling card of some sort."
}

{
  "id": "line:0107abd",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: For all I know,[p/] they could have controlled my body and forced me to draw this symbol myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:034fab9",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: This massacre at the cathedral is related to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce2500",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Aria's fate"
}

{
  "id": "line:0686b60",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't want to dismiss what you said,[p/] but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:002c3a6",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This definitely won't hold up in court."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f67200",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Nor should it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0080aea",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: If my mind has been compromised,[p/] I can't take the risk of leaving this dungeon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da28ea",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Otherwise,[p/] I could end up harming [i]more[/i] people."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b1971",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] you can't exactly spend the rest of your life in this dungeon."
}

{
  "id": "line:079c709",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] Are you serious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090dfc9",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What about Aster?[p/] Weren't you two supposed to be married soon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01cec6c",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He's the king now,[p/] and you can't rule Wyverngarde alongside him from a holding cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acfdc7",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...You're correct,[p/] but he's always been a remarkable person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbaa74",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: He should have no problem finding another suitress. [h=\"I must think|of his well-being too.\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bccbea",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: No."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ed6d9",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your plan is terrible,[p/] and I hate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:019648d",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll just defend you and figure out what really happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:003f9dd",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Mr. Cuthbert,[p/][s/] I am not going to risk [i]more[/i] lives."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a1a7",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: If I were to hurt His Majesty,[p/] I would never be able to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0829d19",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Please don't ask that of me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b38df",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Saving Steelwind's future (ARGUMENT)"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f6946",
  "node": "Talk_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Saving Steelwind's future"
}

{
  "id": "line:074de1c",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm glad you were unharmed, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:08583d9",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I was worried when I saw you lying next to Pierce's corpse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0670c5c",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] I definitely got the least of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2c3ff",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I should consider myself lucky that whoever did this decided not to kill me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b27b9",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Celeste.[p/] I heard that you and I fought during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:04da879",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I apologize if I hurt you in any way."
}

{
  "id": "line:09795c7",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Celeste: S-[p/][s/]Sorry.[p/] This is just a lot to take in."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0b360",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Celeste: A few hours ago,[p/] it really felt like you were trying to kill me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3ed6a",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...I'm truly sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:06eaf7d",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Is Orym working with the Kingsguard to investigate what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08455d3",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He is.[p/] We actually got a lot of our information from him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd5ce2",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: That's reassuring to hear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0207460",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I suppose this is a good opportunity to see how well he works without my guidance."
}

{
  "id": "line:05332b1",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Do you ever stop working?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d5619",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm relieved His Majesty was unharmed during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e570ef",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever orchestrated this trapped him in a [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:015bd8e",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They must have used him as a distraction while they went after their true targets."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a7f51",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: As callous as it is,[p/] I'm glad he wasn't their real target."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b897fb",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I don't know what I would do if anything happened to him."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c80e0",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Alaric"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e5912",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I can't believe I was forced to attack Prince Alaric."
}

{
  "id": "line:027ccf6",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Don't feel too guilty."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5ce47",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: He doesn't seem to have any lasting injuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f60d5",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Regardless,[p/] he's much too young to experience something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08b3920",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Garrick|Autopsy Report:Garrick Pierce"
}

{
  "id": "line:078a1a3",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...I'm sorry about what happened, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f01f8",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I can't imagine the lack of closure you feel right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a643e",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No.[p/] I don't care about that anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aecd1b",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm just glad Tyrion is safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f44330",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Player: Coraline|Autopsy Report: Coraline Sibyl|Lloyd|Autopsy Report: Lloyd von Sanctus"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e84a08",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I can't believe we lost so many House leaders in the course of a few months."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5e00f",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Now my father is the only head of the Four Pillars that still lives."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcbf89",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Beatrice's blackmail revealed that those massacres in the countryside were orchestrated by William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:06940d6",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "But I couldn't help but wonder.[p/] Lucio was now the only surviving Pillar Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c81e53",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Was that a coincidence,[p/] or was it by design?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f74111",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What do you think about this, Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058b12d",
  "node": "Present_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry.[p/] But I'm afraid I can't say much about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0100c72",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "We arrived at the dungeon to speak with Steelwind,[p/] but we didn't see her anywhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5982",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Inquisition and the Kingsguard must still be processing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:037a88c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should come back later."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe4745",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "We arrived at the dungeon and found the prosecutor walking around her holding cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:06605ee",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Several papers with haphazardly scratched notes were scattered around it."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ac47f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "She was pacing back and forth,[p/] head lowered in contemplation as she stared at one of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c3695",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "She didn't even notice us until I knocked on the bars to her cell."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a9a63",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a35f19",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: Mr. Cuthbert...[p/] and Your Grace."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f6d2c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Steelwind's eyes stayed on the Archduke before turned to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:06fc64a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How are you doing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e166f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: As best as I can,[p/] all things considered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae7461",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: What brings you here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6431f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're trying to investigate everything that happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a091d8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: ...I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0535ac3",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I was wondering if you could answer some of our questions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe2ce0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind.[p/] I know your situation is pretty grim right now,[p/] but you know you can trust me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f77b03",
  "node": "Check_Events_Dungeon1",
  "text": "Aria: I know,[p/] but at this moment,[p/] I don't even know if I can trust myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:031b168",
  "node": "AriaArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Aria: I'm not going to debate this anymore, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9892c",
  "node": "AriaArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Aria: This is [i]my[/i] decision,[p/] and I won't risk anyone's life in the hopes of saving myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b7b09",
  "node": "AriaArgument_Fail",
  "text": "Aria: Please...[p/] Just leave me be."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a6c4c",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "Steelwind was going to throw away everything she cared about..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c0bcb",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "Even if [i]she[/i] was the one who did all this,[p/] [i]she's[/i] not the one who's responsible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0477cd2",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "I wouldn't let her resign herself to a fate like this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0563a98",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "Yes"
}

{
  "id": "line:0567327",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "No"
}

{
  "id": "line:0874bb7",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind![p/][s/] Are you seriously just going to throw your life away?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c537c6",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "Aria: ...If it were necessary,[p/] I would give my [i]life[/i] for this kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c632bb",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "Aria: If someone controlled my actions today,[p/] they can and [i]will[/i] do so again."
}

{
  "id": "line:027c225",
  "node": "AriaArgue",
  "text": "Aria: And as long as that possibility exists,[p/] I can't trust myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0633e3f",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Doubt [c=\"But that's assuming this person can continue to do so. We don't know how this mind control works. We can't just drop this without finding out what really happened.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe6cd",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Deflect [c=\"That's not the issue here. If someone else is responsible for what happened, then we need to find out who they are. They're still out there.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc746d",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's not the issue here."
}

{
  "id": "line:091ff90",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: If someone else is responsible for what happened,[p/] then we need to find out who they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0246a",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: They could still be out there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e78701",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Aria: If that's true,[p/] you are fully capable of finding that out yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0395ae7",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Aria: As I've said,[p/] I have no memories of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:04074a0",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sure that you'll be able to find out what happened one day."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c6b0e",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "But she'll already have lost everything by then..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0346794",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Threaten [c=\"Do you even understand what you're saying?! You will lose [i]everything[/i] if you just let this happen!\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0670525",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you even understand what you're saying?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f5fee",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You will lose [i]everything[/i] if you just let this happen!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0847ce5",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Even[/i] if you aren't executed for these charges,[p/][s/] you'll spend the rest of your life in prison!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a3398",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Aria: If that is what my duty demands,[p/][s/] then so be it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0076bae",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Aria: I [i]can't[/i] continue living my life if my mind is vulnerable like this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3f6a8",
  "node": "AriaArgue2",
  "text": "Aria: ...I will [i]not[/i] endanger His Majesty."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c2db0",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that's assuming this person can continue to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:015e613",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You said so yourself.[p/] You haven't found any evidence to prove your theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0604420",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We don't know how this \"mind control\" works.[p/] We don't even know what this magic is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0211153",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can't just drop this without finding out what really happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d84ced",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Aria: I suppose you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:026ffc4",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Aria: ...But I doubt there was [i]any[/i] goal to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0268346",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Aria: I've been investigating these murders for months."
}

{
  "id": "line:070de78",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Aria: The person behind this is a sadistic individual who wanted to cause as much suffering as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd3c3f",
  "node": "AriaArgue3",
  "text": "Aria: There's no way to connect them to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0623b7a",
  "node": "AriaArgue4",
  "text": "Alaric's Testimony|Archeus's Encounter|The Trapped King|The Trapped King 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f489e6",
  "node": "AriaArgue4",
  "text": "Aria: ...What is this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5c36d",
  "node": "AriaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: The perpetrator wasn't nearly as aimless as you think."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d34eac",
  "node": "AriaArgue4",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]this[/i] proves it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de2752",
  "node": "AriaArgue4",
  "text": "Remus: My apologies, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but I don't really see how that proves your claim."
}

{
  "id": "line:0480425",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's not true, Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead82f",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever did this had very specific targets in mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e8d93",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Both Prince Alaric and the High Speaker saw you when the murders were being committed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9ceb2",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not to mention,[p/] they set a trap for Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0633659",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's assume that someone [i]was[/i] controlling you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0805331",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Tyrion: They wouldn't have left Alaric, Archeus, or Aster alive if they were trying to cause as much suffering as possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4d1f8",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Aria: ...I suppose you have a point there,[p/] but even so,[p/] that hardly narrows things down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b70662",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Aria: If someone were controlling me,[p/] they wouldn't need to enter the cathedral to use me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e28915",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Aria: Perhaps you're right,[p/] and the perpetrator only wanted to murder the three victims."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd49d4",
  "node": "AriaArgue5",
  "text": "Aria: There's plenty of people who might want to see those three dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0828407",
  "node": "AriaArgue6",
  "text": "The Trapped King|Contingent Spell|Force Cage"
}

{
  "id": "line:001d833",
  "node": "AriaArgue6",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's evidence that narrows down who's responsible for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0401124",
  "node": "AriaArgue6",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:06243f0",
  "node": "AriaArgue6",
  "text": "Aria: But I don't really follow your logic."
}

{
  "id": "line:07165a3",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's one thing you're overlooking."
}

{
  "id": "line:064f3a5",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Before the murders started,[p/] someone trapped Aster within a [b]Force Cage[/b] using [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a52168",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Aria: But they didn't harm him.[p/] It was probably just a distraction."
}

{
  "id": "line:03141bf",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even so,[p/] this gives us two very important clues."
}

{
  "id": "line:08af152",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The first is that whoever did this was capable of casting those two spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:038e709",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: This means that the perpetrator was either a mage or working with one."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5f126",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Aria: That's true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0212117",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the second clue is the most important one."
}

{
  "id": "line:032e82a",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever set that trap for Aster,[p/] they did so within twenty-four hours of it triggering."
}

{
  "id": "line:0854b86",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Grand Cathedral was closed to the public.[p/] This means that the perpetrator must have been someone who attended the funeral."
}

{
  "id": "line:01ad1cb",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Aria: ...So it was one of them?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04beab9",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: That narrows down our list of suspects substantially."
}

{
  "id": "line:056a7a1",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a chance we can identify who did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:06118e7",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: And if they really [i]did[/i] control your actions,[p/] we can find a way to prevent them from doing so again."
}

{
  "id": "line:056257d",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Steelwind...[p/] You need to fight this."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c78c0",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Aria: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/] I can't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af5b68",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why not?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8de1b",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Aria: If we pursue an individual like this,[p/] they might retaliate even more than they already have."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a27f5",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Aria: They wanted to remove me from my position... How will they react if I try to resist?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d9b67",
  "node": "AriaArgue7",
  "text": "Aria: They might hurt even more people to send a message.[p/] It's far too dangerous."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2afba",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Threaten [c=\"Whoever did this had a goal far bigger than you. And you have no guarantee that they'll stop here. Who will they target next? Your father? ...The king?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dff0ef",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Doubt [c=\"I doubt someone like that would go that far. They might decide to lie low and wait for things to die down. \"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c3f5a",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: I doubt someone like that would go that far."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f7a03",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: They might decide to lie low and wait for things to die down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5c3d8",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Aria: Whoever did this is an unhinged murderer."
}

{
  "id": "line:029b5f0",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Aria: I can't risk everything I care about on the assumption they are acting logically."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3ff3f",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose you have a point."
}

{
  "id": "line:034c35d",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "I couldn't make empty claims like that.[p/] I still had no idea who was behind this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74cd8",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Appeal [c=\"We can't back down in the face of injustice. If we let the perpetrator get away with this, we're letting them [i]know[/i] that their actions will go unanswered.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0606347",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can't back down in the face of injustice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de77f6",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: If we let the perpetrator get away with this,[p/] we're letting them [i]know[/i] that their actions will go unanswered."
}

{
  "id": "line:09245f6",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Tyrion: You need to be strong and fight this, Steelwind![p/][s/] No matter the cost!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb7df5",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Aria: That's easy for you to say."
}

{
  "id": "line:061e908",
  "node": "AriaArgue8",
  "text": "Aria: [i]You're[/i] not the one putting your loved ones in danger."
}

{
  "id": "line:0241908",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Whoever did this had a goal far bigger than you,[p/] and you have no guarantee that they'll stop here."
}

{
  "id": "line:016c265",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Three nobles died today,[p/] and two of them were near the top of the political hierarchy."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fe6dd",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: What if they decide to go after more victims?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015a68a",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who will they target next?[p/][s/] Your father?[p/][s/] ...The king?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed7131",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: We need to catch them before they can do more harm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0304e2e",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know you're frightened about what might happen to the people close to you,[p/] but we can't let someone this dangerous get away with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa002c",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] When you put it that way,[p/] I suppose I have no other choice, do I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08be173",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: I never realized it before, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9a634",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: You really have a bad habit of butting your nose into other people's business, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5f59d",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I suppose I do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0527cca",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: But you're right.[p/] We can't let this go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0873309",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: I'll find a way to dispute this...[p/] somehow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0481bfa",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Aria: ...Thank you, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acaa10",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I think we've known each other long enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0beb5e9",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't need to be so formal."
}

{
  "id": "line:08502b5",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "I successfully PERSUADED Aria Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:048e20d",
  "node": "AriaArgue9",
  "text": "Remus: Hm..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1c7bc",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: I know I agreed to fight this...[p/] But..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0952d79",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: What is it?[p/] You're the most qualified attorney in the nobility."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f3118",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: You'll definitely be able to make a case for yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:031f1e7",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: As you probably know,[p/] House Sibyl controls the legislative [i]and[/i] judicial branches of our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec5db9",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: ...And they've nominated my [i]father[/i] as the prosecutor for my trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:024e83f",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: My theory of mind control is not substantiated by the evidence,[p/] and we can't blame another kingdom's magic because of that."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c59d5",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: Everyone believes that I overspent my magic and gave myself Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9a4c3",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: As a result,[p/] they blame House Steelwind for the Minister of Justice's death."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b29ab",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: Now...[p/] The only way for him to redeem House Steelwind is to convict me and sentence me to death."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff2fde",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: B-[p/][s/]But,[p/] he's your [i]father[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00faa24",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: There's no way he would—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0320c75",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: ...This isn't the first time something like this has happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:025b65b",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: When I was a child,[p/] my mother accidentally overused her magic and induced Mageblight within herself."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f748a",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: ...In her resulting psychotic episode,[p/] she massacred an [i]entire[/i] village of commoners."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a33790",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Tyrion: Scaled Lord..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0164a6a",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: House Steelwind almost lost everything after that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0602a36",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: To redeem himself,[p/] my father personally oversaw my mother's trial and her execution."
}

{
  "id": "line:082618b",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]That's[/i] what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4e944",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: My father values his duty to Wyverngarde over everything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b23f2d",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: Nothing matters more to him than that,[p/] not even his family."
}

{
  "id": "line:069e264",
  "node": "AriaEnd",
  "text": "Aria: I'd like to have confidence in myself,[p/] but I don't know if I can face him like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aa590a",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Remus: Mr. Cuthbert...[p/] What is [i]your[/i] stake in all of this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00dd631",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Remus: You hate the nobility, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00de67c",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Remus: So why are you so intent on helping Ms. Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05744ed",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Because she's innocent.[p/] What else is there to say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a29fb",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Aria: Mr. Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ed3e5",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't matter if she's a noble or a commoner."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3331e",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's being oppressed by the politics of our kingdom like all of my other clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db36fa",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Remus: Well said."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab964",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Remus: I,[p/] Remus Virgilae,[p/] hereby grant you the privilege to serve as Ms. Steelwind's counsel."
}

{
  "id": "line:0067571",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Remus: As the Royal Vizer,[p/] I will be acting as the judge and arbiter of Ms. Steelwind's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1eba4",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Remus: It is within my right to grant you such permissions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0011377",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll gladly accept."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4b2dc",
  "node": "AriaEnd2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If Prosecutor Steelwind will have me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d61f6b",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Aria: Of course.[p/] There's no one else I would trust more with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:06da657",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Aria: ...And please,[p/] you've done a lot for me already."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b176e4",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Aria: You don't have to be so formal."
}

{
  "id": "line:020b7c8",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Aria: Celeste has already taken to calling me by my first name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9fc10",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Aria: ...But [i]since[/i] you'll be defending me,[p/] you'll probably need this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3e928",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Remus: Then it's settled.[p/] We will hold the trial at my home:[p/] the city of Ladon."
}

{
  "id": "line:093c04b",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Ladon\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0030840",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Remus: Speak with Lucio.[p/] He knows the location well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3fb78",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Before I could ask any more questions,[p/] the Archduke left without a word."
}

{
  "id": "line:031d190",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "...He really had a bad habit of just walking away from conversations."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c7fda",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ..,Who [i]is[/i] he?[p/] I didn't even know \"Archdukes\" existed in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c545e",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Aria: Today was the first time I met him as well.[p/] I'm just as confused as you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a01970",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Aria: He seems to be well-acquainted with my father, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:096a2e0",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Well,[p/] I guess it doesn't matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d6961",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "Tyrion: He's just like any other judge."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b4b14",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "I had no idea what I was in for when I agreed to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:081ac14",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "And what proceeded next would be unlike any trial I'd ever defended or prosecuted."
}

{
  "id": "line:08798dc",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "...But I would save Aria's future,[p/] no matter what it took."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d8ffa",
  "node": "AriaEnd3",
  "text": "...Regardless of what I'd have to risk to do so."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dc520",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: I've...[p/] killed people..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01701c2",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: It always came so easily to me.[p/] I was good at it—[p/]a little [i]too[/i] good."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e514e7",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: I've never felt the uneasiness they all mentioned—[p/]not even once..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f7ac8",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe I'm some kind of unfeeling monster..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c55c6",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: You can solve a murder easily,[p/] but you're kind of hopeless when it comes to people's hearts—[p/]even [i]with[/i] the Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bfcbf",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: But you never treated me differently.[p/] At first,[p/] I thought it was because you didn't see the real me."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b792c",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: But then I realized that you were the one who saw me the most.[p/] You made me feel like I was the best version of myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:056d57a",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: Solving murders with you,[p/] walking around Ratholme together,[p/] even just talking to you—[p/]I feel at home when I'm with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:000bbb2",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: It was always my job to protect you,[p/] but [i]you[/i] were the one that always made me feel safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:084bb25",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: You brought light into my world.[p/] You've done the same for so many others."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cc21e",
  "node": "FinalEris",
  "text": "Celeste: You could've done great things.[p/][s/] You could've spent your entire life shining brighter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0445ec5",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: I...[p/] I really [i]don't[/i] understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f16be",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: Why would you throw it all away?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdaeae",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's good to see you, too."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ec9d9",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ow![p/][s/] What was that for?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04498d5",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: You [i]know[/i] what it's for, you jerk!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022e776",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you know what I had to go through just to get you back?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0492a9c",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What else was I supposed to do?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f083f5",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Should I have just [i]let[/i] you die?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c05cfa",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Yes[/i]![p/][s/] That's [i]exactly[/i] what you should have done!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ae497",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: It's a lot better than gambling with your life!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07a15e6",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I was never going to go along with that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ade3c",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you even [i]know[/i] me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0734974",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh my god![p/][s/] [i]This[/i] is why I couldn't tell you the truth!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018586a",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: I knew you'd do something [i]stupid[/i] like this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2540a",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]know[/i] I always get to the truth in the end!"
}

{
  "id": "line:066dec0",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: All you did was make that process [i]extremely[/i] frustrating!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0541787",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I could've gotten away with it."
}

{
  "id": "line:044941a",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't even beat me at chess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0079147",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Tyrion: How are you going to hide a murder from me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09f6e4f",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "She scowled at me.[p/] She couldn't find a response."
}

{
  "id": "line:084c95d",
  "node": "Azathoth2",
  "text": "Then the anger slowly drained from her face."
}

{
  "id": "line:063837d",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] I killed Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1da8",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0889170",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: He was going to be executed in one month anyway,[p] and what was [i]his[/i] life when compared to yours?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041fc1b",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...But when I looked at him just [i]lying[/i] there unconscious,[p/] I felt something welling up inside me."
}

{
  "id": "line:041044e",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: I wanted him to experience a [i]fraction[/i] of the fear and the pain that my dad felt..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce82e3",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: Someone like him didn't deserve a peaceful death."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d13ae",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: So I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed72cb",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You must hate me, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed691b",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: Why couldn't you just let me die?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0914f96",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I've been thinking a lot about these cases over the last few months."
}

{
  "id": "line:0520a0a",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I thought Pierce was pure evil—[p/]von Sanctus too,[p/] but I've started to realize that the world can be really cruel sometimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa81eb",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: They may have chosen to be awful people,[p/] but it's not as if the system gave them any reason to stop."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e22078",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Theodore Redmond thought he was killing someone evil."
}

{
  "id": "line:091281f",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice had everything taken from her,[p/] so she tried to take it back no matter the cost."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c73be2",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even Ruby—[p/]she only worked with criminals because of what the nobility was capable of."
}

{
  "id": "line:002ab63",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I haven't stopped thinking about what von Sanctus almost did to my hometown."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3af39",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: If his plan had succeeded and I [i]knew[/i] about it,[p/] even [i]I[/i] might've—"
}

{
  "id": "line:071cb73",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste, you were manipulated and tempted by demons just like they were."
}

{
  "id": "line:057225e",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You don't hate me then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a01bb",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You are,[p/] and always will be,[p/] extremely important to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f51dff",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Tyrion: One betrayal won't change how I feel about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c761a4",
  "node": "Azathoth3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion, I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0124160",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I won't abandon you.[p/] No matter where you go,[p/] we're going there together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f92a6a",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion,[p/] we might be heading to a [i]pretty[/i] bad place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e54cd6",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: ...Well,[p/] I'm not one to celebrate a victory prematurely."
}

{
  "id": "line:017f8c1",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: But if you're [i]already[/i] admitting defeat,[p/] I won't look a gift horse in the mouth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa0bfd",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Celeste: Eris..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb9341",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: ...I can't believe you brought me [i]here[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:056c0f3",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: I will never hear the end of this from my father."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fac30",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Where are we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc0765",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: The \"courtroom\" of the gods...[p/] The place where truth and reality are determined:[p/] the Court of Azathoth."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0eb5a",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: ...I'll give you one last chance, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:054c89b",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: You made a...[p/] rash decision,[p/] but I can still send you back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1da16",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I knew it."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dd0e8",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7114d",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't come here without a plan.[p/] I noticed something."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c9122",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Tyrion: That sadistically playful demeanor has been cracking since we brought Celeste onto the stand."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c101a",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You're nervous, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ae59e",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a [i]reason[/i] why you didn't want me to bring you here,[p/] and I'm going to find out what."
}

{
  "id": "line:004eaef",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] Your persistence was endearing at first,[p/] but [i]now[/i],[p/] it's just irritating."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e83911",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: I suppose we'll have to do this the hard way then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2c7f0",
  "node": "Azathoth4",
  "text": "Eris: ...Don't say I didn't warn you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f28a0f",
  "node": "ErisCornered_Fail",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, is that the last of your CONFIDENCE?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00d0f5c",
  "node": "ErisCornered_Fail",
  "text": "Eris: Looks like I win!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd4dd7",
  "node": "ErisCornered",
  "text": "Eris: You should have taken my offer when you had the chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3a13d",
  "node": "ErisCornered",
  "text": "Eris: The only way to nullify my Contract is to unequivocally prove that its conditions weren't fulfilled."
}

{
  "id": "line:08316e5",
  "node": "ErisCornered",
  "text": "Eris: So says the Word of Asmodeus."
}

{
  "id": "line:060d819",
  "node": "ErisCornered",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Asmodeus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0833e82",
  "node": "ErisCornered",
  "text": "Eris: By his Word,[p/] demons are incapable of speaking lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2fa23",
  "node": "ErisCornered",
  "text": "Eris: This is [i]my[/i] domain, heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:016c5fc",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Rationalize [c=\"If disputing a Blood Contract was truly impossible, there would be no need for this Court to exist. Demons are powerful but they aren't omniscient.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ead9bc",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Agree [c=\"Your Contract may be without flaw. But that doesn't mean we can't negotiate its terms.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba6045",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Contract may be without flaw,[p/] but that doesn't mean we can't negotiate its terms."
}

{
  "id": "line:04be64f",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Eris: There's nothing [i]to[/i] negotiate, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:007213f",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Eris: I have the soul of the woman you love."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ad24d",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Eris: And the only thing you have to offer [i]me[/i] is your despair."
}

{
  "id": "line:0990043",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Deflect [c=\"It doesn't matter if your Contract is perfect. I am not leaving here until you relinquish Celeste's soul.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f4098",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't matter if your Contract is perfect."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f366cd",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am not leaving here until you relinquish Celeste's soul."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1d5d9",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Eris: You are only [i]permitted[/i] to be here for the purpose of disputing the Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:027e4bc",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Eris: The moment you give up on [i]that[/i],[p/] your fate will be doomed along with hers."
}

{
  "id": "line:041a366",
  "node": "ErisCornered2",
  "text": "Eris: But if you want to [i]graciously[/i] forfeit,[p/] by all means."
}

{
  "id": "line:0199690",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: If disputing a Blood Contract were truly impossible,[p/] there would be no need for this \"Court\" to exist."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d57dc",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Demons are powerful,[p/] but they aren't omniscient."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1a878",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: They can't possibly be aware of contradicting circumstances that may be created when they make a Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4da7a",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're hiding something—[p/]something that you [i]desperately[/i] need to keep hidden."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc9deb",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Eris: ...Oh, really now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f9263",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You tried to confound the investigation by manipulating Celeste's memories,[p/] but the contradiction in her testimony proves one thing."
}

{
  "id": "line:045bb58",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: She didn't see you and Beatrice enter the Prayer Room until 2:00 PM at the earliest."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c3cbf",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Eris: ...Your so-called contradiction is based on the testimony of Laefe Frega, yes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03516cc",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Eris: How are you so sure that her testimony is reliable?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00ce4ed",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's supported by the testimonies of Miriam and Lord Asclepius."
}

{
  "id": "line:00499b4",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: They were all together at the time.[p/] Their testimony is sound."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fb751",
  "node": "ErisCornered3",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, really?[p/] It looks like [i]you've[/i] made a contradiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:027fefe",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "Eris: And that illusion makes their testimonies unreliable."
}

{
  "id": "line:09abb27",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "Tyrion: An illusion?![p/][s/] What [i]kind[/i] of illusion?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d38270",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "Eris: ...Who knows?[p/] My statement still stands."
}

{
  "id": "line:09cb20d",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't just expect us to accept your claims without any evidence!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a54168",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "Eris: I can't speak lies, Tyrion![p/][s/] The immutable fact is all the evidence I need!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6119d",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "Eris: In this Court,[p/] the only thing that matters is what is true and what is false,[p/] and the Word of Asmodeus says that Laefe's testimony is unreliable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0639957",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "She could just say whatever she wanted without having to provide any context..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eab8d7",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": "But she only said that Laefe was tricked.[p/] She didn't specify an exact time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2fe9b",
  "node": "ErisCornered4",
  "text": ":Was there something else that proved Laefe didn't begin her search until 2:00 PM?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d3720",
  "node": "ErisCornered5",
  "text": "The Trapped King 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f390de",
  "node": "ErisCornered5",
  "text": "Liafal's Testimony"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fccf82",
  "node": "ErisCornered5",
  "text": "Laefe's testimony [i]did[/i] contradict what she said,[p/] but she already declared that it wasn't reliable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0377ed1",
  "node": "ErisCornered5",
  "text": "However,[p/] that testimony also mentions something [i]else[/i] that happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c05454",
  "node": "ErisCornered5",
  "text": "Eris: What's this...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:081248a",
  "node": "ErisCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh, I-..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c8769",
  "node": "ErisCornered5",
  "text": "Eris: You're going to have to do better than [i]that[/i] if you want to beat me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f378cc",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless of [i]when[/i] it happened,[p/] Laefe and her party went to search for Beatrice after you two went missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ff5fa",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you confirm or deny [i]that[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011f8c5",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Eris: ...I won't deny it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0adb519",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Perfect.[p/] [i]Whoever[/i] set that trap,[p/] they set it to trigger whenever Aster approached his father's body,[p/] and it didn't trigger until 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bfd9f",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Laefe and her party were about to search for Beatrice,[p/] when the Kingsguard informed them of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:086a096",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Kingsguard did this [i]immediately[/i] after the trap was sprung."
}

{
  "id": "line:03367bf",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Since Laefe was about to begin her search when this happened,[p/] Beatrice [i]couldn't[/i] have gone missing until that time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d10aa4",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Eris: ...You're predicating that on the testimony of the King."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be9cfd",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not just him, Eris.[p/] Several members of the Kingsguard witnessed this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0854979",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Eris: ...True.[p/] And that is why I'll respond with this."
}

{
  "id": "line:002878a",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But how...?[p/] That testimony came from [i]multiple[/i] people."
}

{
  "id": "line:02b1afc",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you saying that the trap was sprung [i]earlier[/i] than that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0adbf1f",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Eris: Don't you remember, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0710145",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Eris: I can manipulate the memories of people who have a Blood Contract with me,[p/] but I'll give you a little clue..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c71b4",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0571ab2",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Eris: I tampered with their memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:054624b",
  "node": "ErisCornered6",
  "text": "Eris: You can't trust their accounts of what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4f158",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: How many people did you make Contracts with?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0c13c",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: Little Lady Steelwind has been investigating my work for the last few months."
}

{
  "id": "line:02384f2",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: But I've had my talons in Wyverngarde for [i]far[/i] longer than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2ef87",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: I've been preparing for this for [i]quite[/i] some time."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e0f20",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But even the Kingsguard?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eaa8f4",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: [i]No one[/i] is safe from temptation.[p/] [i]Everyone[/i] has a price."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1dbdf",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: Your girlfriend should know that better than anyone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c0184",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Still...[p/] There [i]has[/i] to be something..."
}

{
  "id": "line:048ebd6",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I-[p/][s/]I still have more evidence..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4bdee",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, really?[p/] Whose testimony will you be relying on [i]this[/i] time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c9099",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: You can PRESENT all the evidence you want."
}

{
  "id": "line:0837529",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: Most of what you have is based on [i]eyewitness[/i] accounts."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c32fe7",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even so...[p/] Y-[p/][s/]You can't have possibly made a Contract with [i]everyone[/i] there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8a242",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Eris: ...Let's check that again, shall we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0125ebe",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you kidding me?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c93fff",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But you only said it's \"possible\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0febd87",
  "node": "ErisCornered7",
  "text": "Tyrion: You never said that it [i]actually[/i] happened!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04ce1da",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: [i]You're[/i] the one disputing my Contract, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0694a4e",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: The burden of proof is on [i]you[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d436c4",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's completely ridiculous!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03774a0",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Tyrion: How could I [i]possibly[/i] verify a statement like that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0151edb",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: It's simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:02497f5",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: Issue a Divine Edict to each person who was at the Cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8314c",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Celeste: You [i]know[/i] he can't do that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7e39e",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: That sounds more like [i]your[/i] problem than mine!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0828f99",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: Nothing to say, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1e66e",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: Isn't this the part where you PRESENT some ground-breaking piece of evidence?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbfa63",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "As long as her statements stood,[p/] I had to doubt [i]every[/i] piece of testimony I'd gathered."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bf209",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "[i]Everyone[/i] at the Cathedral could have been compromised...[p/] except—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc3332",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Tyrion: A-[p/][s/]Aster...![p/] I know [i]he[/i] doesn't have a Blood Contract with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc62d",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: ...I suppose you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cff3d9",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: So are you going to use [i]his[/i] testimony?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03d0673",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: He couldn't observe [i]much[/i] from within that [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:093e9a4",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: Do you understand now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c30c24",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: You were [i]never[/i] meant to win this game,[p/] but I suppose I should be thankful to you for entertaining me this long!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca21c0",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Eris: [i]This[/i] is the most fun I've ever had,[p/][s/] and I [i]truly[/i] mean that!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7663b",
  "node": "ErisCornered8",
  "text": "Come on![p/][s/] There had to be [i]something[/i] I could use!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0881ece",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "...But all the testimonies I'd gathered could potentially be more lies created by her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9df0e",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion![p/][s/] You have to say something..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06347c2",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "My strength was fading.[p/] The divine light inside me was dimming."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f270c8",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "I could feel the weight of her presence dragging me to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f1261",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "Eris: This has [i]always[/i] been a contest of willpower,[p/] and it looks like you were found lacking."
}

{
  "id": "line:067eb15",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:078f841",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "I recalled what happened during Beatrice's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f88a55",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "I wasn't sure if it was a dream or something else,[p/] but I'd heard my mother's voice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0585d2a",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Mom...[p/] Please."
}

{
  "id": "line:0078070",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: I need your help..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ba70a",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Please...[p/] Just tell me what to do..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec1052",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "I heard nothing back."
}

{
  "id": "line:059772b",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "I knew this was a long shot,[p/] but I was still holding out hope."
}

{
  "id": "line:00277a8",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "However,[p/] Eris was a being who wrapped herself in layers upon layers of lies."
}

{
  "id": "line:009f840",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "She had the power to make me doubt [i]everything[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:00feecb",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "The witness testimonies,[p/] even the physical evidence I possessed could be a fabrication."
}

{
  "id": "line:00971eb",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "How could I possibly argue against someone like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0570567",
  "node": "ErisCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not fair..."
}

{
  "id": "line:039b0d1",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not fair, Ms. Tymora!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0660753",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're not even [i]bothering[/i] to investigate the crime properly!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e09e8f",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: Well...[p/] Of course they're not."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a741f7",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: If they did,[p/] they'd be forced to admit that my client is innocent."
}

{
  "id": "line:05769b9",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: How are you so calm right now...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:028ae68",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Is this what it's [i]always[/i] like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb0290",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: How are you supposed to win like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07e751a",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: They can just keep changing the narrative however they want!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00633db",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: They can,[p/] and that's [i]exactly[/i] how I'll beat them."
}

{
  "id": "line:075a810",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: Look, Cuthbert.[p/] Almost every part of the system is against us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1e412",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: But there's [i]one[/i] advantage we have over the prosecution,[p/] and that's pure and objective logic."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c17f6",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Logic\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d9591",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion.[p/] The prosecutor does all sorts of things to validate their case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1d719",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: They PRESENT evidence,[p/] they call witnesses,[p/] and they use those pieces to create conclusions."
}

{
  "id": "line:032272d",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: They create a box and throw a bunch of \"facts\" into it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0691eeb",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: They tell the court that everything within that box is the truth."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ff888",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: And conversely,[p/] that makes everything [i]outside[/i] of it a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea5b23",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: But how does that help [i]us[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0099757",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: You point out contradictions in their case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f95c19",
  "node": "ErisCornered10",
  "text": "Ruby: That makes them throw more and more \"facts\" into that box to keep their case consistent."
}

{
  "id": "line:007db68",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Ruby: But if even [i]one[/i] \"fact\" in the box is false,[p/] the entire thing falls apart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0639d38",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: But surely they'll realize what you're doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0647198",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: What if they play dumb and refuse to add [i]anything[/i] to this \"box\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a08c28",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Ruby: Well...[p/] You can force them to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3e387",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Ruby: You can PRESENT your [i]own[/i] TRUTHS,[p/] and you force the prosecution to either accept or deny them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f35c7",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Ruby: By doing that,[p/] [i]you[/i] decide the terms of battle.[p/] You control what goes into the box."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a7279",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't know if I'll ever get the hang of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0947b",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Ruby: Don't worry...[p/] You've always been a sharp kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0297f",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Ruby: I know you'll do great things."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74aff",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Ruby: So don't give up."
}

{
  "id": "line:09df450",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "...Eris's last statement hinged on the time that Beatrice disappeared."
}

{
  "id": "line:0311966",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "She could only change Celeste's memories to make her think [i]everything[/i] happened earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0902e3d",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Which could only mean one thing..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd406e",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Beatrice Frega did [i]not[/i] go missing before 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:011d238",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Eris: ...What was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d069",
  "node": "ErisCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: I said..."
}

{
  "id": "line:010815b",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...So says the Word of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c6e75",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bdf5b1",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "I felt myself filled with the radiant power of Horus.[p/] It was the same sensation I'd felt in the Haroldson's gallery last month."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a153a",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "I could feel the divine light of the Upper Planes spreading through me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acfdd9",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] You—"
}

{
  "id": "line:023c163",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Celeste: You have wings!"
}

{
  "id": "line:091d860",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Wait...[p/] Really?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:079c2f7",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "I spun around slowly,[p/] only catching glimpses of the golden wings that had sprouted from my back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d07282",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "I didn't even notice it,[p/] but my feet weren't even touching the ground anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e7ac0",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: You...?![p/][s/] Where did you learn how to do that?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02bf992",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "I just chuckled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0274ffd",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: What could be so god-damned funny?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09958bd",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know,[p/] I've been wondering something,[p/] and it's been bothering me for a while now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9ffb7",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: If demons like Marrunath existed,[p/] then surely angels did as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:02593a8",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: I couldn't be the only person left to stand in your way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffda93",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: There [i]had[/i] to be someone out there who could stop you—[p/][s/]an immortal angel,[p/][s/] a holy warrior,[p/] [i]something[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05da94e",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm a defense attorney for crying out loud!"
}

{
  "id": "line:031d569",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm [i]not[/i] qualified to fight a demon!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0026a1b",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: That's right, you wretch..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c2cf6",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: I have lived a [i]million[/i] of your pathetic lifetimes!"
}

{
  "id": "line:006b5cf",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: I am a [s/][i]GOD[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0082e05",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] You are,[p/] and I don't see any angels or paladins rushing in to help us,[p/] so I guess I'll have to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:044cae1",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]this[/i] is my skill set."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bccc8",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Man,[p/] king,[p/] or god—[p/]you're not leaving here with Celeste's soul!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0459f60",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: Hahahahahaha..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0747247",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Eris: HAHAHAHAHAHAHA!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae5d11",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What...?[p/][s/] What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023efc2",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01afe8f",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I'm here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd6754",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: [i][j]*chuckles*[/j][/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b496aa",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: [j]Since you've so graciously bared your soul to me,[p/] perhaps I should respond in kind.[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:02054f4",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: [j]I am the Lord of Shadows—[p/]sovereign of the Sixth Circle.[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0914e81",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: [j]I am the question that gnaws at every answer.[p/] I am the creeping blight,[p/] feeding off of the arrogant as they crumble from within.[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:04f772d",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: I am—"
}

{
  "id": "line:05decad",
  "node": "ErisCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: ...So says the Word of Asmodeus."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f46de",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "Celeste: What [i]is[/i] that thing?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05add8f",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "FEris: HAHAHAHA![p/][s/] Did you two [i]honestly[/i] think my true form was that of a teenage girl?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fdbd5",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "FEris: No...[p/] I am older than time itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d29938",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "FEris: It feels liberating to break free from that weak mortal shell."
}

{
  "id": "line:026c930",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "Tyrion: So [i]this[/i] is what you really look like...[p/] It suits you."
}

{
  "id": "line:07ec931",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "FEris: Why, thank you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06568c6",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "Tyrion: It doesn't matter what form you take."
}

{
  "id": "line:0333c35",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Whatever[/i] you are,[p/][s/] I'm [i]taking[/i] Celeste's soul back!"
}

{
  "id": "line:013227b",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "Celeste: Kick her ass, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0273bbd",
  "node": "ErisCornered14",
  "text": "FEris: Come then![p/][s/] Let me carve out your souls and mount them in the fields of Malbolge!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01629c8",
  "node": "EmpressCornered_Fail",
  "text": "FEris: And so the story of Tyrion Cuthbert ends..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1b757",
  "node": "EmpressCornered_Fail",
  "text": "FEris: I will enjoy bringing your flayed carcass back to the Sixth Hell."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e19bc",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": "I'd need to be careful.[p/] I was bound by the same rules as her now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d37018",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": "I couldn't tell lies in this form,[p/] even accidentally."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e58d4",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why don't we pick up where we left off?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fad653",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've established that Beatrice didn't go missing until 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:095a541",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": "Tyrion: I wonder...[p/] Why would you go to so much trouble to make me doubt that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d11a9a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": "FEris: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0085356",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": ":When she gave her testimony,[p/] Celeste said that Eris and Beatrice entered the Prayer Room at 1:40 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:047a393",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": ":But from the AXIOM I declared,[p/] I knew Beatrice didn't disappear until 2:00PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:06228e9",
  "node": "EmpressCornered",
  "text": "Eris clearly changed Celeste's memories,[p/] but for what purpose?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0af4f1b",
  "node": "EmpressCornered2",
  "text": "No...[p/] Eris may have been unpredictable,[p/] but even [i]she[/i] acted with purpose."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e37b4e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered2",
  "text": "There was a reason why she changed Celeste's memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:055d335",
  "node": "EmpressCornered2",
  "text": "It was to obscure the timeline of the murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b573f3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I believe you needed Celeste to think that the events happened much earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:07762e8",
  "node": "EmpressCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Staying quiet?[p/] That won't work this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a888a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Nothing to say?[p/] You can't stay quiet forever."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7a6fa",
  "node": "EmpressCornered3",
  "text": "FEris: ...I didn't [i]need[/i] her to think that specifically."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b438ed",
  "node": "EmpressCornered3",
  "text": "FEris: I simply wanted to confound your ability to deduce what [i]actually[/i] happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de626f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That may be,[p/] but I think you had a specific reason to move her timeline back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c28e45",
  "node": "EmpressCornered4",
  "text": ":Autopsy Report: Lloyd von Sanctus|The Murder of von Sanctus|Autopsy Report: Coraline Sibyl"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfec9e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered4",
  "text": ":No...[p/] Eris [i]wanted[/i] me to believe that Celeste signed the Contract with her at 1:40 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:08964d3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered4",
  "text": "She needed me to believe that to keep her narrative logically consistent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df621a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered4",
  "text": ":But I now knew that Eris used Beatrice to attack the Prayer Room [i]no later[/i] than 2:30 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0289092",
  "node": "EmpressCornered4",
  "text": "If the events happened much later,[p/] what followed shortly after that was strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:030e025",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was the death of Lloyd von Sanctus."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e63a2",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: You needed Celeste to think that she signed the Contract much earlier than 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e487f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's because Lloyd von Sanctus's death occurred at 2:05 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ca5ba",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which would imply that you killed me,[p/] convinced Celeste to sign a Contract,[p/] [i]and[/i] made Celeste trick Aria into signing [i]another[/i] Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:085d605",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...All in the span of [i]five[/i] minutes."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f0e7f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: If that's true,[p/] could it be possible that Celeste [i]isn't[/i] the Patron?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9c056",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Celeste: What...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08aafb3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's the only logical conclusion.[p/] The timeline is far too short."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c033e6",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if you [i]remember[/i] being tricked by her,[p/] we can't trust your memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:04723d6",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Isn't that right, Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:016491a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "FEris: Your desperation is almost pitiful!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e978bc",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "FEris: I'll respond so that there's no room for doubt!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0493445",
  "node": "EmpressCornered5",
  "text": "FEris: So says the Word of Asmodeus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f37f16",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I knew it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef1de9",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "FEris: ...Is something wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0f5fb",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "FEris: I know the truth is hard to accept sometimes,[p/] but Celeste [i]did[/i] betray Aria's trust."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9553e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "...She always spoke in technicalities.[p/] I couldn't take that claim at face value."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4555a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "But [i]this[/i] could also be a trick."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbd94d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "I [i]could[/i] declare outright that Celeste wasn't the Patron,[p/] but if I was wrong about that,[p/] I'd most definitely die."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c2773",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "...First,[p/] I would need to assume that Celeste [i]wasn't[/i] the Patron.[p/] What would logically follow from that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f3181",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "If Celeste wasn't the Patron,[p/] that Contract would've already been signed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bba13d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "And I'd already concluded that the Blood Contract was disguised as a normal legal document."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da105c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered6",
  "text": "I recalled something happening before we entered the Prayer Room...[p/] What was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08760fa",
  "node": "EmpressCornered7",
  "text": "No...[p/] I recalled something happening in front of the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:038480d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered7",
  "text": "It was brief,[p/] but there was a short exchange between Celeste and Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec1183",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "As she skittered away,[p/] I saw something fall out of her pocket.[p/] It was her Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12dfb",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, Aria![p/][s/] You dropped something!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07eee82",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "As Celeste went to pick it up,[p/] she accidentally activated it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0684179",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "An image of some evidence appeared for a brief moment,[p/] but Aria quickly snatched it from Celeste's hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0399856",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "Aria: U-[p/][s/]Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0053274",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Wait,[p/] is [i]that[/i] why everyone's gathered here today?"
}

{
  "id": "line:048fad6",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] Don't just invade her privacy like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6d594",
  "node": "EmpressCornered8",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't be like that.[p/] I'm really happy for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cffd2f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Would Aria really have taken a picture of that contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06de57c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "If it were disguised as a legal document,[p/] taking a picture of it would've been illegal."
}

{
  "id": "line:02204ec",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "But if a picture of the Contract had been in Aria's Runestone,[p/] she technically handed it to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bda291",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "...But that didn't necessarily mean she [i]wasn't[/i] the Patron either."
}

{
  "id": "line:047d655",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "FEris: Is something wrong?[p/] You look conflicted."
}

{
  "id": "line:01364b3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "...No.[p/] From the very beginning,[p/] she'd been trying to get in my head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15de0",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "She thrived on doubt and mistrust,[p/] but I'd always known from the very beginning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cac031",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Celeste would [i]never[/i] betray Aria like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e378c3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "FEris: Agh![p/][s/] Even [i]now[/i],[p/] you trust her [i]that[/i] much?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032018c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]Wait...[p/] But, that means!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba75d4",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: You didn't betray Aria, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ef6a3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: She only manipulated your memories after the fact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c00f94",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: She wanted to make you [i]think[/i] that you did."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b0cbf",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Celeste: S-[p/][s/]So...[p/] It's not my fault?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cb745",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It isn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:024b8b1",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "But that had a far more unsettling implication..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff3220",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "Someone [i]else[/i] was the Patron,[p/][s/] but who was it?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2a742",
  "node": "EmpressCornered9",
  "text": "...One move at a time, Tyrion.[p/] The endgame would reveal itself in time."
}

{
  "id": "line:032955d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Celeste[/i] wasn't the one who secured Aria's compliance and cooperation."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bf537",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Doesn't that make your Contract flawed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05280cd",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "FEris: Please.[p/] I thought you were an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7ad85",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "FEris: The Contract states that Celeste would \"engage in actions deemed [i]necessary[/i] to secure the compliance and cooperation of Aria Steelwind\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0817848",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "FEris: No further actions were necessary.[p/] She was already under my influence by then."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e9e2f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: But that means [i]none[/i] of this is her fault!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf05ea",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "FEris: Think again, heavensborn!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae07a0",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] There's still the death of Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afe065",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "FEris: It doesn't matter who's \"responsible\" for the massacre as a whole."
}

{
  "id": "line:04401d1",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "FEris: Here,[p/] all that matters is the validity of my Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f861d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]act[/i] like you're in control of this situation,[p/] but you've been nervous ever since I began disputing your Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0184855",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're hiding something, aren't you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:000f8cc",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "FEris: ...Who can say for sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b6fc2",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: The second paragraph is vague,[p/] but what about the first and third paragraphs?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe36bb",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]Something[/i] is off here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d75b2b",
  "node": "EmpressCornered10",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it possible that I [i]didn't[/i] die?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a83c89",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "FEris: Ha![p/][s/] Are you still in denial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:028b27c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "FEris: I thought you were ready to [i]die[/i] to save your beloved Celeste?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f209c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Answer the question, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fdf7f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: We can't trust Celeste's memories."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3e836",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: That memory where she confirmed my death could all be a fabrication."
}

{
  "id": "line:0064681",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "FEris: You wish to cling to that hope?![p/][s/] Then let me state it plainly for you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0319baf",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "FEris: I did [i]not[/i] alter that memory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bedeed",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry, Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cce111",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: How [i]did[/i] you revive me, Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e079c2",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you even [i]have[/i] the power to resurrect people from the dead?"
}

{
  "id": "line:049c8b5",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "FEris: Who do you think you're talking to?[p/] Of course, I do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae5f5a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "FEris: But if you doubt me,[p/] why don't you declare that \"Tyrion Cuthbert never died\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a44037",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "Knowing her,[p/] she could be baiting me into telling a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:03407f7",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "...But it was equally likely that she was bluffing."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b64ae",
  "node": "EmpressCornered11",
  "text": "FEris: If you still doubt that I resurrected you,[p/] I'll state this."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c2a49",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Interpret [c=\"Why would you need to specify that beings of your power can do that? Is it possible that it's not a simple or easy feat to accomplish?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddad25",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why would you need to specify that \"beings of your power\" can do that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:078d06b",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it possible that it's not a simple or easy feat to accomplish?"
}

{
  "id": "line:003563f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: For example...[p/] Would [i]Marrunath[/i] be able to resurrect a person from the dead using a Contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01adfcc",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: I-..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0512c58",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let me save you some trouble.[p/] I'll say it for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:038f483",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Agree [c=\"If [i]you're[/i] saying that, it must be true...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f27b6e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: If [i]you're[/i] saying that,[p/] it must be true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a22d7f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: Exactly.[p/] I could have resurrected you at that moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dfdd6",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: You can't deny that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0649fd2",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "...She was speaking in hypotheticals.[p/] I doubted she was being upfront"
}

{
  "id": "line:078bc50",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Doubt [c=\"You're [i]clearly[/i] not acting in good faith. How can I trust what you're saying?\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e808a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're [i]clearly[/i] not acting in good faith."
}

{
  "id": "line:094dc94",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "Tyrion: How can I trust what you're saying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:027d6f5",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: ...Did you forget?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa6ab8",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "FEris: The entire [i]premise[/i] of this battle is that we can't lie to each other."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cd49a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "I needed to accept that her claims were undoubtedly true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2a14e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered12",
  "text": "But the [i]meaning[/i] behind her words would be a different thing entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:053c54e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "Tyrion: So says the Word of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b31c6",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "FEris: ...That's not the same as saying that it was [i]impossible[/i] for me to do it."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d0280",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it would require a large amount of effort on your part."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecce91",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "FEris: Perhaps,[p/] but recall my previous declaration.[p/] Celeste [i]was[/i] there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0095666",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "FEris: And by all accounts,[p/] she concluded you were dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:060d2e6",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "Tyrion: How thoroughly did you check me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2ff53",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "Celeste: I have experience in first aid.[p/] It wasn't good."
}

{
  "id": "line:063880f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "Celeste: You weren't breathing,[p/] and your heart was stopped."
}

{
  "id": "line:060bb8a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "FEris: She tried to resuscitate you for several minutes,[p/] but to no avail."
}

{
  "id": "line:09126c3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "Right...[p/] There was no way my body could survive that long naturally without oxygen [i]and[/i] blood flow."
}

{
  "id": "line:074081d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "And Eris just confirmed that Celeste spent several minutes trying to resuscitate me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccf0d4",
  "node": "EmpressCornered13",
  "text": "But there had to be more to this than I was seeing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0400b13",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "Feign Death"
}

{
  "id": "line:077f907",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "Tyrion: You may have been [i]able[/i] to resurrect me,[p/] but you had a far easier way to create that scenario."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c20c72",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And luckily for you,[p/] Beatrice was there and under your control."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e8ac0",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Beatrice[/i] can resurrect people from the dead?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d0d29",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] The opposite is actually true."
}

{
  "id": "line:00eb326",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "No...[p/] Eris was probably capable of resurrecting me from the dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:06af3b3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "But from how she phrased it,[p/] it must be a difficult feat for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:013cb13",
  "node": "EmpressCornered14",
  "text": "Was there a way she could have orchestrated that scenario with significantly less effort?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d43981",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry, Celeste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a3f1b",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I was never dead.[p/] She just used a spell to trick you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6087",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "Celeste: So everything I did—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b9d2e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "FEris: It was for [i]nothing[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3f4a1",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "Celeste: But that means you never resurrected him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a5d56",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "Celeste: He was never dead in the first place!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7335c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "FEris: The Contract only said that he was [i]apparently[/i] dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:028c360",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "FEris: All I did was \"revive\" him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d69218",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "FEris: ...By making Beatrice release her spell,[p/] which allowed him to wake up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0f882",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "...That eliminated the first paragraph as a possible weak point."
}

{
  "id": "line:070aaa5",
  "node": "EmpressCornered15",
  "text": "And that only left the death of Garrick Pierce at Celeste's hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c01d9",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Something happened with Pierce, didn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:041d8f9",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you hiding...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a28359",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "FEris: What [i]ever[/i] could you be talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:037e078",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your Contract says that Celeste must bring about the demise of Garrick Pierce by her own hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eda449",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Since you wrote that Contract,[p/] that must have been your intent from the beginning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d838f8",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...So why are you so nervous?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02e2561",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Something went wrong, didn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0410d02",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: If you want to stay quiet,[p/] I'll just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac7418",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "All of this could be another elaborate trick."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2ad9b",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "I needed to be careful...[p/] I needed to find out [i]exactly[/i] what went wrong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94c34",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "The only person who knew what truly happened in that room was Eris,[p/] but that could still be used to my advantage."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d5d8e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Tyrion: Is it possible that Celeste [i]didn't[/i] kill Garrick Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e486a3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "FEris: ...Are you serious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07893ca",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "FEris: He's the man who killed her adoptive father,[p/] and he was originally slated to be executed next month."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3ee27",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "FEris: She didn't have a rational reason [i]not[/i] to trade his life for yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8d19a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered16",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] As bad as it sounds,[p/] that would've been an easy choice for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06766b3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: She may have [i]wanted[/i] to,[p/] but something else might have happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd9450",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Perhaps Beatrice or Aria misinterpreted one of your commands and killed him against your wishes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0189510",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "FEris: How tedious do you plan to make this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5a7c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]Well...[p/] What if you [i]forced[/i] Celeste to kill him?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0849ecc",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: She signed that Contract already![p/][s/] You had control of her at the time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:017eae1",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Contract states that she needed to kill Pierce of her own volition and agency."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ec9ca",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "FEris: ...Do you honestly think I would make a foolish mistake like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9aac7",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What if someone [i]else[/i] killed Garrick Pierce on accident?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015bd77",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe a member of the Kingsguard who survived and entered the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:01747b3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "FEris: [i]*cackle*[/i] [p/][s/]Try again, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a166ef",
  "node": "EmpressCornered17",
  "text": "FEris: And while I'm at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0418452",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "FEris: Do you understand now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d288e7",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "FEris: I can refute [i]any[/i] possible explanation you may have for Pierce's death,[p/] but the truth of the matter is—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc6057",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "FEris: Have you given up?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0210edd",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "FEris: Have I finally extinguished the light of hope within you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092baba",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0932c7f",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe you [i]fell[/i] for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:035aa5d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "FEris: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3b520",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've never thrown consecutive declarations at me like that before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ec6e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's because I'm getting close, isn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:058a58b",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can freely manipulate Celeste's memories of what happened,[p/] and I don't have any evidence that implies what [i]actually[/i] transpired in the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0169712",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...The only person who could tell me that was [i]you[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5d6b3",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "FEris: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03e9f91",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: You thought you could overwhelm me by shooting down all my theories."
}

{
  "id": "line:044d539",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But all you did was tell me the [i]exact[/i] state of the room when Garrick Pierce died."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edc07d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "Tyrion: And now I can figure out what [i]actually[/i] happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:05991ce",
  "node": "EmpressCornered18",
  "text": "FEris: W-[p/][s/]Wait..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0931654",
  "node": "EmpressCornered19",
  "text": "Garrick"
}

{
  "id": "line:092c1af",
  "node": "EmpressCornered19",
  "text": "No...[p/] By her own admission, she,[p/] Celeste,[p/] Aria,[p/] and Beatrice were the only people in that room."
}

{
  "id": "line:01628dd",
  "node": "EmpressCornered19",
  "text": "She admitted that neither she,[p/] Aria,[p/] nor Beatrice killed Pierce,[p/] but she only declared that Pierce's death occurred because of Celeste's actions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b341ab",
  "node": "EmpressCornered19",
  "text": "If she really wanted to defeat me,[p/] she would have simply declared that \"Celeste brought about Pierce's demise.\""
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b968",
  "node": "EmpressCornered19",
  "text": "But she didn't.[p/] That implied that Celeste [i]wasn't[/i] the one who killed him, either."
}

{
  "id": "line:0996f2e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered19",
  "text": "...That only left one person."
}

{
  "id": "line:0842289",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris Illmater.[p/] Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0547a9a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "FEris: N-[p/]No...[p/][s/] S-[p/][s/]Stop this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02b4f8a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure what would possibly drive him to do something like that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d4d0b",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: But when he was in the Prayer Room,[p/] Garrick Pierce chose to take his own life..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab6028",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know what that means, don't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a12948",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "FEris: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6c34d",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: But for the sake of it,[p/] I'll state it in a way that makes it [i]abundantly[/i] clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:082295e",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "FEris: STOP THIS![p/][s/] STOP THIS [i]RIGHT NOW[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac3373",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: The conditions of your Contract were impossible for Celeste to fulfill."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2df4a",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That[/i] renders it [i]logically[/i] invalid."
}

{
  "id": "line:05616e0",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And that's checkmate, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4f04c",
  "node": "EmpressCornered20",
  "text": "FEris: YOU FILTHY LITTLE—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07c4b82",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "LucioC: You're back?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0856890",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "LucioC: Does this mean you—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0796ced",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Tyrion: I successfully voided Celeste's Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8a55b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "I looked inside my satchel,[p/] opening the folder where I'd been keeping Celeste's Blood Contract.[p/] There was only ash inside it now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2b25d",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Rath: But you're still alive, how—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aefb4e",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Eris: You!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6243e",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Her face was tightened in pure contempt and rage,[p/] but she wasn't looking at me this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69b0f",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023d413",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Eris: You little [i]bitch[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d71de5",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Eris: I [i]could[/i] have accepted losing to a heavensborn,[p/][s/] but you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d27279",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3a672",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]Tyrion's[/i] the one that beat you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a78221",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Wait."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae6dfe",
  "node": "ErisDefeat",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait,[p/][s/] I remember what really happened now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f1c1d",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion![p/][s/] Tyrion, please wake up!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0887281",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]You can't—![p/][s/] This can't be—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cb006",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Eris: ...It appears that he's [i]quite[/i] dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0191eab",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Celeste: You—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b5575",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Eris: You should be more careful, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f94b8c",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Eris: You might hurt someone if you swing that dangerous thing around."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e53de",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Celeste: I was right about you all along!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00cce33",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Celeste: I should have [i]never[/i] trusted you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:067dcf4",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Eris: I like your enthusiasm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0285d51",
  "node": "ErisDefeat2",
  "text": "Eris: ...But there's still something you can do to save him."
}

{
  "id": "line:07458c7",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Garrick: W-[p/][s/]What...?[p/] What is this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0068c46",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Do you feel that pit of dread in your chest?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7c649",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Celeste: It's the [i]same[/i] fear my dad felt after you [i]stabbed[/i] him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:061e23e",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Garrick: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0946db4",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Eris: And with his life,[p/] you'll have your [i]beloved[/i] Tyrion back."
}

{
  "id": "line:081f5ef",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Eris: ...What are you waiting for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:097a99d",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Eris: End him, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:016cad1",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee0438",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Garrick: ...What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01954c1",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Eris: ...What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05d8381",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion...[p/] He...[p/] wouldn't want this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e08f4e",
  "node": "ErisDefeat3",
  "text": "Eris: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] He never [i]has[/i] to know, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:026be19",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Eris: I can protect you from his Eye of Horus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b34af0",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: That doesn't matter!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd877a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: I can't do it...[p/] It's just..."
}

{
  "id": "line:030a686",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Eris: This man [i]killed[/i] your father."
}

{
  "id": "line:05431a4",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Eris: Not to mention he's a dead man walking."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ada91",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Eris: You've lived a [i]lifetime[/i] of killing people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abb5e6",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Eris: What's one more person?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2bb4a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Garrick: I won't suffer your self-righteous pity, bastard."
}

{
  "id": "line:097a72f",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't misunderstand me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9b6dd",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: Right now,[p/][s/] I want [i]nothing[/i] more than to end your worthless life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4fdb9",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...But Tyrion's ideals are what saved me."
}

{
  "id": "line:09314c8",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: That part of him is wonderful and beautiful."
}

{
  "id": "line:07789d5",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: I could never betray those ideals,[p/] not even if it's to save him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ccb53",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Eris: ...You're actually serious, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0869c6e",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Eris: You'd seriously [i]sacrifice[/i] him for [i]that[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f7d4f",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Celeste: I won't do it.[p/] I'm not going to sign that Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d8b9b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Garrick: ...Contract?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0510f9b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Garrick: Ah...[p/] I see now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc2617",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Garrick: So [i]you're[/i] his little consort, aren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e73505",
  "node": "ErisDefeat4",
  "text": "Garrick: ...[b]Figaqua[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:08441ff",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0322d5b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Eris: W-[p/][s/]Wait![p/][s/] G-[p/][s/]Get out of the way, you idiot!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfab20",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Celeste: Drop the weapon, Pierce![p/][s/] Don't be stupid!"
}

{
  "id": "line:044b1c7",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Garrick: The only stupid one here is you, bastard!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0507c8a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Garrick: You should have known from the beginning!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01bfcd5",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Garrick: No matter [i]what[/i] you chose,[p/][s/] they were [i]never[/i] going to let me live!"
}

{
  "id": "line:002e09e",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...\"They\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:097a32c",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Garrick: Every choice I make is mine alone!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07117e5",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait![p/][s/] Stop!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06f1dbf",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Garrick: [j]I'll...[p/] see you all...[p/] in hell...[/j]"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f2c85",
  "node": "ErisDefeat5",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0388f5d",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Celeste: [b]Menas[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:024975b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Eris: ...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:046009b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Eris: Are you trying to [i]heal[/i] him?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc27ac",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Celeste: Damn it...[p/] He aimed straight for his heart."
}

{
  "id": "line:013ab50",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Eris: No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed82c0",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Eris: Come on, you waste of human flesh![p/][s/] Wake up!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8a2e1",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Eris: I need you [i]alive[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ab6d6",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Eris: ...What the [i]hell[/i] did you just do?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2b3a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Celeste: Pierce is dead,[p/] and I signed your stupid Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff5756",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Celeste: Now bring Tyrion back!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ade49",
  "node": "ErisDefeat6",
  "text": "Eris: No no no no[p/][s/] NO!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01e0514",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Celeste: Pierce was dead anyway...[p/] So I thought I could catch her on a technicality,[p/] but I never realized what I [i]actually[/i] did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a74d82",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: You signed a faulty Blood Contract—[p/]one drafted by [i]me[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0789c",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: ...Where do [i]you[/i] get off acting like you're [i]any[/i] better than them?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01936ed",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: \"Ideals\"?![p/][s/] \"Righteousness\"?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0146936",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: Don't give me that bullshit!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f8913",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: I could have accepted losing to a heavensborn..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f08f0",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: But [i]you're[/i] human![p/][s/] And you're a goddamned [i]killer[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:060fb66",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: All of you![p/][s/] [i]All[/i] of you are rotten to your [i]disgusting[/i] cores!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f7fdd",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: You would all tear out each other's throats if I gave you the [i]smallest[/i] reason to!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea5e06",
  "node": "ErisDefeat7",
  "text": "Eris: Tyrion is the [i]only[/i] person here with a trace of the celestials' self-righteous \"morality\"!"
}

{
  "id": "line:000fd69",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: If that's what you think of them,[p/] you really don't know [i]anything[/i] about humanity."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b181d",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste is far more than what you're saying."
}

{
  "id": "line:0268f4a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: She's far more caring and empathic than I am.[p/] I could never even come close."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d133",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: And it has nothing to do with whether [i]I'm[/i] a heavensborn or if [i]she's[/i] a human."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a856a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I think I understand [i]you[/i] a little more, Eris..."
}

{
  "id": "line:016cab7",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Eris: Is that so?"
}

{
  "id": "line:015d00a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let me ask you a question, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:09355a2",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you feel [i]any[/i] amount of satisfaction when you killed my mother?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0638cda",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Eris: So...[p/] You figured that out, did you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ba9b2",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Tyrion: When you went on that little tirade about how much you enjoy killing heavensborn,[p/] I had some suspicions."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c977d8",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Eris: And how does it feel, Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0122a06",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Eris: The person who killed your mother,[p/] the person who ruined your [i]entire[/i] life is standing right in front of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba06f0",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Eris: What do you have to say?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0455a71",
  "node": "ErisDefeat8",
  "text": "Eris: Nothing to say...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e11e8c",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: Say something, damn it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4db8a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I think all I feel for you right now is pity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f055aa",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, [i]that's[/i] rich!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a09f48",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: [i]You[/i] pity [i]me[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6d899",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: Your existence is an infinitesimal moment in my eternal existence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5f598",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: And yet you put [i]all[/i] of this effort into making [i]me[/i] suffer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0242626",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well...?[p/] Was it everything you imagined it would be?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e50e47",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did it satisfy you at all?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e57244",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: I bet you didn't feel [i]anything[/i] when you killed my mother."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b2c46",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was just another drop of evil into your empty soul."
}

{
  "id": "line:0042b73",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: I was...[p/] excited.[p/] It was [i]far[/i] too simple."
}

{
  "id": "line:00324ba",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: I didn't [i]truly[/i] make her suffer.[p/] That's why I didn't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:038e9d0",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, is that right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:001b0d5",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well...[p/] What if you [i]did[/i] succeed in throwing me into despair?"
}

{
  "id": "line:079f2e1",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Would you have felt [i]any[/i] sort of satisfaction?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3abc4",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: Of course, I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4d1eb",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: Demons can't tell lies, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b779a0",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't lie to us,[p/] and you can't lie to yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0241391",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Eris: N-[p/][s/]No...![p/][s/] That can't—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:008350a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat9",
  "text": "Tyrion: And [i]that's[/i] why I pity you."
}

{
  "id": "line:013f7e0",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were fated to be like this from the moment of your creation, weren't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69851",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's why you hate humanity so much.[p/] You envy us."
}

{
  "id": "line:064b84b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Eris: ...[i]What[/i] did you just say?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d8d3a",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're envious of humanity."
}

{
  "id": "line:04af15e",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You don't grow.[p/] You don't change."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d5f0c",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't become a better version of yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:07501ff",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're right.[p/] Your existence probably [i]will[/i] be eternal."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3e39b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You'll be eternally evil."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f07b80",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You'll also be eternally unhappy and eternally pitiful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca256c",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That's[/i] why you envy us,[p/] because you'll never be free from that fate."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a44d95",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Eris: That is completely—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ac273",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't say it, can you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:085f001",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can't refute my claim,[p/] because it would be a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3c084",
  "node": "ErisDefeat10",
  "text": "Eris: You—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0365f44",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Eris: ...You know what?[p/] Maybe you [i]are[/i] right."
}

{
  "id": "line:06de431",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Eris: Maybe I'll [i]never[/i] be satisfied."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffd30c",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Eris: Maybe I [i]won't[/i] feel any satisfaction from killing you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0305dc5",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Eris: ...But I'm still going to try!"
}

{
  "id": "line:018295b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Rath: To think you would threaten violence in [i]my[/i] presence."
}

{
  "id": "line:005b4d8",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Rath: ...Arrogant witch."
}

{
  "id": "line:0606820",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "LucioC: ...This isn't the end for a creature like her."
}

{
  "id": "line:042bfe2",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Tyrion: She'll be back one day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7c703",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "LucioC: Yet,[p/] you look no more perturbed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0983725",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're not done here.[p/] There's something I need to tell all of you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0165b2b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "LucioC: ...Are you serious?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08758ca",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Rath: The Patron is still unknown to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f725df",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Tyrion: But with Celeste's Contract voided,[p/] she should have her real memories back."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a08885",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do you remember what happened in the Prayer Room?[p/] You were the only person who witnessed one of the deaths."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e96cf",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Celeste: I've really been trying to remember what was on Aria's Contract when I caught a glimpse of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd0afb",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Celeste: But I think [i]that's[/i] the memory Eris manipulated the most."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dca67f",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Rath: It's possible that she will need some time to fully recover from the Empress's demonic influence."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc5dc9",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "LucioC: But we don't [i]have[/i] that kind of time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da06f7",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "LucioC: That demon led us around in circles for the entire morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:042204d",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "LucioC: Not to mention that we've lost nearly an hour due to Cuthbert disputing that Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:058685d",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "LucioC: It's just past noon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d934c8",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] We have less than three hours before [i]every[/i] magical trace at the crime scene disappears."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7af3b",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you try testifying?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1f5ab",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe reviewing everything will help jog your memory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f18ea9",
  "node": "ErisDefeat11",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/]Okay...[p/] I'll do my best."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ab0c6",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Chandalier"
}

{
  "id": "line:03a0607",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see your house is still filled with chandeliers..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ed724",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Well,[p/] we've been redecorating the manor."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a4f4c",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I've always found my father's aesthetics to be somewhat tacky,[p/] so I'm excited to make it my own."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e58ef6",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Fireplace"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f306d",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a fireplace.[p/] It's probably used to keep the Study warm during the winter."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dbbc3",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Painting"
}

{
  "id": "line:02c5d34",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a man with a dog."
}

{
  "id": "line:0897e6a",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: That's David Ding,[p/] from House Ding.[p/] They're one of the branch families of House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e72a6",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: He was a dog breeder with a bit of an obsession with the dogs he owned."
}

{
  "id": "line:049956f",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I feel a sort of kinship with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0244084",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker like fellow dog."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7d744",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: He looks like the loyal type."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbce84",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "...How was he inferring that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0e378",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Bookshelf"
}

{
  "id": "line:004502b",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a bookshelf.[p/] It was filled with fake books the last time we were here."
}

{
  "id": "line:05acd58",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Celeste: Some of the books are actually real this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:09527e6",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a window with a view of the outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ea6d4",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Books"
}

{
  "id": "line:06c8ad0",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's various books about economics and political theory."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f955a0",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It looks like they haven't been disturbed since Beatrice's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0299ce6",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I've been meaning to put those away,[p/] but they're actually quite helpful for my new responsibilities."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f18f89",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Table"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f7b5e",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a desk where the head of House Frega would sit."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e64a9",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm still getting used to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abe909",
  "node": "Examine_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: This chair has always felt too big for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d2a7c",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Laefe as a suspect"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b634f6",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Laefe.[p/] I'm sure you know why I'm here,[p/] but I just want to preface this by saying that I highly doubt you were behind this."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ddd61",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: No...[p/] I perfectly understand."
}

{
  "id": "line:03ecf1c",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: ...Well,[p/] [i]I[/i] don't."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d7895",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Lazarick."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbaed1",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:00190fc",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Frankly,[p/] I'm also at a loss.[p/] I have no idea who did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b87095",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: It was obviously that [i]criminal[/i]:[p/] The Eyetaker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2380c",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: Why don't you go interrogate [i]him[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08906b8",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Make no mistake.[p/] We fully intend to,[p/] but I'd like to cover everyone else before we confront him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f89f68",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Let him be, Miriam."
}

{
  "id": "line:05afb95",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: ...It's [i]his[/i] fault that Beatrice is—"
}

{
  "id": "line:06da775",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Our sister knew what she was doing when she gave her testimony."
}

{
  "id": "line:03215df",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Don't insult her bravery by blaming Mr. Cuthbert for what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:098ca76",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Anyways,[p/] Mr. Cuthbert has shown many times that he's acting in good faith."
}

{
  "id": "line:004cf3b",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...And he's capable of convicting the criminals that even [i]we[/i] can't see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e08f45",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03dd022",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mentioned Beatrice before...[p/] Did something happen?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd9b05",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: It happened right after she gave her testimony this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0560a6d",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: She fell unconscious shortly after she left the Scaled Lord's Lair."
}

{
  "id": "line:0228754",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: She hasn't woken up since then.[p/] Marrunath fled afterward."
}

{
  "id": "line:08503d9",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: It must have been the Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0915b25",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: After you manifested Lady Steelwind's Blood Contract,[p/] we all realized why she was acting so strangely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0106920",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...If it weren't for her,[p/] I would've never considered trying to issue a Divine Edict."
}

{
  "id": "line:049205e",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: She sacrificed herself to save Lady Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a61397",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: I-[p/][s/]It seems our esteemed sister put her trust in you, commoner."
}

{
  "id": "line:080cbc4",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: So we will do the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:071d2b9",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: If there's anything we can do to help you,[p/] please ask."
}

{
  "id": "line:08abcfd",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Where were you during the massacre?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f20b2c",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I appreciate all of your trust,[p/] but I have to ask..."
}

{
  "id": "line:011482a",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Where were you all between 2:00 PM and 3:00 PM that day?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0936079",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Luckily,[p/] we were all together."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c66323",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: Me,[p/] Laefe,[p/] Miriam,[p/] Beatrice,[p/] and her friend were all in the garden before 2:00 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0990828",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: But at around 2:00 PM,[p/] my sister went missing."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e55ef",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: I can't believe we trusted [i]her[/i] to take care of our sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f534a7",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Hush now, Miriam.[p/] If the Empress of Discord took control of her,[p/] there was hardly anything Ms. Illmater could do to stop it."
}

{
  "id": "line:002bf2e",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I really [i]do[/i] hope she's okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a25cc2",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: She went to search for Beatrice,[p/] but we haven't seen her since the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a0f24e",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You mentioned that you all went to search for her.[p/] Did you see anything?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c212e",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: No.[p/] We were originally planning to search the cathedral grounds."
}

{
  "id": "line:066076b",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: But when we received word of what happened to His Majesty,[p/] we decided to head back to the Nave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0118f3a",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did any of you lose track of each other during that time?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bae2b",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: No...[p/] We stayed together for the entire time,[p/] but we [i]did[/i] consider splitting up to cover more ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f78707",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] I suppose that makes sense,[p/] and did you see Eris at all when this happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0b565",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: No...[p/] We never saw her."
}

{
  "id": "line:058c512",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: She went missing shortly after Beatrice did..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03aac23",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's [i]really[/i] suspicious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0add564",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: You don't think—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092c58b",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's definitely possible she was involved in this somehow..."
}

{
  "id": "line:063d014",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Not to mention,[p/] the Eyetaker is one of our suspects,[p/] and [i]she's[/i] his daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:099d838",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: She's his [i]what[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:007200f",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Beatrice never mentioned that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093ada2",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: No...[p/] She didn't mention it at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a8e8a",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "...It sounded like Eris had a lot to answer for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9cb43",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "I'd have to find her first, though..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc1d6f",
  "node": "Talk_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Contracts with a demon"
}

{
  "id": "line:01fb0d2",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Ah,[p/] it's your Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c2474",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: You're always showing it to people."
}

{
  "id": "line:0083af4",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess I can't help it..."
}

{
  "id": "line:086ccae",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It took years of studying law for me to get this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d03e98",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "...Were those years really meaningless?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020cdb4",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I envy your bravery, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1a0e7",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: In the face of demons and dragons,[p/] you still seem quite calm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d26753",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Regardless of who's involved,[p/] this is the same as any other trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:06bc712",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Man, king, or god...[p/] I'll save Aria,[p/] no matter what it takes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0723956",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: [i]*chuckle*[/i][p/] What a strange saying.[p/] I can't say I hate it though."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b10f3",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Aria|Autopsy Report: Lloyd von Sanctus|Autopsy Report: Coraline Sibyl|Autopsy Report: Garrick Pierce|Steelwind's Testimony|Aria's Blood Contract"
}

{
  "id": "line:05b3e42",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I can't believe someone did this to Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b5181e",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I've had enough of these demons..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0166625",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: They just violate the wills of those they've enslaved.[p/] It's absolutely abhorrent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd476b",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No matter what happens...[p/] I'll save her from this fate."
}

{
  "id": "line:073749e",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: For everyone's sake,[p/] I hope you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:005acfa",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Eris"
}

{
  "id": "line:018e219",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I wasn't sure what to make of Ms. Illmater at first,[p/] but she was a friend to Beatrice during those five years..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0786af9",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: So I [i]want[/i] to trust her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b6774",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: She attended the Academy.[p/] Isn't that right, Miriam?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2f65f",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: She did,[p/] but I always kept my distance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df0d2e",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: She had quite the unsavory reputation.[p/] I was always too scared to approach her."
}

{
  "id": "line:026ece8",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I see... [h=\"As much as I hate to admit it,|I felt the same way around her.\" e=\"sf\"/ ]"
}

{
  "id": "line:05832f4",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Lazarick"
}

{
  "id": "line:00a281b",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why [i]are[/i] you here, Lord Asclepius?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffb2d7",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: We were discussing plans to lift the ban on studying [b]necromancy[/b] at the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0abd498",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: As the head of House Frega,[p/] I inherited my father's position on the board."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3ce5",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh.[p/][s/] That's great!"
}

{
  "id": "line:072387f",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: I appreciate the enthusiasm,[p/] but we should still approach this carefully."
}

{
  "id": "line:039eef7",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Really?[p/] I thought [i]you[/i] of all people would be excited for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a4e91",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: The kingdom's ban on [b]necromancy[/b] was harsh,[p/] but it was somewhat justified."
}

{
  "id": "line:082abf0",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: The study of something like this has to be regulated and closely monitored."
}

{
  "id": "line:064cdda",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: The last thing I want is a mad necromancer that sets us back another few centuries."
}

{
  "id": "line:003e63a",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Beatrice|Beatrice's Actions|Beatrice's Actions 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df3abc",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04150a2",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know if I have any right to say this,[p/] but I'm sorry about what happened to Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:01011e3",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: No...[p/] For better or for worse,[p/] she's always done what she wanted."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6b952",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: She knew what she was doing,[p/] and she was well aware of the potential consequences."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f147d",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I just wish there was something I could do for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0865dbf",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Marrunath"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cee510",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Have you ever spoken to Beatrice's familiar?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b9c0e",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: Tracker [i]hate[/i] flying rat."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ed6b3",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: He always says mean things to everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:028bf21",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: He's a [i]terrible[/i] pet."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e99f5",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "He wasn't exactly a pet, though...[p/] Or was he?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05207f1",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: Aster|Marriage Meeting|The Trapped King"
}

{
  "id": "line:07d477c",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: I hope His Majesty is okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d471e",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right...[p/] Someone basically used his former fiancée [i]and[/i] his current fiancée to commit several murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:04656a4",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: Despite being royal,[p/] he's always had a soft heart."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f67075",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: I'm sure this whole ordeal is affecting him the most."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a26396",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Player: The Purple Mark"
}

{
  "id": "line:04005a4",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have any of you ever seen this symbol before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfb622",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...No.[p/] I can't say I have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0bd00",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: Me neither..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7bf80",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: I think I've seen it at the Imperial Academy before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a951af",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What...?[p/] Where?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0236953",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: It was carved onto some of the desks in the Imperial Library,[p/] but it was only there for a day."
}

{
  "id": "line:016a599",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Miriam: The faculty probably noticed it and removed it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1ee10",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aria [i]did[/i] mention these cases were happening throughout Wyverngarde,[p/] but were they even happening at the Imperial Academy?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00000d6",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Lady Frega?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9ffe0",
  "node": "Present_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: My apologies.[p/] I don't think I'll be of much help with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0c262",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "We arrived at Frega Manor,[p/] hoping to speak with Laefe and Miriam."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d89252",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "As I walked by,[p/] I passed by several rooms filled with contractors."
}

{
  "id": "line:0504a43",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Some rooms were being repainted.[p/] Others looked like they were being completely reconstructed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0127fea",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "After some asking around,[p/] one of the servants mentioned that the sisters were entertaining a guest in the Study."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe0cae",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "I normally wouldn't interrupt them,[p/] but I needed to use every minute that I could."
}

{
  "id": "line:03223fc",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: ARF[p/][s/] ARF[p/][s/] ARF[p/][s/] ARF!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f59b17",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Celeste: A-[p/][s/]Ah!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04228c6",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "As we entered the Study,[p/] we were met with this floof of an animal."
}

{
  "id": "line:059567b",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "He was barking at us at first,[p/] but his mouth curled up into a dopey smile the moment he recognized me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b99cf1",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: Oh.[p/] Hello, friends."
}

{
  "id": "line:09c8263",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: Sorry for borks.[p/] Tracker thought he smell more rats."
}

{
  "id": "line:0975a51",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You really don't like rats.[p/] Do you, Tracker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:070367a",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tracker: Lot more rats have been showing than usual."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe2dc7",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Oh, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:01998fe",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "I scanned the room.[p/] Miriam was there too,[p/] sitting on what was once William Frega's desk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8202a",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "They appeared to be speaking with Lord Asclepius."
}

{
  "id": "line:0826b5a",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Sorry for barging in, Laefe."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e8d79",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] It's no problem at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:098e640",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "The thickness of the atmosphere seemed to imply they knew why I was there."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bc80a",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll skip the pleasantries...[p/] Do you mind if I ask you a few questions about what happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0978b60",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: Of course...[p/] I'll do anything to help with Lady Steelwind's...[p/] situation."
}

{
  "id": "line:00a48ed",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: ...Should I leave?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2f5ce",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: No...[p/] You were there with me when everything happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:09410da",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Laefe: ...And your testimony will substantiate my alibi."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cea1a5",
  "node": "Check_Events_FregaManor2",
  "text": "Lazarick: Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0377b3c",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose I'll stop beating around the bush."
}

{
  "id": "line:097fef2",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Have any of you made a Blood Contract with a demon lately?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eca88f",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Miriam: How dare you?! [h=\"This presumptious|little peasant!\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c013b9",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Laefe: ...No,[p/] I understand where he's coming from. [h=\"I [i]want[/i] to understand,|but the very idea is infuriating...\" e=\"a\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:06d266d",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Laefe: Of everyone present,[p/] our sister was the only person with [i]known[/i] ties to a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fcb04",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Laefe: ...If she were to share that secret with anyone,[p/] it would've been with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b9b37",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "I didn't catch any incriminating thoughts from them through the Eye,[p/] but I'd been misled by it before..."
}

{
  "id": "line:084d6d3",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "I let out a frustrated sigh.[p/] The lack of evidence pointing to this demon was becoming a giant pain."
}

{
  "id": "line:037fcbf",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...We still have no idea who the Patron is."
}

{
  "id": "line:06607a3",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Lazarick: I was actually meaning to ask you about that after the trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:001bdad",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Lazarick: Can't you just use this \"Divine Edict\" of yours to figure out who the Patron is?"
}

{
  "id": "line:06ac791",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Tyrion: No.[p/] To manifest a Blood Contract,[p/] I need the title of the demon and the name of the human they made that contract with."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f3a6f",
  "node": "EdictAttempt",
  "text": "Lazarick: I understand that,[p/] but why not just apply brute force?"
}

{
  "id": "line:000d55d",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Lazarick: Due to the King's funeral,[p/] the Kingsguard has a detailed list of everyone who was present during the massacre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0603acf",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Lazarick: Whoever this Patron is,[p/] they were working together with the Empress of Discord.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6af28",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Lazarick: They set a trap in the Nave,[p/] which means they might've been present at the funeral."
}

{
  "id": "line:0261930",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Lazarick: That must mean they made a Blood Contract with her, yes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0343a9c",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09dea43",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I could just keep issuing Divine Edicts until a Blood Contract appears!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0378905",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]Wait...[p/] I-[p/][s/]Is that safe?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab23e8",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's only one way to find out."
}

{
  "id": "line:009d054",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "I took out my notes and began looking at my list of suspects."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e856f",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "I would be at it for a while.[p/] So I decided to go in alphabetical order."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f82b6",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's definitely not Alaric.[p/] He's just a kid."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b80541",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And we already know about Aria..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3a3ec",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "I cleared my throat."
}

{
  "id": "line:052747f",
  "node": "EdictAttempt2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Release thy guards and manifest your Blood Contract with Aster de Wyverngarde!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e67975",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Tyrion: AGGGGGGGGGH!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0359c84",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion?![p/][s/] What's wrong?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc3969",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "My breath felt like fire inside my lungs.[p/] It felt like someone had thrown hot oil onto my skin."
}

{
  "id": "line:043de45",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "The magic inside me felt like acid inside my body.[p/] I could only writhe on the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c69172",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "I heard the sound of someone screaming,[p/] only later realizing that it was my voice crying out in agony."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a2509",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Miriam: W-[p/][s/]What...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:008f288",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Miriam: What's happening to him?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:082150d",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Laefe: Lazarick![p/][s/] Your magic!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec300e",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Lazarick: R-[p/][s/]Right!"
}

{
  "id": "line:059d1ed",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, you silly, silly boy."
}

{
  "id": "line:05a2780",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Eris: You may be half-human,[p/] but you can't just go around declaring [i]lies[/i] like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb5fa7",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Eris: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] And I was [i]really[/i] looking forward to bringing you to the end of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c63107",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Eris: I haven't even [i]started[/i] to have my fun with you yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3915b",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Who are you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6627c",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Eris: Actually...[p/] I suppose [i]that[/i] contract is still in effect."
}

{
  "id": "line:017a3c8",
  "node": "EdictAttempt3",
  "text": "Eris: I guess my hands are tied.[p/] I'll save you,[p/] just this once."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f5309",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...rion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:084b398",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion![p/][s/] Please, wake up!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0375090",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]You're okay!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02399c4",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "I certainly didn't [i]feel[/i] \"okay\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cdc9d",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Every part of me ached.[p/] My skin felt like it was being poked with pins and needles."
}

{
  "id": "line:05fd63d",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "I felt soreness as I tried to stand up."
}

{
  "id": "line:030b762",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Tracker: Are you okay, friend?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fff236",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Tracker nestled his head into my lap.[p/] The feeling of petting a white cloud definitely helped."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecdb0a",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What happened?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0618e49",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Lazarick: You died."
}

{
  "id": "line:03da3b7",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7c5c3",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Lazarick: I've never brought anyone back from something like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eb6f6",
  "node": "EdictAttempt4",
  "text": "Lazarick: That was my strongest spell, too.[p/] You have no idea how lucky you are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7626b",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Tyrion: T-[p/][s/]Thank you, Lord Asclepius."
}

{
  "id": "line:0326253",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Lazarick: Thank [i]you[/i].[p/] I've never tried that spell on a human before."
}

{
  "id": "line:051834a",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Lazarick: This is going to be remarkable for my research."
}

{
  "id": "line:0306b1e",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Laefe shot a glare at the young necromancer."
}

{
  "id": "line:0458444",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "He just pursed his lips and looked around nervously.[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:026e94c",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Eventually,[p/] he just sat down in the opposite corner of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:078a8fd",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't understand..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a0d9f",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Tyrion: The last thing I remember was issuing my Divine Edict..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7e2d5",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Laefe: Was [i]that[/i] the cause?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de25c1",
  "node": "EdictAttempt5",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I've done it before without any problems.[p/] I [i]just[/i] used it this morning."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da131c",
  "node": "EdictAttempt6",
  "text": "No...[p/] That pain came [i]after[/i] I attempted to issue a Divine Edict."
}

{
  "id": "line:0422b29",
  "node": "EdictAttempt6",
  "text": "I started at the top of my list of suspects."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c295e",
  "node": "EdictAttempt6",
  "text": "Which meant that I tried to manifest the Blood Contract between the Empress of Discord and Aster."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f2e0",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It [i]might[/i] be because Aster [i]doesn't[/i] have a Blood Contract with the Empress."
}

{
  "id": "line:0563ef8",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: If demons are unable to lie,[p/] the same might hold true for celestials as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a822f2",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Divine Edict is clearly some sort of divine magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:017deed",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Asking for a Blood Contract that doesn't exist might be considered a lie."
}

{
  "id": "line:088b237",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Laefe: I'm sorry Lazarick suggested something so careless."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ef054",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: No...[p/] I was being reckless."
}

{
  "id": "line:0094620",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Celeste: Please be more careful..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b23ef",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't think I can take this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2dfb0",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Well,[p/] at least we know [i]Aster[/i] wasn't behind this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8bfe6",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Celeste: He was trapped in a [b]Force Cage[b/]![p/][s/] It [i]obviously[/i] wasn't him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05c632b",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] Anyways,[p/] it's clear that I can't just issue these edicts without thinking."
}

{
  "id": "line:01326e2",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll just have to wait until I'm certain of the Patron's identity."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad49fe",
  "node": "EdictAttempt7",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] it looked like I'd found everything I could here."
}

{
  "id": "line:02086c4",
  "node": "Examine_Garden1",
  "text": "Player: Statue"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae8c56",
  "node": "Examine_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What goes through the mind of such a tortured creature?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b20c29",
  "node": "Examine_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What is with you and this statue?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b7089",
  "node": "Examine_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know...[p/] But I can feel its emotions as if they were my own."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a45cae",
  "node": "Examine_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: It's an inanimate object, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:074adbd",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Player: Steelwind's Trial"
}

{
  "id": "line:083263d",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: You said that you two were investigating the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:070de38",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Were you planning on defending Lady Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0ba7c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: If she'll have me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6aa0c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: She may be a competent prosecutor,[p/] but I have far more experience defending clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aa5f9",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Unfortunately,[p/] I think the situation is more complicated than that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0592ace",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Several House leaders died today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0291aa9",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: We can't release this information to the public—[p/]not after the news of William Frega's death has already spread."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b09559",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: In the course of two months,[p/] we've lost not one,[p/] but [i]three[/i] Pillar heads."
}

{
  "id": "line:085c321",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But the trial [i]has[/i] to happen soon,[p/] or else the magical traces left will disappear."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee8c39",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: From what I've heard,[p/] we [i]will[/i] be holding a trial,[p/] but it will be handled privately and internally."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3c8d7",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: ...And I'm sorry to say that you won't be permitted to serve in such a trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:007e82a",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Would you be able to pull some strings for us, Aster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08c9941",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I-[p/][s/]I'm sorry.[p/] I'd like nothing more than to give you the opportunity to represent her,[p/] but I clearly have a personal attachment to this case."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b96b56",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: If I try to tip the trial in her favour,[p/] it will only harm her chances."
}

{
  "id": "line:01f138b",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if I can't directly defend her,[p/] we can still investigate the crimes on her behalf."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfc6a1",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: ...Yes.[p/] I would really appreciate that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae1c4a",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: If new evidence is found,[p/] perhaps we can exonerate Ms. Steelwind of the charges against her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0173e64",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Player: The Gathering of Nobles"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ea399",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: After everything that's happened,[p/] I really need to know."
}

{
  "id": "line:077ab37",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why were so many nobles gathered in one place anyways?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e92119",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: All four of the pillar families were present."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b209c0",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I understand if you don't want to tell me,[p/] but this information could be vital in figuring out what really happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccc3a0",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: ...The truth is that we all gathered to mourn the death of my father:[p/] King Olivier de Wyverngarde IX."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1c888",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/][s/] The king is [i]dead[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd9efd",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Yes,[p/] we wanted to avoid releasing this information to the public so close to the death of William Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:04bf2c3",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: My father has been ill for quite some time,[p/] so we were prepared for this."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a3b19",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: ...Or at least,[p/] I [i]thought[/i] I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cea292",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I also lost my mother when I was quite young,[p/] but it's still all a little hard to take in."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dce7a",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry...[p/] You have my condolences."
}

{
  "id": "line:0932c0b",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0704522",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: But if King Olivier is gone...[p/] That would make you—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d318bb",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Yes.[p/] You currently stand before [i]King[/i] Aster de Wyverngarde:[p/] the ruler of our kingdom."
}

{
  "id": "line:03744ba",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "The words came out hollow.[p/] It sounded like he was mourning more than just his late father."
}

{
  "id": "line:0272471",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: No wonder so many nobles were gathered here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2082a",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] They came under the guise of paying their respects,[p/] but I'm sure they just wanted to get close to the [i]new[/i] King."
}

{
  "id": "line:0644a5b",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Ironically,[p/] I think only House Frega came to genuinely give their condolences."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1f920",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Speaking of the Fregas...[p/] I think you need to know."
}

{
  "id": "line:099c506",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]saw[/i] Beatrice before I was knocked out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0082a8d",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think [i]she[/i] may have been the one who killed Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6a009",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: ... [h=\"Why would she|be there?!\" e=\"af\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0249aa8",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry.[p/] I know she was your friend,[p/] but we already know she's not above committing murder."
}

{
  "id": "line:012d665",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I-[p/][s/]I see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a561d4",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I suppose if [i]you're[/i] saying it,[p/] it must be so,[p/] but what possible reason would she have to be involved in something like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:099810b",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not sure yet,[p/] but I plan to find that out."
}

{
  "id": "line:088c78c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the way,[p/] where were [i]you[/i] during the murders?"
}

{
  "id": "line:092f89d",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I remember you left with Steelwind when Celeste and I arrived at the Cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ba9e8",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Ah, yes.[p/] Steelwind and I left to speak with High Speaker Archeus in his quarters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f64063",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What was your meeting about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1beee",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: ...It was actually about our wedding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e60a23",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: With my father's death,[p/] the Grand General demanded that we make our union official."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b7b05",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:087bd1f",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]would[/i] congratulate you two,[p/] but considering the circumstances—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcf811",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I understand.[p/] And I appreciate your words nonetheless."
}

{
  "id": "line:004a04c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] how long did this meeting last?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03de258",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I believe we spoke with him until 1:40 PM,[p/] but von Sanctus died at 2:05 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1474d",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That means that she began her rampage less than half an hour after that meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b8bd1",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Was there anything off about her behaviour?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd27e6",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Now that you mention it,[p/] something about her demeanor changed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0965a3f",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: We were speaking of the wedding when she abruptly left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7208f",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I asked her where she was going,[p/] but she ignored me."
}

{
  "id": "line:050bdbf",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That sounds similar to what happened when Celeste fought her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0209ccc",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's no way she was affected by Mageblight..."
}

{
  "id": "line:097a307",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I honestly didn't think much of it at the time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b98085",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I'm quite used to her giving me the cold shoulder."
}

{
  "id": "line:082269c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Right."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d0b61",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What happened after your meeting with the High Speaker?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b7c45",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see Steelwind after that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:027e600",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Actually,[p/] [i]I[/i] found myself caught up in something else entirely."
}

{
  "id": "line:0554543",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: At 2:00 PM,[p/] I went to pay my respects at my father's coffin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4de92",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: But apparently,[p/] someone had set a magical trap there."
}

{
  "id": "line:012810f",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: It was a [b]Glyph of Contingency[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef27c1",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: I have...[p/] heard of that spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f335b",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: It's like a trap you can set.[p/] You can infuse [i]any[/i] spell into it."
}

{
  "id": "line:02761cc",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But it requires a \"contingent\" spell to [i]place[/i] that trap."
}

{
  "id": "line:038477c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Which spell was it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:056838f",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: It was a [b]Force Cage[/b] targeting [i]me[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c32b37",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Was the murderer trying to attack Aster, too?"
}

{
  "id": "line:087427c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't think so...[p/] They would have used a more lethal spell if they wanted to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2f8aa",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: From the sounds of it,[p/] [b]Force Cage[/b] can't be dispelled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a78e16",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: So Aster would have been trapped inside of it for that full hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f16d1c",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: We think that someone used this as a distraction."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3aff",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Because of that trap,[p/] the Kingsguard consolidated most of their attention and forces in the Nave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c79db6",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: As a result,[p/] there were fewer people guarding von Sanctus, Sibyl, and Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af879b",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: And the ones that [i]were[/i] there all fell comatose."
}

{
  "id": "line:04a2c5f",
  "node": "Talk_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: They can't tell us what happened to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d4eefc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "...It was just me,[p/] Celeste,[p/] and the statue—[p/]the horrible statue."
}

{
  "id": "line:0266d4f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I don't feel safe here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc9d20",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: Why is that statue freaking you out so much?"
}

{
  "id": "line:071d04d",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: That pegasus is [i]literally[/i] a celestial like you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01f7f7a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't know,[p/] but I can feel its suffering through the Eye."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3dce9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: It's an [i]inanimate[/i] object, Tyrion!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f23999",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Let's MOVE somewhere else."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dbecc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright.[p/] Whatever it takes to get you to stop acting so weird."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e00085",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "I was dreading having to face that statue again,[p/] but despite knowing better,[p/] I returned to the Garden."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e4f4d1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's staring into my soul."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a2733",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Celeste: Then stop looking at it!"
}

{
  "id": "line:045ed3c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "The Crown Prince was sitting at a bench nearby.[p/] Several members of the Kingsguard were standing at attention around him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b02da2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "His brow was furrowed.[p/] He didn't even seem to notice us until one of the knights stepped in our way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce5a62",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: O-[p/][s/]Oh, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] and Ms. McCoy too."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c79ab",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: What are you still doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12b90",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're trying to investigate what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edd04f",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0656cf0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: Yes,[p/] I was just thinking how unfortunate this ordeal has been."
}

{
  "id": "line:016808c",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I do hope Lady Steelwind is taking this well."
}

{
  "id": "line:078ffd1",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Right...[p/] She was his fiancée after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0450841",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're trying to find out what exactly happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f17c3",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Aster: I...[p/] see.[p/] Well, I'll do whatever I can to help."
}

{
  "id": "line:01427e5",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "...And yet [i]another[/i] inexplicable event was added to the list."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a92fa8",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "After everything I'd learned,[p/] I knew for certain that Steelwind wasn't afflicted with Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f2faf",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Someone must be behind this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1e2cf",
  "node": "Check_Events_Garden1",
  "text": "Anyways,[p/] he probably didn't witness much after he was trapped by that [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:07fa383",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: This statue..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0551442",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What [i]is[/i] this thing, by the way?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052f704",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: You called it a \"pegasus\" earlier."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ed7f3",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: It's a creature of divine origin."
}

{
  "id": "line:0384172",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Many people believe that the angels of the Upper Planes rode these creatures into battle."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdb05c",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I see..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f30195",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Do you feel some kinship to it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b4ad8",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I can only feel its suffering."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acf9c2",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: What?"
}

{
  "id": "line:019a2ff",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Its face is contorted into an expression of pure agony."
}

{
  "id": "line:05846f6",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It screams out in terror.[p/] Yet no one can hear its pleas for mercy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0718ebe",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tracker: Queen...[p/] I think he's broken."
}

{
  "id": "line:0390403",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Someone ignorant of its plight has placed some sort of vain party hat upon its head."
}

{
  "id": "line:041553f",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's as if they are mocking its torment.[p/] Like some kind of demon torturing a poor soul in the fields of Avernus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2cb07",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: What are you even saying...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d933b3",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4f371",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I need to take a moment to think about what I've just witnessed here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0990f6e",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: We all should."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ba35b",
  "node": "Examine_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Alright, Tyrion.[p/] You go do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:067faed",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: So...[p/] You seem to be doing well,[p/] all things considered."
}

{
  "id": "line:00fe776",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Right...[p/] I suppose you'd expect me to be wallowing in self-pity,[p/] crying over the demon that now has ownership of my soul."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1650e",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Nine hells, heavensborn.[p/] I can't stand when you look at me like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2a071",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: You know...[p/] My offer still stands.[p/] I can try to help you."
}

{
  "id": "line:062b889",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: At the risk of your [i]own[/i] soul?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02aad41",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Which part of the contract would you dispute anyway?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c309e9",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "I couldn't answer.[p/] I'd been combing through her Blood Contract for the last month."
}

{
  "id": "line:00056c4",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "I thought of every angle of attack,[p/] but there was very little room for interpretation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee1db6",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Believe me.[p/] I've had years to look it over,[p/] but it's impossible to break."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5b33a",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm sorry."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c649b9",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Don't be.[p/] You defeated me.[p/] I won't suffer your pity."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b635d",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Player: Eris Illmater"
}

{
  "id": "line:01da1b7",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: We always meet in the strangest places, Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8ea1e",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you doing here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e49fd",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: I requested to accompany Beatrice to this event."
}

{
  "id": "line:0823a79",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: After all,[p/] I don't have many opportunities to enter a Church like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d28577",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I can imagine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fcdd8d",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: By the way,[p/] is your father still—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:020b8da",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: Oh,[p/] if you're worried about him,[p/] we've already had a conversation about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d37983",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: I don't think he'll be accosting you any time soon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0f8ab",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cdc283",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...That sounds too good to be true."
}

{
  "id": "line:0215cdd",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: How'd you pull something like [i]that[/i] off?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cffbf4",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: He may look like a hardened criminal,[p/] but he's always had a soft spot for his family."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a3c3e",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: He also owed me,[p/] and I have a way of making people see things my way."
}

{
  "id": "line:074589a",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice just scoffed when she heard that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0985374",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] If [i]you're[/i] here,[p/] does that mean Marrunath is also—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05817e9",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh, hell no.[p/] They'd never let me bring him [i]here[/i] of all places."
}

{
  "id": "line:017a895",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: He's being guarded by the Kingsguard near the entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0452ccc",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: If he tries to escape,[p/] that knight over there is ordered to kill me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f707da",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "She gestured towards a knight who was silently watching all of us from afar."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d72e5",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...You're surprisingly calm about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:095a100",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I've regularly dealt with demons.[p/] [i]This[/i] is nothing in comparison to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:09af7d2",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: ...You've really changed a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7aa00",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Considering how I was before,[p/] I'll take that as a compliment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f09d97",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] if Marrunath isn't here,[p/] how did you know which statue I was looking at?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9efd8",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: It was a lucky guess."
}

{
  "id": "line:0194c3b",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...That grotesque statue certainly makes an impression on you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f38ed",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh,[p/] Marrunath just spoke with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06350c8",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: He wanted me to let you know that he can smell your \"celestial stink\" from the entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b0b86",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Love you too, Marrunath."
}

{
  "id": "line:097b1a8",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I'm not going to repeat his response to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:05dd055",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Player: The Heavensborn"
}

{
  "id": "line:08751b9",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've been meaning to ask.[p/] During the trial,[p/] you and Marrunath kept calling me \"heavensborn\"."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0254f",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What does that mean?[p/][s/] Do you know about my abilities?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08d595d",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: What?[p/] Did you seriously not know?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b81112",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: You know how to issue a Divine Edict.[p/] That's a very advanced spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:089d698",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't really understand it myself,[p/] but I learned it after solving a riddle on the Earrings of Vitality."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af87bf",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: ...Of [i]course[/i] you did."
}

{
  "id": "line:01309e9",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Anyways,[p/] I'm [i]quite[/i] surprised you don't know about your lineage."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b3650",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Maybe my [i]mother[/i] knew,[p/] but I lost her when I was really young."
}

{
  "id": "line:00deb8a",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I see...[p/] You have my condolences."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1a7c5",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: But to answer your question,[p/] a heavensborn is a human whose bloodline has been touched by the gods."
}

{
  "id": "line:094f606",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm assuming you're not talking about the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9fab7",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: No.[p/] I'm speaking of the [i]actual[/i] gods."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ab14c",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice![p/][s/] You can't say that here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:038cdab",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh, come off it.[p/] What's the Church going to do?[p/] [i]Arrest[/i] me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08bfe29",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Anyways,[p/] your blood has been touched by the celestials of the Upper Planes."
}

{
  "id": "line:027de42",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Much like my soul is tainted and tied to the Abyssal Hells,[p/] [i]your[/i] soul is consecrated by the heavens."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a025c",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: So I [i]am[/i] a cleric, then."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d9b50",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: You are [i]much[/i] more than a cleric.[p/] Your kind is nearly extinct."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aea123",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: And make no mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:015ec92",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: If you find yourself under the wrong circumstances,[p/] even [i]you[/i] can be sent to Hell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0845b83",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Player: The Celestials"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d02ed1",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are there really that few heavensborn?[p/] What about the Theocracy to the west of us?"
}

{
  "id": "line:023491e",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Much like mages,[p/] the power of a heavensborn is passed through bloodlines."
}

{
  "id": "line:003522a",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Many of those bloodlines have been lost over Lumina's history."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a9079",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Some were lost in the previous wars.[p/] Some strayed from the path and were ended by the Theocracy itself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1e7e0",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...And many were ended by the celestial's enemies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce8355",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why is Wyverngarde going to so much trouble to hide this from everyone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e39152",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: The Theocracy has been this kingdom's enemy since it was created."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b68f99",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: The Luminite's greatest weapon is their faith."
}

{
  "id": "line:0744096",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Wyverngarde has always feared that faith would infect the people like a sickness and destroy Wyverngarde from within."
}

{
  "id": "line:07da7e3",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: So like always,[p/] it's all about control."
}

{
  "id": "line:052b6fd",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: It also runs contrary to the Church of Bahamut.[p/] The ancient dragons are also an enemy of heaven."
}

{
  "id": "line:089ab35",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: They've done their best to wipe out any religions that worship the Celestials."
}

{
  "id": "line:002ea84",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: If your bloodline is blessed by the celestials,[p/] does that mean that our kids will also be heavensborn?"
}

{
  "id": "line:094334b",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose so.[p/] I think my mother was also a—"
}

{
  "id": "line:038e615",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "I paused for a moment,[p/] processing what she just said."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e04261",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I-[p/]I asked if your kids will be heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:06820d6",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "...What was I thinking?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03222e3",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: Wow..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbd189",
  "node": "Talk_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...If only it were always that easy."
}

{
  "id": "line:00601cc",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Is that your Attorney's Runestone?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fdaf48",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Why are you PRESENTING it to me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:095ec4a",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I PRESENT it to everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1222d",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Eris [i]did[/i] tell me about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d4e11",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: She kept calling it a \"badge\" for some reason."
}

{
  "id": "line:0424afe",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why [i]do[/i] you call it a badge?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e53690",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: You wouldn't understand.[p/] The meaning is beyond your understanding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5b578",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:081c515",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: You seem to be doing well, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b722e7",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Why are you looking at me like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcdc31",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Are you seriously not angry at me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a0733",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: At this point,[p/] what would it accomplish?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d8099",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: You defeated me despite my best efforts.[p/] I suppose I respect you for that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7eeb7",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "It sort of made sense,[p/] but there was something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1046a",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "It was difficult to see,[p/] but I could sense some dread in her."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f7897",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Player: Miriam"
}

{
  "id": "line:084a6b6",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] It seems that after all these years,[p/] Miriam still hasn't matured."
}

{
  "id": "line:099aaf4",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: ...What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:043ffe2",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Oh, come now.[p/] You won't make any friends with that pompous attitude of yours."
}

{
  "id": "line:0423f08",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: I don't [i]need[/i] friends."
}

{
  "id": "line:0604f81",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: [i]I'm[/i] a Frega,[p/] what need would I have for such things?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e885ae",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: If you truly mean that,[p/] then you don't know anything about our House."
}

{
  "id": "line:035e326",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Your skills and intellect are worthless if you can't win over political allies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7cade",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: You will always have weaknesses.[p/] You need allies who can cover them and support you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eef82c",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: ...Like you and that demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:099bffa",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Yes.[p/] That's [i]exactly[/i] what I mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af59ff",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: P-[p/][s/]Perhaps we should talk about something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:046804d",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Player: Laefe"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3c9af",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Laefe.[p/] Are you really against marrying Jaiden von Sanctus?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c889f9",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: Absolutely![p/][s/] That man is an ignorant know-it-all!"
}

{
  "id": "line:090a777",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: With Aster taken,[p/] there aren't many other suitors capable of strengthening House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f4fe2",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: I just...[p/] [i]can't[/i] marry someone that I don't love."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd505d",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: It's not as if you would need to be married to him for long.[p/] Accidents happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:09ce130",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: All it takes is one false step on a staircase,[p/] and—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bfb96",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: Beatrice!"
}

{
  "id": "line:01d6127",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I'm joking, [i]of course[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:074449b",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I just want to make sure you're both taken care of when I'm gone."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f0a05",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: Stop talking like that![p/][s/] It's as if you're [i]planning[/i] on dying!"
}

{
  "id": "line:097f26a",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: You're [i]not[/i] leaving us again!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0864c99",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: Miriam..."
}

{
  "id": "line:007e620",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: I-[p/][s/]I'm sorry...[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:04bc79d",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...My apologies.[p/] Let's talk about something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aedee2",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I hope Aster is okay.[p/] He was never emotionally strong."
}

{
  "id": "line:0265299",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Wait...[p/] Do you [i]not[/i] know why we're all gathered here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0871c6c",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I've been meaning to ask about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0372ad3",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I'm sorry, then.[p/] It's not my place to tell you."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff958",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I wonder.[p/] Is Aria still a complete mess when she's around Aster?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3c2c4",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Yep."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d5fc6",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...I [i]want[/i] to be happy for her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad669c",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Even when we were engaged,[p/] she was completely infatuated with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b3f07",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]That[/i] sounds awkward."
}

{
  "id": "line:0958332",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I do hope she can learn to be happy with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:05352d1",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Player: Ruby"
}

{
  "id": "line:04b7695",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Have you spoken with Tymora since the trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0365b78",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...No.[p/] I haven't."
}

{
  "id": "line:085ea16",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: She really [i]does[/i] care for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:09dfb65",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: I remember.[p/] Even during the court case,[p/] she would speak of you constantly."
}

{
  "id": "line:010ead8",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Could we talk about something else?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0267b70",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Of course.[p/] My apologies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0809f68",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this, Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bf321",
  "node": "Present_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: My apologies,[p/] but I have nothing to say about that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c3a342",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "We explored the pathways surrounding the Cathedral.[p/] They had created a garden around them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d93555",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "They were filled with flowering hedges,[p/] trimmed with the same reverence they held for the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:010621a",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste walked over to the nearby marigolds and plucked one of them.[p/] She turned its stem thoughtfully between her fingers."
}

{
  "id": "line:00aa0ee",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "The petals shone brightly,[p/] its golden radiance only rivaled by their reflection in her eyes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbf26f",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "She suddenly looked at me.[p/] I realized I was staring."
}

{
  "id": "line:0586961",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry..."
}

{
  "id": "line:04fcee1",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "...I really had a [i]lot[/i] I needed to figure out."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea1b88",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "I cleared my throat as I quickly walked past her,[p/] but I froze as I came across a peculiar statue."
}

{
  "id": "line:02073c5",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Wow...[p/] [i]That's[/i] a little out of place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0401949",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: What even [i]is[/i] it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6fe32",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: If my memory is correct,[p/] it's a pegasus."
}

{
  "id": "line:0890765",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tracker: Hello, friends!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf63e0",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice and Tracker stood up from a nearby bench.[p/] I didn't even notice them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e11f62",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice was carrying a leash which Tracker used to guide her to us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0915f26",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "She seemed to be staring past me,[p/] only turning her head to face in our general direction whenever we spoke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eacb10",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "She was followed by Eris,[p/] who was looming behind her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf568a",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris flashed me a blank smile as I noticed her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0398d99",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]Beatrice![p/][s/] Aren't you supposed to be—?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff8169",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Dead?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e94f9",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I-[p/][s/]I meant to say locked up,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a2221f",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: No.[p/] It's perfectly understandable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0c00e",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: [i]You[/i] of all people know what was on my Blood Contract."
}

{
  "id": "line:020f1ca",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: But it appears the Empress of Discord isn't going to use me just yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0439370",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: But it appears the Empress of Discord isn't going to kill me just yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:06196f2",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Is that really necessary?"
}

{
  "id": "line:069eaba",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Never mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:087cbf4",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice's sisters followed behind her.[p/] Their eyes never met mine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0254c2c",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "They didn't seem hostile,[p/] and all things considered,[p/] I prefered their company over the two pillar heads."
}

{
  "id": "line:069cacb",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "The eldest Frega looked down somberly.[p/] She didn't look defeated.[p/] It was something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:022280d",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "...Was it dread?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042225f",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Anyways,[p/] I'm a little curious about the Theocracy of Lumina..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca5f78",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Frankly,[p/] I'm surprised there's even [i]one[/i] heavensborn living in Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c37929",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: How did your bloodline even find its way here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02974f6",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose I don't really know."
}

{
  "id": "line:026c8b8",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: My mother never told me much about our ancestry."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b3b77",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: That makes sense...[p/] If the Church of Bahamut knew what you were,[p/] they would have definitely hunted you down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3ebe1",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "And the last thing I needed was [i]another[/i] faction that wanted to kill me."
}

{
  "id": "line:007d054",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Anyways,[p/] travel into and out of Wyverngarde is technically illegal, and I doubt Lord Steelwind would make an exemption for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:044f665",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: After all,[p/] House Steelwind suffered the most during the Great Luminite War.[p/] Lucio might as well be a veteran of that conflict."
}

{
  "id": "line:05d97ba",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tracker: ...\"Veteran\"?"
}

{
  "id": "line:091237e",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tracker: ...Vet?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0750f6c",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe: Oh no...[p/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0133988",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tracker: No![p/][s/] I hate the vet![p/][s/] I'm not going!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0747863",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tracker: You'll never take me alive!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad5413",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tracker: [i]ARF ARF ARF ARF ARF[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c68635",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "We all watched as Tracker frantically ran through the garden,[p/] trampling several flowers and barking loudly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcdc02",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Laefe chased after him as he began accosting a passing knight."
}

{
  "id": "line:07f8bb1",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Miriam: I should go help her."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bb05f",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's almost 2:00 PM, anyways.[p/] We should head to the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:053293b",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thanks for answering my questions, Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0811dff",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let me know if there's anything I can do to help you with this Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd5e27",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: She's closer than you think."
}

{
  "id": "line:0218123",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: There's nothing you can do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef7050",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: Try not to look so defeated.[p/] It's almost time for the main event."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c70d7e",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Why did you bring me here?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04a7685",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: Oh,[p/] who knows?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb8feb",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: Whatever you're planning to make me do...[p/] Please."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee7ea6",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: [i]Please[/i] don't make me harm my sisters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c802ed",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: You're in no position to make demands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c4cf5c",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Eris: You'll just have to wait and see for yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:01df13b",
  "node": "Check_Events_GardenIntro",
  "text": "Beatrice: ...Stay safe, heavensborn."
}

{
  "id": "line:094dbd2",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "In the kingdom of Wyverngarde,[p/] there was a gulf between what was lawful and what was just."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bea7ec",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "People suffered.[p/] People died.[p/] All on behalf of the corrupt powers that ruled over us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbeab7",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "The lord of Kornhaven was drunk on the power of his station.[p/] He killed his friend the moment that power was threatened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b7aa6c",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "The headmaster of the Academy was cruelly thrown away—[p/]forced to realize that he built his legacy on borrowed authority.[p/] He committed unforgivable acts to cling to it."
}

{
  "id": "line:06a966d",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "To the Duke of Commerce,[p/] his people were no different than the gold within his coffers.[p/] In his hunger,[p/] he nearly sacrificed hundreds to sit upon a hollow throne."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f8f99",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Frega's inheritor had ambitions of grandeur and had proven herself worthy.[p/] Yet she was stripped of her power all the same.[p/] It drove her to seek liberation in hell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db6aa9",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Even the evilest demons were not responsible for the rot within Wyverngarde.[p/] They only revealed what was always there."
}

{
  "id": "line:031bd44",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "People feared becoming prey,[p/] and that anxiety suffocated them.[p/] Reality had always demanded compromise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba8b04",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "Some learned to numb themselves.[p/] Some learned how to exploit the world's cruelty.[p/] Some felt desperate enough to sell their souls to the devil."
}

{
  "id": "line:040fd3e",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "It was a rigged game,[p/] and sometimes virtues like \"law\" or \"justice\" felt so alien that they might as well have been fiction."
}

{
  "id": "line:010fea0",
  "node": "Start",
  "text": "...Even if they were,[p/] I wanted to embody those ideals all the same."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1b0c",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: It's almost noon.[p/] Are you going to get out of bed?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b442de",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "I shifted under my blanket.[p/] Leaving its warm embrace would surely kill me."
}

{
  "id": "line:039dc4e",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "I had to admit I couldn't spend the rest of my life in this bed.[p/] Eventually,[p/] I'd have to return to the world to do...[p/] anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad0eb7",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "But I wasn't going to knock over the first domino in that chain—[p/]not yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0084042",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Someone is actually here to see you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e99bcc",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'm not interested.[p/] I'm taking another mental health day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb9507",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: At the rate you're going,[p/] it's going to turn into a mental health [i]month[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cefed2",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: I get that you're feeling down,[p/] but you've got to get out there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c10460",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: We can't keep freeloading off of Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d0150",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why not?[p/] Isn't her family rich?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a1f806",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Aria: That's a bit rude,[p/] but I suppose I can overlook it this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:010ffaf",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Steelwind?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0375868",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "My long-time rival walked into my room.[p/] I immediately rolled out of bed and fell to the floor trying to avoid her eyeline."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d42df9",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "I had my pride,[p/] and she was the last person I wanted to see me like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:099755b",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Lying on the floor,[p/] I tried my best to brush my hair through my hands.[p/] After a while,[p/] I just stood up."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c4069",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion...![p/][s/] Pants!"
}

{
  "id": "line:05677be",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right![p/][s/] Sorry!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09594cd",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Steelwind winced as she politely turned her head away.[p/] She and Celeste walked out of the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc5422",
  "node": "Start2",
  "text": "Aria: ...We'll give you some time to ready yourself."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be6673",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Aria: That was certainly...[p/] something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5484c",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not great,[p/] but I don't know what else to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df9c91",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Celeste: I've just been protecting the house until he snaps himself out of it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeac26",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Aria: ...Have there been any incidents with intruders?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca9b7d",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Celeste: Nope.[p/] I expected the Eyetaker to send [i]someone[/i],[p/] but the streets have been quiet."
}

{
  "id": "line:0053196",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Celeste: Maybe they know your people are watching the house?"
}

{
  "id": "line:014f543",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Aria: We'll just have to hope that will be enough of a deterrent."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ec20c6",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Have you seen Ruby lately?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2cb1a",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Aria: I have.[p/] She's still practicing.[p/] I've even faced her in a few trials."
}

{
  "id": "line:0216bf6",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Aria: I think she might be colder than usual,[p/] but it's hard to tell with her disposition."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c692fb",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I don't know what to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:07c60e8",
  "node": "Start3",
  "text": "Aria: It might be best to give both of them time.[p/] A lot has happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0108282",
  "node": "Start4",
  "text": "After taking some time to wash my face and clean my hair,[p/] I walked downstairs to my living room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccc4a5",
  "node": "Start4",
  "text": "Celeste and Steelwind were sitting at the dining table."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b80e",
  "node": "Start4",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/][s/]Sorry about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09633a6",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "There was a bookshelf filled with several fantasy fiction novels."
}

{
  "id": "line:081b39d",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "There were actually a lot of books from several series that I was followed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfc2aa",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I never got a chance to look at this painting the last time we were here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db338f",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He looks like some kind of crime lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb13f1",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "Knight: I think that's one of the [i]previous[/i] Eyetakers."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ef269",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "Knight: Back then,[p/] he had an even [i]tighter[/i] grip on the criminal underbelly of Ratholme."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3d771",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "Knight: People used to call him The Raging Storm."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1a69c",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But isn't \"Eyetaker\" [i]already[/i] a nickname?"
}

{
  "id": "line:059f2b1",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "Knight: Look, sir.[p/] [i]I[/i] don't come up with these names."
}

{
  "id": "line:0333e05",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "The fireplace hadn't been lit in a while,[p/] but I could still see the burnt ashes of some documents."
}

{
  "id": "line:041f54d",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "I could see the back alley entrance from this window."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e57cdb",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "The Eyetaker must have used this to get a good look at anyone approaching his hideout."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab6871",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "This was the table where the Eyetaker sat."
}

{
  "id": "line:044aa7e",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "There was a thick layer of dust on it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0186ff5",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "There were several fantasy novels stacked on the desk."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef7e7a",
  "node": "Examine_Mafia2",
  "text": "The Eyetaker must've been a fan of the genre."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad92dc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Celeste: There's no one here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa7165",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "I kicked one of the nearby tables in frustration.[p/] Several books fell to the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:090a067",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Of [i]course[/i] he wasn't here.[p/] I betrayed him after being brought to his hideout."
}

{
  "id": "line:0443b0a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "I took a close look at the desk he was sitting at during our previous visit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc3b87",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "He must have moved his operation elsewhere the day I convicted Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:00341b4",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Celeste: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] I guess there's no point in staying hidden anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca8ccb",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Celeste tossed away the Kingsguard's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:01507d0",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "A few seconds later,[p/] I heard the footfalls of soldiers rushing towards our location."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5d223",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Knight: Freeze in the name of the Wyverngarde—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f12092",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "He and the other knights froze as they saw the empty room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c35281",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Knight: ...Be careful, Sir.[p/][s/] I believe they're magically disguising themselves as furniture!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a655e2",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're not [i]here[/i], you idiot!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bc520",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Knight: ...Ah."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d058a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "I let out a frustrated breath as I took a seat on a chair nearby."
}

{
  "id": "line:070a8cc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "It launched a cloud of dust into the air."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e86d9",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He was the last piece we needed..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1b73e",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: None of the other suspects had the means or the motive to do this."
}

{
  "id": "line:070bf26",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He's probably long gone by now...[p/] It's over."
}

{
  "id": "line:03bef1a",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sorry, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0f877",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Celeste: But you did everything you could, didn't you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbd804",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What do we do now?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03f7a76",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There [i]has[/i] to be someone who knows where he is."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c94818",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "...A thought came to my head,[p/] but I didn't like it."
}

{
  "id": "line:00873f7",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...There is [i]one[/i] person who might know where he is."
}

{
  "id": "line:01272cc",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Celeste: Wait,[p/] you don't mean..."
}

{
  "id": "line:09992cd",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...At this point,[p/] it's the only option we have."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc77ab",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Celeste: Are you sure?[p/] You two aren't exactly—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ddb889",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but I can't let my personal feelings get in the way of saving Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:0124a04",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "I wasn't looking forward to this...[p/] But at the same time,[p/] I was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9660b",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "It didn't matter.[p/] I had a job to do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0210634",
  "node": "Check_Events_Mafia2",
  "text": "The client came first.[p/] [i]She[/i] was the one who taught me that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0626fb2",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's a chalk outline where Pierce's body probably was."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd9dab",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It looks like he was sitting against this altar when he died."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f2618",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: This blood stain seems to imply that the fatal wound came from his chest."
}

{
  "id": "line:03eb398",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: An autopsy report would really be helpful here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:01af00f",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "I needed to ask the Commander for a copy of it the next time I saw him."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f0b75",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Trans"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5964d",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/]Oh, right![p/] There's a trace of [b]transmutation[/b] here."
}

{
  "id": "line:05389eb",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: It's all over the area around his body."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9f7ac",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Interesting...[p/] Did the murderer wound him using a [b]transmutation[/b] spell?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0721a13",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Detect Sleep"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3b95a",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: There are traces of [b]conjuration[/b] magic all over the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:088912d",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That must have been left by Beatrice's [b]Sleep[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe9804",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Lantern"
}

{
  "id": "line:0495648",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are lanterns hanging around the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:01193c0",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They're still lit."
}

{
  "id": "line:057f41f",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are three stained glass windows."
}

{
  "id": "line:071a3c1",
  "node": "Examine_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They look quite nice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfa7f0",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Player: The Fight with Steelwind"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c59d7e",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Let's review what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:004c093",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Before Beatrice knocked me out,[p/] we heard a commotion outside,[p/] and you went to investigate."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c5841",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Can you tell me more about your fight with Steelwind?[p/] What was she like?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3c790",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/]Well,[p/] she wasn't her usual self.[p/] It's like she was in some kind of daze."
}

{
  "id": "line:032a4c5",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I...[p/] noticed it even before she attacked me.[p/] Something was wrong with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b819fe",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: She didn't even respond to me when I tried to talk to her.[p/] It's like she didn't even recognize me."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b7502",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But from what Lord Asclepius said,[p/] she would've been acting more erratically if she was affected by Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0095a78",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's possible that you fought someone disguised as her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0136809",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I guess that's possible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1087c",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I've sparred with her before,[p/] and this was definitely different."
}

{
  "id": "line:004f655",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: But [i]whoever[/i] they were,[p/] their magic was still extremely powerful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0325f14",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And several members of the four Pillar Families were assembled here."
}

{
  "id": "line:01bff56",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: It could have been one of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a82b9e",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should speak with Commander White when we get the chance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc1726",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: The Grand Cathedral was closed to the public for...[p/] [i]whatever[/i] was happening here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0041992",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: They probably have a list of everyone who was present when the murders happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1990e",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "That meant that whoever did this was one of the nobles who was here today."
}

{
  "id": "line:020ff0a",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Beatrice can cast [b]Invisibility[/b] so I doubt she'd [i]let[/i] you see her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0137440",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But did you see her at any point when you were fighting Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07582c9",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Sorry,[p/] I don't know.[p/] I was too focused on staying alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0572e05",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've actually been meaning to ask you about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:024ba9c",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Aren't you [i]really[/i] strong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0480bc1",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've never even seen you break a sweat in a fight before."
}

{
  "id": "line:013dac8",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Well...[p/] She was [i]really[/i] tough.[p/] It was terrifying, honestly."
}

{
  "id": "line:0503c84",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I've sparred with her before,[p/] but never with magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bae3ea",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I've never fought someone with spells that powerful before."
}

{
  "id": "line:050fcaa",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...She didn't hurt you, did she?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba55e5",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: No,[p/] but it got pretty close."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fbbcb",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I think she realized that she couldn't beat me.[p/] So she just ran past me and into the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:041745c",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...So her [i]real[/i] target was Pierce...[p/] But why?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0615e44",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Did you see the moment she murdered Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:002dfaf",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/]No...[p/] When I arrived at the Prayer Room,[p/] I saw you and Steelwind unconscious on the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:05daf1e",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Pierce was already dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0514569",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I'm assuming you didn't see Beatrice anywhere?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb5e88",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...No.[p/] She wasn't there when I arrived."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c0ed2",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "How did she leave the Prayer Room without Celeste noticing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:062d610",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Did she turn herself invisible?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d39672",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Player: Timeline"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc3bd5",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: We showed up at the Prayer Room for the meeting at 1:50 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:04021e1",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then we interrogated Pierce for about half an hour."
}

{
  "id": "line:018ef30",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That's when we heard that commotion outside,[p/] and you went to investigate it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15a46",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: And I think Beatrice knocked me and Pierce out ten minutes after that."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c91d7",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: How long did you fight Steelwind before she pushed past you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0566c66",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...We definitely fought for a while.[p/] It must have been at least...[p/] twenty minutes?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d3f21",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...After that,[p/] she gave up on fighting me and ran into the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d7a2d",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Which means that Beatrice somehow got into the room [i]during[/i] your fight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb22d1",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: That discounts my theory of [i]her[/i] disguising herself as Steelwind."
}

{
  "id": "line:005d1ea",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": ":I regained consciousness at 3:12 PM.[p/] That meant that I was knocked out for more than forty minutes."
}

{
  "id": "line:050a4b6",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "There were still a lot of unknowns about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0847d6e",
  "node": "Talk_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "I'd need all the pieces if I wanted to set the board."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f3dca",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste, it's my Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea9903",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Oh, sorry![p/][s/] I was just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a43f36",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: The Runestone is very nice, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c26b5f",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you sure you're okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6b297",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I'm only a little drowsy from that [b]Sleep[/b] spell."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d53a8a",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...You shouldn't push yourself if you feel tired."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0eab7",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm sure the Kingsguard are fully capable of investigating what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0baa111",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "She had a point,[p/] but considering who the victims were,[p/] whoever orchestrated this must be high on the political hierarchy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a54bef",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Any of the nobles here could have done this.[p/] The only person I could trust was Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2d429",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hey...[p/] Are you okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0063a85",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0461362",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've been a little...[p/] shaken up since the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be28f9",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:03fddce",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: When I saw you lying next to Pierce's body,[p/] I thought you were—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02f2655",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/]Sorry.[p/] I didn't mean to worry you so much."
}

{
  "id": "line:0382c37",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I'm okay now.[p/] I'm not hurt."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c9399",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah...[p/] I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0736056",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I know Steelwind would never do something like this...[p/] But I [i]saw[/i] her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db79ea",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: Even if she wasn't her usual self,[p/] her attacks were definitely real."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd6e62",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't know what to believe anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:002fd63",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: All the more reason for us to get to the bottom of this."
}

{
  "id": "line:095d9d8",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't believe after everything he did,[p/] Pierce is just...[p/] gone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b483fa",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry we couldn't get the answers you were looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df1714",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hopefully,[p/] something else turns up."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcf6ed",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I honestly don't care about that anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d187e",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm just glad you're alive and safe."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c1b2d",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Tyrion: What can you tell me about this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c5194",
  "node": "Present_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste: S-[p/][s/]Sorry...[p/] I don't think I'll be of much help with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be96da",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "It was time to MOVE somewhere else.[p/] I needed to visit the other crime scenes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a85df4",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "We arrived at the Prayer Room.[p/] It was now swarming with knights from the Inquisition."
}

{
  "id": "line:07dc547",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "I found myself staring at the chalk outline of where Pierce's body once was."
}

{
  "id": "line:097e932",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Now was not the time for an existential crisis...[p/] Steelwind's future counted on us figuring out what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c06f8e",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "The Inquisition believes that Steelwind broke into this room,[p/] knocked out Pierce and me,[p/] and then killed him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1f0c5",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "But I remembered it clearly...[p/] I [i]saw[/i] Beatrice before I lost consciousness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b12077",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "There was something else happening here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aed719",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "Celeste also fought Steelwind after Beatrice knocked me out."
}

{
  "id": "line:05aa604",
  "node": "Check_Events_PrayerRoom1",
  "text": "She could tell me more about how she was acting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b4e84b",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Tyrion: Are you ready?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfbe88",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0927bbd",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: At least...[p/] I [i]hope[/i] so."
}

{
  "id": "line:0449fa0",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Tyrion: You can stand guard outside if you want."
}

{
  "id": "line:0951f70",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Tyrion: I only need a few moments to look into his mind."
}

{
  "id": "line:015232e",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: No.[p/] [i]I'm[/i] the one who asked you to do this,[p/] and I'm not going to leave you alone with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b1ff4",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03bac9d",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Yeah?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00f1f19",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: Thank you for coming here with me.[p/] It really means a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6d0d3",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Tyrion: Honestly,[p/] I think I just needed an excuse to leave the house."
}

{
  "id": "line:0283b1a",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: It's not just this.[p/] You're always looking out for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a10cd0",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: You got me acquitted.[p/] You helped me see the truth behind my dad."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c9186",
  "node": "HitTheFan",
  "text": "Celeste: It feels like I can never repay that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0422e9c",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f62376",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: For the past few months,[p/] all I've been [i]doing[/i] is relying on you."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d8893",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Celeste,[p/] I was going to tell you something at the Lords' Ball."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efbba5",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/][s/] Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cff6b3",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't really know how to say it,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:096b8fc",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]Wait...[p/][s/] We're talking about this [i]now[/i]?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e9e8f1",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I feel like something always happens, so—[p/][s/] Uh—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0249d93",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "I took a deep breath."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff921e",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0977fda",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "The words trailed off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1610d",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] you are—[p/] ...You are [i]very[/i]—[p/] ...Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ba75b4",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Damn it all.[p/] It was happening again."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a5700",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Come on![p/][s/] I [i]knew[/i] what I wanted to say,[p/] and I was fairly certain she felt the same way!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0522115",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "I took in one last breath.[p/] Air filled my lungs.[p/] My heart was pounding.[p/] Sweat was beginning to form under every crevice of my suit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2f0c8",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": ":But I pushed everything from my mind:[p/] the fear,[p/] the anxiety,[p/] the hesitation from leaping over the chasm.[p/] I steeled my resolve."
}

{
  "id": "line:0298925",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": ":I was Tyrion motherfucking Cuthbert![p/][s/] I wouldn't let anyone stand in my way:[p/] man,[p/] king,[p/] or god,[p/] but most of all, myself!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c4deb",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: CELESTE MCCOY![p/] I LOVE—"
}

{
  "id": "line:052c3b9",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Steelwind?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0f18d",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Celeste: A-[p/][s/]Ah![p/][s/] Aria?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f4c572",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Celeste: How long have you been standing there?! [h=\"Are you serious|right now, Aria?!\" e=\"afh\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:04c9b57",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Aria: W-[p/][s/]Well...[p/] I knew you'd be here around this time. [h=\"I'm [i]so[/i] sorry!|I didn't know what to do and froze!\" e=\"sf\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:078574d",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Aria: I wanted to wish you luck,[p/] but then you two seemed to be in the middle of...[p/] something."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f90d",
  "node": "HitTheFan2",
  "text": "Aria: ...I was going to leave,[p/] but then I got worried I'd draw attention to myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:09bc723",
  "node": "HitTheFan2a",
  "text": "Aria: D-[p/][s/]Don't stop on my account."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0fb38",
  "node": "HitTheFan2a",
  "text": "Aria: I-[p/][s/]I'll just get out of your way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0946832",
  "node": "HitTheFan2a",
  "text": "Aria: T-[p/][s/]Thank you..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c164d1",
  "node": "HitTheFan2a",
  "text": "Aria: Um...[p/] Good luck..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dee066",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "...A part of me [i]really[/i] wanted to know what she saw,[p/] but [i]one[/i] of us had to exercise some self-restraint."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caff5a",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Any winds I had in my sails were gone.[p/] There was nothing left to push me forward."
}

{
  "id": "line:092e99e",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "She just silently walked over to me and planted a kiss on my cheek."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad1fc5",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "I jumped back.[p/] My hand went to where her lips had made contact."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3be63",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "She just swayed playfully and giggled as she watched the embarrassed look on my face."
}

{
  "id": "line:05aad7a",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion,[p/] I already know."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f85330",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Y-[p/][s/]You do?![p/] Then—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8fede",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Celeste: But I'm still not saying it before you do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e595f4",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Celeste: You've been stringing me along for a month.[p/] That's what you get."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d414d1",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: Fine.[p/] I guess that's fair."
}

{
  "id": "line:04e4917",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "I looked at the time.[p/] The time of the meeting was approaching."
}

{
  "id": "line:04b9ff8",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...We're going to be late."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d6929",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Celeste: It's fine.[p/] There's always next time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9881e",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "Honestly,[p/] this next part would be far easier than saying those words."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb9c7c",
  "node": "HitTheFan2b",
  "text": "I straightened my tie and wiped the sweat from my brow before entering the Prayer Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b05b58",
  "node": "HitTheFan3",
  "text": "Celeste: What's going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0267504",
  "node": "HitTheFan3",
  "text": "Eris: ...And so the [i]final[/i] act begins."
}

{
  "id": "line:09520f2",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "Aster: Please, Grand General,[p/] I think you're overreacting."
}

{
  "id": "line:04ae91a",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "Aster: I'm sure this is just a practical joke."
}

{
  "id": "line:07545e3",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "The Grand General ignored him and continued taking swings at the forcefield with his greataxe."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ed6b1",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "Aster: Lucio,[p/] you are well aware that you can't destroy this cage with brute force."
}

{
  "id": "line:015f233",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "Lucio: [i]*sigh*[/i][p/] This accursed spell.[p/] It's a nuisance every time I come across it."
}

{
  "id": "line:059a47e",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "Knight: ..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9b1b8",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "Lucio: You![p/] What are you doing away from your post?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cb3788",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "The knight said nothing in response.[p/] He left the room through the east exit."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a373f2",
  "node": "Massacre",
  "text": "Aster: How suspicious..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7fc59",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: ...Where [i]are[/i] they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:057e922",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Miriam: Of [i]all[/i] the times for those two to disappear..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cc0c1",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: ...You don't think she's trying to escape, do you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd431e",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Miriam: Honestly,[p/] I wouldn't put it past—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ac0e07",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Lazarick: Hey..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e6f60",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: Lord Asclepius,[p/] did you find Beatrice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0058503",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Lazarick: I didn't,[p/] but there's something else."
}

{
  "id": "line:092a4d2",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Lazarick: Someone just trapped His Majesty in a [b]Force Cage[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f83d9d",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Miriam: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0df47",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: Oh no,[p/] did Beatrice—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ed8ad",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Miriam: Is [b]Force Cage[b/] even in her Compendium?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0721646",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Lazarick: ...Either way,[p/] I think it's safer if we reconvene with the others in the Nave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aab0d5",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Lazarick: The Kingsguard are forming a perimeter while they wait for the [b]Force Cage[/b] to disappear.[p/] We'll be safe there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c1bb60",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Lazarick: She'll be fine.[p/] She always is."
}

{
  "id": "line:088da16",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: ...I suppose you're right."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b1d86",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: Tracker,[p/] let's go."
}

{
  "id": "line:095c2c4",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Tracker said nothing.[p/] He was growling at the pathway leading north."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f15cc",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: Tracker,[p/] I said let's go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f15cc2",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Tracker: ...I smell evil rats."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e0a2c",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Laefe: You can chase the rats after the funeral.[p/] Let's go."
}

{
  "id": "line:048a386",
  "node": "FregaMassacre",
  "text": "Tracker: Yes, Queen..."
}

{
  "id": "line:06246d0",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "The Duke and the Minister turned the corner and fled into the Common Room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0507501",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Their assailant wasn't far behind,[p/] but hopefully,[p/] they'd lost her."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f99cd",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Coraline: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] This must be some mistake."
}

{
  "id": "line:05eceee",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Coraline: I know Ms. Steelwind.[p/] She would never do this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf7266",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Lloyd: We can't think about that now!"
}

{
  "id": "line:035adc4",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Lloyd: We'll just have to hope that she won't think to look here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3c4ab",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Lloyd tried to check Coraline for any wounds,[p/] but she just slapped his hand away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efd665",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Coraline: Lloyd,[p/] just teleport away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f064f4",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Coraline: Choose a place where your Mageblight won't hurt anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f154da",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Lloyd: I am [i]not[/i] leaving you alone with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0098eea",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Coraline: ...Do you think your recklessness will earn my forgiveness?[p/] Just go."
}

{
  "id": "line:090bb9e",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Lloyd: Damn it all...[p/] She's coming."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edc169",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Aria Steelwind turned the corner and stood at the room's north entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15ad6",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "She walked towards the two Pillar Lords without a word or hint of emotion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5861d",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Coraline: Aria, please.[p/] I don't know what your father told you,[p/] but there [i]has[/i] to be another way."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a88f8",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Coraline: We don't need to give in to our primal urges."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b4ef9",
  "node": "LloydMassacre",
  "text": "Lloyd: You are just another bloodthirsty Steelwind![p/][s/] You barbarians have [i]no[/i] place in our kingdom!"
}

{
  "id": "line:063cbb4",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Coraline: Lloyd,[p/] look out!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c7a431",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Coraline tackled Lloyd as she foresaw an attack from behind."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b81dba",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "The crossbow bolt would have pierced Lloyd's heart if she hadn't acted."
}

{
  "id": "line:05595bc",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Instead,[p/] the bolt pinned itself in the back of Coraline's shoulder."
}

{
  "id": "line:0164845",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Lloyd: C-[p/][s/]Coraline..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d2d3",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Coraline: I-[p/][s/]It's fine.[p/] I can heal this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca950d",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Aster: Well,[p/] we can't have that, can we?"
}

{
  "id": "line:090a76c",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "The shooter stepped into the room from the south entrance,[p/] crossbow in hand."
}

{
  "id": "line:05436d2",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Aria had done a wonderful job of driving the two of them here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0ca68",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Damn it all![p/][s/] Is [i]this[/i] your accomplice?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04e9432",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Lloyd: Show us your face, you coward!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03574c3",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "The assassin said nothing and aimed his crossbow at the two of them."
}

{
  "id": "line:05462de",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Lloyd stayed silent,[p/] but suddenly started breathing more heavily and haggardly."
}

{
  "id": "line:00569c5",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Lloyd: AGGGGGH!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f58d3",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "The Duke of Commerce turned around and tackled Aria to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5a252",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "Again,[p/] her face was blank.[p/] She didn't seem to be bothered at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc4bbf",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "All she did was struggle to break the Duke's grip on her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06da950",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "The assassin was about to shoot,[p/] but cursed under his breath once Aria was brought into the line of fire."
}

{
  "id": "line:04d3f19",
  "node": "LloydMassacre2",
  "text": "It wasn't her time yet.[p/] She needed to live through this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cefcf9",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Lloyd cursed at himself.[p/] Even [i]he[/i] was wondering what he was doing.[p/][s/] It was as if his body had moved on its own."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfd73e",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "For that matter,[p/] why had he refused to teleport away as Coraline asked?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09ee027",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "He [i]had[/i] a bunker specifically [i]designed[/i] for this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0086737",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "No one would have blamed him![p/][s/] He wasn't [i]meant[/i] for combat!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e07a52",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Those thoughts were spinning around in his head,[p/] but they were being pushed away,[p/] overwritten by something he had never felt before."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d83d2",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Lloyd: Coraline![p/][s/] Run![p/][s/] Get away from here!"
}

{
  "id": "line:068875b",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Coraline: But—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:019f537",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Lloyd: GO!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0106ddb",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "The Minister hesitated,[p/] but her survival instincts won over in the end."
}

{
  "id": "line:010608a",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "She ran past Lloyd,[p/] who was keeping Aria pinned to the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a353f8",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "She cried as she ran in terror.[p/] The assassin leveled his crossbow at her."
}

{
  "id": "line:040948d",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "The Duke growled in defiance.[p/] He shoved Aria away and formed a cross with his arms."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a73ca",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Lloyd: [b]Terprotec[b/]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8dc96",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "A thin stone layer suddenly formed to cover the entirety of the Minister of Justice's body."
}

{
  "id": "line:08d910e",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "A crossbow bolt whistled past Lloyd,[p/] but it bounced off of Coraline's hardened skin.[p/] She had gotten away."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d665fb",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Aster: ...[b]Stone Skin[/b] doesn't require concentration, does it?[p/] Not bad, Lloyd."
}

{
  "id": "line:09085cb",
  "node": "LloydMassacre3",
  "text": "Lloyd: Who the hell are you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00cb113",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "The assassin flicked his head toward the hallway that Coraline ran to.[p/] Aria immediately stood up."
}

{
  "id": "line:03a2cbb",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "Aster: Aria,[p/] end her.[p/] I'll handle the Duke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6c6fa",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "Without a word,[p/] Aria sprinted from the Common Room to pursue her prey."
}

{
  "id": "line:09439e1",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "The assassin just shook his head in disbelief as he leisurely began to load another bolt into his crossbow."
}

{
  "id": "line:02ecaf9",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "Aster: ...Scaled Lord, Lloyd.[p/] When did [i]you[/i] grow a spine?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e176f2",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "Lloyd: H-[p/][s/]Ha![p/][s/] What do [i]I[/i] have to fear from you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:022fa42",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "Lloyd: I am Lloyd von Sanctus:[p/][s/] the Duke of Commerce and Master of [b]Abjuration[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a14233",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "Lloyd: So come on![p/][s/] It's time you learned your place, you wretch!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0baf030",
  "node": "LloydMassacre4",
  "text": "...For the first and last time in his life,[p/] Lloyd von Sanctus stood his ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc2ffc",
  "node": "HitTheFan3a",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on![p/][s/] Just tell us the truth, Pierce!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b52c0c",
  "node": "HitTheFan3a",
  "text": "Garrick: You are the [i]last[/i] person I would give this information to!"
}

{
  "id": "line:08b51d8",
  "node": "HitTheFan3a",
  "text": "He was getting more and more stressed,[p/] and it was even easier than last time."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e6895",
  "node": "HitTheFan3a",
  "text": "Just a little more and I would—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbb884",
  "node": "HitTheFan3a",
  "text": "A crash rang out from outside."
}

{
  "id": "line:0093a5d",
  "node": "HitTheFan3a",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcdfa7",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...I'm going to take a look.[p/] Stay here and keep the door closed."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e0fe0",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Garrick: W-[p/][s/]What?![p/][s/] Are you just going to [i]leave[/i] us here?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0773c3c",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Tyrion: H-[p/][s/]He's right.[p/] We don't know what's going on."
}

{
  "id": "line:093f475",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should stay together."
}

{
  "id": "line:028c409",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Celeste: Don't worry.[p/] There were two guards outside,[p/] and they're from the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:0afb683",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Celeste: You'll be fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0751b69",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...That's not what I'm worried about."
}

{
  "id": "line:088c472",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Celeste: Trust me, Tyrion.[p/] When have I ever lost a fight?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0704b78",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "She had a point..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b09fd5",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Fine.[p/] Just be careful."
}

{
  "id": "line:0803991",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah, yeah..."
}

{
  "id": "line:043d648",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Garrick: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02d766f",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "It had been almost ten minutes since Celeste went to investigate the noise."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dffa4",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "I wanted to open the door and check on her,[p/] but she told me to keep the door closed."
}

{
  "id": "line:00b00f9",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "The last time I disobeyed her orders,[p/] I got taken hostage and made her job ten times more difficult."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c4847",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Pierce seemed extremely on edge.[p/] He was sitting at one of the tables and impatiently tapped on the wood with his fingers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c6d1d0",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Tyrion: So,[p/] you never intended to send that letter to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02f03c9",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who [i]did[/i] you send it to, then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fed308",
  "node": "HitTheFan4",
  "text": "Garrick: Oh,[p/] as if I would ever tell [i]you[/i] that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e8f13e",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Luckily for me,[p/] he had accumulated enough stress by now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a21f04",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Garrick: W-[p/][s/]What?[p/] Why are you looking at me like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6e256",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if I wasn't the intended recipient,[p/] you said that you [i]knew[/i] who Celeste's biological parents are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b90537",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Who are they?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a03200",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Garrick: A-[p/][s/]Are you seriously focused on that [i]now[/i]?! [h=\"It's far too important.|It's my only bargaining chip.\" e=\"f\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee604c",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "One last push."
}

{
  "id": "line:07be5e4",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Answer the question, Pierce,[p/] or I'll reveal this letter to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0672504",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Garrick: ...What was that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0258a22",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Beatrice: [b]Somniah[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b153d6",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "Tyrion: W-[p/][s/]What...?[p/] What is this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b35b4f",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "A blue luminous vapor spilled into the room.[p/] It glittered with faint glints of magical light."
}

{
  "id": "line:08ea35e",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "As soon as it fell over me,[p/] I could feel my entire body becoming heavier."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b20545",
  "node": "HitTheFan5",
  "text": "I started to slump over.[p/] My body was being pulled toward the ground."
}

{
  "id": "line:054a806",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "Garrick: A [b]Sleep[/b] spell?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09a199b",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "Garrick: I-[p/][s/]I...[p/] I miscalculated..."
}

{
  "id": "line:083b4e5",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] If they got here,[p/] that means—"
}

{
  "id": "line:00c63e9",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ce...[p/]leste..."
}

{
  "id": "line:051a05a",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "I fought with everything I had to stay awake,[p/] but it was impossible."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f99c98",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "My eyes were closing on their own.[p/] It felt like my eyelids were being dragged down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ada1f2",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "I felt myself fade away,[p/] but I made one last desperate attempt to keep my eyes open."
}

{
  "id": "line:09795a9",
  "node": "HitTheFan6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Bea...[p/]trice?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b16848",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "I was drifting in sleep,[p/] but I soon heard a voice echoing in the distance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0467b82",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...rion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e39a0b",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Tyrion...!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f583d3",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Celeste: Tyrion![p/][s/] I'm so sorry![p/][s/] I should have listened to you!"
}

{
  "id": "line:093428e",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Celeste: I should have never left you alone with him![p/] I—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0afef37",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Hey, it's okay..."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fe7b4",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Tears were streaming down her face.[p/] I'd only ever seen her like this one other time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee5a3b",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "I held her head tightly against my chest.[p/] She was practically clinging to me,[p/] shuddering with each sob."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c4e0f",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "I just stayed quiet and embraced her as she cried in relief."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f958d",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How long was I out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d2c745",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "I scanned the room,[p/] realizing that there were other people here with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0671b59",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "Commander White was leading a group of knights.[p/] They all had their weapons drawn and were surrounding someone who was lying unconscious in the room with us."
}

{
  "id": "line:005fd51",
  "node": "AfterMurder2",
  "text": "It was Steelwind!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0650aa8",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Aster: Commander.[p/] I understand your position,[p/] but there [i]has[/i] to be another explanation."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d70a3c",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Orym: Look, Your Majesty.[p/][s/] I feel about this the same way you do."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a59428",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Orym: ...But it [i]has[/i] to be a case of Mageblight."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acde24",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "I looked around the room and saw a pool of blood at the end of one of the tables.[p/] There was even a chalk outline around it already."
}

{
  "id": "line:048917e",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "A horrible realization came over me."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f9147",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...?[p/] Where's Pierce?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7709c",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "She just looked away from me,[p/] tears welling up in her eyes again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bcf028",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Orym: I don't know how to tell you this, kid,[p/] but he's dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce344c",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Orym: Honestly,[p/] consider yourself lucky you're in one piece."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ef2e42",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Orym: Whatever you're paying the mage girl,[p/] it's not enough."
}

{
  "id": "line:0935cd3",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But who—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08a4abf",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "I looked at the knights who all had their weapons pointed at the prosecutor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe9d0f",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Tyrion: You think [i]Steelwind[/i] did this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0faa7ed",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Aster: It wasn't just Lord Pierce, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd3537",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Aster: We also found the bodies of Lord von Sanctus and Lady Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:08161d7",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Aster: All of us were attacked,[p/] and several members of the Kingsguard have gone comatose."
}

{
  "id": "line:01e03c0",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Orym: I don't want to believe it,[p/] but..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0515b94",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Orym: Several people saw Steelwind acting off at the scenes of [i]each[/i] of the murders."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0b6bb",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Aster: We also found her unconscious here."
}

{
  "id": "line:07066d4",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Aster: ...Pierce's body was lying next to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d56b2c",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No![p/][s/] It wasn't her!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1a097",
  "node": "AfterMurder3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]saw[/i] Beatrice before I passed out![p/][s/] [i]She[/i] was the one that knocked us out!"
}

{
  "id": "line:050bfa2",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Aster: Beatrice...?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0866211",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Orym: ...What the [i]hell[/i] is going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3e275",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Suddenly,[p/] the knights surrounding Steelwind began shouting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0759aeb",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "It looked like the Prosecutor had regained consciousness."
}

{
  "id": "line:0216c21",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Aria rose limply,[p/] still half-asleep.[p/] Her body was swaying,[p/] as if it were taking all of her energy to sit upright."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c50113",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Her eyes slowly scanned the room,[p/] noticing the knights who were surrounding her with their weapons drawn."
}

{
  "id": "line:032554f",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "She then noticed the blood on the floor.[p/] Her eyes became wide."
}

{
  "id": "line:0526fb8",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "She quickly raised the palms of her hands.[p/] Her gloves were dirty and ripped."
}

{
  "id": "line:081e0c0",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Aria: Commander White,[p/][s/] you need to put me in a holding cell!"
}

{
  "id": "line:032fe42",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Aria: It needs to be one with an [b]Anti-Magic Field[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07db794",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Orym: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a75941",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Aria: I'm not in control of my actions.[p/] We need to go [i]now[/i]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0540870",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Aria: [i]Now[/i] is not the time![p/][s/] Do it, Commander!"
}

{
  "id": "line:000c3cd",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Orym: R-[p/][s/]Right."
}

{
  "id": "line:0983dc9",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "She lay down flat on the ground,[p/] placing her hands on her head.[p/] Even in her own arrest,[p/] she was taking the lead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0480462",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "I watched as the Inquisition placed a pair of mantacles around her wrists."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9f7ac",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "We exchanged glances before she left the room.[p/] She just looked down, defeated."
}

{
  "id": "line:0898b59",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Damn it all...[p/] What [i]happened[/i]?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c19d95",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Aster: I know you have many questions, Mr. Cuthbert,[p/] but we should make sure that you're okay."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e05d1b",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] There's a necromancer in the Nave."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ae7267",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "I still had no idea what happened while I was asleep,[p/] but I could feel weariness still holding my body."
}

{
  "id": "line:06226ff",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": "They both helped me up.[p/] I made a note of the current time."
}

{
  "id": "line:008f7cf",
  "node": "AfterMurder4",
  "text": ":It was 3:12 PM."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15227",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "I arrived back at the Nave,[p/] meeting with the necromancer they were talking about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0953fc7",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "I couldn't stay still,[p/] not after discovering what had happened while I was asleep."
}

{
  "id": "line:0212504",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "But he only reprimanded me,[p/] telling me that I wouldn't be any good to anyone if I collapsed from an unseen injury."
}

{
  "id": "line:0daec38",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "...I couldn't really ARGUE against that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0816bb1",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: Nothing seems to be out of the ordinary.[p/] Except—"
}

{
  "id": "line:076649d",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Celeste: What?![p/][s/] What's wrong with him?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:095967c",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: If you would just let me [i]finish[/i]—"
}

{
  "id": "line:08f9f7c",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: —There appears to be a trace of [b]necromancy[/b] on you, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e569a4",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Tyrion: [b]Necromancy[/b]...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:054d485",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: It's probably nothing.[p/] Did your assistant cast any spells on you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0267c13",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Celeste: O-[p/][s/]Oh, right.[p/][s/] I used [b]Mend Wounds[/b] on him when I found him unconscious."
}

{
  "id": "line:074af09",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: Ah,[p/] I expected as much,[p/] but it never hurts to make sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d9f65c",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: Nothing seems out of the ordinary.[p/] You're quite healthy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6047a",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Celeste breathed a sigh of relief as she went to sit down at one of the benchs near the altar."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7ef14",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "She took a deep breath,[p/] allowing the knots in her shoulders to unravel."
}

{
  "id": "line:0efa727",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "She sat there for a while,[p/] eyes staring into space,[p/] waiting for the feeling to pass."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bc494",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: It seems like the only thing that hit you was that [b]Sleep[/b] spell.[p/] Consider yourself lucky."
}

{
  "id": "line:06d4d82",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: She didn't even think to check you before trying to heal you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0605e91",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: I'd expect a bodyguard to keep a more level head."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c932a",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "I just narrowed my eyes at him and said nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:05743ce",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: ...But I guess no one is ever prepared for when these things happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:08011cf",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: [i]I[/i] definitely wasn't."
}

{
  "id": "line:0792cc6",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: You should be fine to go about your business,[p/] but feel free to speak with me again if you experience anything out of the ordinary."
}

{
  "id": "line:0809e09",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Thank you.[p/] Um—"
}

{
  "id": "line:085c5f7",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: I am Lord Lazarick Asclepius,[p/] of House Asclepius."
}

{
  "id": "line:0095731",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "He was wrapped in a large cloak.[p/] Every part of him was covered except his face."
}

{
  "id": "line:016bf0e",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "At first,[p/] I found him to be a bit too blunt and standoffish,[p/] but it seemed to come from a place of caring."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e6db7b",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "When he checked my body for injuries,[p/] his hands and eyes moved efficiently and not carelessly."
}

{
  "id": "line:013cd97",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "He looked like someone who was passionate about his work and nothing else."
}

{
  "id": "line:011437b",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: And there are no thanks needed.[p/] My apprentice apparently owes you a lot."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a24d3a",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Tyrion: \"Apprentice\"...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0243b12",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Lazarick: Wallace Nightgrave.[p/] He said he was one of your clients a few months ago."
}

{
  "id": "line:0caeaa5",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh, right.[p/] Steelwind [i]did[/i] mention that she introduced you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c448c3",
  "node": "AfterMurder5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Speaking of,[p/] I'm finding it difficult to believe that she did this."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c2c5a",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: Mageblight isn't exactly a [i]benign[/i] condition."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3dc0e",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: When it takes hold of a mage,[p/] it doesn't matter [i]what[/i] kind of person they are."
}

{
  "id": "line:0576917",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: Violent behavior is almost always a result of the rage-filled delirium it puts them in."
}

{
  "id": "line:010ddeb",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: It's unfortunate,[p/] but mages have to be held responsible when cases like this happen."
}

{
  "id": "line:000750e",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...[i]Unless[/i] someone is framing her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bc99a4",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion...[p/] I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e82118",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Celeste: I fought her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0952c79",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you remember back when we heard that weird sound?[p/] I went outside to see what was going on."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ff33ea",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Celeste: I saw her standing over a bunch of unconscious guards."
}

{
  "id": "line:0da47ba",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Celeste: I tried to ask her what was going on,[p/] but she didn't say anything.[p/] She just attacked me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0238ebf",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Celeste: She was so cold and emotionless.[p/] It almost looked like she was sleepwalking."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e0e05",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: That's...[p/] [i]actually[/i] pretty strange."
}

{
  "id": "line:0919c44",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: When someone is affected by Mageblight,[p/] they enter a state of extreme psychosis and rage."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1f66e",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: Psychotic episodes like that raise the affected mage's paranoia to ridiculous levels."
}

{
  "id": "line:0649887",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: [i]That's[/i] why these cases almost always end in violence."
}

{
  "id": "line:04124e5",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Tyrion: But from what Celeste said,[p/] she wasn't acting psychotic.[p/] She was completely emotionless."
}

{
  "id": "line:001c86e",
  "node": "AfterMurder6",
  "text": "Lazarick: You might be onto something, Mr. Cuthbert."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fc64a5",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "Tyrion: If what you're saying is true,[p/] there [i]has[/i] to be more to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7f83e",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What are you going to do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05a4e2e",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "Tyrion: At the very least,[p/] we need to find out what actually happened..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbcbd5",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "Celeste: ...But you saw her, right?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d42628",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "Celeste: She [i]wanted[/i] them to arrest her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2874a",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "But something else was happening here.[p/] With who died,[p/] this felt far too coincidental to be a simple accident."
}

{
  "id": "line:0024101",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "I wasn't sure where each of the murders occurred,[p/] but the Inquisition could tell me more about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9c464",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "There was also Steelwind.[p/] If she really [i]was[/i] affected by Mageblight,[p/] she would remember what may have caused it."
}

{
  "id": "line:015ad98",
  "node": "AfterMurder7",
  "text": "I stood up.[p/] There was work to be done,[p/] and it was about time I ended my sabbatical."
}

{
  "id": "line:029d81f",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Player: View"
}

{
  "id": "line:0541306",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "I could see several commoner houses from here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0983e0f",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "If I squinted really hard,[p/] I could've [i]just[/i] made out my house."
}

{
  "id": "line:06ae6a8",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Player: Courthouse"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cd873",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "It was the city courthouse."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3c4ec",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Every trial I'd taken part in has been held in this building."
}

{
  "id": "line:0247211",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "...Excluding the current trial, obviously."
}

{
  "id": "line:03f8a09",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Player: Merchant's Guild"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eae555",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "It's one of the many offices of Von Sanctus Industries."
}

{
  "id": "line:079f8dc",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "...With the death of Lloyd,[p/] I'm sure his business will be thrown into chaos for a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6564f",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Player: Shop"
}

{
  "id": "line:0623737",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "It's a shop selling various wares."
}

{
  "id": "line:09b492b",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "The items they sell are more suited for adventurers."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2cbdb",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "I've tagged along when Celeste went to window shop there that one time.."
}

{
  "id": "line:0553f36",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Player: Elevation"
}

{
  "id": "line:041d728",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "There was a great view of the city from this ledge."
}

{
  "id": "line:0acaaf4",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "I frequently went there whenever I needed to think something over."
}

{
  "id": "line:0612855",
  "node": "Examine_TownSquare2",
  "text": "...I've been going there a lot for the last month."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce85ff",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Player: The Investigation"
}

{
  "id": "line:06a3a6a",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There are still so many unknowns..."
}

{
  "id": "line:076fe61",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should continue looking for more clues."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fbe3d0",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Don't push yourself too hard, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fd1ae9",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'll be fine.[p/] I'm making sure to pace myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:088608e",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Player: Next Lead"
}

{
  "id": "line:05cf415",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Where do you think we should go next?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c10650",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh, sorry.[p/] Did you say something?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04cac9f",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "She was probably still shaken up over what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d806b8",
  "node": "Talk_TownSquare2",
  "text": "It'd be best to take the lead and let her focus on her job."
}

{
  "id": "line:058606d",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Using the Kingsguard's teleportation network,[p/] we arrived back in Ratholme."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fa1b12",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "At Celeste's insistence,[p/] we were being escorted by a division of the Kingsguard."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d893e",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Knight: Sir...[p/] Where will we be heading first?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039b85e",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Uh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f9b1df",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "My newfound authority was definitely going to take some getting used to."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e0381",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Celeste: What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7f293",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Tyrion: There's definitely something I'm fundamentally missing...[p/] But what?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01a844f",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Just don't push yourself too hard, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a48a2",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We should speak with each of the suspects and confirm their alibis.[p/] That might help me finally put things together."
}

{
  "id": "line:02dff61",
  "node": "Check_Events_TownSquare2",
  "text": "Knight: Each of the nobles have returned to their respective homes,[p/] but our teleportation network should help you travel around Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:059949d",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "The sun had gone down.[p/] We only had a few hours left."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dccb53",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Desk"
}

{
  "id": "line:06cd9b4",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "It was Ruby's desk.[p/] It was made out of pure mahogany."
}

{
  "id": "line:0597bcb",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "The Eyetaker clearly paid her really well."
}

{
  "id": "line:039fabc",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "...But there was obviously a cost to that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0277b34",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I always wondered how you could afford these things..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0515ef5",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I guess I finally know now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db3e64",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Chair"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab732d",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "It was a chair for guests."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2d9be",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "I used to sit here for hours while Ruby would do the paperwork for her clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:0582f35",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "I used to sit here for hours while Tymora would do the paperwork for her clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:015d492",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "It was a bookshelf.[p/] There were several books about law and national history."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e477e4",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "I read a lot of these books front to back while studying to be an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:046d0d6",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "I even remember that time Celeste tried to sneak a \"Death at Daggerfall\" book here.[p/] My mentor was furious."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb0bfa",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Seat"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3a229",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "It was a seat for Ruby's clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:029df05",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "It was a seat for Tymora's clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d4c3c",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "It looked extremely comfortable,[p/] but she never let me sit in them when I was a child."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce4f96",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Painting 1"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e86cdc",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of a...[p/] noble?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042e8be",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Not quite.[p/] That's Eliza Tantivy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8b0c8",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: She was a commonfolk professor at the Imperial Academy."
}

{
  "id": "line:017b5f7",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: This portrait was commissioned by one of her noble patrons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0081eca",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: It really just shows off their wealth, though."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2f915",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: It doesn't celebrate anything noteworthy."
}

{
  "id": "line:08cdbe3",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why do you have this then?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c46f22",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I like her,[p/] and she's a good reminder of what the commonfolk can accomplish."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6936c",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Painting 2"
}

{
  "id": "line:04fb61b",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's a painting of some sort of pirate."
}

{
  "id": "line:04cb5be",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: He was a pirate who was famous for ruthlessly destroying the ships of anyone who stood in his way."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cde46e",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: During the Great Luminite War,[p/] the Wyverngarde Crown hired him as a privateer to protect Aurinax from the Theocracy's navy."
}

{
  "id": "line:049230a",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: He sailed near my hometown?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7d78",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: During the Great War,[p/] Aurinax was a vital foothold for Wyverngarde's navy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab953a",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Unfortunately,[p/] he was captured by the Theocracy and executed for his crimes."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f01a61",
  "node": "Examine_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: But I hear he gave them the runaround for eight years before he was captured."
}

{
  "id": "line:061ed23",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Small Talk"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb4da9",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Is McCoy okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f8385b",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: She's not being her usual self."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e8bf7",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] She's just been overprotective lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:0aced3f",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I don't really blame her..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0474154",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...What do you mean?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e55a09",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's a long story,[p/] and I don't think I'm even allowed to talk about it—[p/]especially not with you."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e9537",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "That last part came out with a lot more venom than I'd meant for it to."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e3dd4c",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Another moment of silence followed that."
}

{
  "id": "line:01732aa",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I received your letters."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ece698",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: O-[p/][s/]Oh...[p/] Did you—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:076e225",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I haven't gotten the chance to read them yet."
}

{
  "id": "line:000699d",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Of course...[p/] Whenever you're not busy."
}

{
  "id": "line:000b325",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Tymora's Actions"
}

{
  "id": "line:07127c1",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora..."
}

{
  "id": "line:099e295",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] trusted you."
}

{
  "id": "line:041c5d3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I know."
}

{
  "id": "line:031dbf1",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I trusted you.[p/] I told you things about myself that I'd never told anyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:074821f",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: And you told a [i]criminal[/i] about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c48312",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: It took me years before I was comfortable enough to tell [i]you[/i] about the Eye of Horus,[p/] and you [i]knew[/i] that."
}

{
  "id": "line:01b5f3a",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Why would you pull me into this?[p/] Did you ever think I would go along with it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05bbd12",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "For a long moment,[p/] nothing came to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:06623ff",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Tymora's Past"
}

{
  "id": "line:052001b",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I had a son once—[p/][i]before[/i] you,[p/] I mean."
}

{
  "id": "line:038e2a9",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I wasn't [i]always[/i] a city-person.[p/] I used to live in an old farm town,[p/] just like McCoy's."
}

{
  "id": "line:056b675",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait,[p/] [i]you[/i] lived in a village like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00b21ae",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: My son and I used to run an old tea shop,[p/] just the two of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:041b506",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: It's almost alien now that I think about it,[p/] but I was really happy back then."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6173b",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: One night,[p/] the ruling lord had too much to drink at the local tavern."
}

{
  "id": "line:049e0e5",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: He barged into our shop and started destroying it with his magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:095fb7f",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: My son tried to stop him,[p/] but—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0698992",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...The Inquisition swept that entire case under the rug, obviously."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf1bc8",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: They said that Lord Randall felt threatened and acted in self-defense."
}

{
  "id": "line:09d0756",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Her fist clenched and shuddered at the thought.[p/] Even now,[p/] it looked like her rage would boil over at any moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad3c77",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...What was your son's name?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d8d3f5",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: It was Ryan."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c4c21",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Oh."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd3149",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: What did you do?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0637ac3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: It felt like all the color disappeared from the world."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a55b7",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: How could I find beauty in a world where my son could die so pointlessly?"
}

{
  "id": "line:011b2a5",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I tried to tell everyone about what Randall had done."
}

{
  "id": "line:07bf175",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I sent letters to his family.[p/] I visited his fellow nobles in the other cities."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e2478",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I even travelled to Ratholme to personally talk to representatives from the House of Lords."
}

{
  "id": "line:0301131",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: That's when a retainer from House Sibyl came into contact with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:02508fc",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I thought this was it.[p/] I thought someone had finally listened,[p/] and Ryan would finally get justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:036ca97",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: But when I met with them,[p/] they just gave me a sack of gold and told me to stop pushing the matter."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dcd921",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...They wanted to pay you off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b9e0ff",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Do you know what the worst part was?[p/] That retainer was just looking out for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:051302c",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: They told me what the nobility was really like.[p/] Stories like what happened to my son were commonplace among them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e11d55",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: No one ever spoke about it,[p/] but there was a silent understanding."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b0f43",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Everyone I'd talked to—[p/]every noble that threw false sympathy at me—[p/]none of them actually cared."
}

{
  "id": "line:04c951b",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: They thought they could pay me to let go."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c98632",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: They gave me 100 gold coins—[p/]that's how much my son's life was worth to them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6f1e3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I decided I would take justice into my own hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c07c35",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Wait...[p/] You didn't—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1c4e9",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: No...[p/] I told myself that killing him would be too easy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0352d1e",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I broke into Lord Randall's manor.[p/] I found [i]every[/i] incriminating document I could find."
}

{
  "id": "line:07015b4",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I found everything,[p/] from records of illegitimate children,[p/] to plots he was making against the other noble houses."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ceb492",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I released [i]everything[/i] to the public.[p/] It absolutely ruined him."
}

{
  "id": "line:02746db",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: That's when I realized that there [i]was[/i] a way to punish them."
}

{
  "id": "line:003e715",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I didn't have to harm or kill anyone.[p/] I just had to beat them at their own game."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2b977",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I could use the laws [i]they[/i] created as a weapon against them."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f69e6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Just like an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c8525e",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Just like an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a56657",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: When I realized that,[p/] I moved to the city and started studying law."
}

{
  "id": "line:0277bbc",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I read every book there was to read about Wyverngarde's laws,[p/] and I learned how to work the system."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e22c3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I started representing clients.[p/] It was nice to save people,[p/] but tearing those nobles down was what gave me life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dafe24",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I was on the warpath.[p/] I was acquitting more commoners than any other attorney in Wyverngarde.[p/] I felt invincible."
}

{
  "id": "line:082e91d",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: That's when the Eyetaker reached out to me.[p/] He said he believed in my cause and wanted to help me."
}

{
  "id": "line:019d7dd",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: But it was obvious he just needed me for his enterprise.[p/] I turned him down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bd197d",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How did he react to that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee8558",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: He didn't do anything.[p/] He wasn't even angry.[p/] He just told me his offer would stay open."
}

{
  "id": "line:0900162",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I continued my work,[p/] but as I started punching higher,[p/] the nobles got smarter and more influential."
}

{
  "id": "line:0273004",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I was still winning,[p/] but the trials got closer and closer each time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dac4ff",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I didn't care, though.[p/] I thought that no matter what happened,[p/] justice was on my side."
}

{
  "id": "line:06cfd36",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...But then I started losing."
}

{
  "id": "line:011a3d5",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I thought it was par for the course.[p/] I told myself I couldn't save everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b4aed",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: But it kept happening over and over again.[p/] I kept seeing lives taken away.[p/] I kept seeing families shattered."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb33fb",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I remember each and every one of their names and faces.[p/] I attended their executions because I was powerless to do anything else."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f93e19",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: The screams of despair of each of their families still keep me up at night."
}

{
  "id": "line:044cb52",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I tried my best to carry that weight,[p/] but it got harder each time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0521e",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...And then Frey's trial happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:01cf477",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I've never met someone that remarkable before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0059596",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: She had this way of lifting your spirits...[p/] It didn't matter how much was burdening you.[p/] It was like magic."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e61573",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Yeah...[p/] I remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ecc041",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: But I failed her.[p/] I failed you."
}

{
  "id": "line:027e7e9",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I never [i]once[/i] blamed you for what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3a6d6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I know,[p/] but that doesn't change the fact that I [i]couldn't[/i] acquit her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc366d",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...After her execution,[p/] I couldn't bear to look at you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe7cb6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: This child was broken—[p/]forever shattered because I had too much pride to take help from a criminal."
}

{
  "id": "line:053e9b7",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: If I'd just done that,[p/] your mother would still be alive."
}

{
  "id": "line:0630edb",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I ran away from Aurinax.[p/] I wanted to forget about you."
}

{
  "id": "line:00dcb90",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: But then you showed up at my doorstep,[p/] asking [i]me[/i] to make you an attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b937fe",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I felt so alone and helpless.[p/] I wanted someone—[i]anyone[/i]—to carry this burden with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:08eba91",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: So how pathetic must [i]I[/i] have been to look for that in a grieving ten-year-old child?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07fa2a5",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: When I looked at you,[p/] all I wanted to see was myself."
}

{
  "id": "line:00f4edb",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I saw a hurt and broken person who wanted to burn them to the ground,[p/] but I never even tried to notice that you were [i]nothing[/i] like me."
}

{
  "id": "line:06eb65d",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: You [i]cared[/i] about people,[p/] and you cared about saving your clients."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dee2da",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...But I always thought that's what would bring you to my side."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ce470f",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...How could you possibly think that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c74577",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Because I thought you'd start losing too."
}

{
  "id": "line:09df5c6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I thought the justice system would break you."
}

{
  "id": "line:05e0fc3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I hated myself for it,[p/] but I wanted you to fail so you'd see that the Eyetaker was the only way to win."
}

{
  "id": "line:08fc1de",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Maybe you were right about me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5b735",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Maybe I was just using you.[p/] I forced you to dedicate your life to [i]my[/i] dream."
}

{
  "id": "line:074c7b3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: If I really [i]did[/i] care about you,[p/] I would have never pulled you into this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0238949",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: Reconciliation"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d38097",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I've been thinking a lot about what happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:01652f2",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I imagined what it would be like to have a helpless child show up on your doorstep like that."
}

{
  "id": "line:09746f5",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You were living your own life and fighting your own demons.[p/] I just thrust myself into it."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf1bc3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I didn't give you much of a choice, did I?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f26759",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Cuthbert..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0381d3b",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: We both could have made better choices."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab5de7",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You're right.[p/] I really don't know what it's like to lose."
}

{
  "id": "line:09fd0c0",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm able to see angles that no one else can,[p/] and that's served me well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0416649",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But most of the time,[p/] I just get lucky and things work out for me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0816281",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You never had a prosecutor who went easy on you.[p/] You never had the Eye of Horus to show you what people were hiding."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b3163b",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You fought by yourself,[p/] and I can't imagine how resilient you must have been to do that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df4246",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But I still don't know if I can forgive you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03da170",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I don't blame you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be9cc6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But I want to try."
}

{
  "id": "line:09a9ba1",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ms. Tymora,[p/] I still want you to be in my life."
}

{
  "id": "line:02cf286",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if we don't always see eye to eye,[p/] the years I spent with you were just as precious to me as the times I had with my mother."
}

{
  "id": "line:0196474",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "She had to blink back a tear as I said that.[p/] She shook her head, annoyed."
}

{
  "id": "line:0218d01",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Damn it, Tyrion.[p/] Why'd you have to go and say that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0de42a5",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Ms. Tymora."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a9e502",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: No...[p/] Stop calling me that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ebe51f",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I want things to be different this time."
}

{
  "id": "line:08a87bc",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: I'm not your superior nor your mentor anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b11d0b",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: We're equals now.[p/] You don't answer to me,[p/] so call me by my first name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0768443",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: O-[p/][s/]Oh, okay.[p/] Um...[p/] Ruby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0090ca6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Saying it felt really strange after all these years..."
}

{
  "id": "line:03956e4",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Player: The Eyetaker"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bee4b3",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right...[p/] I almost forgot the entire reason why I came here..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc10c6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: What is it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0565394",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] didn't [i]just[/i] come here to reconcile."
}

{
  "id": "line:007090c",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I actually need your help with something."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b32036",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0801d8c",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I need you to help me speak to the Eyetaker."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d76ba6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02afc1e",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know...[p/] Considering the circumstances,[p/] it would probably strain your partnership with him even more."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d96c4",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cbc7e6",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But if you just tell me where he is,[p/] I'll do my best to make sure it doesn't get traced back to you."
}

{
  "id": "line:04eafcc",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion.[p/] The Eyetaker is dead."
}

{
  "id": "line:0569d56",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: He died right after you convicted Beatrice.[p/] He was lynched by a mob of civilians."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dfd1e4",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Everyone's saying that it must have have been some sort of retaliation from House Frega."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cde892",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Didn't you notice that he didn't send anyone after you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed53db",
  "node": "Talk_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: But Eris said—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:089a407",
  "node": "Present_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...It's your Attorney's Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0df58ff",
  "node": "Present_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Tyrion: You [i]are[/i] the one that gave it to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c37421",
  "node": "Present_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "Ruby: Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:096850e",
  "node": "Present_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "This wasn't really the time to PRESENT things to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:079a447",
  "node": "Present_TymoraOffice2",
  "text": "It would probably be a bad idea to show her evidence relevant to the case."
}

{
  "id": "line:019227e",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "We arrived at the office of Tymora's law firm.[p/] Aria had told us that she was still practicing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e79b78",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "It was located in the lower districts.[p/] It honestly seemed kind of out of place there from how pristine and clean it looked."
}

{
  "id": "line:08bcb35",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "A place like this belonged in the upper district,[p/] where the nobles and the merchants lived."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e629e9",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "But Tymora needed her office to be close to her clients.[p/] They needed to know they had a place to turn to when the kingdom turned their back on them."
}

{
  "id": "line:048977f",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "I remembered the first day I came to this office."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e95ab2",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "I was starving and filthy.[p/] Looking back,[p/] it's a miracle I'd even made it here at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fec657",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "That was the lowest point of my life,[p/] and she—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d3bffa",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "Knight: ...Sir?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb12b4",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "After everything that had happened,[p/] I didn't feel ready."
}

{
  "id": "line:07a5975",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "For the past month,[p/] everything that I'd said to her was replaying in my head."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fff604",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "I wasn't thinking clearly,[p/] but a part of me meant everything that I'd said to her."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f24ba",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "Would I have said anything differently?"
}

{
  "id": "line:093a0a8",
  "node": "TymoraRev",
  "text": "I felt the familiar warmth of Celeste's hand within mine again."
}

{
  "id": "line:0612aa0",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "I took a deep breath and knocked on the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cab4a7",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "Every moment of silence following that filled me with anxiety and dread."
}

{
  "id": "line:05abc5d",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "Ruby: I don't know who you think you are,[p/] but we—"
}

{
  "id": "line:087a54e",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "She froze when she saw who her visitor was."
}

{
  "id": "line:00bd663",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "She looked completely frozen for a while,[p/] but her gaze narrowed at the legion of knights flanking."
}

{
  "id": "line:01dfc8d",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Am I under arrest?"
}

{
  "id": "line:09d33e0",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "Tyrion: N-[p/][s/]No...![p/][s/] Of course, not![p/][s/] I—"
}

{
  "id": "line:085506c",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "I drew in a sharp breath and just exhaled."
}

{
  "id": "line:0877f7b",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Can we come in?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f689e",
  "node": "TymoraRev2",
  "text": "Ruby: Y-[p/][s/]Yes...[p/] Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:059fde4",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "I took a seat inside her office,[p/] staying silent as I looked around.[p/] It hadn't changed at all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7092",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "...Even though they were my escorts,[p/] the knights felt like they were looming over the two of us."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bf7e7d",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Hey, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dff629",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Could you take the knights outside and do a perimeter of the building?"
}

{
  "id": "line:042ded8",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Celeste: What?[p/] But—"
}

{
  "id": "line:01c9b28",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Are you sure?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0067945",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0be4927",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Celeste: B-[p/][s/]But what if something happens?"
}

{
  "id": "line:04360a6",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] we're in a populated building in the capital city of Wyverngarde.[p/] I think I'll be fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b1cb8e",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Celeste: N-[p/][s/]No...[p/] But—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e59dfc",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "She stopped when I raised an eyebrow at her.[p/] I knew she was worried,[p/] but this was starting to get overbearing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd75f1",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Celeste: S-[p/][s/]Sorry...[p/] You're right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:057d6fe",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll just—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0cfe7b6",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "With a motion of her hand,[p/] the knights followed her out of the office."
}

{
  "id": "line:00c11e9",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "She was the last one out of the door.[p/] She looked back at me before leaving."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e2d5dd",
  "node": "TymoraRev3",
  "text": "...But after a while,[p/] she realized how long she'd been staring and quickly closed the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:072fa66",
  "node": "ErisReveal",
  "text": "Wait a minute..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0666f44",
  "node": "ErisReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: Then why would Eris say that...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab67a8",
  "node": "ErisReveal",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Eris?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0aba8c3",
  "node": "ErisReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've met her before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0696dd6",
  "node": "ErisReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: She has long black hair,[p/] and she wears a black dress."
}

{
  "id": "line:00edfbf",
  "node": "ErisReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I suppose she really likes black."
}

{
  "id": "line:08c202f",
  "node": "ErisReveal",
  "text": "Tyrion: B-[p/][s/]But anyways,[p/] she's the Eyetaker's daughter."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d4c1b",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion...[p/] The Eyetaker's daughter has [i]red[/i] hair."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c99eea",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "Tyrion: What?[p/][s/] She was [i]there[/i] when we spoke to him during Beatrice's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ee9755",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "Ruby: ...That's right."
}

{
  "id": "line:060d97c",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "Ruby: What are you talking about?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c11803",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "Ruby: She was never [i]at[/i] that meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a4c872",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "What was going on?[p/] She was [i]clearly[/i] there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f108a1",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "If it weren't for her intervention,[p/] the Eyetaker would've attacked at that very moment."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a7eca1",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "Tyrion: No..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0504001",
  "node": "ErisReveal2",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion?[p/] What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab394e",
  "node": "ErisReveal3",
  "text": "Ruby: Why are you looking at me like that?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b8ca3",
  "node": "ErisReveal3",
  "text": "A part of me really hoped that I was wrong about this..."
}

{
  "id": "line:02fce50",
  "node": "ErisReveal3a",
  "text": "No...[p/] Ruby didn't remember that Eris was at that meeting."
}

{
  "id": "line:01d9c61",
  "node": "ErisReveal3a",
  "text": "That didn't make sense.[p/] [i]Eris[/i] was the one who got us out of that situation in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ffc479",
  "node": "ErisReveal3a",
  "text": "...There was only one reason why she wouldn't remember."
}

{
  "id": "line:03b26b0",
  "node": "ErisReveal4",
  "text": "That was the only explanation I could think of...[p/][s/] But why?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02a3979",
  "node": "ErisReveal4",
  "text": "...Her memories seemed intact,[p/] [i]except[/i] for her memories of Eris."
}

{
  "id": "line:05979d2",
  "node": "ErisReveal4",
  "text": "Since her disappearance,[p/] I suspected that she may have been involved in this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f79f6d",
  "node": "ErisReveal4",
  "text": "Not only was she at the scene of the crime,[p/] but she went missing at the same time that Beatrice did."
}

{
  "id": "line:05bfa60",
  "node": "ErisReveal4",
  "text": "But I never thought to ask one question."
}

{
  "id": "line:00e458d",
  "node": "ErisReveal4a",
  "text": "000|020"
}

{
  "id": "line:01416d4",
  "node": "ErisReveal4a",
  "text": "No...[p/] Ruby signed a Blood Contract with a demon,[p/] and that demon changed Ruby's memories of Eris Illmater."
}

{
  "id": "line:0344d65",
  "node": "ErisReveal4a",
  "text": "Eris Illmater was present at the crime scene during the massacre,[p/] and in addition to that,[p/] she'd been missing since everything happened."
}

{
  "id": "line:079c1bc",
  "node": "ErisReveal4b",
  "text": "CELESTE: Tyrion.[p/] I’ve fought literal monsters and barely escaped with my life."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c33439",
  "node": "ErisReveal4b",
  "text": "CELESTE: But when I’m near Eris,[p/] none of those creatures come even close."
}

{
  "id": "line:084c47f",
  "node": "ErisReveal4b",
  "text": "CELESTE: I get this feeling.[p/] It's like I’m in front of a predator that I couldn’t ever hope to beat."
}

{
  "id": "line:0450049",
  "node": "ErisReveal4b",
  "text": "CELESTE: Every instinct I have tells me to run whenever she’s close by."
}

{
  "id": "line:07383dd",
  "node": "ErisReveal4b",
  "text": "Laefe: I-[p/][s/]I'm terribly sorry![p/][s/] He's not usually like this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b30e8b",
  "node": "ErisReveal4b",
  "text": "Eris: Ah, it's to be expected."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dedf15",
  "node": "ErisReveal4b",
  "text": "ERIS: I'm not sure why,[p/] but animals have always been able to see me for what I am."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7d06c",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "There was still very little I knew about demons."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7b951",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "So who was to say that one couldn't take the appearance of a human?"
}

{
  "id": "line:03b7fc9",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "It was a long shot,[p/] but there [i]was[/i] one way to find out for sure."
}

{
  "id": "line:0487bbd",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Ruby: Tyrion, talk to me.[p/] What's wrong?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b819c",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ruby...[p/] I'm about to do something stupid..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fb7855",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: If I fall into medical distress,[p/] I need you to call Celeste and tell her to contact Lord Asclepius or the Archduke."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb35f6",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Ruby: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:02fdb04",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "There was no way either of them would get here in time,[p/] but it was already late,[p/] and the trial would resume tomorrow."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e70c69",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Eris Illmater![p/][s/] Wherever and [i]whatever[/i] you are!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0df116e",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: Release thy guards and manifest your Blood Contract with Ruby Tymora!"
}

{
  "id": "line:06e83cd",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Eris: So...[p/] You finally figured it out, my dearest Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:00d87a1",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: This entire time...[p/][s/] I've been chasing [i]you[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e783a",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Eris: You have...[p/] It's been so entertaining watching you scramble around."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c45ddb",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've been making contracts with people across Wyverngarde."
}

{
  "id": "line:0075faa",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: You took control of Aria [i]and[/i] Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c97896",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: But...[p/] Why?![p/][s/] Why would you want to do any of this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00df7b3",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Eris: Oh,[p/] I can't possibly reveal [i]all[/i] my secrets."
}

{
  "id": "line:09682e5",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Eris: This isn't the proper stage to have our final battle."
}

{
  "id": "line:05c0753",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Tyrion: You..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0002aa8",
  "node": "ErisReveal4c",
  "text": "Eris: But I suppose that you've come this far,[p/] so how about I give you a little gift?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d6cf25",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Ruby: What was that...?"
}

{
  "id": "line:05e099b",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ruby...[p/] Eris Illmater is a demon..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d59f73",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: And she's not just [i]any[/i] demon.[p/] She's the Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0de525d",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...And [i]you[/i] signed a Blood Contract with her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6ef94",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: [i]That's[/i] why you can't remember anything about her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d67e45",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Ruby: What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e80515",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Ruby: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion![p/] I-[p/][s/]I..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f6c823",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Ruby: I swear on my life that I didn't know anything about this!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07f9c10",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know...[p/] She probably tricked you into signing this."
}

{
  "id": "line:009c28d",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Just like she tricked Aria."
}

{
  "id": "line:07cbfc4",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Ruby: What does Prosecutor Steelwind have to do with this?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:03ebd4b",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Celeste: Come on, you two."
}

{
  "id": "line:007f40c",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Celeste: I know things are kind of tense,[p/] but there's no need to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0636d5e",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What are you holding?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eeb9af",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]Is that a Blood Contract?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:010fe15",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste...[p/] Eris is the Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c06ad4",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Celeste: W-[p/][s/]What?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e078c3",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was [i]her[/i] the entire time!"
}

{
  "id": "line:012cd37",
  "node": "ErisReveal5",
  "text": "Tyrion: She [i]tricked[/i] Aria into signing a Blood Contract,[p/] and she used her [i]and[/i] Beatrice to orchestrate the entire massacre!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e43bcf",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Celeste: T-[p/][s/]Tyrion![p/][s/] This is crazy!"
}

{
  "id": "line:04d40fc",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Celeste: I-[p/][s/]I know I was scared of her that [i]one[/i] time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ed4996",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Celeste: But how could [i]Eris[/i] be a demon?![p/][s/] She looks nothing [i]like[/i] Marrunath!"
}

{
  "id": "line:00bd548",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know how unbelievable it is,[p/] but I used my Divine Edict with her name."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3756b",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: That wouldn't have worked unless she [i]was[/i] a demon."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb4981",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Celeste: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah...[p/] I guess I can't disagree with that."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fed65d",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Knight: ...We'll need to contact the Grand General immediately."
}

{
  "id": "line:07d64d5",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Ugh...[p/] But if she's really a demon,[p/] is it even possible to arrest her?"
}

{
  "id": "line:07b87b3",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "It had already been a day."
}

{
  "id": "line:0658c2a",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "For someone like her,[p/] that would be [i]more[/i] than enough time to skip town."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c8ba5",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll need to speak with the Scaled—[p/] the Archduke about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:082d7c2",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Thank you...[p/] Ruby."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7a5c4",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: You've helped us more than you could ever know."
}

{
  "id": "line:000ea2c",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Ruby: Y-[p/][s/]Yeah, of course..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd762e",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: Celeste,[p/] let's meet up with everyone."
}

{
  "id": "line:072dc4a",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Tyrion: We'll need to discuss our next course of action."
}

{
  "id": "line:0849208",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "Celeste rushed out of the door and began barking orders to the knights."
}

{
  "id": "line:024fa10",
  "node": "ErisReveal6",
  "text": "I was about to follow her when Ruby pulled at my wrist."
}

{
  "id": "line:03912e1",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: Have you been using the Eye of Horus lately?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0677059",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Tyrion: Uh...[p/] Yeah."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e264dd",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't say much about what I'm doing right now,[p/] but I [i]am[/i] in the middle of a case."
}

{
  "id": "line:06251a9",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: It's just that—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0d5a42c",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: Never mind...[p/] I don't think it's my place to say anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f66194",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: It's not as if it's [i]my[/i] ability anyways.[p/] It's probably nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d7eef",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: ...I know you can't tell me about what you're doing."
}

{
  "id": "line:083b5ae",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: And I have no idea what could possibly involve the Kingsguard,[p/] Steelwind, [i]and[/i] this Empress of Discord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0823bfb",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: Just stay safe, okay?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01beed9",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: ...You're the only family I have left."
}

{
  "id": "line:070c004",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Tyrion: I will.[p/] I promise."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6f578",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "Ruby: ...Thank you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d27d15",
  "node": "ErisReveal7",
  "text": "I'd finally found the lead I'd been looking for,[p/] but I wasn't sure where this would take me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0537a29",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Who [i]was[/i] Eris?[p/] What stake could she possibly have in the politics of Wyverngarde?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0eb34c3",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "She not only impersonated the Eyetaker's daughter.[p/] She also pretended to be my friend."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e92eb7",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "...I was terrified of what she was planning."
}

{
  "id": "line:004145d",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Eris: Is something wrong, commander?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a43663",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Orym: ...Don't play dumb with me."
}

{
  "id": "line:060341f",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Orym: They told me what you [i]really[/i] are.[p/] What's your game, demon?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0bbe589",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Orym: Why would you just deliver yourself to our doorstep?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0104e48",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Eris: Oh, Orym.[p/] I've put far too much work into this story to [i]miss[/i] the final act."
}

{
  "id": "line:0628331",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Eris: I can't wait to see how this ends."
}

{
  "id": "line:0114381",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Orym: You [i]killed[/i] three nobles and enslaved an innocent girl!"
}

{
  "id": "line:09e21ca",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Orym: Is this all some kind of game to you?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0678899",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Eris: That's [i]exactly[/i] what this is to me."
}

{
  "id": "line:05be6bb",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Eris: I'll admit...[p/] Looking back,[p/] it [i]does[/i] feel a bit derivative."
}

{
  "id": "line:0edd326",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Eris: But I think I've done enough to differentiate myself from those that came before."
}

{
  "id": "line:0069a76",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Eris: I even made sure to go over everything a second time."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ab28ee",
  "node": "ErisReveal8",
  "text": "Orym: ...You're insane."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5d0a3",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: [i]That[/i] took you long enough to notice."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ae4b9",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: I guess the oafish Inquisition Commander [i]does[/i] have some observational skills after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dc0ec6",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Orym: ...Whatever.[p/] You just better not try anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:09de1d6",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: You know I can't lie.[p/] So I'll reassure you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c03ea5",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: I [i]promise[/i].[p/] I won't harm anyone—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0293231",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: —while I'm in this prison."
}

{
  "id": "line:0870340",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Orym: Ugh..."
}

{
  "id": "line:07279f1",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: We're finally approaching the climax, Tyrion."
}

{
  "id": "line:0380d3a",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: No more DEDUCTIONS.[p/] No more TALKING.[p/] No more god-awful teasing."
}

{
  "id": "line:098d5f7",
  "node": "ErisReveal9",
  "text": "Eris: It's just [i]me[/i][p/] and you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0866526",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: Guest Room"
}

{
  "id": "line:03117de",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh.[p/] Remember when I helped you move this bed from the flea market?"
}

{
  "id": "line:039c54c",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ea0229",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "I recall her doing most,[p/] if not all,[p/] of the work."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfaf93",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "I didn't even know that carrying a bed frame singlehandedly was humanly possible...[p/] She didn't even take out the mattress."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e2e79",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "It was a fantasy novel that I'd been reading through."
}

{
  "id": "line:0021d8a",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "...I've had a lot of free time to read through my collection."
}

{
  "id": "line:073e0f9",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Did you read that mystery novel I lent you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f5454b",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I [i]did[/i], but...[p/] I kind of guessed the twist from the beginning..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c887aa",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...What?![p/][s/] How?!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c460ab",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: The author called a lot of attention to the vials she dropped."
}

{
  "id": "line:0583fca",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It was pretty obvious the nurse accidentally switched them."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a18528",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: What a sad life you must live to never be surprised..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d19833",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: I think I've had enough surprises for the time being."
}

{
  "id": "line:095e287",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: Upstairs"
}

{
  "id": "line:07ba185",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "A stairway led to the second story of my home."
}

{
  "id": "line:070c5ea",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "...I hadn't cleaned up the upper floor in a while."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a3bd86",
  "node": "Examine_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "It would probably be best to make sure Steelwind didn't wander up there."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b59852",
  "node": "Talk_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: Celeste McCoy"
}

{
  "id": "line:02af61d",
  "node": "Talk_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Player: Ruby Tymora"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f2600c",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Aria: Are you doing well, Mr. Cuthbert?[p/] You seem—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0919a6b",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm fine."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c2929",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Aria: ...Of course."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb49c2",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Aria: I just couldn't help but notice your absence."
}

{
  "id": "line:034975d",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Aria: You haven't taken any other clients since Beatrice's trial."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a48d56",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm not even sure if I'm going to practice law anymore."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e12372",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I only did this because Tymora told me to,[p/] and now—"
}

{
  "id": "line:02acedd",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "My words trailed off."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b40dda",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Aria: Did you not enjoy it?[p/] You [i]were[/i] very skilled at it."
}

{
  "id": "line:01c984d",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know,[p/] but I need more time to think about this."
}

{
  "id": "line:08274a7",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Aria: Have you considered becoming a prosecutor?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ccb63f",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Aria: You did a remarkable job of prosecuting Beatrice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0ca3ac6",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "If she'd asked me that last year I'd just laugh at her offer,[p/] but Beatrice showed me that there [i]were[/i] criminals that needed to be brought to justice."
}

{
  "id": "line:0682dcd",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Steelwind was an iron wall of an attorney.[p/] She never had to exploit the system like the other prosecutors of the Crown did."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a89c8a",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Following her example might not be a bad idea,[p/] but a part of me was also tired of following in someone else's footsteps."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f7b6fb",
  "node": "TyrIntroTyrConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I'll think about it."
}

{
  "id": "line:064d186",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have your injuries been healing well?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ec376",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: Yes.[p/] Nightgrave's skill in [b]necromancy[/b] is quite remarkable."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0f4c9",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: I'm glad I introduced him to House Asclepius."
}

{
  "id": "line:0667506",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Asclepius?"
}

{
  "id": "line:002f36f",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: House Asclepius specializes in the study of [b]necromancy[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:084fa41",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: After Nightgrave's expulsion from the academy,[p/] I thought it was only right that he be allowed to continue his studies."
}

{
  "id": "line:06af100",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Right.[p/] He mentioned that he owed you a favour."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d39e7c",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: It was only logical.[p/] It would be a waste to let someone of his talents fade into obscurity."
}

{
  "id": "line:006dadf",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Even after everything that had happened at the Academy,[p/] he was still following his own path."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f149a9",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even so,[p/] should you still be moving around like this?"
}

{
  "id": "line:08ff6d7",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: You should take some time off to recover."
}

{
  "id": "line:07b7f8b",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: As much as I would like to,[p/] there's been a recent uptick in cases of Mageblight lately."
}

{
  "id": "line:00ecf2e",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Mageblight...[p/] I recalled hearing about that many times."
}

{
  "id": "line:02a05a2",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "If a mage exceeded their stamina by overusing their magic,[p/] it would cloud their mind and send them into a violent frenzy."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cd4f86",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: The nobility has been trying to suppress information about these incidents."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d1c190",
  "node": "TyrIntroAriaConv",
  "text": "Aria: If I'm not there,[p/] there's no one to keep the Inquisition from capitulating to their demands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d20550",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Aria: I was actually surprised to see you here, Celeste."
}

{
  "id": "line:03abf62",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Well...[p/] I can't just leave him alone anymore.[p/] He ticked off a criminal overlord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b89736",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Celeste: They're definitely going to send someone after him. [h=\"...And he can't really take care of himself right now.\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0adee",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: Your thoughts are leaking."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dd607b",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Get out of my head."
}

{
  "id": "line:08604d0",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...It's nothing."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c061b5",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Aria: I [i]am[/i] surprised, though.[p/] Not many people slight the Eyetaker and live."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a6c956",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Aria: He's been known for taking swift retaliation against his enemies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e1d4ad",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: We're hoping he's laying low after his plan with Beatrice fell through."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f0937",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Either that,[p/] or Ruby's doing what she can to protect him."
}

{
  "id": "line:02148df",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Aria: Supposedly,[p/] he's been absent from many of his enterprises."
}

{
  "id": "line:099250b",
  "node": "TyrIntroCelConv",
  "text": "Either way...[p/] He'd need to be dealt with eventually."
}

{
  "id": "line:0106261",
  "node": "TyrIntroRubyConv",
  "text": "Celeste: ...By the way, Tyrion.[p/] Ruby sent another letter."
}

{
  "id": "line:08e4081",
  "node": "TyrIntroRubyConv",
  "text": "Celeste: Do you want to—?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00cfbc7",
  "node": "TyrIntroRubyConv",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Put it with the rest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0333f21",
  "node": "TyrIntroRubyConv",
  "text": "Celeste: R-[p/]Right..."
}

{
  "id": "line:05b2b00",
  "node": "TyrIntroRubyConv",
  "text": "Aria: ...Have you spoken to her since the trial?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0c0a5a2",
  "node": "TyrIntroRubyConv",
  "text": "Aria: Of course.[p/] My apologies."
}

{
  "id": "line:0364f81",
  "node": "Present_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Aria: It’s an Attorney’s Runestone."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c9a65d",
  "node": "Present_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: ...It proves that you're a certified attorney."
}

{
  "id": "line:09db277",
  "node": "Present_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: It does, doesn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b0b316",
  "node": "Present_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Aria: ...Why are you showing this to me?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0fab0ef",
  "node": "Present_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Tyrion: S-[p/]Sorry.[p/] Force of habit."
}

{
  "id": "line:08f7b63",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh![p/] The tea's ready."
}

{
  "id": "line:0af9696",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Aria: Oh,[p/] thank you.[p/] Some tea sounds lovely right now."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e7ee9c",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: R-[p/]Right...[p/] I was [i]totally[/i] making it for you guys."
}

{
  "id": "line:01a5680",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "She trotted to the kitchen,[p/] taking out two more tea cups out of one of my cabinets."
}

{
  "id": "line:044fe31",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "Celeste: You guys better enjoy this.[p/] These are my last bags of—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0109313",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "As she was carrying the cups of tea to us,[p/] she stumbled and slipped on a scroll case lying on the floor."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bfabb0",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "She caught herself,[p/] but the teacups slipped out of her hands."
}

{
  "id": "line:0211ec2",
  "node": "Check_Events_TyrionRoomIntro",
  "text": "The boiling liquid was airborne,[p/] and it was heading right toward my face."
}

{
  "id": "line:025f109",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Celeste: [b]Figaqua[/b]!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e5a471",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Celeste's index finger shot to point at the airborne tea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b2559d",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Her magic took hold,[p/] and the molten tea froze just inches from my face."
}

{
  "id": "line:06db5d3",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "She let out a sigh,[p/] and slowly started to twist her hand.[p/] She magically guided tea back into their cups."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e0e748",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Celeste: You really need to clean this place."
}

{
  "id": "line:001b656",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm your bodyguard,[p/] not your maid."
}

{
  "id": "line:06e83c3",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Tyrion: R-[p/][s/]Right.[p/] Sorry about that..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0db900c",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Aria: That was [b]Shape Liquid[/b], wasn't it?"
}

{
  "id": "line:009b2ef",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Tyrion: Oh...[p/] I never expected you to—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0111bed",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Celeste: I know,[p/] but it's just too convenient [i]not[/i] to have,[p/] and my expertise [i]is[/i] [b]transmutation[b/]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cc512d",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "She's really opened her mind about learning new spells."
}

{
  "id": "line:07654aa",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "I remember when I first met her.[p/] She only knew how to cast [b]Mage Blade[/b]."
}

{
  "id": "line:08247b5",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "She hated her magic back then...[p/] I never imagined how diverse her repertoire would become."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f70790",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "There was another knock at the door.[p/] I could've really done without all of the visitors today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c5d7c9",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm already up.[p/] I'll answer it."
}

{
  "id": "line:08220dc",
  "node": "LetterGet",
  "text": "Celeste: Well, [i]whoever[/i] they are,[p/] I'm not giving up any more of my Lotus Tea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a51381",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "I looked through the peephole.[p/] It didn't look like anyone else was there."
}

{
  "id": "line:06f351a",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "I slowly opened the door.[p/] A chain kept it partially locked."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f77a05",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "No one was on the street,[p/] but there was a letter in my mailbox."
}

{
  "id": "line:03c9601",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "I quickly snatched it before shutting the door."
}

{
  "id": "line:06c768d",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "It was an envelope sealed with candle wax."
}

{
  "id": "line:06722b9",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "There was a crest on it...[p/][s/] It was the insignia of House Pierce!"
}

{
  "id": "line:07095c8",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "I quickly opened the letter and read it."
}

{
  "id": "line:09e741c",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "Despite clearly being written by Pierce,[p/] the paper had been torn in half,[p/] but the message was clear."
}

{
  "id": "line:080e6fd",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]I hope you understand...[p/] I would've never contacted you unless I had no other choice.[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0dea9ea",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]I know the truth behind McCoy's [i]true[/i] parentage,[p/] and I'm aware of how vital this information is to you.[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0250d2b",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]As you know,[p/] my execution is scheduled for next month,[p/] and I'm running out of time.[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:018e8a1",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]I want to trade this information with you.[p/] In exchange,[p/] you [b]will[/b] grant me my freedom.[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0162cce",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]Meet me in the private Prayer Room within the Grand Cathedral of the Scaled Lord at 2:00 PM...[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:01addf0",
  "node": "LetterGet2",
  "text": "Garrick: [i]You [b]will[/b] save me from my fate,[p/] or else[/i]"
}

{
  "id": "line:0460872",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Celeste: If he thinks for a second that we'd even [i]think[/i] of helping him—!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a34bf5",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Tyrion: I know how you feel,[p/] but aren't these the answers you've been looking for?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0105e77",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Celeste: I don't care![p/][s/] We're [i]not[/i] going to help him!"
}

{
  "id": "line:0e401eb",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Tyrion: That was never an option,[p/] but there's clearly more to this."
}

{
  "id": "line:0653314",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: ...I agree.[p/] How was he able to find out in the first place?"
}

{
  "id": "line:02ffca4",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: The truth is, Celeste...[p/] I've also been looking into your parentage."
}

{
  "id": "line:04f7644",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry for not telling you,[p/] but I didn't want to raise your hopes."
}

{
  "id": "line:040cb8d",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: Even with the resources available to me,[p/] I couldn't find [i]any[/i] information regarding your birth."
}

{
  "id": "line:023b807",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Tyrion: So if [i]you[/i] couldn't find anything,[p/] how was [i]Pierce[/i] able to?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01476e5",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: House Pierce is low on the political hierarchy.[p/] He shouldn't have access to the resources I do."
}

{
  "id": "line:09f9729",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Tyrion: He [i]was[/i] ruling lord of the land the McCoy Tavern is on."
}

{
  "id": "line:02e5fc1",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: That's true,[p/] but I still find this whole situation is quite suspect."
}

{
  "id": "line:01926b9",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Tyrion: And why would he ask for [i]my[/i] help?[p/] [i]I[/i] was the one who indicted him in the first place."
}

{
  "id": "line:02d4ee1",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Tyrion: Even if I [i]did[/i] agree to help him,[p/] it would be nearly impossible for me to get him an acquittal.[p/] It would be a conflict of interest."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f0e70b",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: He must be desperate.[p/] His execution is scheduled for next month, after all."
}

{
  "id": "line:0547eb7",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: It's possible that he reached out to Tymora as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2dd55",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: I can't believe he'd set up a meeting at the Grand Cathedral, [i]today[/i] of all days."
}

{
  "id": "line:003ab24",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Why?[p/] What's happening there?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0a15df8",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: I'm sorry,[p/] but it's not my place to tell you."
}

{
  "id": "line:0e488c1",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Celeste: Aria,[p/] can I talk with Tyrion alone for a minute?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b97a7c",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: Of course.[p/] I'm sure you have much to discuss."
}

{
  "id": "line:07e81b7",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: I should also start heading to the Cathedral today. [h=\"I can't believe he'd use|what happened as an opportunity.\" e=\"as\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:041bfd5",
  "node": "LetterGet3",
  "text": "Aria: Good luck."
}

{
  "id": "line:0cf41b7",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I'm sorry...[p/] I'm sure this is just bringing up bad memories for you."
}

{
  "id": "line:060004a",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: ...We should meet with him."
}

{
  "id": "line:0497698",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: We're not going to help him, obviously,[p/] but I had an idea."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c2a76b",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: He's probably really scared of his execution, right?[p/] He's even desperate enough to ask [i]you[/i] for help."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b8add3",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Tyrion: I suppose that's true..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0eed4ff",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: So...[p/] Think about how stressed he would be if you showed up and refused to help him."
}

{
  "id": "line:061095e",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...I could use the Eye of Horus on him."
}

{
  "id": "line:08648bb",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: We can get the info we need without having to give him [i]anything[/i]."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d308b5",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...But are you really okay with this?[p/] You'll have to see him again."
}

{
  "id": "line:071e93e",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: I'll manage."
}

{
  "id": "line:01305a5",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: It'll be worth it if we can finally get the answers I'm looking for."
}

{
  "id": "line:060a4b4",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "This letter had already gotten her hopes up,[p/] but there was no guarantee that he actually knew anything."
}

{
  "id": "line:0522438",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "I was worried about how this might affect her,[p/] but it was ultimately her decision."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a5097a",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "She'd done a lot for me.[p/] This was the least I could do."
}

{
  "id": "line:01fbed6",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Celeste: So [i]this[/i] is the Grand Cathedral of the Scaled Lord."
}

{
  "id": "line:0b6ae77",
  "node": "LetterGet4",
  "text": "Tyrion: Have you never been here before?"
}

{
  "id": "line:072e762",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Celeste: The Church of Bahamut wasn't that popular in my hometown,[p/] and I've never been the religious type."
}

{
  "id": "line:048be85",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Celeste: What about you?"
}

{
  "id": "line:052abd3",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It never really caught on with me.[p/] Apparently,[p/] my roots tie to the celestials."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d0fe9f",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Celeste: Yeah.[p/] I guess that makes sense. [h=\"He certainly has|the looks for it...\"/]"
}

{
  "id": "line:070145a",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Tyrion: ...Your thoughts are leaking again."
}

{
  "id": "line:067c044",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Celeste: Can you stop?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0b15b08",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I can't exactly turn it off, you know."
}

{
  "id": "line:034261f",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Do those mental exercises I told you about."
}

{
  "id": "line:0c469e9",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm a little annoyed that you've been looking into my mind for the last few months without telling me..."
}

{
  "id": "line:0534f79",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Tyrion: It's not something I can tell people about recklessly.[p/] You and Tymora are the only ones who know."
}

{
  "id": "line:01732cb",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Celeste: ...Wait.[p/] I'm at the same level as Ruby?"
}

{
  "id": "line:00eb496",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Tyrion: Right now,[p/] you're much higher than her."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bec333",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "That seemed to add a cheerful stride to her step."
}

{
  "id": "line:056e3fb",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "We approached the gates of the Grand Cathedral.[p/] There was a large blockade walling off the entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:0658033",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "A large crowd of sightseers had gathered around the gates."
}

{
  "id": "line:023733e",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Celeste: It's closed off...[p/] Is there some kind of event going on?"
}

{
  "id": "line:060baec",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "I recalled Steelwind mentioning that she was heading here as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a009bc",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "The nobility must have been using the cathedral grounds for some kind of private event."
}

{
  "id": "line:02c69d8",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "It might explain why Pierce wanted to meet us here.[p/] It was probably secluded from prying eyes today."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f754f5",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Knight: ...Tyrion Cuthbert?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0070733",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "As we approached the blockade,[p/] one of the knights noticed us."
}

{
  "id": "line:06b0a33",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "He looked Celeste and me up and down."
}

{
  "id": "line:025a1e5",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Knight: ...We've been expecting you."
}

{
  "id": "line:03e8dca",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "Tyrion: I...[p/] see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0a81705",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "I exchanged glances with Celeste.[p/] She raised her eyebrow at me.[p/] I just shrugged."
}

{
  "id": "line:0461e03",
  "node": "LetterGet5",
  "text": "We went past the gate and into the Cathedral."
}

{
  "id": "line:0bb65a3",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "The walls of the cathedral nave towered high.[p/] The afternoon sun shone through the stained glass near the ceiling."
}

{
  "id": "line:0dde166",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "It definitely inspired awe,[p/] but like most things,[p/] it was a grim reminder of an excess that the commoners would never see."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f3da02",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "The pews of the cathedral looked like they could host hundreds of people at a time,[p/] but it was completely empty,[p/] save for a few people standing near the altar."
}

{
  "id": "line:070b91c",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "Aside from the servants,[p/] most of them were quite familiar.[p/] They were all speaking in hushed whispers."
}

{
  "id": "line:05ea1aa",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "I spotted Laefe and Miriam as we walked into the room."
}

{
  "id": "line:0819f21",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "They both avoided eye contact with us.[p/] Understandable,[p/] considering how I'd indicted their sister."
}

{
  "id": "line:0118333",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "As soon as they spotted us,[p/] they moved their conversation elsewhere."
}

{
  "id": "line:071a15f",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "In another corner of the room,[p/] I spotted von Sanctus and Sibyl."
}

{
  "id": "line:070bbf6",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "I always seemed to spot them together.[p/] Maybe they were friends."
}

{
  "id": "line:02bd5e4",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "As soon as we began approaching them,[p/] von Sanctus flashed us a quick look of disdain."
}

{
  "id": "line:070c136",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "He and Sibyl moved their conversation away as well."
}

{
  "id": "line:05f2d5c",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "And finally,[p/] there was Prosecutor Steelwind and her father—"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f84006",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "—along with the two princes."
}

{
  "id": "line:071b163",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "Although,[p/] there was someone speaking to them that I didn't recognize."
}

{
  "id": "line:0155079",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "When he noticed us,[p/] his face darkened.[p/] He stared the two of us down."
}

{
  "id": "line:0fe3d81",
  "node": "LetterGet6",
  "text": "The Crown Prince, especially,[p/] seemed surprised to see us here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0655e5a",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "He and Lucio said something to Aria,[p/] but I couldn't hear it from where we were."
}

{
  "id": "line:0d7a233",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "When she responded,[p/] Aster's eyes widened while Lucio's narrowed."
}

{
  "id": "line:05254c7",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Celeste: This is a little awkward."
}

{
  "id": "line:00871f4",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Tyrion: It is,[p/] but we have some time before our meeting with Pierce."
}

{
  "id": "line:0144581",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Tyrion: This is my first time here, too.[p/] Do you want to do some sightseeing?"
}

{
  "id": "line:01b0543",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Celeste: Oh?[p/] Are you asking me out?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0ad8571",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Tyrion: We are [i]literally[/i] already out."
}

{
  "id": "line:03d3175",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Celeste: Sure.[p/] Why not?"
}

{
  "id": "line:0f1694b",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Celeste: I picked up this map from the entrance."
}

{
  "id": "line:004ffbd",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "Celeste: I'm kind of curious about why they're all here."
}

{
  "id": "line:0f354fe",
  "node": "LetterGet7",
  "text": "It [i]was[/i] strange."
}
